INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (122,1,'2019-10-17 13:08:16','2019-10-17 07:38:16','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>American actress, film producer, and businesswoman Jennifer Joanna Aniston has done lots of work in <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\">Hollywood</a>. She is the star of the FRIENDS TV Series.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>She is on Instagram Now!!</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/the-story-of-jennifer-aniston-or-rachel-green-friends/\">Aniston</a> was not on Instagram before but this is the old news now. She has signed up on Instagram and gave a shock to others. Even Instagram didn\'t know for some time what happened.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>Her First Post!!</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Recently She is in news because of her Instagram account. She created her account and uploaded a picture with FRIENDS TV Serial stars Courteney Cox as Monica Geller, Matthew Perry as Chandler Bing, Lisa Kudrow as Phoebe Buffay, Matt LeBlanc as Joye Tribbiani and <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/david-schwimmer-most-popular-movies-tv-series/\">David Schwimmer as Ross Geller</a>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Also, she wrote something for them \"And now we’re Instagram FRIENDS too. HI INSTAGRAM 👋🏻\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3o8vWDhlOh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-versio