her were facing some issues and not able to follow her. We don\'t know that not being able to follow her is a feature of Instagram or a bug but Jennifer Aniston found it very well. Now Instagram has solved this problem.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>She made History!!!</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>After this one more thing comes, Today She has made history on Instagram. She is the only user on Instagram who was followed by 10 million people in just a little time you can say less than one day.<br />Now she has made the Guinness world record. The shocking news isn\'t it?</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>Her Second Post!!</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Jennifer Aniston uploaded one video, in that clip she is broking a phone but not in reality. She is thankful to her fans and said \" I swear I didn’t mean to break it…</p>\r\n<p>Thank you guys for the kind, glitchy welcome ❤️\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3scmO3hAcK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"12\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 16px;\">\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\"> </div>\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;\"> </div