ilm producer and a designer for a long time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Her design work is not for everyone, she does it for only high profile people such as business and <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/celebrities/\">Bollywood celebrities</a>. Now she revealed that she has designed jeans for Shahrukh Khan for a particular role.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/arre/image/upload/c_scale,w_760,h_425,e_sharpen:100,f_auto,q_auto/v1541997425/Baazigar_06_py4cgl.gif\" alt=\"baazigar\" />\n<figcaption>Picture Source: Arre.co.in</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I think you have seen the movie Baazigar(1993). This is the epic Blockbuster movie directed by Mustan Burmawalla, Abbas Burmawalla. In this movie, Shahrukh Khan is a killer and wants to destroy a family.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:image {\"id\":141} -->\n<figure><img src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/ye-kaali-kaali-ankhen-song_5d7b1d2a2bb68.jpg\" alt=\"Shah Rukh Khan with Kajol in song ye kali kali aankhen \" /></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now Gauri Khan revealed that the look of her husband Shah Rukh Khan in the song \"ye kali kali aankhen\" . In this song, Shah Rukh Khan is in jeans with colored designed one leg and another leg is just plane. This was designed by Gauri Khan, she said.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She shared this photo on Instagram and said \" Can’t believe I designed this look in the 90s ... Those jeans, #legwarmer tee, bullet belt and a red shirt thrown over. The hand painted jeans were my favourite. #Gaurikhandesigns has come a long way! Major throwback..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Gauri Khan reveals she designed Shahrukh Khan\'s look in Baazigar','','publish','open','open','','gauri-khan-reveals-she-designed-shahrukh-khans-look-in-baazigar','','','2020-12-20 17:34:26','2020-12-20 12:04:26','',0,'http://thetvfreak.com/?p=140',0,'post','',0),(145,1,'2019-10-19 04:00:20','2019-10-18 22:30:20','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Karwa Chauth is one of the best festivals in India. This is a one-day festival and on this day Hindu Wifes fast and pray for the long life of her husbands and celebrate the day o love. This is the day of husband and wives. Do you ever think, what happens in celebrities Karwa Chauth.</p>\r\n<p>Some of the husbands fast too for his wife showing his love to her that show balancing in the caring.</p>\r\n<p><br />This Karwa Chauth was on 17th Oct or yesterday. Lots of Bollywood celebrities share their photos on this day with their partners. This is lovely and shows the bonding between them.</p>\r\n<p><br />Nick Jonas and Priyanka Chopra, Virat Kohli and Anushka Sharma, Karan Singh Grover and Bipasha Basu, Shilpa Shetty Kundra and Raj Kundra or Tahira Kashyap and Ayushmann Khurrana, many celebrity couples shared their moments on social media.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>1. Anushka Sharma and Virat Kohli Karwa Chauth</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3ujURip7Sn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"12\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 16px;\">\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\"> </div>\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-