-20 17:03:04','2019-10-20 11:33:04','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2><strong>Why Watch These</strong>:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>People watch Best movies for entertainment. We watch movies to get some relax. When you are feeling lonely or feeling empty and if you watch a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">movie lover</a> then you watch movies.</p>\r\n<p>These make your mood so movies are the mood changer. There are different benefits of movies like relaxation, to expand your knowledge to entertain yourself. it also enhances analytical thinking.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Nowadays the movies are being made on true events, which means you are getting some knowledge in the form of entertainment. If you are a movie lover then this blog is for you. We are providing you with some movies here, you can\'t live without watching. You will regret it if you watch these movies lately. Some of these movies you have already watched but I am sure some of them are extremely new for you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h2><strong>Here are Top Rated Movies that you should watch.</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>1.The Shawshank Redemption</strong> (IMBD- 9.2/10) :</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Achievements</strong>: IMDB: 9.2/10<br /><strong>Oscar</strong>: Shawshank was nominated for seven Oscars for best picture, best actor, Best Adapted Screenplay, Best Cinematography, Best Sound, Best Film Editing and Best Original Score but it didn\'t win a single award.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":160} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-160\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/The_Shawshank_Rede_3292896b-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Shawshank Redemption movie is based on the true event. In 1959 Frank Freshwaters or Stephen King novella (in the movie) was set in Prison in Maine but this film made at Ohio State Reformatory.</p>\r\n<p>This movie has a huge amount of suspense and you will never know what is going to happen at the end of the movie. In the last ten minutes, you will ask yourself that what happened, is it true? is it real? This movie is directed by Frank Darabont and it is around the bond between two men during the years of their imprisonment where they shared some emotion.</p>\r\n<p><br />The best part is in this movie the hero Frank freshwaters break the prison and after 56 years he was recaptured in real.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This movie also gives some lessons.<br />1. Hope is always a good thing.<br />2. Get busy living or get busy dying<br />3. Just crawl through the river of shit <br />4. Two things Persistence and perseverance are key to success<br />5. Keep your mind occupied when things around aren’t just fine for you<br />6. Exploiting others will lead to endless trouble</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Trailer:</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hB3S9bIaco[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>2. The God Father ( 1972 ) :</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>IMBD- 9.1/10<br />If you are a true movie lover, then you must have seen one of the greatest movies ever made “The Godfather if not then you are not a movie lover.<br />This one is my favourite movie series. Yes, this is a series having three sequel parts. If you have seen Gangs of Wasseypur then you can understand this movie. But this is 10 times better than Gangs of Wasseypur.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":164} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img cla