<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>5.The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King (2003)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://www.thecourieronline.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/lotr-online.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King (2003)\" />\r\n<figcaption>Picture source: The Courier Online</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This movie is based on a novel by JRR Tolkien. It is an action, adventure, drama, fantasy, science fiction movie. it is a long and steady movie just like Godfather. In this movie, background actors caste were 20,602 and 19000 costumes designed. Real horses in one scene were 250, in short, it was a very huge movie having a lot of people and work in it.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>There are lots of Academy Awards has won by this movie, some of which are in the direction, cinematography, costume design, directing the film, editing makeup using, best picture, sound editing, sound mixing, and writing as well. I am sure if you will watch it you will complete the whole series of it. This movie makes a connection with the viewer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5X-hFf6Bwo[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>6. Schindler\'s List (1993)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":172} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-172\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hh-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<figcaption>Picture Source: Medium.com</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Schindlers List is not only the movie but experience of naked reality</strong>, this is the movie you will be repeating inside you after watching it. This is on top of my list. In the last of this movie, I am sure you will be crying and searching for this man on the internet. Yes, it is based on a brutal true event.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://qphs.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-f950d3a0be4e81de5bdac6507c2b01db\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>SCHINDLER\'S LIST, the 1993 winner of the Academy Award for Best Picture. But that\'s not why you should watch this movie. Watch it for the brilliant storytelling, Watch it for the great acting, Watch it for the humanity inside you. It\'s a message that one person can make a difference in the face of evil.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This is about Oskar Schindler, a German industrialist and member of the Nazi party who tried to save his Jewish employees. They were being killed day by day.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":173} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-173\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/image.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>How a rock-hearted industrialist changed into the greatest man. I have a question for you if thousands of men are known by you and using your name how would you feel.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gG22XNhtnoY[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>7. Forrest Gump (1994)</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/forrest-gump-1994-the-tv-freak/\">Forrest Gump</a> is based on the 1986 novel by Winston Groom. However, the film primarily focuses on the first eleven chapters of the novel. This is a funny, entertaining, heartwarming movie that makes us feel so good by the end of the film.  That\'s what a good film does. It is also an inspirational movie because In this movie Forrest Gump does best whats he wants to do or his mom says. He did lots of jobs in it.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://10carderj.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/tumblr_nn9ck8zymb1sa4xl1o1_1280.jpg?w=640\" alt=\"tumblr_nn9ck8zymb1sa4xl1o1_1280\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Jack Ma </strong>(co-founder of Alibaba and the richest man in China) explains<strong> said Forrest Gump is his favourite movie, </strong>and <strong>how the movie changed his life.</strong><br />He said: \" He is <em>simple</em>, he <em>never gives up</em>. <em>People think that he is dumb</em>. But <em>he knows what he is doing</em>. And I was very depressed and watched the movie at my friend’s house. When I saw him, I thought, <em>this is the guy we should learn from</em>. <em>Believe </em>what you do. <em>Love it whether people like it or not, be simple</em>. And I like the word (quote): “<strong>Life is like a box of chocolates, you never know what you are gonna get</strong>”. I never know I would be here talking to you, talking to Charlie Rose. But, today, I made it. \" Copied from Quora.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://quoteparrot.com/images/quote/i-got-my-story-my-dream-from-america-the-hero-i-had-is-forrest-gump-i-like-that-guy-ive-been-watching-that-movie-about-10-times-every-time-i-get-frustrated-i-watch-the-movie-i-watched-the-movie-before-i-came-here-again-to-new-york-i-watched-the-movie-again-telling-me-that-no-matter-whatever-changed-you-are-you-240023.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for jack ma on forrest gump\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Forrest Gump won lots of Awards:</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em>Six</em> Academy Awards: Best Picture, Best Actor in a Leading Role to Tom Hanks, Best Director to Wendy Finerman, Best Visual Effects, Best Adapted Screenplay, and Best Film Editing.</li>\r\n<li>Nominated for seven Golden Globe Award, winning three of them, including Best Actor – Motion Picture Drama, Best Director – Motion Picture, and Best Motion Picture – Drama.</li>\r\n<li>The film was also nominated for six Saturn Awards and won two for Best Fantasy Film and Best Supporting Actor (Film).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Bollywood Forrest Gump</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In March 2019, Bollywood actor and filmmaker Aamir Khan with Advait Chandan as the director announced he will produce and star in <em>Lal Singh Chaddha</em>, an Indian remake of <em>Forrest Gump</em>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLvqoHBptjg[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>8. The Prestige (2006)</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://www.spectatornews.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/WEB_ThePrestige_sadiesedlmayr-900x638.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for the prestige review\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>“<strong>The Prestige</strong>” is one of my favourite Christopher Nolan\'s movies. Prestige is not on top of the list, but still not far behind “Memento” and “The Dark Knight”. The best thing about this movie is that you never know what happened and how it has happened. There is a lot of suspense in it. That\'s what a good movie should have.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://qphs.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-90383d13c2af64f570be12c3bb94c518-c\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This unsettling and fascinating movie has two big casts Hugh Jackman and Christian Bale. And I hope you know well about them. The suspense, love, revenge and all the other elements of this movie make it classic and best.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o4gHCmTQDVI[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>9. Pulp Fiction ( 1994 )</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51rC33JTLuL.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for pulp fiction poster\" />\r\n<figcaption>Picture Source: Amazon.com</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Oscar-winning movie Pulp Fiction is based on crimes. Most of the people didn\'t understand the movie and most of them love this movie like none others.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://nofilmschool.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_wide/public/pulp-fiction-gradient.jpg?itok=Sd1OxB6S\" alt=\"Image result for pulp fiction\" />\r\n<figcaption>Picture Source: Nofilmschool.com</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This movie nominated for several Oscar titles such as  Best Picture, Best Leading Actor, Best Supporting Actor, Best Supporting Actress, Best Director, Best Editing. And it won Oscar in <em><strong>Best Original Screenplay</strong></em><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>