est-fright-and-horror-movies-for-halloween-2020/\">list of best horror movies</a> that you must watch.</p>\r\n<h2>1. The Shining</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 23 May 1980 || IMDB - 8.4 || Rotten Tomatoes - 93%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":175} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-175\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/the-shining.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Shining is a movie, based on a novel written by  <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_King\">Stephen </a>King in 1977. In the movie, Jack Torrance, a writer, becomes the caretaker of the Overlook Hotel.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Hotel closed down in summer, he becomes caretaker to make sure it\'s asset remain safe. He starts losing his temper, becomes restless, hallucinated, even attacks his wife...</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Cb3ik6zP2I</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>2. The Lighthouse | Best Horror Movies</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 19 May 2019 || IMDB - 8.1 || Rotten Tomatoes - 93%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":176} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-176\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Capture-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>A story of two lighthouse keepers, where they stayed for a very long time. The story about their friendship, how they faced their worst fear, how\'d they get out of that, how did they stayed together, fight together. It\'s about adventure...</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yec0jwBO66U</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>3. Psycho</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 16 June 1960 || IMDB - 8.5 || Rotten Tomatoes - 96%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":177} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-177\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Psycho.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Marion Crane and her boyfriend want to get married, but they can\'t because of his boyfriend Sam\'s debt. She steals his boss\'s money $4000 and runs away to his boyfriend Fairvale. On the way, she stops at a Bates motel due to bad weather, where she takes a shower and a shadow comes and murder her.</p>\r\n<p>A policeman also comes in search and gets killed. Marion\'s sister and her boyfriend Sam comes in search for her and interrogates the proprietor, Norman Bates, and they suspect he is hiding something, Marion\'s sister Lila runs to the upper room and sees there is a mummified corpse on the chair.....</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wz719b9QUqY</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>4. Get Out</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 24 February 2017 || IMDB - 7.7 || Rotten Tomatoes - 98%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":178} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-178\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Get-out.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Finally, Chris Washington agrees to meet his white girlfriend, Rose Armitage\'s parents. Her mom Missy, was a hypnotherapist. When Chris was not able to sleep, she pressurizes him for a hypnotherapy session. There was a get-together when Chris did not feel well, he convinced Rose to leave, while he packs, he finds photos of Rose with her old black boyfriends. They try to convince him that Chris is his first boyfriend when he rushes to leave, Missy hypnotizes him. When he wakes up, he finds himself strapped to a chair in the basement, where Rose\'s grandfather Roman explains him about transplanting their brain into the physical bodies......</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzfpyUB60YY</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>5. The Conjuring</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 2 August 2013 || IMDB - 7.5 || Rotten Tomatoes - 85%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":179} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-179\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/the-conjuring.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This all started when Roger and Carolyn Perron move into a farmhouse in Harrisville, Rhode Island with their daughters and a dog. The dog Saddie does not enter the house. Their daughters play a game, \"Hide and Clap\" one of them finds a door to the cellar, and the youngest one April finds a music box and when she plays it, she gets in touch with a spirit of a boy named Rory. he tells her about his story that they lived there for a long time, and something very bad happened, when all clocks stopped exactly at 3:07 am.....</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Watch Trailer:</h4>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k10ETZ41q5o</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>6. Sleep Tight</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --