n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>8. Scream</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 18 December 1996 || IMDB - 7.2 || Rotten Tomatoes - 79%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":182} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-182\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/scream.jpg\" alt=\"best horror movies scream\" width=\"765\" height=\"492\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Casey Becker receives a phone call from an unknown person, asking about her favourite scary movie. When she refuses to answer, he informs her that her boyfriend is kidnapped and he is with him, if she will not answer he will kill him. She starts to answer, she gets one answer wrong and he kills his boyfriend. She refuses to answer more, he kills her too. Her parents visit her and find her body hanging from the tree and...</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --><!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>9. The Conjuring 2</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Released on - 10 June 2016 || IMDB - 7.3 || Rotten Tomatoes - 80%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":183} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-183\" src=\"http://thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/the-conjuring-2.jpg\" alt=\"best horror movies the conjuring 2\" width=\"934\" height=\"517\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Hodgson family starts to feel something different in their house. Janet starts to walk in the night and starts to talk in her dream to an angry old man, who sits in the family armchair. After some time, they all start to feel something including their mother. That old man wants to claim his house. And Anabelle doll.....</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {