's Vin Diesel. This movie is based on a comic book Bloodshot.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As we all know Vin Diesel has done Riddick, this is just like a superhero movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We all know most of the comic book movies have come from <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvel_Cinematic_Universe\">Marvel</a> and DC production. And these movies made us surprised like wow!! This is the first Trailer for this <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">movie</a>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Story of Bloodshot Movie</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He and his wife were murdered and then he was resurrected by a team of scientists working on the human body with technology. Then he remembers how he and his wife died, who murdered him. Then he goes to take revenge. After the Revenge then the process starts again and he walkup again and this time he was remembered that the murderer is this person and then he goes again for revenge. In the whole story, he goes through much time, without knowing that he has done it several times.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Watch the trailer:</h2>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/embed/vOUVVDWdXbo</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html --><!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Bloodshot Trailer: Vin Diesel’s As a Comic Book Super Hero','','publish','open','open','','bloodshot-trailer-vin-diesels-as-a-comic-book-super-hero','','','2020-12-21 12:09:36','2020-12-21 06:39:36','',0,'http://thetvfreak.com/?p=245',0,'post','',0),(255,1,'2019-10-26 02:41:04','2019-10-25 21:11:04','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Salman Khan has launched the trailer of movie Dabangg 3 today on the 26th of October. This movie is directed by Prabhu Deva and produced by Salman Khan, Arbaaz Khan and Nikhil Dwivedi. Dabangg 3 will be launching on 28 December 2019.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Dabangg 3 Storyline</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As the name says, this is the part of Salman Khan\'s movie series Dabangg. in this movie, he is still a police officer like before but that\'s not the interesting part.</p>\r\n<p>The interesting part is the history of Chulbul Pandey, Now this History is revealing in this movie. We will know in this part how Chulbul Pandey became a police officer and how this kind of serious attitude came from.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Sonakshi Sinha is still his wife. we think her acting would be as usual awesome. Sudeep is in the negative character in the past of Chulbul Pande.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Chulbul Pandey was a good genuine person and he loves a girl and she is killed by the villain. Now the villain came again into Chulbul Pandey\'s life. But at this time Chulbul Pande didn\'t forgive him.</p>\r\n<p>After watching the official trailer your all questions will be answered. You can stay updated with The Tv Freak for <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/bollywood/\">Bollywood Updates</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<figure>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-AJ7cLi1Jfk[/embedyt]</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Overview of the Trailer</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Basically, it would be a very good movie and will hit the blockbuster. Everybody is waiting for Bhai\'s movie. And they are shouting like Salman bhai... Salman bhai... Salman bhai… everyone is saying this after watching the trailer. We can say he is a personality of a funny and a serious role actor.</p>\r\n<p>The thing is we do not have a lot of movies having sequels in Bollywood and now Salman Khan is doing that for us. Dabangg 1 and Dabangg 2 were awesome, now we hope Dabangg 3 would more than these.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"left\",\"level\":4} --><!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Dabangg 3: Check out the Official Trailer','','publish','open','open','','dabangg-3-official-trailer','','https://thetvfreak.com/commando-3-official-trailer/\nhttps://thetvfreak.com/terminator-dark-fate-trailer/','2020-12-19 17:20:59','2020-12-19 11:50:59','',0,'https://thetvfreak.com/?p=255',0,'post','',0),(276,1,'2019-10-27 06:58:57','2019-10-27 01:28:57','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Bollywood film actress Deepika Padukone is known for her tremendous acting. Everybody loves her. She has started with zero backbone of Bollywood and she is now a most living actress and a Bollywood celebrity which is known worldwide. Now Deepika Padukone as Draupadi is working in the movie Mahabharat </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Deepika Padukone was born in Denmark and moved to Bangalore in her childhood when she was 11 years old. Deepika has done lots of Bollywood hit movies that you don\'t want to miss.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1495 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/9-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Deepika Padukone\" width=\"820\" height=\"532\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":281} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Now the big news is that she is working on the movie project Chhapaak that is directed by Meghna Gulzar and one more project on which she is working \"83\" which is directed by Kabir Khan.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h2>Big News</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Today on the 25th of October she revealed that she will be working on a very big project name Mahabharata and she will be playing the role of Draupadi. It will be a reimagination of the Mahabharata from the point of view of Draupadi.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What Deepika Padukone said?</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>She told it about Mid-day and also she said about the role which she will be playing as Draupadi. She said \" We all know the Mahabharat for its mythological tales and socio-cultural influence. We derive many of life’s lessons from the epic. But the narrative we are most familiar with is that of the epic’s leading men. This new perspective will be not only interesting but also significant \"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The best thing is that this film is not one part film, this film will be a multi-part franchise and this will be the first part of this Mahabharat Movie Series on Diwali 2021.</p>\r\n<p>The rest of the cast and the director is yet to be revealed. It is not known that they are chosen or not. It is possible that they will be revealed after some time. We don\'t know that Who will be directing and who will play the role of the Other characters but we can say that this project will be the most awaiting Bollywood project. Deepika Padukone has teamed up with Madhu Mantena to produce the film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html --><!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We all know that the Mahabharata is a very big story there are lots of characters that are very important. In just two or three hours we cannot summarise this Sanskrit epic. Because every character has its own quality and own story we can not summarise all these things in just a few minutes. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/bollywood/\">Bollywood</a> should make a movie on each character then it should merge those. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Deepika Padukone as Draupadi  in upcoming Film  Mahabharata','','publish','open','open','','deepika-padukone-as-draupadi-in-upcoming-film-mahabharata','','','2020-12-20 23:19:07','2020-12-20 17:49:07','',0,'https://thetvfreak.com/?p=276',0,'post','',1),(309,1,'2019-11-01 02:04:17','2019-10-31 20:34:17','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Here is the list of refined Horror Comedy movies for you, Hope you will love them</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>1. Shaun of the Dead</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":314,\"width\":470,\"height\":394} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Shaun of the Dead is the first part of the <em>Three Flavours Cornetto</em> trilogy, it is a horror movie but it is also a comedy movie. You will not be feeling scared because the movie isn\'t serious and it can make you laugh a lot.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The funny part is the situation with Zombies in this movie, they are falling and randomly doing something stupid. They are eating and looking funny.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>Three Flavours Cornetto</em> trilogy was started in 2004 with Shaun of the Dead as the first movie and then followed by the second movie <em>Hot Fuzz</em> (2007). Then the last movie of this trilogy, <em>The World\'s End</em> released in 2013.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3811 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1.jpg\" alt=\"Shaun of the Dead\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Just like in Scary Movie the title says that it would so a horror and scary movie but when you watch it, you feel it and you enjoy it. It is just opposite to its title. Just like Scary Movie, it is a comedy horror movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The storyline is a little bit different and very funny. In this movie a bunch of people, who are not Zombies and trying to survive. But they aren\'t really good at surviving and they go to Pub and waiting for the outbreak. Now the two groups of the different peoples came together and start fighting without any reason.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Shaun of the Dead is directed by Edgar Wright. And then he completed this Trilogy by writing and directing two more movies Hot fuzz and the world\'s End. You will not believe that Adventure of Tintin is also written by him The Marvel movie Ant-Man is also written by Edgar Wright.</p>\r\n<p>The recent <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/list-of-top-10-car-racing-movies-including-fast-and-furious/\">top car racing movie</a> the Baby Driver achieved lots of heart is also the imagination of this man and he directed it and the movie scored good business of more than 200 million Dollars. Now his is an upcoming movie in 2020 is <em>Last Night in Soho</em>.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIfcaZ4pC-4[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>2. What We Do In The Shadows</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":315,\"width\":470,\"height\":394} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Whenever someone Superhuman around humans then he faces some problems created by humans. I am sure that you have watched tons of movies like this. Some of the movies are buffy the Vampire Slayer, Dead Like Me, The Incredibles, and your favorite the Spider-Man. In these movies, there is someone more efficient than human.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3812 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p>Lots of things that are made by human in this world because of these they have to face some issues and problems i.e. the human concepts and in between he has to hide his identity as well some of the people say that it is a movie like this and that but I\'m damn sure that you haven\'t seen this kind of movie with the same concept. If you are a fan of movies like Zombie Land then this is the movie for you.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>What We Do In The Shadows</em> was released in 2014 mockumentary horror comedy film written and directed by Jemaine Clement. The story starts with vampires who live together in a flat somewhere in Wellington. Then a documentary crew comes to the flat and starts living with the vampires but they didn\'t know about it.</p>\r\n<p>All the vampires having some Supernatural powers likes one of them can be transformed into animals, the other one of them is very old like 370 years old from 18 century who has his own story. He was in search of his love for 300 years. The third one is 862 years old. So you will watch something unusual funny and sometimes which can make you this movie on your favorite list. This can be a must-watch movie.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IAZEWtyhpes[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>3. One Cut Of The Dead</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":316,\"width\":470,\"height\":394} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><em>One Cut Of The Dead</em> war released in 2007 and it is related to zombies. It was made in Japan. This Japanese zombie comedy film is written and directed by Shin\'ichirô Ueda.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3813 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>You will be surprised after reading that it is a low budget movie that is made in 3 million Japanese bucks that is $25,000. The funny thing is the actors are unknown. It has made history at the box office by earning over 1000 times its budget. This film received universal acclaim from critics. The most important thing about this film is its originality, writing, and humor.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This film was released in a small theatre only for six days and then shut down but after its success in other countries, it was re-released in Japan and made a good business.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Du2XfUDfjN0[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>4. Tucker &amp; Dale vs. Evil</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":317,\"width\":470,\"height\":394} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3814 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/4.jpg\" alt=\"Tucker &amp; Dale vs. Evil\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Tucker &amp; Dale vs. Evil, a 2010 comedy horror movie. This is a story of a pair of hillbillies and a group of college students. The story starts when a bunch of college friends was going camping in West Virginia. On the way, they meet two hillbillies Tucker and Dale, at a gas station.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Tucker and Dale have just bought their dream vacation home, in the woods. Then something bad happens there, but the college students thought, hillbillies are responsible for that when police investigate, it surprised them. It is a good movie, you will love it. It is a good combination of horror and fun.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l1t8OZn_uhE[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>5. The Evil Dead</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":321,\"width\":470,\"height\":394} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3815 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/5.jpg\" alt=\"The Evil Dead\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Evil Dead is a Supernatural horror comedy film. It was written and directed by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Raimi\">Sam Raimi</a>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>There is a controversy in this movie that is it horror or comedy. Basically, it only depends on who is watching. it is different than a straight horror film having lots of funny moments. Also, it is terrifying sometimes. Normally if a movie balances its <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-horror-movies/\">horror movies</a> and comedy part then it can be called a good horror comedy film.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0cQmKgV0cug[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Horror comedy Movie You Must Watch','','publish','open','open','','horror-comedy','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-horror-movies/','2020-12-20 23:50:09','2020-12-20 18:20:09','',0,'https://thetvfreak.com/?p=309',0,'post','',0),(327,1,'2019-11-02 14:13:27','2019-11-02 08:43:27','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>About Jungle Cruise (2020)</h2>\r\n<p>Jungle Cruise (2020) is a movie about the Amazon forest Ride. It is made by Disney, which has done lots of work in Entertainment and is keep entertaining us.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Jungle Cruise (2020) is based on Disneyland\'s theme park ride of the same name. Johnson is playing a boat skipper\'s name, Frank. Blunt is playing the role of Lily who comes to his boat.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Lily is going with her brother McGregor a British stand-up comedian Jack Whitehall. Mr. Whitehall has done the Good Omens series on Amazon Prime. This is a good series with a mission to find a tree that has magical healing power.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<figure>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydnzilTiBcY[/embedyt]</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The journey in this movie begins with this ride and after some time of introduction, they are fighting with wild animals and sometimes against some German. Disney also has told that there would be a Supernatural element in this movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>Characters:</h2>\r\n<p>Blunt, one of the characters of Disney\'s recent movie Mary Poppins said: \"it\'s a love story\". So it is possible that you will watch some romance. Rock Johnson may be the partner of the female leading character Emily Blunt. The rock behind the scene of the video said \"The adventure of a lifetime\". \"Blunt\'s character also looks like the female version of Indiana Jones\" he added.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3816 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":329} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He said in his Instagram post in June and also added: \" relentless ambition to find the one, elusive magical thing that could change humanity for the better -- forever \".</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>According to Dwayne Johnson Skipper\'s character the Amazon River better than any other, he loved his character and only care about the money. So you will be watching the rock as a greedy person in this movie. He added: \" Good luck lady is trying to change the world, and not falling for my charm \"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"backgroundColor\":\"light-green-cyan\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\r\n<p>To watch <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Hollywood and Bollywood movies</a> trailer you can stay updated with the tv freak.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Disney’s Jungle Cruise(2020): Official Trailer','','publish','open','open','','disneys-jungle-cruise-official-trailer','','','2020-12-20 23:52:36','2020-12-20 18:22:36','',0,'https://thetvfreak.com/?p=327',0,'post','',0),(381,1,'2019-11-07 02:33:52','2019-11-06 21:03:52','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":383} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Everybody knows about Munna Bhai and Circuit. These two actors have made a comedy series very famous. Yes, we are talking about Munna Bhai MBBS and 1st sequel Lago Raho Munna Bhai. These are two <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-50-ultimate-list-of-comedy-movies-funniest-films-you-must-watch/\">comedy/ Drama Movies</a> having so much energy in them. Arshad Warsi and Sanjay Dutt have done very good work in these films. Now, we can\'t even imagine this movie without these two actors. </p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3817 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/7.jpg\" alt=\"Sanjay Dutt and Arshad Warsi \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We all have seen Munna Bhai MBBS and Lage Raho Munna Bhai and I know that these are the great movies of Bollywood. Without these veteran actors, this movie was nothing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Arshad Warsi is famous for his comedy in Bollywood and macho man. Sanjay Dutt is a man who can act in every situation in a comedy or serious role. We haven\'t seen these two actors together after Munna Bhai MBBS and Lage Raho Munna Bhai as they were in these films.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Now the big news is that we are gonna watch Munna Bhai and Circuit on screen again. Yes, You read it right. Arshad Warsi has revealed that they are now going to work in a movie with Sanjay Dutt.</p>\r\n<p>The movie is a Comedy Drama movie but this is not the sequel of Munna Bhai MBBS, it is a different movie. This is a new project for them. Arshad Warsi has said that they will start the work in the coming year.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html --><!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Story:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This will be a comedy movie. In this film, Sanjay is a blind don and Arshad Warsi is his eyes. He directs him in every situation and the challenges, that nobody can know he is blind. He also can not tell anyone he is blind. It\'s a funny story.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>It will be directed by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sajid-Farhad\">Sajid-Farhad</a>. Arshad Warsi said\" It’s a crazy script, a project by Sajid-Farhad. The film is likely to go on the floor by March-April next year. We’ll probably head to Budapest for the first schedule of the film.”</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Apart from this Sanjay Dutt\'s movie Panipat trailer has been launched and watched millions of times on youtube. This movie will hit the theatres on 6th Dec 2019.</p>\r\n<p>Directed by Ashutosh Gowariker this movie is based on the third battle of Panipat between the Maratha Empire and the Durrani Empire in 1761.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Once again Sanjay Dutt and Arshad Warsi are together on screen','','publish','open','open','','sanjay-dutt-to-play-a-blind-don-arshad-warsi-to-be-his-eyes-in-their-next-comedy-no-it-s-not-munna-bhai-sequel','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-50-ultimate-list-of-comedy-movies-funniest-films-you-must-watch/','2020-12-20 23:57:08','2020-12-20 18:27:08','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=381',0,'post','',0),(385,1,'2019-11-09 00:29:41','2019-11-08 18:59:41','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":386} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Alia Bhatt is now working for  <strong>Gangubai Kathiawadi </strong>with a famous director Sanjay Leela Bhansali. He has given so many best-rated movies to Bollywood. Alia is now playing the lead role in her upcoming movie <strong>Gangubai Kathiawadi</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-386 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Gangubai-Kathiawadi-Sanjay-Leela-Bhansali-approaches-Supriya-Pathak-Manoj-Joshi-to-tutor-Alia-Bhatt-in-Kathiawadi.jpg\" alt=\"Gangubai Kathiawadi: Alia Bhatt approaches Supriya Pathak, Manoj Joshi to tutor  in Kathiawadi\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Gangubai Kathiawadi was an Indian criminal, Don, Sex worker, Businesswoman, and controversial personality from Kathiawar, India. She was running a sex racket and she was having strong power in Mumbai. This movie depends on her character.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Alia Bhatt is working hard for this film and trying to make every possible effort to make this film realistic. This is her first film with Mr. Bhansali. She is now learning a new language Kathiawadi for this movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Basically Alia\'s paternal grandfather Nanabhai Bhatt was a Gujrati Brahmin who hailed from Kathiawad. But Alia Bhatt does not know this language. There are some reports that say that Alia has approached Marathi actors Manoj Joshi and Supriya Pathak for help.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The shoots of this film depend on her classes. The dialogues have a strong Sindh influence because the area was inhabited by Kathis and Rajputs.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2192 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-min-10.jpg\" alt=\"Alia Bhat income fee\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>By the way, it\'s not the first time for Alia that she is learning a language for the movie. She has done it earlier for two movies as well. She learned Tamil for her <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">movie</a> 2 States with Arjun Kapoor and learned Urdu for her character in Razi.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Alia Bhatt Gangubai Kathiawadi will be release on 11 September 2020.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Apart from this movie, Alia Bhatt is working in Ayan Mukharji\'s film <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brahm%C4%81stra_(film)\"><strong>Brahmastra</strong></a>.</p>\r\n<p>She will be working with Ranbeer Kapoor, Mouni Roy, and Amitabh Bachchan. She will also be seen in Karan Johar\'s film <strong>Takht</strong>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Gangubai Kathiawadi | Alia Bhatt approaches Marathi Stars','','publish','open','open','','gangubai-kathiawadi-alia-bhatt-approaches-supriya-pathak-manoj-joshi-to-tutor-in-kathiawadi','','','2020-12-21 00:08:58','2020-12-20 18:38:58','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=385',0,'post','',0),(388,1,'2019-11-09 00:22:22','2019-11-08 18:52:22','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":405} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Kamal Haasan is a great actor. We know about his contribution to Indian cinema. He is an Indian actor, politician, film director, screenwriter, producer, playback singer, and lyricist as well. He has done more than 200 movies, in which he was an actor.</p>\r\n<p>This is a great number that any actor could have. There are more than 30 movies are there that\'s direction done by Kamal Haasan.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3829 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/11.jpg\" alt=\"Kamal Haasan nominations for Oscar\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":393} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>You will be surprised after reading that 7 movies of his, in which, he was starred did very well in the cinema. These movies were selected for the nominations of Oscar for the best foreign movie category.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2><strong>Kamal Haasan nominations for Oscar:</strong></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Saagar (1985)</li>\r\n<li>Swati Mutyam (1985)</li>\r\n<li>Nayagan (1987)</li>\r\n<li>Thevar Magan (1992)</li>\r\n<li>Kuruthipunal (1995)</li>\r\n<li>Indian (1996)</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hey_Ram\">Hey Ram (2000)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":403} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-403\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/kamal-hassan-min.jpg\" alt=\"Kamal Haasan oscar movies\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This is the highest number by any Indian who has scored this much nomination in Oscar. He is also a Classical dancer in the form of Bharatanatyam.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><strong>How did he</strong> <strong>start his career?</strong></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Let\'s see a little bit about his early life first. Kamal Haasan was born on 7th November 1954 in Paramakudi, it is in Ramanathapuram district of Tamil Nadu. D Srinivasan, his father was a lawyer and her mother Rajalakshmi was a housewife.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He has two brothers, one of them Charu Haasan is a National Film Award-winning actor and the other is Chandra Haasan. He has a sister named Nalini.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3830 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>His father wants him to become an actor so he started his career from his childhood. In 1960 started his career from the first of his film Kalathur Kannamma, the director was Bhim Singh. By his acting in Kalathur Kannamma, he wins lots of heart and gets awards for National Award and President\'s gold medal. After this successful movie Kalathur Kannamma, he did some child roles in some movies but after that, for almost 9 years, he was out of the cinema and was not doing any movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>History</h2>\r\n<p>In the \'70s, his father asked him to go to the cinema again and then he left his study and concentrate on the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/bollywood/\">Indian film industry</a>. On his father\'s recommendation, he started learning a classical dance that helped his career.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In a 1975 movie with Apoorva Raagangal directed by K.Balachander, he returned to the film industry. After a long time, he started working as a dance assistant under choreographer Thankappan, and in the meanwhile, he was giving a short appearance in some movies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He then changed his route and started to do some supporting roles. In some movies such as ‘Gumasthavin Magal’ (1974), ‘Aval Oru Thodar Kathai’ (1974), and ‘Naan Avanillai’, he did outstanding acting as a supporting actor. And in the same year, his time started. He was offered to play his first lead role in Malayalam.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Then he moved towards Tamil cinema, he had his breakthrough in Tamil Cinema as a lead actor in Balachander\'s ‘Apoorva Raagangal’. And from here his filmi life started to go on a hike.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Kamal Haasan | Biography, Awards, Movies and Tv Shows','','publish','open','open','','kamal_hassan_indian_cinema','','','2021-01-24 17:08:56','2021-01-24 11:38:56','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=388',0,'post','',0),(415,1,'2019-11-09 00:11:35','2019-11-08 18:41:35','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":416} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Andaz Apna Apna is a fantastic movie. This is the movie, that we call an all-time favorite movie. Every time when you watch this movie you laugh. The dialogue delivery situation in this film is the heart of the film. Salman Khan, Amir Khan, Ravina Tandon, and Karishma Kapoor are the main cast.<br />The storyline is very simple. Salman Khan and Aamir Khan were from poor family but they wanted to be rich men. They tried every kind of good and bad thing to get the money. One was selling his father\'s shop and the other was doing something worst.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3818 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/8.jpg\" alt=\"Andaz Apna Apna\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Then they read a newspaper that said that a rich girl wants to marry a good man. So they started their journey to get Raveena Tandon, the rich girl. It is a very funny movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What did Raveena Tandon say?</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Now Raveena Tandon has revealed something unusual about this film. She said that on the set of this film nobody was talking to nobody. Yes, you read it right. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/list-of-top-10-most-popular-salman-khan-dialogues-ever/\">Salman Khan</a> and Amir Khan were not talking to each other. Raveena Tandin and Karishma Kapoor were not talking to each other. And Salman Khan and Rajaji also were not talking.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3819 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/9.jpg\" alt=\"Andaz Apna Apna\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":417} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>There was a dispute between every two. She said, \"it was very interesting and enjoying. Everybody was behaving like a child\". She didn\'t even know how this movie Andaz Apna Apna was completed. \"In the meanwhile, Salman and Amir were trying to solve our (me and Karishma) problem.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>It was amazing to work with so many actors and actresses on a set. We were enjoying the movie because the dialogues were too funny.</p>\r\n<p>Even we were laughing after every dialogue.\" She added. \"I am happy that I am in touch with those actors and I met them\" She added. Even Salman is a good friend of hers now.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Raveena Tandon Reveals The Cast of Andaz Apna Apna','','publish','open','open','','aamir-khan-salman-khan-raveena-tandon-karisma-kapoor-were-not-talking-during-andaz-apna-apna','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/list-of-top-10-most-popular-salman-khan-dialogues-ever/','2020-12-20 23:59:04','2020-12-20 18:29:04','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=415',0,'post','',0),(430,1,'2019-11-11 02:04:36','2019-11-10 20:34:36','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":431} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly we would like to tell you that Akshay Kumar has given hit movies back to back. And we all know his work towards movies for the nation. Secondly, the thing is that, After giving successful movies like Gold, Airlift, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/\">Akshay Kumar Dekh Bhagat movie</a>  Kesari and many more, he is going to work on one more movie based on true events is Bell Bottom.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3836 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bell-Bottom\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Bell-Bottom Story and Direction</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The poster of the Akshay Kumar Bell Bottom movie has been released and it says quite a lot of things about the movie. This film will be directed by Lucknow Central director Ranjit M Tewari. The production is by Akshay Kumar, Nikkhil Advani, and Vashu Bhagnani.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3D9g4erlOVE[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The story revolves around one of India\'s forgotten heroes. According to the information from official accounts, the estimate is that this film will be on the floor in mid of 2020.</p>\r\n<p>And the releasing date will be 22nd January 2021, 4 days before Republic Day 26th January.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Akshay Look in Bell-Bottom</h2>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3837 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bell-Bottom\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Akshay features in a mind-blowing avatar in the poster are mind-blowing. You will feel that you are in the 90s century.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In the Poster, he is standing near the Red Car. The look says that the film will be a classic movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Is Bell Bottom a Remake of a <strong>Kannada film</strong>?</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":432} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>A source says from The Free Press Journal says \"The Akshay Kumar starrer is an official adaption of a Kannada film, titled Bell-Bottom\".</p>\r\n<p>The direction of Jayathirtha with Rishab Shetty and Haripriya playing the lead roles, This Kannada film is releasing this year. This is a successful and entertaining south film.</p>\r\n<p>This is the big Kannada blockbuster in 2019. This movie shows the 80s era live on-screen in a beautiful way.</p>\r\n<p>By the way, everybody loves him for his different angle in the industry. Some people say about his schedules and most people complaining about his number of movies he does in a year. Apart from the big numbers of movies his most movies are best in everything. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Akshay Kumar Upcoming Movie \"Bell-Bottom\"','','publish','open','open','','akshay-kumars-upcoming-movie-bell-bottom-is-based-on-a-true-events','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/','2020-12-21 00:23:08','2020-12-20 18:53:08','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=430',0,'post','',0),(443,1,'2019-11-14 02:16:13','2019-11-13 20:46:13','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>Marjaavaan Movie Star Cast</h2>\r\n<p>Here is the top star cast of Marjaavaan movie:</p>\r\n<p>Tara Sutaria, Riteish Deshmukh, Sidharth Malhotra and Rakul Preet Singh are in main cast.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Release date:</strong> 15th Nov 2019<br /><strong>Directed by: </strong>Milap Zaveri</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Rating of Marjaavaan</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>IMDb</strong>: 4.4/10<br /><strong>News18</strong>: 1/5<br /><strong>NDTV</strong>: 1/5 <br /><strong>Rediff</strong>: 1/5<br /><strong>Bollywood</strong> <strong>Hungama</strong>: 3.5/5<br /><strong>Book my Show</strong>: 74% (don\'t know why) <br /><strong>Google User</strong>: 89% (don\'t know why)</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Marjaavaan Movie Collection</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>1st Day:- 07.03cr <br />2nd Day:- 07.21cr <br />3rd Day:- 10.18cr <br />4th Day:- 04.05cr* <br />Domestic :- 28.50cr* (Range)</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Read Story of Marjaavaan Movie</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Nasar is a tanker Mafia in this <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">movie</a> and the character name is Anna. Anna adopted Raghu ( Siddharth Malhotra) when he was a baby from a Gutter.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-456 size-large\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Marjaavaan-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Marjaavaan movie\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p>Raghu was raised under Anna and because Anna is a tanker Mafia so Raghu became a criminal or you can say a mafia.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He raised Raghu according to his desire. And after he becomes the right-hand of Anna. Raghu considers Anna as his father and does whatever anna says no matter it is right or wrong.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He strictly followed Anna\'s order. That\'s why Anna loves him like his son.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>But the tragedy is Riteish Deshmukh, who is playing the character Vishnu, is a real son of Anna and Vishnu doesn\'t like Raghu, he feels jealous and always in the anger for Raghu like he wanted to kill Raghu.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Being physically unfit Riteish Deshmukh always thinks that everybody gives respect to Raghu, not to him, that\'s why he is always in a bad mood and wanted to kill Raghu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">But Everybody from the area is happy with Raghu. <br />After sometime Raghu meets a girl who came from Kashmir and she couldn\'t speak and after meeting her, his life changes. That girl is Tara Sutaria who is playing the character of Zoya.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When Vishnu came to know that this is the situation about Raghu and this Kashmiri girl then he creates a difficult situation for Siddharth Malhotra. Raghu has to kill her girlfriend Tara Sutaria and after this Raghu was like a dead person.</p>\r\n<p>On the other side, Ritesh Deshmukh or Vishnu was teasing and killing the people who love Raghu. This is almost the whole story of the movie and the rest of the part is filled with unnecessary actions, how Raghu takes revenge from Vishnu.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Review of Marjaavaan (2019) Movie</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The director of Marjaavaan, Milap Zaveri always thinks more than Cinema. He always makes a movie that is more than cinema life like you can\'t even compare it.</p>\r\n<p>After watching this movie most of the people say that it is a zero logic movie or this is the movie that they have watched when they were a kid. Basically, the plot of the movie was like 18 or 19 centuries.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Some people are comparing this movie with Bihari movies in which you have seen a lot of a stunt or we can see a lot of illogical stunts. Some of the audience are saying that this film doesn\'t have even a story.</p>\r\n<p>Milap Zaveri tried to make a movie with lots of stunts, action, and thrillers but by mistake, he made a Bihari movie. But unfortunately, the time of Dharmendra and Amitabh Bachchan\'s movies has passed now.</p>\r\n<p>Everybody watches a movie because of its direction, acting, logical thing, and story but almost everything was missing in this film according to reviews on different portals.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>***There are some dialogues in the movie you won\'t able to listen to them. There is a dialogue When Sidharth Malhotra who is playing the character of Hero Raghu shows himself the first time in the film is having a first aid kid in his hand and he says</p>\r\n<p><br />\"<em>Main todunga bhi aur tod kar jodunga bhi\"</em>. <br />What is this, this is hilarious. And here another one comes <br />\"<em>Main marunga mar jaega, dobara janam lene se dar jaega</em>\". <br /><em>“Main badla nahin, inteqam loonga Zoya. Inteqam.”</em></p>\r\n<p><br />We bet you can justify Marjaavan film by these two dialogues only, this movie may be a good hit if the action came with logic and conviction to match.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Marjaavaan Review by KRK</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cA5K5-86Cck[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Watch Trailer of Marjaavaan</h2>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L7TbPUOn1hc[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Marjaavaan is an action <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">romantic film</a>, releasing on 15 Nov. The stars in Marjaavaan movie are Tara Sutaria, Riteish Deshmukh,</p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">“A love worth dying for “ Presenting <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Marjaavaan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Marjaavaan</a> .A thrilling game of love and death with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Riteishd?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Riteishd</a> again! Very excited to begin working with this amazingly talented team <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zmilap?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@zmilap</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/itsBhushanKumar?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@itsBhushanKumar</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nikkhiladvani?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@nikkhiladvani</a> @tarasutaria__ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TSeries?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TSeries</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EmmayEntertain?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EmmayEntertain</a> 🙌 <br />See u on 2nd OCTOBER 2019 <a href=\"https://t.co/ydMFWN9wNV\">pic.twitter.com/ydMFWN9wNV</a></p>\r\n— Sidharth Malhotra (@SidMalhotra) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SidMalhotra/status/1057490121279373313?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 31, 2018</a></blockquote>\r\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>Sidharth Malhotra, and Rakul Preet. Milap Zaveri is the director of this movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Sidharth took Twitter to announce this movie on 31 Oct 2018. This movie was supposed to be released on 2nd October, but it got delayed for some reason and scheduled on 15th Nov 2019.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h3><strong>Five songs are released till now, from T-series:</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Music by - Tanishk Bagchi, Meet Bros, and Payal Dev <br />Lyrics by -  Kumaar, Tanishk Bagchi, Manoj Muntashir, Kunaal Vermaa, A. M. Turaz and Rashmi Virag</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\r\n<p><strong>1. The Song \"Tum hi aana\" break the internet, this song was sung by Jubin Nautiyal and lyrics by Kunaal Vermaa.</strong></p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFTSW817JlI[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>2. The song \"Thodi Jagah\" was also popular, it has been seen almost 30 million times on Youtube. This song was sung by Arijit Singh and lyrics by Rashmi Virag.</strong></p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qCgjpLEzBkg[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>3. Ek Toh Kum Zindagani - Singers are Neha Kakkar, Yash, and lyrics by Tanishk Bagchi, A. M. Turaz</strong></p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a39rulFFJlM[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. Haiya Ho - Singers are Tulsi Kumar, Jubin Nautiyal, and lyrics by Tanishk Bagchi.</strong></p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AJyIqxp9yqM[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<p><strong>5. Kinna Sona - Singers are Jubin Nautiyal, Dhvani Bhanushali, lyrics by Kumaar</strong></p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4s2mSWiraSg[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Be in cinemas on 15 Nov to watch Marjaavaan movie, You will enjoy the work of Riteish, Sidharth, Tara and Rakul Preet.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Marjaavaan movie | Story, Star Cast, Rating, Review and Trailer','','publish','open','open','','marjaavaan-the-tv-freak','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/','2020-12-21 00:31:44','2020-12-20 19:01:44','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=443',0,'post','',0),(444,1,'2019-11-14 02:18:12','2019-11-13 20:48:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2><strong>Motichoor Chaknachoor Cast</strong>:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Nawazuddin Siddiqui as Pushpinder Tyagi</li>\r\n<li>Athiya Shetty as Annie (Daughter of Sunil Shetty )</li>\r\n<li>Vibha Chibber</li>\r\n<li>Navni Parihar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Director</strong>: Debamitra Biswal ( Her first Movie )</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Release</strong>: 15th November 2019</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>About Motichoor Chaknachoor:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Motichoor Chaknachoor is an Indian comedy film. Direction by a TV Director Debamitra Biswal. Rajiv and Kiran Bhatia are producing this film.</p>\r\n<p>Firstly Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Athiya Shetty are in the lead role and the film also has some veteran stars like Vivek Mishra, Karuna Pandey, Sanjeev Vats, Abhishek Rawat, Sapna Sand, and Usha Nagar in supporting roles.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3840 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-4.jpg\" alt=\"Motichoor Chaknachoor:\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Secondly, The official trailer of this film was released on 11th October 2019 and it went viral. As usual, Nawazuddin is performing a simple gentleman character.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Finally, The audience loved the trailer very much and it has been viewed by millions of people on YouTube.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U6J_Pkqk5Fs[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Story of Motichoor Chaknachoor :</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, In this comedy film, Nawazuddin Siddiqui is playing an unmarried guy character who is desperate for a wife and he was frustrated about being single. Even, he was ready to marry an ugly girl. Secondly, It shows his desperation for marriage. On the other side, Athiya Shetti plays a girl character who is desperate to marry a guy who is an NRI. Both are looking for someone for a long time.</p>\r\n<p>Then by a misunderstanding or maybe planning, they start to see each other and then they got married. Siddiqui didn\'t tell her that he is not an NRI and he is an unemployed man.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>By the way, there is so much more that we need to see in the movie. The trailer didn\'t show that there is a happy at the end of this movie but as usual in all <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Indian Bollywood films</a>, there is a happy ending so we can watch a happy end here.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Songs:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Choti Choti Gal -Motichoor Chaknachoor| Nawazuddin S, Athiya S| Arjuna Harjai ft Yasser Desai, Kumaar</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<figure>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyjINBz7WSQ[/embedyt]</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>2. Battiyan Bujhaado - Motichoor Chaknachoor| Nawazuddin S, Sunny L <br />| Jyotica Tangri, Ramji G | Kumaar</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<figure>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rrpdaG_nSF8[/embedyt]</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>3. Crazy Lagdi - Motichoor Chaknachoor|Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Athiya Shetty|Swaroop K, Amjad Nadeem, Kumaar</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<figure>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DT1WeS1Wk6k[/embedyt]</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>About Athiya Shetti</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Athiya Shetty started her career with a Hero movie directed by Nikhil Advani as Radha Mathur with Aditya Pancholi\'s son Sooraj Pancholi.</p>\r\n<p>In Mubarakan with Anil Kapoor, Arjun Kapoor, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ileana_official/\">Ileana D\'Cruz</a>, Athiya Shetty, Neha Sharma, and Ratna Pathak. Now the last film by her is Nawabzaade.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What\'s with Motichoor Chaknachoor?</h2>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3841 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Motichoor Chaknachoor:\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":455} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The director Debamitra Biswal filed a commercial arbitration petition. On Bombay High Court to stay on the release of this film.</p>\r\n<p>She did it because she didn\'t receive her payment of dues by the makers. This movie was supposed to release earlier but due to this problem, it is releasing on 15th November 2019.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Motichoor Chaknachoor | Story, Star Cast, Release date and Trailer','','publish','open','open','','motichoor-chaknachoor','','','2020-12-21 00:43:24','2020-12-20 19:13:24','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=444',0,'post','',0),(459,1,'2019-11-14 18:35:45','2019-11-14 13:05:45','<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<p>Good Newwz is a comedy-drama movie in the direction of Mr. Raj Mehta. Know the details about the movie star cast, storyline, and releasing date of Good Newwz.</p>\r\n<h2>The cast of Good Newwz</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":465} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/\">Akshay Kumar</a> as Kabir Mehra</li>\r\n<li>Kareena Kapoor</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/why-do-celebrities-pay-10x-for-their-sports-and-stuff/\">Diljit Dosanjh</a> as Honey</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/kiara-advani-biography-movies-photos-and-controversies/\">Kiara Advani</a> as Monika D’Souza</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Director: <strong>Raj Mehta </strong> <br />Releasing Date: 27th December 2019</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html --><!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Good Newwz</strong> is an upcoming Indian comedy-drama film. Starring Akshay Kumar, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Diljit Dosanjh, and Kiara Advani, it will be a successful comedy movie, because Diljit has made so many comedy hits and Akshay Kumar has a good number in making the best comedy.</p>\r\n<p>The director of this Good Newwz is <strong>Raj Mehta </strong>and produced by Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Hiroo Yash Johar, Shashank Khaitan, and Aruna Bhatia.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3845 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/750x600-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":462} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The name of this film was announced on Twitter as Good Newwz. It is Diljit Dosanjh\'s first movie with Dharma production. Information about this movie came out in December 2018 by Diljit Dosanjh and Kaira Advani that they are filming together after that Akshay Kumar and Kareena Kapoor joined and told about the filming in January.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html --><!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>They are very active on Instagram and gave information on Instagram. On social media, Akshay Kumar has said about Kareena Kapoor Khan that they are extremely fond of each other. Bebo and Lolo tease him about the money I am making and he teases them about having a flat in every building in Bandra.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Releasing Date of Good Newwz</h2>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3844 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/750x600-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Good Newwz\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The release date of this film 16 September 2019 but because of some unknown reason it was pushed forward and decided to release on 29th November and now again it is pushed due to some reason and the final date of the release is 27th December 2019.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>About Kiara Advani:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>27 years old Kiara Advani has done many successful movies like Fugly, M.S.Dhoni, Machine, Lust Stories, and more. Her last movie is Kabir Singh with Shahid Kapoor. She is a remarkable actress and because of this, she is casting in big movies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Good Newwz : Star Cast, Storyline and Releasing Date','','publish','open','open','','good-newwz-the-tv-freak','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/why-do-celebrities-pay-10x-for-their-sports-and-stuff/','2020-12-21 00:51:09','2020-12-20 19:21:09','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=459',0,'post','',0),(513,1,'2020-01-21 01:23:07','2020-01-20 19:53:07','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":518} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In August 2018, a source of English news portal DNA told that Mr perfectionist Amir Khan is planning a movie (Laal Singh Chaddha) that will be a Hindi remake of 6 times Academy Award winner English Movie \"The Forrest Gump\".</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Forrest Gump was released in 1994 and nominated more than 12 times in the different categories of Oscar and won 6 of them.</p>\r\n<p>The year 1994 is called the Golden time of Hollywood because in this year lots of outstanding movies hit theatres and liked by millions of people.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3868 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1.jpg\" alt=\"Laal Singh Chaddha\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Actor Tom Hank is in the leading role in The Forrest Gump Movie. He won 2nd Oscar for Best Acting for this Film. This was his 2nd award continuously. The previous Oscar was for his role in <em>Philadelphia</em>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\",\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/forrest-gump-1994-the-tv-freak/\">Checkout, Why did Amir Khan Select Forrest Gump for Hindi Remake?</a></em></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Laal Singh Chaddha\'s First Poster / Amir Khan\'s New look</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Recently Aamir Khan has shared a poster of Laal Singh Chaddha his upcoming new movie on 18 November 2019.</p>\r\n<p>In this upcoming mo