ovie Forrest Gump is based on the 1986 novel by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Winston_Groom\">Winston Groom</a> with the same name.</li>\r\n<li>Before the movie, Forrest Gump, only approximately 30,000 copies were sold of this novel. But after the movie, the 1.7 million copied has been sold.</li>\r\n<li>Also, this movie has done the best score in the Oscars.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3869 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.jpg\" alt=\"Laal Singh Chaddha novel\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Director of Laal Singh Chaddha:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This film is being directed by Advait Chandan and will open in theatres on Christmas</li>\r\n<li>Advait is known for his direction for Secret Superstar (2017)</li>\r\n<li>He was an assistant director and casting director in Dhobi Ghat (2010)</li>\r\n<li>He also worked in Taare Zameen Par as the assistant production manager</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":520} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Cast of LaalSinghChaddha:</h3>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3870 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"Laal Singh Chaddha cast\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Aamir Khan is in the lead role is playing the character of Forrest Gump ( Tom Hanks ).</li>\r\n<li>Kareena Kapoor is in the second lead role in Laas Singh Chaddha. This movie is the third movie of Kareena Kapoor with Amir Khan. Amir and Kareena have worked before in <em>3 Idiots</em> and <em>Talaash: The Answer Lies</em>.</li>\r\n<li>Vijay Sethupathi, Sharman Joshi, Mona Singh, Manav Vij, Vivek Mushran, Manav Gohil.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":523} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list --><!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":522} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list --><!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Producer of Laal Singh Chaddha:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Amir Khan is producing the film \"Laal Sigh Chaddha\". Amir Khan is called Mr. Perfectionist because he always invests where he feels 100% and all the stuff is a hundred percent perfect. That\'s why he always read the script very precisely and select the best one.</li>\r\n<li>Also, Faisal Khan is working as an Executive Producer and Kiran Rao is the producer here.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Some recent news about Laal Singh Chaddha</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Amir Khan said that he and his team are very excited about Laal Singh Chaddha. They have seen lots of locations such as Delhi, Punjab, Amritsar, Chandigarh, Ladakh, Rajasthan.</p>\r\n<p>In each city, he has traveled for 2 or 3 days for the perfect location.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":521} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In an interview, Gippy Grewal said that the maximum shoot is in Punjab. So Amir is learning the Punjabi Accent.</p>\r\n<p>Gippy Grewal also said that firstly the script of the movie was written in English then it was rewritten in the Hindi Language and because it is being shot in Punjab so now the script is converted to Punjabi. This will be a big movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n<div> </div>\r\n</div>','Laal Singh Chaddha (2020) | Based on Forrest Gump','','publish','open','open','','laal-singh-chaddha-2020-based-on-forrest-gump','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/forrest-gump-1994-the-tv-freak/','2020-12-21 11:23:18','2020-12-21 05:53:18','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=513',0,'post','',0),(526,1,'2019-11-21 10:15:48','2019-11-21 04:45:48','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":519} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-519\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Forrest-Gump-movie-and-novel.jpg\" alt=\"Forrest Gump Movie\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Here are some inspirational quotes that have changed so many lives.</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>“My mama always said, ‘Life was like a box of chocolates. You never know what you’re gonna get.’” – Forrest Gump.</li>\r\n<li>“You have to do the best with what God gave you.” – Mrs. Gump.</li>\r\n<li>“Death is just a part of life. It’s something we’re all destined to do” -- Forrest Gump.</li>\r\n<li>“My mama always said you can tell a lot about a person by their shoes, where they going, where they been”.</li>\r\n<li>“I happened to believe you make your own destiny. You have to do the best with what God gave you”.</li>\r\n<li>“My Mama always said you’ve got to put the past behind you before you can move on”.</li>\r\n<li>“What’s my destiny, Mama? – You’re gonna have to figure that out for yourself”.</li>\r\n<li> “Don’t be a feather in the wind, take ownership of your life”.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Why did Jack Ma like this movie?</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Jack Ma </strong>(co-founder of Alibaba and the richest man in China) said that Forrest Gump is his favourite movie and told why is it so.<br />So you will find why Forrest Gump is his favourite movie, and how the movie changed his life?</li>\r\n<li>He said that he first watched Forrest Gump back in 1995 while he was in his friend’s house in Seattle. At that time he was nothing but a man with big dreams. That week was the most frustrating dismay period. He was so depressed for getting cheated on by friends and all of his five projects failed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":528,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img class=\"wp-image-528\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/jack-ma.jpg\" alt=\" Jack Ma on Forrest Gump\" /></a></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Then he explained \"I watched the movie and I said we have to stay foolish with our dream, don’t think we are smart, and we have to continue. It is this simple.\"</li>\r\n<li>Forrest Gump is very simple. He is not a smart guy, he continued to running running running. That is the beauty of him and his achievements. We also can do this.</li>\r\n<li>He is the only one who wants to make business benefit from catching shrimps. A lot of people want to make business, make money by catching whales, sharks, but he did it, why? and the answer was \"running and doing it whatever is the condition.</li>\r\n<li>He added \"So, be simple, stay foolish, and no matter what, just continue and don\'t complain about others. Only complain about yourself and check what the problems are with you. Did I change myself? \"</li>\r\n<li>He said, \" Later, I found a lot of people fail because when they fail, they always complain about others. The people who always check their own problems survive and succeed in life. \"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Director:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Forrest Gump is an American Drama Film. It is directed by Robert Zemeckis. He has directed and written so many movies and Back To \"The Future is one of them\". Back to the future is a trilogy and it was nominated for the many awards. Robert won Academy Award for the Best Director for his work in Forrest Gump and this movie itself won the Acadamy Award for Best Picture.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":530} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-530\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Forrest-gump-Director-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"robert zemeckis director of forrest gump\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He sacrificed his personnel life for cinema. He said \"I won an Academy Award when I was 44 years old,\" he explained, \"but I paid for it with my 20s. That decade of my life from film school till 30 was nothing but work, nothing but absolute, driving work. I had no money. I had no life.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Written By:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Forrest Gump movie is written by Eric Roth. He is an American screenwriter. He has been nominated five times for the Academy Award for Best Adapted Screenplay for <em>Forrest Gump</em> (1994), <em>The Insider</em> (1999), <em>Munich</em> (2005), <em>The Curious Case of Benjamin Button</em> (2008), and <em>A Star Is Born</em> (2018), and he won the Acadamy Award for his work in <em>Forrest Gump</em>.</li>\r\n<li>Basically, this movie is based on a novel with the same name \"Forrest Gump\". and written by Winston Groom.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Tough Competition in Oscars- 1994</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The year 1994 is called the Golden year of Hollywood. This year there are so many movies that are as good as Forrest Gump.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>You will also get confused while giving the awards but it has to go to the only one.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In 1994 there are some movies including Forrest Gump, Pulp Fiction, The Shawshank Redemption, Quiz Show, The Lion King, Heavenly Creatures, The Mask, Dumb and Dumber, Speed and Hoop Dreams which won lots of hearts. And the competition for Acadamy Arords was so high for this.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":549} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-549\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"The Mask 1994, 1994 movie list\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":551} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-551\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/4-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"1994 movie list, Pulp Fiction 1994, Quiz Show 1994, The Lion King 1994\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":550} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-550\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"1994 movie list, Speed 1994, Hoop Dreams 1994, Dumb and dumber 1994\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This movie was nominated for 13 Oscars in different categories and won 6 of them. <em>Forrest Gump</em> won Best Picture, Best Actor in a Leading Role (Hanks won the previous year for <em>Philadelphia</em>), Best Director, Best Visual Effects, Best Adapted Screenplay, and Best Film Editing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Some Important and Amazing Fact About Forrest Gump</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The Director of Forrest Gump Approtched  Bill Murray (<em>Zombieland</em> ),  Chevy Chase and John Travolta then it went to Tom Hanks.</li>\r\n<li>The film was based on a 1986 book by the same name by author Winston Groom. He wrote a sequel to the tale in 1995 called Gump and Co., which featured Forrest meeting Tom Hanks. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":560} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-560\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/novel-Copy-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bollywood Superstar Amir Khan is now making a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/lal-singh-chaddha-2020-amir-khan-movie-punjab-based/\">Hindi Remake of Forrest Gump</a>. The name of the movie is Laal Singh Chaddha.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":559,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/lal-singh-chaddha-2020-amir-khan-movie-punjab-based/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img class=\"wp-image-559\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Laal-Singh-Chaddha-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ice Cube was considered for the role of Benjamin Buford \"Bubba\" Blue, but Mykelti Williamson got the role. <br />Cube was in the midst of writing the 1995 comedy \"Friday\". He did well in this too. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":553} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-553\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cuba-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>According to the information in the Internet Movie Database, both Demi Moore and an Academy Award, two Primetime Emmy Awards winner Nicole Kidman turned down the role of Jenny, which went to Robin Wright Penn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":554} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-554\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/actress-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tom Hanks wasn\'t paid for the iconic role and instead of that, he asked that he take a part of the film\'s profits. And that ended up paying off to the tune of $70 million, according to Internet Movie Database.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":555} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-555\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/tom-hanks-forrest-gump-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Capt. Dale Dye trained the Forrest Gump actors in advance of the scenes set in Vietnam. He is a highly decorated USMC veteran Captain.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":556} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-556\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/tom-hanks-in-army-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Forrest\'s epic run across the country was over 10,000 miles and it is possible according to running geeks, though he probably would have foot and bone issues for years after. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":557} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-557\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/tom-hanks-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>In real life, Sally Field is only 10 years older than Hanks (who played Forrest\'s mother).<br />She had previously played his love interest in 1988\'s \"Punchline.\"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":558} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-558\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/his-mom-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Forrest Gump (1994) Most Inspiring Movie','','publish','open','open','','forrest-gump-1994-the-tv-freak','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/lal-singh-chaddha-2020-amir-khan-movie-punjab-based/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/','2020-12-20 15:51:31','2020-12-20 10:21:31','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=526',0,'post','',0),(601,1,'2019-11-28 00:55:19','2019-11-27 19:25:19','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Salman Khan is planning a new surprise for his audience. <em>Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai is</em> the upcoming Action and Thriller Bollywood film of Superstar Salman Khan. He has revealed so much about the movie. The title \"Radhe\" is taken from his movie <em>Tere Naam</em> (2003).</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[614]} --><!-- /wp:gallery -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai is the Hindi remake of a Korean crime thriller, <em>The Outlaws</em> <em>(2017)</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Outlaws_(2017_film)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"The Outlaws (2017). (opens in a new tab)\">.</a> There would be some major changes.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3850 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-3.jpg\" alt=\"Radhe Your Most Wanted Bhai (2020)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Salman Khan has told his team to go for every action just like that film or better than that. This is why they decided to get the Korean team on board for <em>Radhe</em>,”. Yes, a Korean team will work on this Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai project.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>A Korean action team and an Indian Action team will work for the action of Radhe because an Indian only knows the taste of the Indian audience.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The Cast of <em>Radhe: Your Most Wanted</em> <em>Bhai</em></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Salman Khan as Radhe is in the lead role. Salman will be seen in the role of <em>Radhe</em> (name) for the third time in his filming career after <em>Tere Naam</em> and <em>Wanted</em>, however, the film has no connection with these two. This may be because Radhe is his favourite name as a character or this can be lucky for him.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3849 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Disha Patani, Randeep Hooda, Jackie Shroff, and Gautam Gulati are joining the cast of the film.<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --></li>\r\n<li>For Randeep Hooda, it will be the third movie after <em>Kick</em> and <em>Sultan</em>.<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --></li>\r\n<li>Gautam Gulati won the Famous Tv Show Bigg Boss 8. And after that, he got a chance to work with Salman Khan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Because this film is gonna have lots of action, so the director Prabhu Dheva has got renowned some actors from the South Indian film industry to join the cast of the film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>After <em>Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai</em> movie Salman Khan will be cast in Sanjay Leela Bhansali\'s new movie Inshallah.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Director of <em>Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai</em></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Salman Khan\'s upcoming movie Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai is directed by Prabhu Deva. Before this Prabhu Deva has also directed Salman Khan\'s most awaited movie Dabangg 3 (2019), which will be released on 20 December 2019. And you will be surprised to know that Salman Khan\'s movie <em>Wanted</em> (2009) was also directed by Prabhu Deva.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Producer of <em>Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai</em></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This big Bollywood most awaited film is produced by Sohail Khan, Atul Agnihotri, and Salman Khan. Atul Agnihotri is an Indian film actor, producer, and director. He was also part of some of Salman Khan\'s movies like <em>Hello</em> (2008) <em>Bodyguard</em> (2011), and <em>Bharat</em> (2019).</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What\'s Hot About this movie</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/list-of-top-10-most-popular-salman-khan-dialogues-ever/\">Salman Khan</a> is very serious as usual for this movie and hitting the gym daily to get into the lean avatar. He is working and flaunting his six-pack abs on the big screen of Bollywood.</li>\r\n<li>Radhe will be his most stylish look to the date.</li>\r\n<li>The shoot of Radhe is started with a Dance scene of superstar Salman and Dish Patani and it was completed in 6-7 days.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Radhe Your Most Wanted Bhai (2020)','','publish','open','open','','radhe-your-most-wanted-bhai-2020','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/dabangg-3-official-trailer/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/list-of-top-10-most-popular-salman-khan-dialogues-ever/','2020-12-21 01:05:01','2020-12-20 19:35:01','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=601',0,'post','',0),(612,1,'2019-11-28 03:18:31','2019-11-27 21:48:31','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h2>Tony (2019) is a Bollywood Thriller Movie</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h3>Tony Releasing on 29 November 2019</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[621]} --><!-- /wp:gallery -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h3>Story overview:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The story starts with Four psychology students. They plan for something different to get to know new things about human psychology. So the plan was to plant a camera in a church\'s confession box. From there they want to know what people say about themselves when they feel guilty.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3854 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/750x600-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tony (2019)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This plan gets them across a serial killer who was confessing to murder to the priest. From here the actual story begins. And they meet with TONY. He is a serial killer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h3>Tony(2019) Movie Cast:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Yashodhan Rana, Akshay Verma, Jinal Belani, Manoj Chandila, Mahesh Jilowa, Dhruv Souran, and Kabeer Chilwell.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h3>Writer and Director of Tony (2019):</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/movies/\">movie</a> Tony (2019) is written and directed by Vipul K. Rawal. Vipul is from Rustom (2016) as a writer and award-winning movie Iqbal (2005) as a story writer. The concept of Batti Gul Meter Chalu (2018) is also written by him, but it didn\'t do so well as expected.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Associate Producer:</strong> Manoj Srivastava <br /><strong>Cinematography:</strong> Mohit Kakodkar <br /><strong>Film Editing</strong>: Ajay Varma <br /><strong>Sound</strong>: Subash Sahoo</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ce4k_-AtqJA[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Vipul K Rawal got a legal notice for hurting the sentiments of the Christian community. The legal notice was sent by a Mumbai based lawyer. He demanded to change the poster, but Rawal denied to do so. He said he will not change the poster until he gets the order from the court</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Rawal told - \"My trailer and poster have not hurt an entire community, but some fringe group consisting mainly of converts, who are just looking for some publicity\".</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Tony: Official Trailer | Yashodhan Rana | Akshay Verma','','publish','open','open','','tony-official-trailer-yashodhan-rana-akshay-verma','','','2020-12-21 01:16:38','2020-12-20 19:46:38','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=612',0,'post','',0),(640,1,'2019-11-28 13:48:09','2019-11-28 08:18:09','<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[646]} -->\r\n<figure><img class=\"wp-image-646\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/darkwaters-min-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Dark Waters Movie 2019\" data-id=\"646\" data-link=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/?attachment_id=646\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, Dark Waters (2019 film) is based on the article \"The Lawyer Who Became DuPont\'s Worst Nightmare\" by Nathaniel Rich. It is a story of a Dark secret of the world\'s largest organization, about hazardous chemicals released in the river, where Mark Ruffalo takes risk of his career and his family for the civilians. Secondly, it is based on a true event that can not be ignored.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Initial release: </h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>27 November 2019 (Indonesia)<br />22 November 2019 (USA)</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Rating and Review</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>IMDb: 6.8 / 10<br />Rotten Tomatoes: 94%<br />Metacritic: 73%<br />CommonSenseMedia.org: 4 / 5<br />Google Users: 82%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Director of Dark Waters (2019 film)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Direction of the film is by Todd Haynes and he is the director of many movies and some of these appeared in Nomination for Academy Awards. The nomination of film <em>Far from Heaven</em> for Academy Award for Best Original Screenplay and also get the nomination in Golden Globe Award for Best Screenplay.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Producers:</strong> Mark Ruffalo, Christine Vachon, Pamela Koffler</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Screenplay:</strong> Mario Correa, Matthew Michael Carnahan</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Production companies:</strong> Participant, Killer Films</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Based on a Ture Event</h2>\r\n<p>This movie is based on a true event and is one of the best of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/courtroom-movies-based-on-real-life-stories/\">11 Top Courtroom Movies based on Real Life Stories.</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, DARK WATERS tells the shocking and heroic story of an attorney (Mark Ruffalo). He risks his career and family to uncover a dark secret that was important for civilians.</p>\r\n<p>Secondly, This big secret was hidden by one of the world’s largest corporations. He tried for humanity and did his best to bring justice to a community dangerously exposed for decades to deadly chemicals. That hazardous chemical was released from the big companies in the river. The civilians were using that water for their daily purpose like drinking, making food, washing, and bathing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Finally, Dark Waters (2019 film) is based on the 2016 article \"The Lawyer Who Became DuPont\'s Worst Nightmare\" by Nathaniel Rich, published in The New York Times Magazine.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The cast of Dark Waters (2019 film)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>At the last, This film stars Mark Ruffalo (Hulk), Anne Hathaway, Tim Robbins, Bill Camp, Victor Garber, Mare Winningham, William Jackson Harper, Bill Pullman.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The trailer of Dark Waters (2019 film)</h2>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/embed/RvAOuhyunhY</p>\r\n<p>Stay updated with <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">The Tv Freak</a> for more entertainment news.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->','Dark Waters (2019 film) Official Trailer','','publish','open','open','','dark-waters-2019-film','','','2020-12-21 01:20:48','2020-12-20 19:50:48','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=640',0,'post','',0),(665,1,'2020-01-10 17:31:46','2020-01-10 12:01:46','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":667} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1696 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/black-widow-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black Widow marvel movie\" width=\"600\" height=\"314\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Black Widow (2020) </strong>is an upcoming American superhero film. It is based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name as Black Widow. It seems to be the twenty-fourth film (24th) in the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU). Marvel Studios has made lots of superhero movies and approximately all are inspired by Marvel Comics.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Producer</strong>: Marvel Studio</li>\r\n<li><strong>Written</strong> <strong>By</strong>:  Jac Schaeffer and Ned Benson,</li>\r\n<li><strong>Distributed</strong> <strong>By</strong>:  Walt Disney Studios Motion Pictures</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Director of Black Widow:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Australian film and television writer and director, Cate Shortland will direct this movie. She didn\'t direct any film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The cast of Black Widow (2020):</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Scarlett Johansson as Natasha Romanoff / Black Widow</li>\r\n<li>David Harbour as Alexei Shostakov / Red Guardian</li>\r\n<li>Florence Pugh as Yelena Belova</li>\r\n<li>O-T Fagbenle as Mason: An ally from Romanoff\'s S.H.I.E.L.D.</li>\r\n<li>Rachel Weisz as Melina (winner of Academy Award for a best-supporting actress)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Release Date:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This is very surprising that BW (2020 film) will be releasing a day before it will be released in the U.S.</li>\r\n<li>Marvel announced last Friday about this. They told us that the next film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe will release a day earlier in India.</li>\r\n<li>Black Widow (2020 film) will be released in India on April 30, 2020. And it will come to the U.S on 1st May.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:core-embed/twitter {\"url\":\"https://twitter.com/Marvel_India/status/1200291829502988290?s=20\",\"type\":\"rich\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"twitter\",\"className\":\"\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-twitter wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">https://twitter.com/Marvel_India/status/1200291829502988290?s=20</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Marvel also revealed that the BW movie will be released in multiple Indian Regional Language. So it would have five local language voice dubs in India: Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam, and Kannada.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fNcAT0VjWA\\u0026t=13s\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fNcAT0VjWA&amp;t=13s</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Trailer BW (2020):</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The trailer of <strong>Black Widow</strong> will arrive on December 3.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RxAtuMu_ph4[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>News about Black Widow (2020)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The film previously being written and directed by Lionsgate, with David Hayter. This movie was being developed in April 2004.</li>\r\n<li>Then the Rights of the film was revert to Marvel Studio in June 2006.</li>\r\n<li>Marvel and Johansson were planning for the solo film for Scarlett Johansson.</li>\r\n<li>Hayter and Marvel tried getting another financier to develop the project. But it didn\'t work out for Hayter. And the original writer of this movie, Hayter never felt comfortable about it. He thought that Marvel will not do this movie. Then he left.</li>\r\n<li>In Iron Man 2, Scarlett had the first appearance as Black Widow.</li>\r\n<li>In 2009 while making Iron Man 2, Marvel talks with Emily Blunt to play Black Widow in Iron Man. But she was unable to take the role because she was filming <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gulliver%27s_Travels\">Gulliver\'s Travels.</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:core-embed/twitter {\"url\":\"https://twitter.com/EW/status/769551308529467392?s=20\",\"type\":\"rich\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"twitter\",\"className\":\"\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-twitter wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">https://twitter.com/EW/status/769551308529467392?s=20</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>In March 2009, Scarlett Johansson signed the project. She agreed to play Natasha Romanoff / Black Widow and she deals with including options for multiple films as the project goes on accordingly.</li>\r\n<li>It is saying by some Hollywood reporter that Johansson will increase her earning in this movie.</li>\r\n<li>As compared to earned for starring in <strong>The Avengers</strong>, She will earn $ 15 Million and this will equal the earning for <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-movies-of-chris-evans-except-mcu/\">Chris Evans</a> and Chris Hemsworth each earned in <strong>Captain America: Civil War</strong>, <strong>Thor: Ragnarok,</strong> <strong>Avengers: Infinity War, and Avengers: Endgame. </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Also Watch:</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/three-christs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Three Christs (2020) trailer and read the full story starred Game of Thrones Character Tyrin Lynister. (opens in a new tab)\">Three Christs (2020) trailer and read the full story starred Game of Thrones Character Tyrin Lynister.</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/dark-waters-2019-film/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Dark Waters (2019 film) Trailer and the facts about the film starring Mark Ruffalo.   (opens in a new tab)\">Dark Waters (2019 film) Trailer and the facts about the film starring Mark Ruffalo. </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>','Black Widow (2020 film) | News, Trailer and Release Date','','publish','open','open','','black-widow-2020-film','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/three-christs/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/dark-waters-2019-film/','2020-12-21 11:05:59','2020-12-21 05:35:59','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=665',0,'post','',0),(688,1,'2019-11-30 14:09:53','2019-11-30 08:39:53','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":621} -->\r\n<p>Check the Tony rating to judge if you want to watch it or not. We have listed almost all type of ratings here so that this article can help you a lot.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-image\">Rating of Tony (2019)</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>IMDb: -<br />Times of India: 2.5/5<br />Book My Show: 85%</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/tony-official-trailer-yashodhan-rana-akshay-verma/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Story (opens in a new tab)\">Story</a>:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The story starts with Four psychology students. They plan for something different to get to know new things about human psychology. Basically, the got an idea of p.resenting a different, real, and unique analysis of psychoanalysis <br />So These four colleges made a plan and the plan was to plant a camera in a church’s confession box. From there they want to know what people say about themselves when they feel guilty.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3854 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/750x600-1.jpg\" alt=\"tony\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p>This plan gets them across a serial killer who was confessing to murder the priest. From here the actual story begins. And they meet with TONY. He is a serial killer. Then they befriend that serial killer, Tony.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"left\",\"id\":690,\"width\":563,\"height\":74,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Review:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Tony is a great psychological thriller/ crime drama. The story is quite interesting.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Ashish (Mahesh Jilowa), Martin (Dhruv Souran), Kamya (Jinal Belani), and Kartik (Kabir Chilwal) are the psychology students. But the most negative thing about this movie which made the rating so low is the acting. All of the actors and actresses did worst acting, they fail to do justice to their respective characters.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Leading character of the movie Tony was played by<a href=\"https://in.bookmyshow.com/person/yashodhan-rana/1096440\"> Yoshodhan Rana</a>. He was not even looking fit in the scene.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Rana was not able to deliver the information as a killer. He exhibits coldness throughout the movie. We can say, it was a major setback to the plot. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading --><!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":689,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"very-dark-gray\",\"backgroundColor\":\"pale-cyan-blue\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Tony (2019 Film)- Rating and Review','','publish','open','open','','tony-2019-film-rating-and-review','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/tony-official-trailer-yashodhan-rana-akshay-verma/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/commando-3-2019-rating-and-review/','2020-12-21 01:25:48','2020-12-20 19:55:48','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=688',0,'post','',0),(699,1,'2019-11-30 16:59:10','2019-11-30 11:29:10','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, Commando 3 was released on 29 November 2019, it earned 4.7cr on the very first day. The storyline of the first half is good, but you will lose little interest in the second half because it is mainly action and dialogues will put you off at places.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3861 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/750x600-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Commando 3 is the third film of the Commando franchise. It is directed by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aditya_Datt\">Aditya Datt</a>. And it is produced by Vipul Amrutlal Shah, Reliance Entertainment and Motion Picture Capital.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Here we are providing all possible ratings so that you can judge by yourself to watch it. According to The TV Freak, it is an average movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If you are considering this as a part of the Rambo movie then you are mistaken.</p>\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m-JIofHHU6s[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The leading actor Vidyut has done his role best as usual but the problem is with the lack of effectiveness. You can predict the movie till the end. And nowadays the audience needs a movie that has a story that is not predictable. The audience wants to be surprised until the last.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>IMDb:</strong> 7.8/10</li>\r\n<li><strong>Times of India:</strong> 2.5/10</li>\r\n<li><strong>NDTV:</strong> 1/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bollywood Hungama:</strong> 2.5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Indian Express:</strong> 2/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>News18:</strong> 1.5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Times Now News: </strong> 2.5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>First Post:</strong> 1/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sify</strong>: 2/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Google Users:</strong> 95%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":690,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} --><!-- /wp:image --></div>','Commando 3 (2019) Rating and Review','','publish','open','open','','commando-3-2019-rating-and-review','','','2020-12-21 01:31:43','2020-12-20 20:01:43','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=699',0,'post','',0),(708,1,'2019-12-01 14:27:24','2019-12-01 08:57:24','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Nowadays in Bollywood, biopics have been started, next is Lala Amarnath. Every year we get one or two or more than that movie that is based on biopics. The thing is that, like Hollywood, Bollywood has adapted that movie based on the real story does well on box office and also win hearts.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Lala Amarnath: Director</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Rajkumar Hirani, a well-known director has made his last movie Sajnu in 2018. Sanju (2018) Movie is based on a real story of Super Star Sanjay Datt. Sanju (2018) did well on Box Office and also liked my audience.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He has directed every genre movies, few of them are Sanju, 3 idiots, PK, Munna Bhai MBBS, Lage Raho Munna Bhai, Saala Khadoos, Ferrari Ki Sawari. It is also being said that he will not direct the complete movie but a part of it.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Now Rajkumar Hirani is planning for the next movie based on a real story and screenwriter Abhijat Joshi is working with him for this biopic.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":711} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-711\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Writer:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Abhijat Joshi is an Indian screenwriter, he is also a producer and director. He has written so many scripts that liked by most famous directors and producers. Mr Joshi is known for his humour in the most liked Bollywood movies like Lage Raho Munna Bhai,3 Idiots, PK and Sanju.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to know something different about him then you should know that he is also a professor of English at Otterbein University in Westerville, Ohio, since 2003.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The movie is based on Legendary cricketer Lala Amarnath. He was the first Test Match Captain for the Indian cricket team. It was first Independent India’s cricket team. He has so many remarkable records.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":710} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-710\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/LALA-AMARNATH.jpg\" alt=\"LALA Amarnath biopic by rajkumar hirani and Abhijat joshi\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Lala Amarnath was also the first Indian cricketer who had scored a hundred for the country in the test match. He is one of the men who has made us proud in sports and helped to make cricket what it is now.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Commando review - <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/commando-3-2019-rating-and-review/\">Click here</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>To know more about upcoming movies and trailers -<a href=\"http://thetvfreak.com/trailers\"> Click here</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Lala Amarnath: Rajkumar Hirani and Abhijat Joshi’s next biopic','','publish','open','open','','lala-amarnath-rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshis-next-biopic','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/commando-3-2019-rating-and-review/','2020-12-20 16:52:05','2020-12-20 11:22:05','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=708',0,'post','',0),(720,1,'2019-12-03 00:20:23','2019-12-02 18:50:23','<div align=\"JUSTIFY\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":732} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-732 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/sab-kushal-mangal.jpg\" alt=\"sab kushal mangal\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What\'s About the movie \"Sab Kushal Mangal (2020)\"</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Sab Kushal Mangal is a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">Comedy Drama Romance film</a>. This film is in news this week because Star Akshaye Khanna is in the lead role. He has done lots of movies almost every type.</p>\r\n<p>He is known for his acting in a comedy role and Every comedy movie like Hulchal, Hungama, etc he was into, did well at the box office and on audience hearts. But on the other hand, he has done lots of heart touching serious movie like Section 375\", \"The Accidental Prime Minister\" and \"Mom\".</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He also said, <strong><em>\"I really liked the story and the character. Also, the fact that the comedy is never forced, it is situational,\"</em></strong>. And we all know for Bollywood cinema it is need to make the comedy that should be based on the situation not only on acting.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We haven\'t seen him in the Comedy role for so long. Now the Expectations are high with this movie.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Released Date of Sab Kushal Mangal (2020):</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Release date :</strong> 3 Jan 2020.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Director:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This movie is directed by Karan Vishwanath Kashyap. He is a Bollywood Movie Director.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This is his first movie apart from this he was an assistant director in Chak de! India(2007), Don (2006) and Bunty Aur Babli (2005)</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Producer:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Prachi Nitin Manmohan is the producer of this Comedy movie and She has also directed Gali Gali Chor Hai in 2012.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":721} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The cast of Sab Kushal Mangal (2020):</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Akshaye Khanna</li>\r\n<li>Nalneesh Neel: He is an Indian actor and did lots of famous Bollywood movies such as <em>Manikarnika</em>, <em>Chhichhore</em>, <em>Fukrey Returns, </em>etc.</li>\r\n<li>Padmini Kolhapure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Trailer:</h2>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/embed/yzbyiA10jlk</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} --><!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>','Sab Kushal Mangal (2020) Comedy Movie','','publish','open','open','','sab-kushal-mangal-2020-movie','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/biopic-on-dr-vashistha-narayan-singh/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/lala-amarnath-rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshis-next-biopic/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/','2020-12-21 10:54:42','2020-12-21 05:24:42','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=720',0,'post','',0),(739,1,'2019-12-04 10:07:45','2019-12-04 04:37:45','<div align=\"jsutify\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":737} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1707 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/visishth-nayaran-singh-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"vashishtha narayan singh biopic\" width=\"720\" height=\"377\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh</h2>\r\n<p>As we know lots of movies are made in <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/hollywood/\">Hollywood</a> that is based on a true event. Whether it is a story of a great scientist or describing a logical concept. The movies like<em> A Beautiful Mind, The Imitation Game, The Theory of Everything and The Secret Of Nikola Tesla</em>, are liked by the audience very much. Here is another biopic on Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If you are a movie freak then you also know a movie based on an Indian Mathematician “The man Who Knew Infinity” describes the hidden talent of India. Nowadays in Bollywood Biopics are stealing the audience. Everybody loves his country and if he watches the journey and struggle of Indian with the big achievement, in the end, they become happy and satisfying.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Directed By:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The movie based on this great Man will be directed by Neeraj Pathak.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Produced By:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>It will be produced by Excel Entertainment.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>What is it about?</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>So here is another biopic that is a little bit different because it is not based on any Player not about the Sports Game. It is about an Indian Mathematician who did something strange.</p>\r\n<p>Yes, this story is about Legendary Indian mathematician Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh. Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh was a great scientist and a Lecturer. There are some unique things that keep him unique.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>About Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vashistha Narayan Singh challenged Einstein\'s theory of relativity E = MC<sup>2</sup>. And we all know that Einstein was a great scientist. He gave lots of theories, some of them are still to be implemented. Since then, the world began to recognize Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh\'s talent.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>There is another exciting story about him and we are sure you will not believe or you will get shocked after reading it. He was at NASA when NASA was launching the Apollo. At that time the computers at NASA were shut down just before the launch. There were 31 computers using for launch. In the meanwhile, Vashistha Narayan continued his calculations with only pen and paper. At the end, when the system was recovered, the calculus of Dr Vashistha and the 31 computers was the same.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:list --></div>','Biopic on Dr Vashistha Narayan Singh','','publish','open','open','','biopic-on-dr-vashistha-narayan-singh','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/lala-amarnath-rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshis-next-biopic/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/ananya-pandey/','2020-12-20 17:01:11','2020-12-20 11:31:11','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=739',0,'post','',0),(743,1,'2019-12-05 09:02:50','2019-12-05 03:32:50','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Looking for an entertaining movie this week? The wait is over. After the Motichoor ChaknaChoor movie that is a situational Comedy, Pati Patni Aur Woh is the movie that is full of acting, comedy, a little bit of suspense. The movie comes to the theatre this week on 6 December.</p>\r\n<h2>Rating of Pati Patni Aur Woh:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>IMDb:</strong> 7.1/10</li>\r\n<li><strong>TOI:</strong> 3.5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Mouth Shut:</strong> 5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>KoiMoi:</strong> 3/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bollywood Hungama:</strong> 3.5/5</li>\r\n<li><strong>Reddit:</strong> 3.5/10</li>\r\n<li><strong>The TV Freak:</strong> 3/5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Story:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This film is a remake of the Indian Cult Comedy Drama of Pati Patni Aur Woh (1978) but in a modern way. The story is the same but with a different presentation and energy. Like the old film, a married man falls for another woman and then he starts making a mountain of lies. The situation becomes critical and tried to manage everything so that no one can know.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3011 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-4.jpg\" alt=\"Pati Patni Aur Woh (2019)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Pati Patni Aur Woh: Review</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Our hero Chintu Tyagi or Abhinav Tyagi (Kartik) is a government employee working in Kanpur. He is married to feisty Vedika ( Bhumi). They did arrange marriage. When their parents found out that they are a perfect match and very prospective match for each other they tie the knot.</p>\r\n<p>The couple was enjoying their marital life. Now she enters, who is she? Yes, Tapasya Singh (Ananya). She comes into their life. She, the young and hot girl comes to Chintu. Now he just wants to spend time with this beautiful, young hot girl.</p>\r\n<p>He starts doing everything she likes and wants to do. She wants to set up her boutique in Delhi. Chintu helps her in that not only help but also doing stuff she likes, he is so crazy about her. After that he finds that Tapasya is hesitant to be friendly because of his marital status, he tries to manage this as well.</p>\r\n<p>He adds his friend Fahim Rizvi (Aparshakti) to clear everything out. Rizvi always helps Chintu when he is in trouble. But after adding him to this situation things goes wrong and out of control. And then lots of confusion starts. One lie in another lie then everything becomes an ocean of lies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h2>Final Recommendations:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Overall it is a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/movies/\">great movie</a>. You should watch it for entertainment. You can say this is the worth of money and you can invest your time and money for this.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Pati Patni Aur Woh: Review and Rating','','publish','open','open','','pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating','','','2020-12-21 10:57:17','2020-12-21 05:27:17','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=743',0,'post','',0),(754,1,'2019-12-07 01:08:22','2019-12-06 19:38:22','<div align=\"jsutify\">\r\n<h2>Who is Ananya Pandey?</h2>\r\nAnanya Pandey entered the world of Bollywood with Student Of The Year 2, and her second movie was Pati Patni Aur Woh. Ananya is the daughter of Suyash Pandey ( Screen name Chunky Pandey).\r\n\r\nShe completed her schooling at Dhirubhai Ambani International School, Mumbai. Ananya doing her graduating from the University of Southern California, Los Angeles.<img class=\"wp-image-773 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ananya.jpeg\" alt=\"Ananya Pandey\" data-id=\"773\" data-link=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/ananya-pandey/ananya/\" />\r\n<h2>Want to know more about her?</h2>\r\nYou can wish her Happy Birthday on 30th Oct, and Ananya was born in the year 1998. She just turned 21. Isn\'t she adorable?\r\n\r\nAnanya Pandey\'s mother is Bhavna Pandey, and her younger sister is Rysa Pandey. She is 5\'7\", and have dark brown eyes and black hairs and Ananya is a Serial Chiller.\r\n<h3>Funny and Cute:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OK2kdZf4JD4[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nIf you want to follow her on Instagram and Twitter-\r\nAnanya Pandey Instagram account - ananyapandey\r\nAnanya Pandey Twitter account - @ananyapandayy\r\n\r\nPandey is very close to Shahrukh Khan\'s Daughter Suhana Khan. They spend a good amount of time together.\r\n<figure><img class=\"wp-image-766 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/suhana-shanaya-ananya.jpg\" alt=\"Ananya pandey and suhana khan\" data-id=\"766\" data-link=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/?attachment_id=766\" /></figure>\r\n<h2>Ananya Pandey\'s journey</h2>\r\nPandey started her career with Dharma Production produced Student of the year 2, in a leading role, co-starring Tiger Shroff and Tara Sutaria. That was the sequel of Karan Johar\'s Student of the Year.\r\n\r\nStudent of the Year 2 did not do so well on the screen but Ananya did a hell of a work and made her way into Bollywood.\r\n<figure><img class=\"wp-image-765 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ananya-pandey-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Ananya Pandey Pati Patni aur woh and Student of the year 2\" data-id=\"765\" data-link=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/?attachment_id=765\" /></figure>\r\nPandey\'s second movie is Pati Patni Aur Woh and you know what She is in the lead role of Mistress, co-starring Bhumi Pednekar and Kartik Aaryan. Pati Patni Aur Woh is a remake of a 1978 film, had the same storyline.\r\n<h3>Watch this amazing movie trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L7a1JSeqaXk[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nThis movie releasing on 6th Dec 2019, and doing very well on the box office collection. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating/\">Reviews of Pati Patni Aur Woh</a> are also out and the rating is also good that is the best thing for an artist to get the best rating is starting its career.\r\n<h3>With her father:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jdRjkArFJ4A[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>The upcoming movie of Ananya Pandey</h2>\r\nKhaali Peeli is the next movie in the bucket of Pandey and this film features Ananya Pandey and Ishaan Khattar in the lead role. This comedy thriller will be directed by Maqbool Khan and produced by Ali Abbas Zafar, and the banner will be Zee Studios. Khaali Peeli will be released on 12 Jun 2020\r\n\r\n</div>','Ananya Pandey: Immensely and Remarkable Actress','','publish','open','open','','ananya-pandey','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/biopic-on-dr-vashistha-narayan-singh/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/lala-amarnath-rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshis-next-biopic/','2021-01-16 00:38:47','2021-01-15 19:08:47','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=754',0,'post','',0),(782,1,'2019-12-07 09:56:49','2019-12-07 04:26:49','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>About the story of Bombshell:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Bombshell 2019 movie is an upcoming American drama film. It this movie the greater tries to show what happens in media. Basically, you can say it is an interview of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Media, News and entertainment</a> Companies.</p>\r\n<p>This movie certainly based on serval women at News. You will see how will they try to expose the famous person CEO Roger Ailes for Sexual harassment.</p>\r\n<p>You will see the downfalls of Roger Ailes that he faced after some women exposed him.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The movie continues and Roger Ailes was fired from Fox News when serval movie women come forward with the same harassment issue.</p>\r\n<p>One of the news chief\'s strongest supporters Mr Murdoch hired and put Ailes on that big position. Now after this, he made the decision to fire him.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Murdoch, who put Ailes in charge of the network in 1996, was one of the news chief’s strongest supporters, though he ultimately made the decision to fire Ailes.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Releasing on:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The initial release if Bombshell is in the USA on 13 Dec 2019.<br />After that in India, it will be released on 3 Jan 2020.</p>\r\n<p>https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1203156982019919872?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Bombshell Director:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Mathew Jay Roach is an American film director, producer, and screenwriter as well. He has done lots of good movies like the <em>Austin Powers</em> films and <em>Meets the Parents</em><em>. </em></p>\r\n<p>He has also made some comedy movies like Dinner for Schmuchs (2010) and Recount.</p>\r\n<p>https://twitter.com/AndreaKMR/status/1203086212044447744?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Producers and Production House.</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Producers: </h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Jay Roach, Charles Randolph, Aaron L. Gilbert, Beth Kono, Margaret Riley, and A.J. Dix are producing the film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Production companies: </h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Bron Studios, Denver and Delilah Productions, and Everyman Pictures are the Production House for this Fox News Film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Bombshell Cast:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, These women who expose Roger Ailes were Gretchen Carlson (Nicole Kidman) and Megyn Kelly (Charlize Theron). They sue him for harassment.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Secondly, Apart from these famous celebrities, there are some more interesting characters in this movie. You will see Alice Eve (Replicas), Alanna Ubach (Coco), Elisabeth Rohm, Spencer Garrett, Ashley Greene (The Twilight Saga) in the expressive role. The cast also includes Bree Condon and Nazanin Boniadi from Hotel Mumbai movie<strong>.</strong> You will all of them as the news host for Fox News.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Emmy award-nominated actress Connie Britton also has her role as Roger Ailes’ wife along with Rob Delaney from Deadpool 2 movie and Ahna O’Reilly from Help movie<strong>.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Bombshell Trailer:</h2>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/embed/YXL33tEUA3g</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Some Behind the scene Pictures:</h3>\r\n<p>https://twitter.com/spun_sugar1/status/1203016376824156160?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Lets Talk about OSCAR:</h3>\r\n<p>https://twitter.com/ScottMendelson/status/1203009471414321152?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><!-- /wp:list --></div>','Bombshell (2019)-Stars Charlize Theron, Nicole Kidman, Margot Robbie','','publish','open','open','','bombshell-2019-stars-charlize-theron-nicole-kidman-margot-robbie','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/biopic-on-dr-vashistha-narayan-singh/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/lala-amarnath-rajkumar-hirani-and-abhijat-joshis-next-biopic/','2020-12-21 12:05:04','2020-12-21 06:35:04','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=782',0,'post','',4),(845,1,'2019-12-13 00:19:02','2019-12-12 18:49:02','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, you should know that <em><strong>Jai Mummy Di</strong></em> trailer is out. Secondly, It is an upcoming Indian Hindi-language and family comedy film. This film is the mother centered.</p>\r\n<p>Finally, After <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/motichoor-chaknachoor/\">Motichoor Chaknachoor</a>, this is the movie that includes Romance, Love, Family issues, Dispute, Comedy, and full of Entertainment.</p>\r\n<p>Jai Mummy Di is a light-hearted family comedy.</p>\r\n<p>https://twitter.com/SonnalliSeygall/status/1204635121250230272?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:core-embed/twitter {\"url\":\"https://twitter.com/SonnalliSeygall/status/1204635121250230272?s=20\",\"type\":\"rich\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"twitter\",\"className\":\"\"} --><!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Jai Mummy Di trailer tells a lot about the story and you will see conflicting dynamics between the mothers. And leads to muddled chemistry between their own children.</p>\r\n<p>Other members of both families also got connected, but the mother is always a mother.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Some of the moments are very natural in Jai Mummy Di trailer and you just live those moments.</p>\r\n<p>Sunny is with another girl, who visited his house for marriage related discussion. This scene is so realistic, we should appreciate the writer and the director.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Release Date:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Initial release: 17 January 2020</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Director:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Firstly, you should know that<em><strong> Jai Mummy Di </strong></em>is directed by Navjot Gulati. He is a Hindi film writer and director. He wrote the movie <em>Running Shaadi</em> (2017) with some famous stars Amit Sadh and Taapsee Pannu.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Producer and the Production House:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This family comedy-drama is produced by Luv Films and distributed by T-Series. Producers are Luv Ranjan, Ankur Garg, Bhushan Kumar,  and Krishan Kumar.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Cast:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sunny Sharma is in the leading male role. He is very famous after his movie Pyar Ka 