liSeygall/status/1169832214650994688?s=20</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/twitter -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Trailer: Watch Now</h2>\r\n<p>https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kc3SXIN3620</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube --></div>','Jai Mummy Di Trailer (2020): A Comedy-Drama','','publish','open','open','','jai-mummy-di-trailer','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/motichoor-chaknachoor/','2020-12-21 12:04:17','2020-12-21 06:34:17','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=845',0,'post','',0),(922,11,'2020-06-13 01:09:25','2020-06-12 19:39:25','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":923} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-923 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Aparshakti-Khurana-Copy.png\" alt=\"Aparshakti Khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurrana is a popular Indian Bollywood actor as well as a Radio jockey and a television host. His birth date is 18th November in 1987.</p>\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurana is the brother of one of the well-known and versatile actors of Bollywood at this time, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/ayushmann-starts-to-transform-physically-for-his-upcoming-movie/\">Ayushman Khurana</a>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":931} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-931 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/aparshakti-Khurana-ayushman-khurana.jpg\" alt=\"aparshakti Khurana ayushman khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurrana participated in the audition of the famous youth show Roadies MTV in season3, Episode 2. It was the first time when he faced the camera.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Debut and breakthrough</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Aparshakti Khurana in Year: 2016-2017</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":924} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-924 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Saat-Uchakkey.jpg\" alt=\"Saat Uchakkey\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Khurrana made his Bollywood debut in 2016 in <strong><em>Saat Uchakkey</em> </strong>by playing the role of Khappe.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":925} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-925 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Aparshakti-Khurana-Dangal.jpg\" alt=\"Aparshakti Khurana Dangal\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurrana did his first Bollywood project in which he made his acting debut with Nitesh Tiwari\'s sports biopic <strong><em>Dangal (2016)</em></strong> which gave him several recognitions as an actor.</p>\r\n<p>For this film, he won and nominated for many awards like Most Promising New Comer(Male) in Star Screen Awards which he won in 2017.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He also nominated for Best Actor In Comic Role In Star Screen Awards &amp; Best Male debut in 62 and Filmfare Awards in 2017.</p>\r\n<p>After the success of Dangal, he was cast as a co-star in Shashank Khaitan directed romantic comedy based Film <strong><em>Badrinath ki Dulhania</em></strong> in 2017 which was also successful and one of the top economic production of the year worldwide.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Aparshakti Khurana in Year: 2018</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":926} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-926 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/happy-phirr-bhag-jayegi-aparshakti-khurana.jpg\" alt=\"happy phirr bhag jayegi aparshakti khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>After that Khurana was cast in three films in 2018 Mudassar Aziz\'s comedy film <strong><em>Happy Phir Bhag Jayegi</em></strong> which was a sequel to the 2016 film Happy Bhag Jayagi.</p>\r\n<p>His co-stars were Sonakshi Sinha &amp; Diana Penty and he played the supporting part of Aman Wadhwa.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":927} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-927 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Stree-Aparshakti-Khurana-.jpg\" alt=\"Stree Aparshakti Khurana \" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In 2018 he also appeared in the horror-comedy film <strong><em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stree_(2018_film)\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stree</a></em></strong> which was directed by Amar Kaushik. This film emerged as a commercially successful film. His co-stars were Rajkumar Rao &amp; Shraddha Kapoor.</p>\r\n<p>This film \'Stree\' also gave him much recognization as an actor &amp; huge popularity worldwide. His performance in Stree gave him The Best Supporting Actor nomination at Filmfare &amp; won Lions Gold Awards for Best Actor in Best Actor in a Comic Role (Male).</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":928} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-928 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Rajma-Chawal-Aparshakti-Khurana.jpg\" alt=\"Rajma Chawal Aparshakti Khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Directed in the same year 2018, Khurana\'s final release was the NETFLIX FIlM ‘<strong><em>RAJMA ChAWAL’</em></strong> by Leena Yadav.</p>\r\n<p>In this film, he shared the screen with a senior actor of Bollywood Rishi Kapoor, Anirudh Talwar &amp; Amyra Dastur. After all these star cast Leena Yadev Netflix film Rajma Chawal was not a commercially successful film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Aparshakti Khurana in Year: 2019</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":929} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-929 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/luka-chuppi-Aparshakti-Khurana.jpg\" alt=\"luka chuppi Aparshakti Khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In 2019, he came back with new releases like Laxman Utekar\'s romantic comedy film <strong><em>Lukka Chuppi</em></strong>. He played a supporting role in this film and his co-stars were Kartik Aaryan &amp; Kriti Sanon.</p>\r\n<p>This film ran successfully at the box office and critics appreciated his acting in this film.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":930} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-930 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Pati-Patni-Aur-Woh-aparshakti-khurana.jpg\" alt=\"Pati Patni Aur Woh aparshakti khurana\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>His next film in 2019 was Prashant Singh\'s <strong><em>Jabariya Jodi</em></strong>, which was not running successfully. After that, he played a special appearance in his brother Ayushman Khurana\'s most successful Film Bala.</p>\r\n<p>In 2019, Khurrana\'s last release was Mudassar Aziz’s comedy film <strong><em>Pati Pati Aur Woh</em></strong>, It was a remake film with the same name in the year 1978.</p>\r\n<p>Checkout: <strong><em><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating/\">Pati Pati Aur Woh</a></em></strong><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating/\"> Reviews</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Aparshakti Khurana’s Personal life</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":932} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-932 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ayushman-aparshakti-Khurana.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurrana born in Chandigarh. His father P. Khurana is an astrologer and author while his mother Poonam is a housewife.</p>\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurana did his schooling and graduated in law from Chandigarh. He was the sports captain in his school days and want to pursue his career in the sports field like a cricket anchor or host. He was also the captain of the under 19 Haryana Cricket Team.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":933} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-933 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ayushman-aparshakti-radio-jockey.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Mr. Khurrana shifted to Delhi from Chandigarh for his practice in law at the Delhi High court. But he was not happy so he then decided to start his career as a Radio Jockey With Big FM in Delhi.</p>\r\n<p>Therefore he joined the Dramatech theatre group III, Delhi to improve his voice modulation and expression. After that, he is a popular RJ and host in the television industry also.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Aparshakti Khurana Wife:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":934} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-934 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ayushman-aparshakti-wife.jpg\" alt=\"ayushman aparshakti wife\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Aparshakti Khurrana married Aakriti Ahuja on 7th September 2014. They met at a dance class in Chandigarh. <strong>Aparshakti Khurrana wife Aakriti</strong> is a financial analyst and consultant.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>','Aparshakti Khurana | Wife, Age and Movies','','publish','open','open','','aparshakti-khurana-wife-age-and-movies','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/pati-patni-aur-woh-review-and-rating/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/ayushmann-starts-to-transform-physically-for-his-upcoming-movie/','2020-12-26 13:50:37','2020-12-26 08:20:37','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=922',0,'post','',0),(937,11,'2020-06-16 13:20:18','2020-06-16 07:50:18','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":938} --><!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Gulabo Sitabo is a much-awaited film of the Bollywood industry. The main cast of this Lucknow based movie is Amitabh Bachchan &amp; Ayushman Khurana.  Gulabo Sitabo is the first movie to premiere for the first time on the OTT platform, Amazon Prime.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Due to the Covind -19 pandemic, the film was not released on theatre but was released on Amazon Prime. And the released date was 12th June 2020. It will be available in 200 countries worldwide at a time.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":939} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-939 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-director-shoojit-sircar.jpg\" alt=\"director shoojit sircar\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Gulabo Sitabo is an Indian Hindi language film, oriented towards comedy-drama and an amazing story with a lesson. Shoojit Sircar is the director of this movie. He is a famous director and made a very famous movie like Piku, Vicky Donar, etc.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Trailer:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:html -->\r\n<p>[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0qeQ_yHqtA[/embedyt]</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:html -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":940} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-940 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ronnie-Lahiri-Sheel-Kumar-producer-of-gulabo-sitabo.jpg\" alt=\"producers Ronnie Lahiri &amp; Sheel Kumar\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><span class=\"word\">Ronnie</span> <span class=\"word\">Lahiri</span> &amp; <span class=\"word\">Sheel</span> <span class=\"word\">Kumar</span> <span class=\"word\">are</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">producers</span> <span class=\"word\">of</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">Gulabo</span> <span class=\"word\">Sitabo</span> <span class=\"word\">Film</span>.  <span class=\"word\">Juhi</span> <span class=\"word\">Chaturvedi</span> <span class=\"word\">is</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">writer</span> <span class=\"word\">of</span> <span class=\"word\">this</span> <span class=\"word\">amazing</span> <span class=\"word\">film</span>. <span class=\"word\">She</span> <span class=\"word\">has</span> <span class=\"word\">done</span> <span class=\"word\">quite</span> <span class=\"word\">impressive</span> <span class=\"word\">work</span>. <span class=\"word\">She</span> <span class=\"word\">tried</span> <span class=\"word\">to</span> <span class=\"word\">show</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">life</span> <span class=\"word\">of</span> <span class=\"word\">an</span> <span class=\"word\">old</span> <span class=\"word\">Nawab</span> <span class=\"word\">who</span> <span class=\"word\">wanted</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">Haweli</span>. <span class=\"word\">The</span> <span class=\"word\">entire</span> <span class=\"word\">film</span> <span class=\"word\">is</span> <span class=\"word\">based</span> <span class=\"word\">on</span> <span class=\"word\">Lucknow</span>. <span class=\"word\">And</span> <span class=\"word\">that\'s</span> <span class=\"word\">why</span> <span class=\"word\">the</span> <span class=\"word\">maximum</span> <span class=\"word\">Scene</span> <span class=\"word\">was</span> <span class=\"word\">shoot</span> <span class=\"word\">there</span>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":941} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-941 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/juhi-Chaturvedi-writer-of-gulabo-sitabo.jpg\" alt=\"Juhi Chaturvedi\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Story of Gulabo Sitabo:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":942} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-942 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/gulabo-sitabo-movie-scene-amitabh-bachchan-ayushman-khurana.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 movie\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Gulabo Sitabo set in nawab ka sharer Lucknow (India). Gulabo Sitabo is a social satire about the two impossible peculiar human beings- <strong><em>Mirza Chunnan Nawab</em></strong>, Bollywood Royalty Amitabh Bachchan played the role who stays in a dilapidated house &amp; there are some tenants in his house.</p>\r\n<p>One of his tenants, <strong><em>Baankey Rastogi</em></strong>, the role played by Bollywood superstar actor Ayushman Khurana. Everybody knows him for his acting talent. This film is simple humor between the landlord and tenants.</p>\r\n<p>The mansion may have seen many dramas unfold over a century of its existence, but still has a final act left as the drama of the battle of ownership unfolds, with a priceless lesson to teach.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The first look of Gulabo Sitabo:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":943} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-943 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/gulabo-sitabo-movie-scene-first-look-.jpg\" alt=\" first look\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The first look of the film was a quirky teaser poster of Amitabh Bachchan on 21st June 2019. The production team also told that the release date of the film will is 17th April 2020.</p>\r\n<p>Due to the current situation and COVID 19 pandemic the film director, Shoojit Sirkar took the decision to release this film on Amazon prime as “the dawn of a new era for Indian entertainment”.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The story behind making GULABO SITABO:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":944} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-944 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-making.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 making\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In May 2019, Shoojit Sircar announced that in a press conference that he will back on screen with a new Lucknow based movie.</p>\r\n<p>In this film, Juhi Chaturvedi worked with him. Piku director said that it was a quirky story. when he read the script from Juhi Chaturvedi he shared it with Mr. Bachchan and Ayushman Khurana.</p>\r\n<p>Both of them liked the script and agreed to work on this script, Amitabh Bachchan &amp; Ayushman Khurana were the two lead roles in this film. The first shooting was on the 3rd week of June in Lucknow in 2019.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Pair of Amitabh Bachchan and Ayushman Khurana in Gulabo Sitabo:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":945} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-945 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-making-2.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 making\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Gulabo Sitabo also took the attention of the audience for its star casts. In this movie, for the first time, Amitabh Bachchan and Ayushman Khurana shared screen space.</p>\r\n<p>The filmmaker Shoojit Sircar has worked with them in different films. He has worked with Ayushman Khurana in Vicky Donar (2012) and Amitabh Bachchan in Piku (2015). He was bringing the two great actors in one film together for the first time.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>The Film Music of Gulabo Sitabo:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Shantanu Moitra, Abhishek Arora, and Anuj Garg composed the music with lyrics written by Puneet Sharma, Dinesh Pant, and Vinod Dubey. The music of this film released on 27th May 2020. In this film, there are totally of 10 songs.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Songs of the film:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<h3>There are 10 songs in this film:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>“ <strong><em>Madari ka Bandar</em></strong> “is the first song &amp; sang by Tochi Raina, Anuj Garg</li>\r\n<li>The second song of this film is released “ <strong><em>Jootam Phenk</em></strong>” music by Abhishek Arora sang by Piyush Mishra</li>\r\n<li>The song “<strong><em>Kanjoos</em></strong>’” composed by Shantanu Moitra sang by Mika Singh</li>\r\n<li>The fourth song of this movie is “<strong><em>kya Leke Aaya Jagne</em></strong>” compose by Shantanu Moitra sang by Vinod Dubey</li>\r\n<li>There are other songs like “<strong><em>Do Dinka Ye Mela Respire</em></strong>” by Tochi Raina composed by Anuj Garg</li>\r\n<li>The sixth songs of this movie are “<strong><em>Budhau Respire</em></strong>” version by Bhanwari Devi and composed by Anuj Garg</li>\r\n<li>Anuj Garg composed another two songs for this film like “<strong><em>Do Dinka Ye Mela</em></strong>” and “<strong><em>Buddha</em></strong>”</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Two songs of this film “<strong><em>Gulabo Sitabo theme</em></strong>” and “<strong><em>Gulabo Sitabo Clarinet theme\"</em></strong> both were composed by Shantanu Moitra one is 3:41 and the other is 0:56 duration.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Working Experience Of the stars in Gulabo Sitabo:</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>Mr. Amitabh Bachchan</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Rising Sun Films production “GUlABO SITABO” is written by Juhi Chaturvedi and produced by Ronnie Lahiri and Sheel Kumar. </p>\r\n<p>About this film, Bollywood Badshah Amitabh Bachchan said in an interview about Gulabo Sitabo. He said, “ Gulabo Sitabo is a slice of life dramedy that is must watch for families at home.”</p>\r\n<p>He also added, \" I was excited about my role since the first time Shoojit showed me the character\'s look. It took me almost three hours each day to get into character with its different looks.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":946} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-946\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-making-4.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 making\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>I had a wonderful time working with my very talented costar Ayushman Khurana. Even though we are constantly bantering in the film, it has been a pleasure working with him for the first time.</p>\r\n<p>This family entertainment has the power to cut across geographic boundaries and we are pleased to bring Gulabo Sitabo to the audience across the globe.”</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ayushmann_Khurrana\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mr. Ayushman Khurana</a></h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":947} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-947 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-making-3.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 making\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The other protagonist of this film Khurrana added, “ Gulabo Sitabo is a special film for me. It made me reunite with my mentor Shoojit da after Vicky Donar.</p>\r\n<p>Whatever I am today is because of him. I am happy that he makes me a part of his vision again. Gulabo Sitabo also see me share the screen space with Mr.Amitabh Bachchan for the first time and it\'s a huge moment, it’s a dream come true for me.</p>\r\n<p>I have secretly wished to work with him for many years and Shoojit da made this happen and I will be indebted to him forever. It has truly been an honour for me to work with a legend and I feel enriched as an actor after the experience.”</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading -->\r\n<h2>Released On The Digital Platform</h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Gulabo Sitabo</strong> is the first Bollywood commercial movie on the OTT platform, Amazon prime video. The move to the OTT is the new normal for India as Cinema halls and Multiplex are not open from March due to lockdown.</p>\r\n<p>The future will also remain uncertain due to social distance. The pandemic audience cannot go to the cinema hall or multiplex to watch the new movie.</p>\r\n<p>A digital platform like Amazon Prime, Netflix, Disney Hotstar is the only and main platform to the Bollywood director and producer to release the film now.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":948} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img class=\"wp-image-948 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Gulabo-Sitabo-2020-making-5-amazon-prime.jpg\" alt=\"Gulabo Sitabo 2020 making 5 amazon prime\" /></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Many producers and directors released the web series on digital platforms all over the world. They also run good business but Gulabo Sitabo is the first movie of Bollywood on Amazon Prime.</p>\r\n<p>Without the release in the cinema hall, only those people who like to watch movies on the internet will be able to watch this film at the moment.</p>\r\n<p>Now it’s time to see how many people watch the film and admire the decision of the director and set a new era in the Indian Hindi film industry.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Also Read:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/aparshakti-khurana/\">Aparshakti Khurana: His journey to the film industry</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/trending/new-trailers/\">Check New Trailers</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>','Gulabo Sitabo Movie (2020) | Trailer and Story','','publish','open','open','','gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/aparshakti-khurana/','2020-12-26 13:49:29','2020-12-26 08:19:29','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=937',0,'post','',0),(951,11,'2020-06-19 23:26:13','2020-06-19 17:56:13','<div align=\"justify\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The world lost a gem of an actor on June 14, 2020. Sushant Singh Rajput was a talented man and a smart guy too. Most people especially his fans knew about his journey from wanting to being am an engineer to become an actor in the Indian film industry.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":954,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-954 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Shushant-Singh-Rajput-life-movies-photo1.jpg\" alt=\"Sushant Singh Rajput\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sushantsinghrajput\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">@sushantsinghrajput</a> <br />Twitter: @itsSSR <br />DOB: 21 January 1986<br />Died: 14 June 2020 <br />Age: 34<br />Height: 1.78 m</p>\