e the concept and storyline out of consideration, and a surprisingly robotic but accurate expression as it was what the character demanded from Keanu Reeves, this franchise would still make it to the top ten solely for its cinematography and visual effects.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This sci-fi action blockbuster introduced to the film industry a whole new bunch of possibilities of parallel reality. Which revolver around aliens and monsters earlier. Followed by a number of brilliant later attempts like Mr. Nobody or The Inception to revoke the theory of the presence of only one factual world that we live in.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKQi3bBA1y8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>4. Star Wars:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1130 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/star-wars-trilogy-movies-min.jpg\" alt=\"star wars trilogy movies Hollywood Franchises\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First released during the height of the space race. This franchise soon captured everyone’s imagination with vivid picturization of the far future galaxy and its divergent civilizations. It takes a typical war action movie genre to a galactic level with extensive visualization. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though sometimes hard to follow as the original story was released in the late ’70s, prequels in the late ’90s, and the sequels during the last couple of years, but still very enjoyable because of the thrill and drama every segment presents. And as our reach slowly but steadily expending to the outer edges of the solar system, this franchise is now more rational than ever.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1129 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/star-wars-movies-min.jpg\" alt=\"star wars trilogy movies\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>3. Dollars Trilogy Movies: </strong></span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1120 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Dollars-Trilogy-min.jpg\" alt=\"star wars trilogy movies Hollywood Franchises\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From a general perspective, Hollywood is all about big-time and big-budget productions.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> By the early ’60s, Hollywood was already enjoying some extravagant box office super hits like Cleopatra, Spartacus, or Decline and Fall of Roman Empire, it was Sergio Leone, who with his low budget spaghetti westerns starring Clint Eastwood as new age sensation of Hollywood, marked the era. A superb franchise with captivating music, punk action, phony dialogues all steaming up to a spicy combination. It will forever be marked as American classics.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-X2DtiE7VLw[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>2.The Godfather Hollywood Movie:</strong><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1135 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/the-godfather-trilogy-min.jpg\" alt=\"the godfather trilogy\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Arguably this is the only movie on the list that actually overcame the perception of its source literature, considering there is still a number one to be announced. It’s a rare combination, Marlon Brando, Al Pacino, Robert De Nero all in a Francisco Ford Coppola movie and they all manage to give their best!. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And most ironically, this franchise successfully immortalizes the Sicilian Mafioso culture as a social nobility. With all its bloodshed and corruption. A real classic cult drama, which can always be revisited.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1134 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/the-godfather-trilogy-quotos-min.jpg\" alt=\"the godfather trilogy Hollywood Franchises\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer GF 1:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sY1S34973zA[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer GF 2:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9O1Iy9od7-A[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer GF 1:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TQQyM43P6y0[/embedyt]\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<h2><strong>1.The Lord of the Rings:</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1136 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/the-lord-of-the-rings-min.jpg\" alt=\"the godfather trilogy Hollywood Franchises\" width=\"682\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peter Jackson with his Lord of the Rings proves that epics can not only be found in parchments but also can be written on celluloid. This adaptation is on J. R. R. Tolkien’s famous novel series of the same name. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This series takes us to the fictional world of middle earth on an epic journey with men, elves, dwarves, orcs, trolls, and many other magnificent creatures. It’s like visualizing a whole new world with a whole new history. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The book is vividly picturized. Tolkien even invented a whole new alphabet to put on the elvish tongue. The success of Peter Jackson is in the true to life adaptation and graphic presentation with grand settings and following the exact mood of the storyline.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With fine editing, he manages to compact the epic story in three parts, although it should be count as one single plot, and later narrates the journey of Bilbo Baggins in “The Hobbit” in another three parts. The audience still awaits more similar production from the team as still there is a lot of middle earth remains to be put on motion pictures.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1127 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lord-of-the-rings-q-min.jpg\" alt=\"the godfather trilogy Hollywood Franchises\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1128 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lord-of-the-rings-min.jpg\" alt=\"the godfather trilogy\" width=\"658\" height=\"552\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this list, we tried to incorporate all pioneers of a new genre in the vast world of Hollywood entertainment. In case there is any movie that you think should be on this list but isn\'t, and any movie that shouldn’t be but is, please let us know in the commentary box.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thanks for reading. </span>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">  <strong>By: Shafayet Hossain</strong></h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h2>You can also read some other interesting articles<strong>:</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/\">Top-rated movies you should watch</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/shweta-tripathi-biography-tv-shows-movies-and-commercial-ads/\">About Shweta Tripathi\'s life and movies</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/laal-singh-chaddha-2020-based-on-forrest-gump/\">Lal Singh Chadhdha, a story based on Forest Gump</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','A Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch','','publish','open','open','','a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/shweta-tripathi-biography-tv-shows-movies-and-commercial-ads/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/laal-singh-chaddha-2020-based-on-forrest-gump/','2021-01-06 23:03:48','2021-01-06 17:33:48','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1142',0,'post','',0),(1157,4,'2020-07-01 11:42:37','2020-07-01 06:12:37','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indian Cricketers and drama go hand in hand. While Indians Cricketer and Bollywood is a love story that has no limits. So what happens when the drama of Bollywood and the love for Cricket are the centre of attention? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The ultimate gossip topic for all Indians, all over. The rumours confirmed stories and page 3 gossip of relationships, affairs, and marriage between the cricketing elite and the fashionable divas of Bollywood is always the talk of the town.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So what have been the popular all glamour stories of the inseparable combination of Bollywood and Cricket? Read on ahead to find out about the stories you haven’t heard of before and the ones you want to know more about.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>9. Cricketer Mansoor Ali Khan Pataudi and Sharmila Tagore</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1159 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Abhishek-Banerjee-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Mansoor Ali Khan Pataudi and Sharmila Tagore\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In one of the early glamour tales not of our times, the ex-captain of the Indian cricket team<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mansoor_Ali_Khan_Pataudi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Mansoor Ali Khan Pataudi</a> and Bollywood star Sharmila Tagore grabbed the attention of the gossip columns. The couple was one of the first unisons of Bollywood and Cricket.  One of there mutual friends introduces them before they fell for each other and later married. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the popular families of the industry to this time with their children (Saif Ali Khan, Soha Ali Khan, and Saba Ali Khan) being a prominent part of the industry. With Saif Ali Khan being a Superstar in the industry and his daughter Sara Ali Khan an upcoming star as well. </span>\r\n<h2><strong>8. Cricketer Ravi Shastri and Amrita Singh</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1162 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ravi-shastri-amrita-rao-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Ravi Shastri and Amrita Singh\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another headline-grabbing cricketer, Ravi Shastri was a very well reputed man in his playing days. And all the talk about him grabbed the attention of Amrita Singh. When at his peak, Ravi Shastri was the heartthrob for many all over the country. The stories of the couple kept cropping up. With Amrita Singh seen cheering on for him in certain matches as well. But these stories remained Page 3 news as the couple eventually separated. Ravi Shastri later married to Ritu Singh while Amrita took for the then young star Saif Ali Khan.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>7. Cricketer Yuvraj Singh and Actress Hazel Keech</strong><i></i></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1165 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Yuvraj-Singh-and-Hazel-Keech-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Yuvraj Singh and Hazel Keech\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1164 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Yuvraj-Singh-and-Hazel-Keech-1-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Yuvraj Singh and Hazel Keech \" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So many of us know Hazel Keech as the young Indian start In<strong> Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire.</strong> The rest of us know her as the initial love interest and then, wife of Cricketing superstar Yuvraj Singh. The tabloids were filled with tales of their relationships and photos of them together. After dating several women, Yuvraj Singh eventually found the love of his life in Hazel Keech and settled down. The couple had an extravagant wedding in Goa, with many prominent personalities in attendance as well.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>6. Yuvraj Singh and Kim Sharma</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1166 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Yuvraj-Singh-and-Kim-Sharma-min.jpg\" alt=\"Yuvraj Singh and Kim Sharma\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We did mention that Yuvraj Singh dated several women, didn’t we? Kim Sharma is best in our memories because of her prominent role in a movie so many of us know so well, Mohabbatein. Her fame remained majorly because of her role in the movie and was in a relationship with Yuvraj for a long time too. Their relationship catching the eye of so many all over. Although, the couple eventually separated with Yuvraj finding love as we mentioned with Hazel Keech and Kim Sharma marrying a business tycoon from Kenya, Ali Punjani.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>5. Cricketer Zaheer Khan and Isha Sharvani</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1167 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Zaheer-Khan-and-Isha-Sharvani-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Zaheer Khan and Isha Sharvani\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once considered one of the strongest unions of Bollywood and Cricket. This celebrity couple was once the fan-favourite and attracted attention all over. The fans were sure of them being in wedlock as well. Although it went to a halt after 8 years of being together as the couple called it quits. It Still considered one of the popular couples of the time. It isn’t completely disappointing as Zaheer later fell in love with one about whom you can read next.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>4. Zaheer Khan and Sagarika Ghatge</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1168 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Zaheer-Khan-and-Sagarika-Ghatge-min.jpg\" alt=\"Zaheer Khan and Sagarika Ghatge-min\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we did mention earlier, Zaheer did find love eventually. And he found it with Chak De India star Sagarika Ghatge. The relationship between the couple was very secretive and they both didn\'t tell about it. It was brought to attention and confirmed when the couple was found at the Yuvraj Singh - Hazel Keech wedding hand in hand walking out of there. They got married later in a very low key event with minimal people in 2017. A string of wedding functions continued to follow even after the wedding, The couple continues to stay strong and are enjoying a happily married life.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>3. Harbhajan Singh and Geeta Basra</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1160 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Harbhajan-Singh-and-Geeta-Basra-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Zaheer Khan and Actress Sagarika Ghatge\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ex - Indian Cricketer Harbhajan Singh is a part of the tales as well. The popular off-spinner and mouthy player was in a relationship with former Bollywood actress Geeta Basra for a very long time. The couple eventually got hitched and got married to one another in October 2015. The two of them were introduced by mutual friends and remained among the gossips for a long time. The cricket turned commentator and ex-star now lead a happily married life and are parents to an adorable daughter as well.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>2. KL Rahul and Nidhi Agerwal</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1161 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/KL-Rahul-and-Nidhi-Agerwal-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter KL Rahul and Actress Nidhi Agerwal\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The stylish young cricket has unsurprisingly caught the eye of some of the divas of Bollywood. One of them being Nidhi Agerwal. The cricketer and up and coming actress were together in various spots. In this day of Social media, it is very difficult for something so high profile to remain such a secret. KL Rahul was also embroiled in the controversy involving his fellow star Hardik Pandya on the show Koffee with Karan on the comments that were made. While the cricketer continues to fight for a place in the team and the actress for footholds in the industry. It is obvious that the two of them have been spending a lot of time together.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/imVkohli?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\" rel=\"nofollow\">Virat Kohli</a> and Anushka Sharma</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1163 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Virat-Kohli-and-Anushka-Sharma-min.jpg\" alt=\"Crickter Virat Kohli and Anushka Sharma\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The couple we’ve kept for the last, but the one that needs no introduction. They have attracted attention from every aspect of media, national, and International. One of the most popular celebrity couples of our time continues to steal our hearts. The couple dated for a long time, and never denied being in a relationship while being present in various spots throughout. After harboring through the difficult phases of the relationship the couple eventually married in a beautiful destination wedding in Italy. They were and continue to be the talk of the town and remain relationship goals for each and every one of us.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you think there are more couples or relationships that should be here then you can comment below. Thanks for reading.\r\n<h2>Also, Read About:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" rel=\"bookmark\">A Top 10 Picks of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/abhishek-banerjee-casting-director-and-acting