hite web series of India.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> I recommend it to teenagers (especially with a science background and aiming to join IIT) so that they can show it to their parents that just going to Kota does not ensure you a seat in IIT and it also gives you the primitive picture so that you can think for yourself that if you can survive in Kota or not (tells you about the various circumstances, mental pressure, environment).</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAlso, Read About:\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/9-indian-cricketer-who-married-to-bollywood-actresses/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Indian Cricketer Who Married to Hot Bollywood Actresses</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/abhishek-banerjee-casting-director-and-acting-journey/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The journey of Hathoda Tyagi or Abhishek Banerjee in Bollywood</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Top 10 Recent Bollywood Web Series You Should Watch','','publish','open','open','','top-10-recent-bollywood-web-series-you-should-watch','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/9-indian-cricketer-who-married-to-bollywood-actresses/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/','2020-12-26 13:37:16','2020-12-26 08:07:16','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1180',0,'post','',1),(1201,11,'2020-07-03 13:12:35','2020-07-03 07:42:35','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1202 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/paatal-lok.jpg\" alt=\"paatal lok 2020\" width=\"800\" height=\"560\" /></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Paatal Lok Review &amp; Rating:</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Paatal Lok is a new web series in Amazon prime. It is basically a crime thriller which is now much talked about today. Most of the people have already seen this series and gave it the rank 1 in the web series 2020. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The teaser of the Paatal Lok web series was released in the month of April on 27th while the trailer was out on 5th May. This story has come from the story of Tarun Tejpal\'s \' The story of My Assassins \' in the year 2010. </span>\r\n\r\n<strong>IMDb: 7.6/10\r\nTimes Of India: 4/5\r\nGoogle Rating: 4.1/5 or 82%</strong>\r\n<h2>Watch Paatal Lok Trailer:</h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cNwWMW4mxO8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>Writers, Directors &amp; Actors of Paatal Lok:</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1203 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/paatal-lok-director.jpg\" alt=\"paatal lok director\" width=\"896\" height=\"302\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this web series, some highly recommended stars have worked like Jaideep Ahlawat, Gul Panag, Neeraj Kabi, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/abhishek-banerjee-casting-director-and-acting-journey/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Abhishek Banerjee</a>, and  Swastika Mukherjee. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This web series has made its space in the<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-recent-bollywood-web-series-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> top 10 web series of Bollywood web series</a>. Sudip Sharma, Sagar Haveli, Hardik Mehta, and Gunjit Chopra have written this web series. Sudip Sharma was also the writer of the movie NH10 (2015). </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The directors of Paatal Lok are Avinash Arun, Projit Roy. Avinash has worked in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Masaan\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maasan (2015)</a>,  Drishyam (2015), and in many movies as a Cinematographer.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Anushka Sharma has directed this most famous web series 2020.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Structure &amp; Plot of Paatal Lok:</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1205 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/paatal-lok1.jpg\" alt=\"paatal lok\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The series begins with Hathi Ram Chaudhary where he tells his junior inspector Imraan Ansari, who worked under him on the irredeemable nature of every human being. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The world is divided into three parts, he told Ansari that, \" The Svarog Lok (called heaven) where the God\'s reside in the middle there is the \'Dharti Lok\' which is where men like Hathi Ram and Imraan live and at the bottom is the \'Paatal Lok\', the hell from which Vermin occasionally escape and wreak havoc above \"waise toh yeh Shastron mein likha tha, Par Maine WhatsApp pe padha.”</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If we talk about the word then Paatal Lok is like an old-fashioned, evocative word which means hell, the exact opposite of Swarg-Lok that means Heaven.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This series was set in rural Punjab, Chitrakoot, and Delhi. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The entire series is based on the three places of North-India. In this series Paatal Lok the director perfectly captured the wickedness of the capital city of Delhi like it shows the lush beauty of its NDMC avenues, the rustic charm of the government quarters, and the unspoken agreement that the area near Yamuna river is generally out of bounds.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Story Review of Paatal Lok:</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1204 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/paatal-lok-abkishek.jpg\" alt=\"paatal lok\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Four Suspects are hired for a conspiracy to murder. Their target is to murder a very famous and reputed news anchor at a Delhi National channel. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The character of news anchor Sanjeev Mehra is also interesting and Neeraj Kabi played the role very well. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At the outer Jamuna Paar police outpost, much to the chagrin of his Senior officer, Hathi Ram Chaudhary, the role was played by the versatile actor Jaideep Ahlawat, who is assigned the high profile case.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Episodes of Paatal Lok:</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This series has nine episodes, the story unfolds the two-levels of our society like the upper class and middle class. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While the first one shows the elite upper-class Delhi News anchor\'s world whose life deals with an anxiety-ridden and dog-loving wife. Her name is Dolly. Dolly is a Bengali girl and Bengali actress Swastika Mukherjee played this role. The character Sanjeev Mehra also deals with some power play of a newsroom. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another side that shows the middle-class Delhi family life where people faced many problems to lead their everyday life. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hathi Ram is a police officer but in his career, he did not get the proper o</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">pportunity in his workplace that proves his potentiality in his work. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hathi Ram doesn\'t catch a break, in his personal or professional life, but he earned the respect for his family and for his son. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though it is very slow starting from the second episode the series actually began. There are a lot of characters in this web series but the two characters attract audience attraction with their acting ability. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">