s, and violence corruption and power play at all levels. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When inspector Hathiram begins his investigation about the Sanjeev Mehra\'s attempt to murder case that took him to the darkest side of the paatal Lok web series. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the end, though he discovered the actual truth for some upper-level power play he did not disclose the actual truth before the public. </span>\r\n<h2><strong>Abhishek Banerjee, A Most Interesting Character:</strong></h2>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OlmRqB-c4S4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Abhishek Banerjee played another important role in this web series. Vishal Tyagi or Hathoda Tyagi is the main antagonist of the story. No one can do this character better than Abhishek. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He totally justified the character and also received appreciation and praise from the critics and audience also. He gained a huge fan base after this character. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview, Abhishek said,\" I never thought about this play that I would get to play in this amazing Series such a high- octane character so early in my life.\" </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Paatal Lok web series</strong> is an intense exploration of Indian Morality. It is the most successful web series in Amazon prime video. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So the bottom line is that if you want to watch any top latest web series then you can choose it.</span>\r\n<h2>Also, Read About:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/9-indian-cricketer-who-married-to-bollywood-actresses/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Indian Cricketer Who Married to Bollywood Actresses</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-sin