>The story will revolve around the Loki who escaped after the Battle of New-York during the time travel adventures in Endgame. In short, we will see the pure evil Loki. One who hasn’t turned towards the good guys.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Michael Waldron will serve as the showrunner for Loki, he previously worked as a writer and producer for the hit animated series Rick and Morty.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G4JuopziR3Q[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Early rumors also suggested that there would be more time travel in this series. But there is no such confirmation yet from the officials. Nonetheless, we are glad to see Hiddleston portray the role of his lifetime!</span>\r\n<h2><strong>7. What If…</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1290 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/what-if..-2021-min.jpg\" alt=\"what if.. 2021\" width=\"575\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Release date: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Summer 2021 (on Disney+)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The first-ever animated show produced by Marvel Studios. It is based on the What If… comic series. It will feature Jeffrey Wright as The Watcher, a member of a race of beings who watch the events of the MCU.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Each episode will focus on a different question, like ‘What if the Fantastic Four never got their powers’ or ‘What if Captain America wasn’t frozen in ice for 70 years’ and so on.</span>\r\n<h3>The First Look:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4iLVoEg9aLk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>8. Hawkeye</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1293 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/hawkeye-2021-marvel-min.jpg\" alt=\"what if.. 2021\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Release date: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Autumn 2021 (on Disney+)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This was the last show announced by Marvel at the San Diego Comic-Con 2019. It will also be released in Disney+ OTT platform and will feature Jeremy Renner as Hawkeye. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The series will focus on Clint Barton training a young sharpshooter Kate Bishop who later on takes the mantle of Hawkeye. It is reported that Kate Bishop will be played by Hailee Steinfield.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EcSOe5chlLY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>9. Thor: Love and Thunder</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1298 size-large\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Thor-Love-and-Thunder-min-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Love and Thunder\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Release date: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">11 February 2022</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chris Hemsworth is all set to feature in the fourth installment of Thor series. But this time there would be a major twist in the proceedings. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This time around, he will be handing over the Mjolnir to his former love interest Jane Foster, played by Natalie Portman. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Taika Waititi will return to direct the 4th installment after the major success of Thor: Ragnarok. Tessa Thompson will also reprise her role of Valkyrie, the queen of Asgard. Christian Bale is playing to star as an unannounced villain.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>10. Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1292 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Doctor-Strange-in-the-Multiverse-of-Madness-min.jpg\" alt=\"Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness\" width=\"1000\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Release date: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5 March 2022</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The sequel to the Benedict Cumberbatch starred Doctor Strange was also confirmed at San Diego Comic-Con 2019. Fans were surprised to know that Wanda Maximoff will be the sidekick of Doctor Strange this time. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The plot is speculating to be around events follow in the WandaVision series. There would be a concept of alternate universes and time travel. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, it is speculated that there would be massive destruction in the universe which Strange will apparently try to fix.</span>\r\n\r\nAlso Read:\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-pick-of-hollywood-tv-web-series/\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood TV/ Web Series</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/black-widow-2020-film/\">Black Widow (2020 film) | Latest News, Trailer, and Release Date</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','What’s Next in Marvel Series | Movies and Release Date','','publish','open','open','','whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/black-widow-2020-film/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-pick-of-hollywood-tv-web-series/','2021-01-17 10:32:14','2021-01-17 05:02:14','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1276',0,'post','',0),(1302,5,'2020-07-07 11:15:15','2020-07-07 05:45:15','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The entire world has been hit by the novel coronavirus or Covid-19 and the tremors have capacitated almost each and every industry. Even the Bollywood industry is one of them. India has been affected drastically as this has led to the slowdown of people\'s lives.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Considering the vast stretch of the effects, Bollywood has likewise been thumped.  The closure of movie theatres has restricted the release of the upcoming movies which were normally going to land soon and crash the box office.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generally, a huge Bollywood movie spends somewhere around Rs 15-20 crores whereas a medium to small budgeted movie keeps it to Rs 5 crores exclusively for its publicity.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Considering the very structure, quite a bunch of moviemakers was taking a gulp of the loss.</span>\r\n<h2><b>SOME EXAMPLES OF HOW BOLLYWOOD HAS BEEN SHAKEN:</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rohit Shetty\'s Sooryavanshi, featuring Akshay Kumar, Ajay Devgn, Ranveer, and Katrina recently launched its trailer with much pomp and show but has pushed the release of the film till further notice.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1305 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/sooryavanshi.jpg\" alt=\"Sooryavanshi bollywood coronavirus\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">83, a sports biopic depicting the life of the legendary coach Kapil Dev, who made India hold the 1983 cricket World Cup, featuring the reel and real-life power couple Ranveer and Deepika playing Dev &amp; his wife, directed by Kabir Khan. </span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie was all in to land on 10 April but lockdown put a hold to it. To this Kabir Khan spoke, </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We’re really ti</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ngling to exhibit the movie to the entire world. But some things are way greater than all this.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1303 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/83-movie.jpg\" alt=\"83 movie bollywood coronavirus\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Today, the whole planet is on standstill, so I believe watching a film comes to be a much downward priority.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">”</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brahm%C4%81stra_(film)\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bhramastra</a>, a multi-star mega-movie, was in the final gear to announce the launch on 10 December, but due to the virus, the schedule was called off. The movie now stands still.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1304 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bharamastra.jpg\" alt=\"Bhramastra bollywood coronavirus\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is roundabout a loss of Rs. 900 Crores that have been foreseen but the actual loss could go way beyond the limits.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Movies existing in the theatres have witnessed a fierce drop in viewership and the film that suffered the most was Tiger Shroff\'s Baaghi 3.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>HOW IS BOLLYWOOD COPING UP WITH THE VIRUS?</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The pandemic has spread its clutches multiple folds. However, this does not limit the biggest entertainment source in India from catching up with their audiences.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A banger, “Angrezi Medium”, starring Irrfan Khan, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Radhika Madaan, and Deepak Dobriyal, challenged the virus spread by going ahead with its release.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1307\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"640\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1307 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/angrezi-medium-min.jpg\" alt=\"angrezi medium bollywood coronavirus\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /> bollywood coronavirus[/caption]\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many moviemakers have resorted to releasing their movies through tie-ups with OTT platforms. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gulabo Sitabo</a> featuring Aayushmaan Khurana and Amitabh Bachchan was released over Amazon Prime on 12th June 2020 and received appreciation all over.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recently, a launch of around 7 movies was declared over Disney Plus Hotstar featuring some megastars of Bollywood. The audience is eagerly waiting for those to drop.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1309 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/new-movies.jpg\" alt=\"new movies\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h2><b>WILL THIS ACTUALLY LEAD TO A SHIFT FROM MOVIE SCREENS TO PHONES?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We guess no. Indians have always loved cinema, and they will always come what may. Movies in themselves prove to be a very popular and impactful medium. It is one of the most easily accessible forms of entertainment.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As far as India\'s movie industry is concerned, it has been flourishing endlessly for decades. The main factor associated is the affordability of cinema in the country. From the very beginning, Indian cinema has made films easily accessible to a wider public base.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1308 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/cinema-to-ott-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"cinema to ott\" width=\"661\" height=\"372\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coming to popularity; Bollywood has gained a massive fan following in the West, showcasing the evolution of Indian cinema. From being looked down upon to actually being appreciated(3 Idiots), to receiving a standing ovation at Cannes (Masaan, Gangs of Wasseypur), Indian cinema has traveled a long way.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, it might take quite a lot of time to get the audience crowd back to normal, but, possibilities always exist, and we hope we get to go to theatres soon!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comment below and tell us do you agree? Also, how long do you think the virus is going to exist in our lives? Share it with your friends and family and let us know your thoughts.</span>\r\n\r\nIf you liked the post of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">The Tv Freak</a>, then please share it with Friends. Stay tuned for more movie updates.\r\n<h2>Read More:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marvel Series: Next 10 Movies</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-pick-of-hollywood-tv-web-series/\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood TV/ Web Series</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/black-widow-2020-film/\">Black Widow (2020 film) | Latest News, Trailer, and Release Date</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Bollywood Industry Slammed by the Virus','','publish','open','open','','bollywood-industry-slammed-by-the-virus','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/black-widow-2020-film/','2020-12-26 13:16:00','2020-12-26 07:46:00','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1302',0,'post','',0),(1317,6,'2020-07-08 19:56:11','2020-07-08 14:26:11','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1326 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/sonu-sood-in-lock-down-min.jpg\" alt=\"sonu sood in lock down\" width=\"597\" height=\"430\" /></h2>\r\n<h2>Overview Of The Pandemic</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Right after the first case of coronavirus was detected in the month of February, the spread of the virus in the country took a great spread with over 6 Lakh cases presently. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maharashtra is the worst-hit state by the pandemic. Thousands of daily wage workers, especially the people who come to work in the capital  ‘Mumbai’ became jobless.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So they started to retreat to their hometowns but most of them had no option but to start with walking as the majority of transportation means was shut down due to the Nationwide lockdown from March 25.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Sonu Sood coming into action to help others</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Actor Sonu Sood started his public work by distributing cooked food to homeless people and providing them with essential protective items like hand Sanitizers and facial masks.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1325 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/people-going-home-in-corona-virus-min.jpg\" alt=\"people going home in corona virus\" width=\"614\" height=\"345\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When Sone was distributing these pieces of stuff to needy people then a woman came to him and asked him to give double food and fruits because they have to travel so long by foot. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sonu Sood was shocked and asked her about this matter. Then she told him that there are no buses, trains or any kind of transport, she has to go so long on foot with her children. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sonu Sood told her to stay there he will arrange something, then she said that she was not alone there are hundreds of people like her.</span>\r\n\r\nThis was a shock for Sonu Sood. Then he decided that he will do something for them and send them to their home. He has to take lots of approvals for this process.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1324 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/sonu-sood-during-corona-virus-min.jpg\" alt=\"sonu sood during corona virus\" width=\"595\" height=\"428\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the above two photos, he is seen waving off the Busses arranged by Sonu Sood to take the migrant workers to their hometown(especially workers from Bihar and Uttar Pradesh).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> He also wishes them Good Luck so that their journey is smooth and safe.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Sone sent the first bus<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on May 11 which carried approximately a batch of 200 people.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He made a deep impact in the heart of his fans when he funded the Chartered flight to carry the textile workers stranded in Kerela to their home state.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>What Motivated Sonu Sood?</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview with BBC, Sood told that he got Goosebumps when he visualized the condition of the migrant workers walking hundreds of kilometres especially women with children. And many of them died while walking long distances in the scorching heat without food.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Sood in an interview with “</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Economic Times” </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> told that the sole reason of why he started “</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ghar bhejo Project”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> was he did not want any of the migrants to go to their places by walking “</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">koi bhi chal ke na Jaye”.</span></i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Even the Rains can’t stop this superhero from coming out and helping the migrants. ❣️Keep inspiring us sir <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SonuSood?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@SonuSood</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/ug6ccF21yj\">pic.twitter.com/ug6ccF21yj</a></p>\r\n— yogesh bhateja (@yogesh_fitness) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/yogesh_fitness/status/1275320382992474112?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 23, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, he stated that the project started with him and his friend Miss Priety Goel did have many contributions. People contributed by funding many buses of migrants workers, some used to fund the food for the migrant workers, some provided water facility.</span></li>\r\n <li>177 Migrant Workers were without hope In Kerala then Sonu Sood Airlifted them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAecYHzhXH8[/embedyt]\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The final answer,” It is the smiles of the poor helpless migrant workers that lights the fire inside me and boost my energy high to help the needy ones”- Sonu Sood.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to a data Sood’s </span><b>“Ghar Bhejo Project” </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">has helped up to more than 30,000 </span>Stranded people.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><b>Criticism of  Sonu’s Social Service-</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Despite doing great work for the homeless migrants,  MP from Maharashtra Sanjay Raut alleged that the social work of Sonu Sood saying that he is having a political director from behind.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout, What did Sanjay Raut said:</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CX4T_gONy-E[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=keXpCiDACzw[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, on a reply to MP Sanjay Raut Sood said that </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">-</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Everybody has an opinion and it is his opinion. The clear intention is that people are getting home.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Appreciation of Sonu’s work-</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Celebrities like <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kangana_Ranaut\">Kangana Ranaut</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akshay_Kumar\">Akshay Kumar</a> have appreciated Sood’s work.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Famous celebrity chef Mr Vikas Khanna named a dish after’s Sonu Sood birthplace.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Dear <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SonuSood?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@SonuSood</a> everyday you are inspiring us.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Can’t cook for you right now in appreciation of your work.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">So sending you a dish Im going to name “MOGA” after your birthplace. ❤️<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Respect?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Respect</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RealHero?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#RealHero</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/F7D61AfrgN\">pic.twitter.com/F7D61AfrgN</a></p>\r\n— Vikas Khanna (@TheVikasKhanna) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheVikasKhanna/status/1262830776342716416?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 19, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We should take inspiration from Sonu Sood and help the needy ones. Do comment down below and feel free to share your views.</span>\r\n\r\nAlso Read:\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/bollywood-industry-slammed-by-the-virus/\">Bollywood vs Corona Virus</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marvel Series: Next 10 Movies</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-pick-of-hollywood-tv-web-series/\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood TV/ Web Series</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Unstoppable Sonu Sood | Helping Migrants in Coronavirus','','publish','open','open','','unstoppable-sonu-sood-helping-migrants-in-coronavirus','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/bollywood-industry-slammed-by-the-virus/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/','2020-12-05 23:47:35','2020-12-05 18:17:35','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1317',0,'post','',0),(1328,6,'2020-07-09 22:43:03','2020-07-09 17:13:03','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1699 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/nepotism-in-bollywood-min.jpg\" alt=\"nepotism in bollywood\" width=\"600\" height=\"314\" /></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is Nepotism?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For all the viewers who don’t know what  Nepotism is here is a short description ---Nepotism is the practice to promote the relative or friend of the person who is in power. To understand in just one word, it is </span><b>“</b> <b>Favouritism”.</b>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nepotism in Bollywood</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nepotism is not a new phenomenon in Bollywood. It’s coming from decades in this industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Despite the Hardships of a few artists who did not have a Godfather in Bollywood,  they ( like Shahrukh Khan,  Late <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\">Sushant Singh Rajput</a>) have made big fame like the shining stars in the sky. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But this hardship of actors ( who do not have a Godfather or any link in the Bollywood) is slowing down due to an increase in the Nepotism Factor.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The recent rise of “Nepotism” in news</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-954 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Shushant-Singh-Rajput-life-movies-photo1.jpg\" alt=\"Shushant-Singh-Rajput - Nepotism\" width=\"451\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Recently the Nepotism factor in Bollywood ignited after the demise of the famous actor Sushant Singh Rajput.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Just after his death fans trolled in fame celebrities for Nepotism and promoting their favourites. People trolled Some of the celebrities like Karan Johar, Alia Bhatt,  Sonakshi Sinha, Ananya Pandey, and many others.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>The reaction of Bollywood Celebrities</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1341 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/nepotish-in-bollywood.jpg\" alt=\"nepotism in Bollywood | Kangana Ranaut\" width=\"575\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indian Actress, Kangana Ranaut raised and expressed her views on the “ Koffee with Karan show” wher</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">e she called Karan Johar a </span><b>“movie mafia” </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and alleged him that he is promoting Nepotism.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D3qD51clUxk[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> She spoke about this topic on a TV show named </span><b>“ Anupam Kher’s People”</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WF8WDdSyNOI[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"justify\">\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a recent talk with a journalist, The Nawab of the Industry- Saif Ali Khan commented that- he was also a victim of Nepotism for which fans trolled him highly.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1342 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/saif-ali-khan-sonakshi.jpg\" alt=\"saif ali khan sonakshi - Nepotism\" width=\"575\" height=\"350\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Recently Actress Sonakshi Sinha quitted twitter with a reason that she wanted to stay away from negativity. But Getting Trolled for nepotism continuously can also be a burning reason for her quitting.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indian Actress </span><b>Taapsee Pannu</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in a recent interview with the Indian news channel “Republic World” expressed her views on nepotism.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most of the viewers purchase the movie tickets if that particular film is launching a star kid. But when it comes to launching an artist who is not from the Bollywood background i.e an outsider then viewers buy tickets based on recent reviews of the movie or some words of appreciation from someone for the movie.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She also stated that some media networks only cover the work of  Star kids in a majority rather than covering other actors who do or have done some better work than those star kids.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  Famous Actor Anupam Kher also talked about it. He said about criticizing when he was starting his career in Bollywood. But he also spoked some lines which are an inspiration for the budding actors-</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1DibF4z80o[/embedyt]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Legendary Bollywood Singer Kumar Sanu in talking with the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bombaytimes </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">spoke about nepotism,  He said that Nepotism is everywhere, in Bollywood industry it is more and in other industries, it is quite a bit less compared to Bollywood.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H6TLDt2U3rE[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>What Bollywood Actors say on Nepotism openly?</h2>\r\n<h3>REAL TRUTH OF FILM AWARDS</h3>\r\n<h4><b>Emraan Hashmi on Nepotism</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emraan_Hashmi\">Emraan Hashmi</a> said in an interview boldly that,”  I wouldn’t have been an actor if my uncle Mahesh Bhatt hadn’t been there.</span>\r\n<h4><b>Ranvir Shorey on Nepotism</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The famous who has made many parts in several films put allegations on the Film Award Functions. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ranvir_Shorey\">Ranvir Shorey</a> said once in an award function a star kid was awarded the prize and that too the personalities who presented the award were the star kid’s parents. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can go and check out his twitter-</span>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">This actually unfolded on a popular Bollywood awards show:</p>\r\nA star kid is co-hosting the show. They announce the next category - Best Actor. The nominees are played out, and the star kid is one of the nominees. Surprise-surprise!\r\n\r\n— Ranvir Shorey (@RanvirShorey) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RanvirShorey/status/1272791941206257672?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 16, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<h4><b>Ayushmaan Khurrana</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ayushmann commented that if Nepotism hadn’t been there I would have definitely made my debut earlier i.e. at the age of 22.  </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though he made his debut at the age of 27.</span>\r\n<h4>Kangana Ranaut</h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finally, the Crackdown when Kangana Ranaut on a TV show “Aapki Adalat with Rajat Sharma”  commented upon The Film Awards. She said that the film awards show is not all worth it because in Bollywood pre-decide awards are there and it’s all for the TRP. </span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cm29nrskTQ0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do feel free to share your views in the comment section - <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">The Tv Freak</a></span>\r\n<h2>Read More:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marvel Series: Next 10 Movies</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-pick-of-hollywood-tv-web-series/\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood TV/ Web Series</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/black-widow-2020-film/\">Black Widow (2020 film) | Latest News, Trailer, and Release Date</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Nepotism and Favouritism in Bollywood | Star Kids Vs Outsiders','','publish','open','open','','nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date/','2020-12-26 13:16:52','2020-12-26 07:46:52','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1328',0,'post','',0),(1330,4,'2020-07-11 18:39:59','2020-07-11 13:09:59','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1365 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iron-man-last-scene-end-game-min-1024x665.jpg\" alt=\"iron man last scene end game-min\" width=\"730\" height=\"474\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When Thanos snapped his fingers at the end of Avengers: Infinity War, almost all that was beloved to Iron Man was taken away from him. Tony Stark, which would be his true name then fought back to snap his own fingers at the end of Avengers: Endgame. But this snap resulted in him being taken away from everyone who loved him. Including us. </span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_anDMGmck-k[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Billionaire, Playboy, Genius, Philanthropist that he so confidently called himself, was one of the favourites for fans all over. As noted in stories such as Spiderman: Far From Home, the death of the Superhero was mourned and took a toll on everyone.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1363 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iron-man-fans1-min.jpg\" alt=\"iron man fans1-min\" width=\"680\" height=\"441\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2KcrcCOBjiU[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So the question remains. Will Iron Man return? Will Tony Stark return? All the fans all over are sitting fingers crossed hoping for a miracle for him to return. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Read ahead to find out whether he would be returning to the MCU. And if so, in what manner would he be returning?</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Will Tony Stark be back?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The simple answer is yes. Tony Stark will return to the MCU in one way or another. Now it’s a question of how. There have been a variety of reports suggesting he would be returning for future Marvel movies. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One way in which he could is with cameo appearances across the various movies that would be coming out. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giving appearances in a manner similar to Nick Fury with flashbacks to previous unseen events that have taken place.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Tony Stark’s return confirmed?</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1364 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/the-Grandmaster-thor-rang-rock-min.jpg\" alt=\"the Grandmaster thor rang rock-min\" width=\"749\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jeff Goldblum, who plays the Grandmaster in Thor: Ragnarock recently confirmed via a Buzzfeed interview that Tony Stark would be returning in the Marvel ‘What if’ series. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This news came as a shock to many who did not expect his return to the Marvel Cinematic Universe. Especially, after his character in Avengers: Endgame sacrificed his life.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is “What if”?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-in-marvel-series-movies-and-release-date/\">There are lots of movies gonna come to MARVEL</a>. Marvel has confirmed a new Disney+ series called “What if” that would be a part of a series of shows that they are creating. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alongside ‘Wanda-Vision’ and ‘The Falcon and the Winter Soldier’, ‘What if’ will complete the original trio of shows announced. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The show is said to be an animated universe of different and various possible scenarios that could have been different. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It has been confirmed that Robert Downey Jr. would be returning to give the voice over for the Iron Man character that would be featuring in that series.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1290 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/what-if..-2021-min.jpg\" alt=\"what if.. 2021\" width=\"575\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jeff Goldblum mentioned that he had played the character of Grandmaster once again recently. He had said that he had done so for an episode for the show ‘What if’. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He mentioned that it\'s an animated show comprising of all of our favourite characters and that the episode he mentioned consisted of the Grandmaster and Iron man as well. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The ‘What if’ show is based on the Marvel Comic that is of the same name. The series will consist of each episode with a separate storyline based on an alternate reality in the universe.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Iron Man 4 in the works?</strong></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-xMtOBSBAI[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Robert Downey Jr. appeared on the Ellen show and Ellen immediately questioned about his return to the MCU. And whether there is another Iron Man movie in the works. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The question came after several reports came out mentioning that Iron Man 4 is going to be a part of the next batch of movies.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The deadline also questioned the star asking him about the rumour. The rumour had mentioned that he would only make another Iron Man movie only if Mel Gibson would direct the movie. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To which the actor responded positively. While it was taken on as some light-hearted talk from the start, it gave hope that he would be willing to return in the future.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Tony Stark may not but will Iron Man return?</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1366 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/spiderman-as-iron-man-min.jpg\" alt=\"spiderman as iron man-min\" width=\"699\" height=\"393\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In Spiderman: Far From Home, the entire premise revolved around who would take up the mantle of Iron Man after Tony Stark’s death. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A character of Iron Man’s power and ability needs to be present to inspire and help the world with the work that he does. The movies have teased the idea of the mantle of Iron Man being based on ahead to other characters. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tony’s best friend and army general ‘James Rhodes’ has a suit similar to his to be War Machine.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1368 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/James-Rhodes-as-iron-man-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"717\" height=\"466\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In Avengers Endgame Pepper Potts, Tony’s wife also has a suit with the name ‘Rescue’ to be comic accurate. Endgame also teased his daughter wearing the ‘Rescue’ helmet as well. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tony removes off her head immediately. It could be taken as a hint as to her eventually taking up the mantle of Iron Man or maybe ‘Iron Woman’ as in her case in the eventual possible future.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1367 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/pepper-potts-as-iron-man-min.jpg\" alt=\"pepper potts as iron man-min\" width=\"679\" height=\"382\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During the funeral scene in Endgame, the presence of the kid ‘Harley Keener’ with whom Tony develops a bond during ‘<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iron_Man_3\" rel=\"nofollow\">Iron Man 3</a>’. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It could be a tease of the fact that he is going to be the next person to take up the mantle. Which would make sense, considering Tony nurtured his talent and helped him be the person he is.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1369 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iron-man-3-min.jpg\" alt=\"iron man 3-min\" width=\"676\" height=\"380\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So what next for Iron Man?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For now, there has been no official word as to the return neither Iron Man nor Tony Stark. We have to fell good with his return in ‘What if’ for the time being. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are several possibilities with which either him or the mantle of Iron Man to return. What are your thoughts on the return of Iron Man? Do you know any other way in which he could return? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Give us your thoughts in the comment section below!</span>\r\n<h2>Read More:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/how-powerful-is-captain-america-marvel/\">How Powerful is Captain America | Marvel</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/whats-next-