0;\">Release Date: July 10, 2020</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Platform: Amazon Prime Video</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star cast: Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram Malhotra</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breath season one was an outstanding thriller that showcased R Madhavan as a loving father and a serial killer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The plot was concluded, and hence the makers have come up with a different story this time, with Vikram Malhotra as the drunk cop.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With this, the Junior Big B, Abhishek Bachchan will make his debut on the digital platform. And that\'s why he would be the central character around whom the story will revolve. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This suspense psychological thriller is definitely something you don’t want to miss.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nxE-k2MLQIA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>The Family Man 2</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1432 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/5-min.jpg\" alt=\"The Family Man 2\" width=\"820\" height=\"532\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Release Date: October 2020</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Cast: Manoj Bajpayee, Samantha Akkineni</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the career-best performances of Manoj Bajpayee was the Amazon Prime Original, ‘The Family Man’. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It revolved around a RAW agent, who has to balance between fighting terrorist but also leading a normal life as a caring husband and loving father. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">W</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">hat follows is an out to out action series, with ample comedy and witty acting which would leave a lasting impression on the audience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Family Man season one ended on a major cliff-hanger and hence fans all over the world are waiting for the makers to release season 2 at once. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bajpayee promised everyone that the sequel would be even bigger and better than the initial and would take the series to a whole another level.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>A Married Woman</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1430 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4-min.jpg\" alt=\"A Married Woman\" width=\"820\" height=\"532\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Platform: ALT Balaji &amp; Zee 5</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Cast: Ridhi Dogra and Monica Dogra</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Based on the acclaimed novel by Manju Kapur, ‘A Married Woman’ follows an unconventional love story between two women in the era of 1992. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It showcases a blend of love, spirituality, and sexuality at times when inter-caste marriages were regarded as shameful. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This love story will focus on the difficult and challenging times faced by both the women as they come from different religions and different beliefs but fall for each other.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZdKeNhPG58[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>Hostages 2</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1429 size-large\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-1024x665.jpg\" alt=\"Hostages 2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"665\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Release Date: 2020</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Platform: Disney+ Hotstar</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">‘Hostages’ was fast-paced and brilliantly executed. It had Tisca Chopra and Ronit Roy in the first season who gave their best to make the series loved by the audience. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The series was directed by Sudhir Mishra who hinted at another season in making. Since there was no cliff-hanger at the finale of the series, it is rumoured that the makers will venture into a different story-line with some new characters and a new scenario. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whatever it may be, one thing is for sure. The series will be a perfect blend of suspense thriller and perfect direction.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Masaba Masaba</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1431 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-min.jpg\" alt=\"Masaba Masaba\" width=\"820\" height=\"532\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Platform: Netflix</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Cast: Masaba Gupta</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaba Masaba is a Netflix documentary-style web series that focuses on the life of designer Masaba Gupta. Also, It focuses on her early days and trying to juggle between her tough job and supporting her family in fulfilling her passion for fashion designing. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaba went on to launch her own enchanting label. And collaborating with India’s top designers and models. Her products are one of the kind, and she has created a perfect unique niche for herself.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaba Gupta will play herself in this Netflix web series, where we would find out about her journey and her early life as an entrepreneur besides this, it gonna be a self-made web series on herself.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Bandish Bandits</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1436 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Bandish Bandits\" width=\"574\" height=\"373\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Platform: Amazon Prime Video</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Cast: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naseeruddin_Shah\" rel=\"nofollow\">Naseeruddin Shah</a>, Atul Kulkarni</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bandish Bandits on paper seems to be a smashing hit. Even before dropping the trailer, the series has generated fans who are waiting desperately to witness veteran Naseeruddin Shah in his first-ever web series. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He will be joined by another prolific Marathi actor Atul Kulkarni whom fans might remember from ‘The Gazi Attack’. The talking point for the series, however, is the music that would be composed by none other than the majestic trio, Shankar-Ehsaan-Loy.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maneesh Sharma will direct Bandish Bandit, who directed gem of a movie ‘Band Baja Baraat’ back in 2010.</span>\r\n<h3>Read more interesting articles:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top 10 Pick of Hollywood Franchises You Should Watch Before Die</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Best Upcoming Indian/Hindi Web Series 2020','','publish','open','open','','best-upcoming-indian-hindi-web-series-2020','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/a-top-10-pick-of-hollywood-franchises-you-should-watch/','2020-12-26 13:23:09','2020-12-26 07:53:09','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1332',0,'post','',0),(1334,4,'2020-07-10 23:46:41','2020-07-10 18:16:41','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1347 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-min.jpg\" alt=\"Captain America\" width=\"717\" height=\"466\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When it comes to Marvel characters, one of the names always at the tip of everyone’s tongue is Captain Steve Rogers. Also known as Captain America. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our favourite American Patriot has retired in the Marvel Cinematic Universe with the conclusion in Avengers Endgame. But exactly how powerful was the American war hero? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Was he the most powerful of them all? Read ahead to find out the extremity of his ability based on the movies and comics as well.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Captain America Attributes</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Complete name: <strong>Steve Rogers</strong>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aliases: Captain America\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Height: 6’2”\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Eye Colour: Blue\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First Appearance in Comics: Captain America Comics #1 (1941)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First Appearance in Movies: Captain America - The First Avenger (2011)</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">the</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">origin</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">of</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">his</span> Captain America <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">powers?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Steve Rogers is the son of a War Veteran, he was, unfortunately, a weak and frail kid. Always inspired to be a part of the Army like his father, he enrolled several times but was unable to get in. His weak physique always the source of his downfall. Professor Abraham Erskine found this weak young man and saw the good heart that resided in him. He enlisted him for Project Rebirth, which was to use the Super Soldier Serum to help fight the war.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1353\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-begining.jpg\" alt=\"Captain America begining\" width=\"655\" height=\"426\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The good that resided in Steve won him over and was the recipient of the Serum which enhanced him in all possible ways. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The weeks of tests that were conducted to check for the good in him had borne fruit. He was now as powerful as they came. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Immediately being instrumental in the War, helping millions. Which as we realize, is the mere beginning of his adventure.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F020aNi0wS0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><strong>What are Captain America\'s known powers?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While Captain America isn’t superhuman, he is as strong a human can possibly be and even stronger as well. Ability wise he has agility, strength, speed, and endurance among several others greater than any Olympic athlete that we’ve ever known. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The super soldier enhanced all of his abilities to an extremely great level. Notably, the serum has resulted in him not having as much fatigue. Giving him extraordinary levels of Endurance.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kknc1HFkoZg[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He has mastered the American fighting forms of Judo and Boxing along with his own unique fighting style. The combination of all of these skills makes him a worthy adversary indeed. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While he is extraordinary as compared to a regular human he has human vulnerabilities as well. Although, his immunity to diseases is extraordinary.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>What is his choice of Weapon?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We always relate Captain Steve Rogers to the Shield that he carries into every battle. He has had the shield from Day 1 of being Captain America. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The shield is made of Vibranium and carries the symbolic star and stripes of Captain America to this day. The design and creation credits have to be given to Howard Stark, the father of our beloved Iron Man, Tony Stark. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vibranium is one of the strongest metals present on Earth makes it a very strong and durable weapon for a man of his calibre to carry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the comics, the shield is made from a combination of Vibranium and Adamantium (the metal of which Wolverine’s claws are made of). </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Due to the unique nature of its creation, the shield was not ever made again as it was not possible. It was later awarded to Captain America at the start of his career by the government.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1350\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-with-thor-hammer-2-min.jpg\" alt=\"Captain with thor hammer 2\" width=\"529\" height=\"529\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then comes Thor’s magic hammer Mjolnir. Odin, Thor’s father curses the hammer that only the worthy may be able to lift it and wield the power of the hammer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As we see in Avengers Endgame and two instances in the comics, Captain America lifts the hammer and is one of the few characters worthy of lifting the magical hammer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We see him pick up the hammer and fight the final battle alongside the other Avengers against Thanos. In a similar instance, he picks up the hammer in the comics in the finale of the fear event and wrecks havoc across the battlefield.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Who are the strongest people he has fought?</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1349\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-vs-iron-man-min.jpg\" alt=\"Captain vs iron man\" width=\"695\" height=\"391\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When considering the Marvel Cinematic Universe, Captain America has had some memorable battles. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether the intervention between Iron Man and Thor in the first Avengers movie when the three iconic characters on the screen together for the first-ever time. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Or the battle with Iron Man at the end of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_Civil_War\" rel=\"nofollow\">Captain America: Civil War</a> when he battles Iron Man alongside Bucky Barnes.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1348\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-vs-iron-man-suit-broken-min.jpg\" alt=\" iron man suit broken\" width=\"702\" height=\"395\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZr2AEw3dos[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Again in that battle, Captain America comes out on top defeating Iron Man with relative ease. We have to even consider the battle he had with Thanos at the end of Avengers Endgame in which he fought tooth and nail in order to defeat Thanos. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His ability to wield the Mjolnir and use his shield to fight Thanos when all hope was lost was tremendous. His ability to be willing to take on the entire army by himself fighting the battle he had to is an inspiration to all of us.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1351\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Captain-America-with-thor-hammer-min.jpg\" alt=\" thor hammer\" width=\"691\" height=\"389\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B3dPoo_Yn8w[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But when considering the entire Marvel Universe, the strongest person that Cap would have defeated would have to be Spider-Man.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> If there is any marvel hero that has managed to beat almost anyone that has come along it is Spider-Man. He has fought and defeated the X-Men, Dr Doom, The Hulk, and Silver Surfer just to name a few. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And for Captain America to have held his own against him would say a lot. But not just hold his own, rather when it has mattered Captain America has managed to get the better of Spidey and won several battles.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, is</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">he</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">the</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">strongest</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marvel</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Character?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So what do we know now? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Captain America has proved himself to be one of the strongest characters in Marvel. And then you add to it the fact that he has defeated the strongest Marvel character there is in Spiderman. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So then it is safe to suggest that Captain America is the strongest character on Marvel’s roster.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What do you think? Is Captain America the strongest one around? Who is your favourite among Captain America and Iron man? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comment below and let us know your thoughts as well! -