e=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 8</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Netflix, Amazon Prime</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast: Benedict Cumberbatch, Keira Knightley </b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bring in mathematics into a war and is what you will get in this movie. Alan Turing, the famous British mathematician with a team of other mathematicians joins the cryptography team. With the help of his team, he creates a machine to help them break down the german codes being transmitted during the war. This <strong>Science and mathematics movie</strong> has a fan following like none of the movies yet.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nuPZUUED5uk[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are there any such <strong>inspirational science and mathematics movies</strong> that we have missed out on? What are your <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\"><strong>favorite movies</strong></a> in this genre? Let us know in the comment section below!</span>\r\n\r\n</div>','Science and Mathematics Movies Based on Real Life','','publish','open','open','','science-and-mathematics-movies-based-on-real-life','','','2021-01-24 09:10:00','2021-01-24 03:40:00','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1666',0,'post','',1),(1721,3,'2020-07-28 22:36:46','2020-07-28 17:06:46','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Raksha Bandhan is the only occasion that gives us an opportunity to celebrate with our first partners-in-crime, our siblings. You might be curious to know how Bollywood Stars Raksha Bandhan Celebration happens.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> It is seen that the brother gets a Rakhi tied by his sister and in return, the sister receives tons of protection, “Raksha”, and also various gifts. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While the buzz around