 on a personal note, it was joyful for the actor even more as his son Zain Kapoor celebrated his first Raksha Bandhan with his elder sister Misha Kapoor. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The couple Shahid and Meera celebrated the Rakhi Festival by having relatives over and organizing a small party in the house. </span>\r\n<h2><b>5) Bachchan Family</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1725 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"609\" height=\"390\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Two generations of Bachchans always come together to celebrate the Rakhi Festival. Abhishek Bachchan celebrates the festival with his sibling Shweta Bachchan Nanda. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While Shweta’s son, Agastya Nanda gets a rakhi tied by Aradhya Bachchan, daughter of Abhishek Bachchan and Aishwarya Rai Bachchan. Navya Naveli Nanda, daughter of Shweta Bachchan Nanda is also present at the auspicious festival. </span>\r\n<h2><b>4) The Sanon Sisters</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1726 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kriti Sanon and Nupur Sanon end up tying Rakhis to each other every year with a vow to protect each other. It’s a common practice for them from childhood as they don’t have any brother to tie the rakhi. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They also shower each other with gifts and take loads of selfies. Nupur aspires to be an actor and always takes tips from her sister Kriti Sanon.</span>\r\n<h2><b>3) The Little Deshmukh\'s</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1727 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/5-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"663\" height=\"424\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ritesh Deshmukh is the father of two sons, namely Riaan and Rahyl. They both celebrate their Raksha Bandhan with their cousins. This group is often called The Little Deshmukh\'s. One sister Diviyaana showered with gifts from her five brothers Avir, Vansh, Avan, Riaan, and Rahyl. </span>\r\n<h2><b>2) Deepika Padukone and her Bodyguard</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1728 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6-min-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"630\" height=\"403\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Deepika is known to set new trends in Bollywood. Since her debut in Om Shanti Om, Deepika has risen to become the <strong>highest-rated actresses in Bollywood</strong>. Last year, Deepika started a new tradition on Rakhi by tying it to her Bodyguard Jalal. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It paid tribute to all the male figures who had supported her and protected her in the journey of becoming an actress. </span>\r\n<h2><b>1) The Mom-daughter pair</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1722 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/7-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"678\" height=\"434\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Hassan family has always been in the limelight in the south industry. But last year in the 2019 celebrations of Raksha Bandhan, Shruti Hassan made headlines as she tied Rakhi to her mom Sarika. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sarika recommended it after questioning the power of two women protecting each other. This is the best example of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Women%27s_empowerment\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>women empowerment</strong></a> shown by the Hassan family. </span>\r\n\r\nSo this is all about <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bollywood Stars Raksha Bandhan Celebration \"Happy Raksha Badhan 2020\"</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who according to you are the best brother-sister pair of Bollywood? What are you planning to do for your siblings or cousins this <strong>Raksha Bandhan</strong>? Write down to us in the comment section below!</span>\r\n<h3>Also Read:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/bollywood-actors-ranking-as-per-their-net-worth/\">Who is the richest in Bollywood? The answer is also Unpredictable too.</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\">The struggle of Shushant Life, You should know about it.</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Bollywood Stars Raksha Bandhan Celebration | See Pics','','publish','open','open','','bollywood-stars-raksha-bandhan-celebration-see-pics','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/bollywood-actors-ranking-as-per-their-net-worth/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/','2020-12-26 13:00:39','2020-12-26 07:30:39','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=1721',0,'post','',0),(1747,4,'2020-07-30 00:02:29','2020-07-29 18:32:29','<div align=\"justify\">\r\n\r\nTerrorism is one of the modern world\'s biggest problems. In the memories of each of us, there are difficult memories about having read, seen, or experienced an act of terror. Terrorism movies show that all.\r\n\r\nWith the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-13-war-movies-based-on-real-stories/\">battle</a> between such terror groups and the people of the world continuing for so many years. There have been attacks on hotels and towers that have had planes crashed into them. Here is a <strong>list of top terrorism films</strong>.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What have been the movies that have been able to show the sorrow, horror, and dread that goes through the minds of each person experiencing along with the onlookers? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Read on ahead to find out the <strong>most popular terrorism movies</strong> that have done so in the best manner and shocked the world. These movies show the real face of humanity and you will find yourself living in hell. These movies will motivate you to do something for humanity, Nation, or yourself. </span>\r\n<h2><b>11) Hotel Mumbai (2019)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1751 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Hotel Mumbai (2019) Terrorism Movies\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 8.1</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Not yet available</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Dev Patel, Anupam Kher, Amandeep Singh</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the best popular and recent terrorism movies! With their back against the walls, what were the staff of the Taj Hotel supposed to do with the hotel under attack? The dangerous and scary story of the people in the hotel during the attack, trying to survive and fight against the terrorists that had them hostages and trapped within the walls of the Hotel.</span>\r\n<h2><b>10) Snowden (2016)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1752 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Snowden (2016)\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 7.3</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Netflix</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Joseph Gordan-Levitt, Shailene Woodley</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Edward Snowden. A hero to some, a traitor to others but a fugitive on the run from the law in most places. The very well known name was a top contractor who questioned the data mountain which would monitor the people all over. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Snowden then decides to become a whistleblower and a man of question all over the world. It is one of the <strong>best terrorism movies on Netflix</strong>.</span>\r\n<h2><b>9) United 93 (2006)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1753 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"United 93 (2006) Terrorism Movies\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 7.5</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Netflix</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: David Alan Basche, Trish Gates</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another best <strong>terrorism movie on Netflix</strong>! When a flight is hijacked by terrorists the passengers are shocked and worried. But learning about the attacks on the Pentagon and World Trade Center, the passengers decide to rise up and fight against the hijackers and battle for their own safety.</span>\r\n<h2><b>8) World Trade Center (2006)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1754 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/5-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"World Trade Center (2006)\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 5.9</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: N/A</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Nicholas Cage, Michael Pena, Maria Bello</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All of us know about the 9/11 attack that took place at the World Trade Center. There are so many stories about the attack and struggle that did take place. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But what about the ones who were stuck under the rubble and debris of the attack that did take place. With their lives at stake, you can watch how two men stuck under the debris struggle for safety.</span>\r\n<h2><b>7) Shahid (2012)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1755 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Shahid (2012) Terrorism Movies\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 8.2</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Amazon Prime Video</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Rajkumar Rao, Kay Kay Menon, Tigmanshu Dhulia</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Discrimination still exists in this world, and this movie will show it with a minority religion man faced terror over his identity. Growing up to become a lawyer and Human Rights activist, he defended the case of Mr. Ansari who was accused of planning on the 26/11 incident. He is an inspiration who took it upon himself to defend the ones who were jailed under the Prevention of Terrorism act and were unjustly jailed.</span>\r\n<h2><b>6) Flight 93 (2006)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1756 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/7-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Flight 93 (2006)\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 6.3</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: N/A</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast: Jeffery Nordling, Kendall Cross</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Going back to the flights that were hijacked, among the four flights that were taken over, one had the passengers rising up to fight. This is their story, this is the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/\">inspirational story</a> behind fighting for your own safety instead of giving in to the terrorist demands.</span>\r\n<h2><b>5) One Less God (2017)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1757 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/8-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"One Less God (2017) Terrorism Movies\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 5.4</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: N/A</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Kabir Duhan Singh, Nicole Fantl</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most movies tell you an act of terrorism from the point of view of the locals, or police. This one addresses the problems faced by the foreigners caught in the crossfire. It showed the struggle and problems faced by a group of tourists who were in the hotel at the time of the attack.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4) Zero Dark Thirty (2012)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1758 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/9-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"Zero Dark Thirty (2012)\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 7.4</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Netflix</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Jessica Chastain, Chris Pratt, Jason Clarke</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the names that spark terror in the world all over. <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Osama_bin_Laden\" rel=\"nofollow\">Osama Bin Laden</a>. The man who caused terror all over the world. What went on when there was finally a terror operation to take him down? Showcasing a group of operatives of CIA and how they tracked him for years to know his location.</span>\r\n<h2><b>3) 12 Strong (2018)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1759 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/10-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"12 Strong (2018) Terrorism Movies\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 6.6</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Netflix, Amazon Prime</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Chris Hemsworth, Michael Pena, Michael Shannon</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A group of operatives went to Afghanistan in order to take down the Taliban. They must now with the help of the Northern Alliance fight a difficult battle in the post 9/11 era. In a movie built like a video game with grit and agony all over the movie, it’s as difficult a world as it can get.</span>\r\n<h2><b>2) The Attacks of 26/11 (2013)</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1760 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/11-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"The Attacks of 26/11 (2013)\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>IMDb Rating</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 7.5</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Platform</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: N/A</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Star Cast: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nana Patekar, Atul Kulkarni, Ganesh Yadav</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Possibly the only Indian movie that accurately retraces the entire sequence of events that took place. This is a dreadful date into the minds of so many people for all the wrong reasons. From the way in which the terrorists en