Big B\" of Bollywood or the \"King Khan\"; everybody had their battle they were reluctant to give up on. </span>\r\n<h2>Here is a list of 10 such Bollywood actors/ actresses who were not the first choice for the movie.</h2>\r\n<h3><b>1. SHAHRUKH KHAN</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1496\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/10-min-1024x665.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Actor Shahrukh khan struggle\" width=\"779\" height=\"506\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The king khan we know now has struggled a lot during his starting career phase. He used to work in various TV series namely Fauji before he got his first movie Deewana.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But that\'s not what got him in the game. It was actually the movie \"Baazigar\" that established him. He often mentions \"If today I own Mannat, it\'s solely because of Baazigar.\"</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1871 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1-min-8.jpg\" alt=\" Bollywood Actor Salman shahrukh\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Initially, he was not the first choice for this movie. It was when Salman Khan rejected the movie is when Shahrukh made it through. There are other movies namely Dilwale Dulhaniya Le Jayenge, Chakde India, Kal Ho Na   Ho, etc. that were all rejected by Salman and made Shahrukh the heartthrob of Bollywood.</span>\r\n<h3><b>2. RANVEER SINGH</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1872 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2-min-8.jpg\" alt=\" Bollywood Actor RANVEER SINGH\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The powerhouse of Bollywood had no godfather either. He received his first movie Band Baaja Baarat and then there was no turning back. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even he was not the first choice for the movie. It was actually when Ranbir Kapoor turned the movie down is how he acquired the project.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He, in fact, wasn\'t the first choice for Goliyon ki Raasleela- Ram Leela. It was also turned down and then he got it. The actor now knows no bounds when it comes to acting. He holds numerous awards to himself and is a power-packed performer. </span>\r\n<h3><b>3. AYUSHMANN KHURANA</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1873 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3-min-7.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Actor AYUSHMANN KHURANA struggle\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The versatile performer of Bollywood made his way to the industry after various failed attempts.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He was a VJ and Roadies winner before he came to Bollywood with his first movie, a romantic comedy- Vicky Donor. The actor is also a singer and has given quite some amazing songs to his own movies as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie Andhadhun that crashed the box office completely won numerous awards, wasn\'t initially featuring Ayushmaan. The director reveals how a lot of actors turned the movie down before Khurana actually made it.</span>\r\n<h3><b>4. TAPSEE PANNU</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1874 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4-min-7.jpg\" alt=\"TAPSEE PANNU\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The banger lady of Bollywood who can fiddle any role making it her own and living the most out of it made her way into Bollywood after quite some struggle.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She initially used to work in Tollywood and then made her way into the dreamland with the movie Chashme Baddoor which didn\'t pay off that well but got Pannu into the league.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> She played a variety of roles in