n>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After this, she played a variety of roles in movies like Fukrey, Gangs of Wasseypur, Masaan, Ram Leela, etc. featured as both a lead actress and a side gig. She nailed all her roles.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even she wasn\'t the first choice for most movies. She mentions how she only used to get calls offering roles where heights of cursing were there. She also mentions how she has struggled with her way of being an outsider.</span>\r\n<h3><b>7. KANGANA RANAUT</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1480 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Actor KANGANA RANAUT\" width=\"820\" height=\"532\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The ultimate queen of Bollywood who fears nobody entered the industry at quite a young age. Starting her career as a model, Ranaut stretched a hand in Bollywood but didn\'t actually make it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She wasn\'t the first choice for her debut movie <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gangster_(2006_film)\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gangster</a>. It was actually her luck that she was at the right spot, at the right time. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She recalls, \" I was on set for the audition which didn\'t happen. Whilst leaving is when I came to know the lead actress has backed out. They called me in, took the audition and that\'s how I got Gangster.\" </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Queen hasn\'t looked back since then. She gave various hits including Queen, Tanu weds Manu, Tanu weds Manu Returns and many more.</span>\r\n<h3><b>8. </b><b>NAWAAZUDDIN SIDDIQUI</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1876 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6-min-9.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Actor NAWAAZUDDIN SIDDIQUI struggle\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </spa