amalhotra #happybirthdaysanya #28thbirthday</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\">A post shared by <a style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px;\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dancelikesanya/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Dance Like Sanya</a> (@dancelikesanya) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2020-02-25T09:20:25+00:00\">Feb 25, 2020 at 1:20am PST</time></p>\r\n\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n<script async=\"\" src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\"></script>\r\n<h2><strong>What has she done since?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pataakha:</span></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2105 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5-min-4.jpg\" alt=\"pataakha\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After Dangal It took her a couple of years, but she did find her next role. It came in the form of starring aside another debutant in <strong>Radhika Madan</strong> when she signed for Pataakha, the comedy-drama made by <strong>Vishal Bharadwaj</strong>. The dedication was again there, as she went to Rajasthan and lived there in order to learn the dialect. According to her it was essential for the role that she was going to play.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Badhai Ho:</span></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2106 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6-min-4.jpg\" alt=\"badhai ho\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Including putting on 10kgs for the role, we can say that she is a fearless actor with the unhinged enthusiasm that she would show in her roles. She went ahead to star in another comedy called <strong>Badhaai Ho</strong> in which she starred alongside another <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/successful-self-made-bollywood-stars-who-had-no-root-in-industry/\">self-made superstar in our industry</a> who is the favourite of so many, Ayushmann Khurrana. </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shakuntala Devi:</span></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7-min-4.jpg\" alt=\"Shakuntala Devi\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2020 seems to be the best year for her with her release ‘Shakuntala Devi’ getting positive reviews. She takes on the role of the daughter of the famed Indian Mathematician in this new role of hers. Shakuntala Devi played by <strong>Vidya Balan</strong> has a slightly difficult relationship with her daughter. Sanya seems to have played the role exceptionally well once again.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Well, This is just a Start:</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alongside this movie, she is also expected to release a couple more movies within 2020 making it the most successful year of her young career. And with this, she is also going to be starring in an <strong>Anurag Basu</strong> drama that has no name yet. But this star-studded cast includes the talented <strong>Rajkumar Rao</strong>, the underrated <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards/\">Pankaj Tripathi</a>, her former co-star Fatima Sana Shaikh and others such as <strong>Abhishek Bachchan</strong> as well. With such a cast and a talented director, the movie is definitely going to be one to watch!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2109 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/post-750X480-1.jpg\