r ones are called? <a href=\"https://t.co/jAMMoYCzy3\">pic.twitter.com/jAMMoYCzy3</a></p>\r\n— Amrita Puri (@_Amrita_Puri) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Amrita_Puri/status/1069628793902387200?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 3, 2018</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>','Amrita Puri | Movies, Tv Shows and Web Series','','publish','open','open','','amrita-puri-movies-tv-shows-and-web-series','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/','2021-02-12 13:27:06','2021-02-12 07:57:06','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=2279',0,'post','',0),(2297,4,'2020-08-20 00:33:58','2020-08-19 19:03:58','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2313 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-min-min.jpg\" alt=\"randeep hooda films\" width=\"840\" height=\"520\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Randeep Hooda in Rohtak, Haryana in 1976, this underrated actor has been at the back of the limelight for several years now. Although a fairly successful career with a few significant movies, he isn’t a household name yet. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His talent is very obvious and has been wonderful in everything he has acted in.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From Highway to Extraction, the quality he has shown has not found the recognition that he deserves. So what has been the story of the star that is <strong>Randeep Hooda</strong>? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Read on ahead to find out what has been the story of his rise from the bottom to the top.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Young Days</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Born to a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jat_people\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hindu Jat family</a>, he had an orthodox family with his father a doctor along with his sister as well. A middle-class family with his mother a social worker and his younger brother is a software engineer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He lived many of his young years with his grandmother with his parents traveling very often having several years in the Middle East living there as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2329 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/4-min-13.jpg\" alt=\"randeep hooda happy birthday\" width=\"840\" height=\"520\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While his family wanted him to become a doctor, his ambitions were very different. Doing well in sports while in his boarding school at a young age. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When moved to Delhi Public School he admitted that the transition was difficult for him. Considering that his interests were elsewhere and his sports so good that he had reached a National Level it was quickly realized that he would not be becoming a Doctor as his family wanted him to be. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Moving to Australia in the 90s, he studied for his master’s degree in marketing while working several jobs such as a waiter and taxi driver as well. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His interests found their way to theatre acting as well as he took on roles and excelled at them. He kept working on his roles and moving forwards before his good work found some attention in the early 2000s, where everything changed for him.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Career Begins with many struggles</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mira Nair saw his theatre rehearsals and offered him a role in her movie in 2001. He played the role of an Indian in Australia. While the critics and everyone loved the movie along with it being a commercial success as well, he did not continue to get roles in movies.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-movies-list-must-watch-these-top-10/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2331 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-min-14.jpg\" alt=\"randeep hooda movies randeep hooda movies\" width=\"840\" height=\"520\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His next role coming much much later in the middle of the decade in 2005. In 2005 he was then cast in Ram Gopal Varma’s gangster movie ‘D’. Once again his acting received a lot of positive reviews with many applauding the quality of his performances. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But once again the roles he was receiving dried up. The lack of roles for such a talent showing the problems in our industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then in 2010 came the big break of his career, while his roles previously could be considered big breaks, none of them affected his career as this one did. And what a movie it was. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Starring in ‘Once upon a time in Mumbai’ alongside stars such as Ajay Devgn and Imraan Hashmi, the movie that was made by Milan Luthria, finally gave him the limelight that he deserved.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film was a huge commercial success as well and Randeep a success along with it. His acting was even compared by some critics to that of Amitabh Bachchan which is definitely the highest of praises!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> His screen presence and aura in this gangster movie was loved by everyone. Him himself admitting that filmmakers starting looking at him in a different light after this role.</span>\r\n<h2>Read: <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-movies-list-must-watch-these-top-10/\">Randeep Hooda Movies List</a></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Making Strides in the Industry</span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Randeep Hooda then landed a role in ‘Saheb, Biwi Aur Gangster’ the following year. And once again he earned praise for his performance. He played the role of a driver falling in love with his employer. The story, music, and acting of this <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Hindi Movie</a> earned praise from everywhere. </span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He continued to showcase his talent in more movies, which included the popular hit ‘Highway’. In Highway movie, he starred opposite the ever so talented Alia Bhatt. His dedication to the role is such that because he must show a distant personality to Alia’s character. He did not speak to her for around 25 days before the shooting in order to get into the role. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2330 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-min-13.jpg\" alt=\"randeep hooda haryana randeep hooda haryana\" width=\"840\" height=\"520\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The acting career of Randeep Hooda continued with roles such as the policeman. He did a movie with Salman Khan and Jacqueline Fernandes cast movie, ‘Kick’. This movie was a huge box office hit earning money all over and being a big commercial hit. </span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His most successful year being 2016 in which he was a part of four different films, starting with ‘Laal Rang’ the crime drama, then the biopic ‘Sarabjit’ and followed by ‘Do Lafzon Ki Kahani’ and the mega-hit ‘Sultan’. Out of which two of them were huge hits, including Sarabjit being premiered in the Cannes Film Festival that year. Followed by another movie which included Salman Khan named ‘Sultan’.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie along with Salman Khan had Anushka Sharma in the lead as well. A huge hit in all departments, the movie lived up to the expectations, and although Randeep didn’t have a huge role he did showcase his acting talent once again.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Media Image and Struggle since.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2332 \" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/3-min-14.jpg\" alt=\"randeep hooda birthday randeep hooda birthday\" width=\"685\" height=\"424\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Being the good looking man that he is, the media has always had his looks in focus. </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Randeep Hooda is named in the<strong> top 50 sexiest men</strong> alive in Indian magazines and the popular movie website IMDB.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He is also named in the top 20 sexiest men alive. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mr. Hooda has welcomed the praise and label. He has always said he has tried to be more than what an image such as that makes a person out to be. And to his credit, he has shown why he should be taken more seriously in terms of his acting ability as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But since 2016, Randeep has fairly struggled to find new roles, it shows how the industry is when a man of his talents is unable to find good roles in this modern time. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although he had been a part of a couple of projects some problems or others have come up and the movies have not been made. It is a shame an actor of his talents is unable to get more roles.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What are your thoughts on the recent struggles of Randeep Hooda? With his wonderful acting ability, it is a surprise he doesn’t get more movies. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know your favourite roles of Randeep Hooda and whether you think <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders/\">nepotism has affected his chances in the industry</a>. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tell us your thoughts in the comment section below!</span>\r\n<h3><b>ALSO READ:</b>