er.com/hashtag/Saifalikhan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Saifalikhan</a> to write his own autobiography</p>\r\nIndian auidence still: <a href=\"https://t.co/AXOBKQbOEw\">pic.twitter.com/AXOBKQbOEw</a>\r\n\r\n— Arun Singh (@_arun_67) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_arun_67/status/1298146263339130880?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 25, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SaifAliKhan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SaifAliKhan</a> announces his autobiography, Written by Taimur Ali Khan. <a href=\"https://t.co/1gzmokEA0g\">pic.twitter.com/1gzmokEA0g</a></p>\r\n— Wellu (@Wellutwt) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Wellutwt/status/1298128845346750464?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 25, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SaifAliKhan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SaifAliKhan</a> to write his own biography</p>\r\nSolemon bhoi reaction <a href=\"https://t.co/8VjGDkVxpT\">pic.twitter.com/8VjGDkVxpT</a>\r\n\r\n— Rathu Mahata (@MahataRathu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MahataRathu/status/1298119951497060352?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 25, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SaifAliKhan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SaifAliKhan</a>\r\nWhile saifali khan write his auto biography\r\nAfter failure to him <a href=\"https://t.co/wxt2z4BlXG\">pic.twitter.com/wxt2z4BlXG</a></p>\r\n— Tushar being Indian (@TusharbeingInd1) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TusharbeingInd1/status/1298172877259198465?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 25, 2020</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<h2>Let\'s Do The Serious Talk Now</h2>\r\n<h2><b>Saif’s Bollywood Journey</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saif made his Bollywood debut in the action thriller Bollywood movie <strong>Main Khiladi Tu Anadi</strong> in the year 1994. But it did not gain so much popularity as per hype created due to a star kid being launched. But after five years his career started to climb up the graph with his movie <strong>Hum Saath Saath Hain</strong> in the year 1999.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2379 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-min-16.jpg\" alt=\"Dil chata hai Saif Ali Khan\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thereafter he was sort of qualified to play comedy lead roles in the Bollywood movies <strong>Dil Chahta hai</strong> and Kal Ho Na Ho. Dil Chata hai now is one of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-15-movies-on-friendship-that-you-must-watch/\">the best and top-rated movies based on friendship.</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saif did not stop after that he went on to do<strong> Hum Tum</strong> alongside <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rani_Mukerji\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rani Mukherjee</a>. Saif played a single male lead in this Hindi movie, and you would be surprised to know that he was awarded the <strong>National Film Award</strong> for the same movie. Then After a few years of in and out in the Bollywood movie Industry. And his comeback in the year 2012 with the movie <strong>Cocktail</strong>.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although it is debatable that his golden period was from 2006 to 2012 where he appeared in numerous Hindi movies such as <strong>Kurbann(2009)</strong>, the blockbuster<strong> Race </strong>(2008 and it’s a sequel in 2013). But he made a strong comeback in recent times with the Patriotic Biopic of <strong>Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior (2020).</strong> He took a good amount for this movie and increase his free and he came in <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/highest-paid-actors-and-actress-in-bollywood/\">the Highest paid actor list of Bollywood</a>. Mr.Saif Ali Khan. He has his upcoming movie<strong> Bunty Aur Babli 2</strong> for which his fans are super excited.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2380 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/3-min-16.jpg\" alt=\"Tanhaji Saif Ali Khan\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h2><b>Interesting Facts of Saif Ali Khan</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saif was initially going to debut in the movie Bekhudi opposite to Kajol but later on, he was replaced just a few days before the shoot. And it was on Bekhudi’s sets where he met Amrita Singh and fell in love with her.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After his Divorce, Saif dated a Swiss Actress but after three years they broke up. Saif is a very introverted person and his hobbies are playing the guitar and traveling around the world.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you know that Nawab’s real name is Sajid Ali Khan but after entering into the Bollywood Industry he changed it to Saif Ali Khan?</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saif’s grandfather and his father were cricketers and both represented India and her mother hails from a Bollywood background, she also tells that Saif was very spontaneous at his young age. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>What we Can Expect from his Autobiography?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Everyone is very curious about the upcoming Autobiography on Saif Ali Khan. As soon as he shares this news in social media everyone started to predict that what are the things which might be included in Nawab’s Autobiography. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us discuss and predict some of the incidents which might be included in Saif’s Autobiography.</span>\r\n<h3>Marriage at Young Age:</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2381 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/4-min-15.jpg\" alt=\"Saif Ali Khan Amrita marriage\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We can expect a short clip of Khan’s education especially abroad and then his return to Indian and working for an <strong>advertising firm</strong>. Nawab’s personal life is also too interesting to show it on the screen like getting married at a very young age and them becoming the father of his two children <strong>Sara Ali Khan</strong> and <strong>Ibrahim</strong>. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then after a healthy relationship of about 13 years getting separated from Amrita Singh. And after a couple of years marrying the famous Actress Kareena Kapoor and again becoming the father of Taimur (who already is a social media sensation).</span>\r\n<h3>Struggle Time:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His struggling days can also be portrayed in his autobiography. His struggle started after his father Shri Mansur Ali Khan Pataudi‘s demise, where he and his family lost the ownership of their iconic Pataudi Residence, they had to pay rent to some Hotel Owners for that House. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Later after a lot of hustle Saif regained ownership of the house with his hard-earned money from the Hindi Film Industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once he also stated in an interview that after his education was over abroad and when he returned to India, his father had sent him to his ad agency to get a job because he was partying a lot. And the ad truly happened in Gwalior. So this incident might also be shown in his movie. Also, the roller coaster ride of his filmy career might also be shown.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2377 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5-min-11.jpg\" alt=\"Saif Ali Khan \" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let’s talk about criticization. So as Saif Ali Khan posted the news of his upcoming Autobiography on social media, trolls became highly active. All the trollers started trolling in a massive way. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even a few days ago Saif was trolled for a comment which he passed on Nepotism which was that ‘he was also the<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders/\"> victim of Nepotism’.</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So that’s it, hope you like the content. Do comment down below on how much you are excited about his Autobiography. Also, Subscribe to the webpage to get regular updates and daily news in the entertainment industry.</span>','Saif Ali Khan Said About his Autobiography | Reactions on Twitter','','publish','open','open','','saif-ali-khan-said-about-his-autobiography-reactions-on-twitter','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-15-movies-on-friendship-that-you-must-watch/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/highest-paid-actors-and-actress-in-bollywood/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders/','2021-01-24 17:07:52','2021-01-24 11:37:52','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=2374',0,'post','',0),(2422,6,'2020-08-29 23:32:39','2020-08-29 18:02:39','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2428 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7-min-11.jpg\" alt=\"Chadwick Boseman died\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A piece of fresh news is coming up From the United States of America that Chadwick Boseman passed away at the age of 43. He was born on 29th November in the year 1976. And the series of unexpected in the fearful year 2020 continues. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">let’s take a look at Chadwick Boseman’s Bollywood and Personal Life and thereafter we\'ll talk about some of his struggles.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Chadwick Boseman\'s Journey to Hollywood </b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chadwick Boseman started his acting by appearing on Television Screen that is from Television work. His first television appearance was in the year 2003 with the American Television Drama series<strong> ‘<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Third_Watch\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Third Watch</a></strong> ‘ in the episode named ‘In Lieu of Johnson. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thereafter doing some famous TV series such as<strong> Cold Case, Castle</strong> and after spending approximately five years in the American TV industry, he received the good news for his first breakthrough on the Hollywood screen from the movie </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The Express: The Ernie Davis Story</strong> in the year 2008. He played the famous American Personality Floyd Little, Floyd little is the only All American Black to </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">compete for the Syracuse University Orangemen.</span>\r\n<h2>Let us talk about Some of the most famous movies of Chadwick Boseman in recent years:-</h2>\r\n<h3><b>1. Black Panther(2018)</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb- 7.3/10</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Rotten Tomatoes - 96%</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2401 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/18-min.jpg\" alt=\"Black Panther (2018)\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chadwick Boseman played the role of T’Challa in the movie <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1825683/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Black Panther</strong></a>. The story goes as when T’ Challa’s father dies then T’Challa returns to their ancestors Kingdom Wakanda to sit on the Throne. His job was to Save Wakanda from Enemy Threats, Keep the existence of Wakanda a secret, Help the poor in need, and most important to protect the huge reserves of Vibranium and avoid misuse in the future.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then Kill Monger comes and Challenger T’Challa (Black Panther) saying he is the perfect contender for the king. Black Panther gets defeated but after a huge struggle, he rises again wins again.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The funniest incident in the movie Black Panther was when Boseman’s sister Shuri tries to gift his brother the most advanced shoes for running. But T’Challa says what’s wrong with these old shoes of his, these look cool all our have ancestors have wore it. Then Shuri replies with a cheeky smile that Brother, You need to change the shoes they are pretty old sneakers which old people wear, but you are a king, and you should have the best.</span>\r\n<h3><b>2. Captain America: Civil War(2016)</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb - 7.8/10</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Rotten Tomatoes - 91%</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2431 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/3-min-18.jpg\" alt=\"Chadwick Boseman died civil war\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you know that it was in this movie in which Chadwick Boseman made his first appearance in the Marvel Cinematic Universe, And thereafter he became a personality that no one can forget?</span>\r\n<h3><b>3. Avengers: Infinity War(2018)</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb - 8.4/10</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Rotten Tomatoes - 85%</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2433 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5-min-13.jpg\" alt=\"Chadwick Boseman died infinity war\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who can forget Chadwick Boseman’s contribution in Avengers: Infinity War. From helping the Avengers to save Vision, fighting the most powerful villain Thanos and leading his Wakadian Army from the front. And Yes he played a very vital role in keeping Thanos’s army from the Wakadian people. But do you the crowd who sat in theatres interacted and cheered the most when Chadwick Boseman(aka. Black Panther) gave a strong voice YEEEeeeeebammmbeee!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yeeeebaammmbeee! Do you remember that?</span>\r\n<h2><b>Interesting Facts:-</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you know that Chadwick Boseman once played a role as a gang member on a soap opera? His role was in various assumptions but anyway it went great and gathered a lot of appreciation. But when he asked the scriptwriter that why did he write his part of the role in an occurred way then Chadwick was fired.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It will be interesting to know that Chadwick was born and raised in South Carolina. His parents were African American. But after his DNA test once it was noted that his ancestral roots were from Sierra Leone which is a country in West Africa.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you know that Boseman always wanted to become a character in the Marvel Cinematic Universe? You know, he used to pray to get the role of Black Panther? He is a vegetarian too.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So that’s it, hope you like the content. Do comment down to pay your condolences to Chadwick Boseman. Also, Subscribe to the webpage to get regular updates and daily news in the entertainment industry.</span>\r\n<h2>Also Read:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/how-powerful-is-captain-america-marvel/\">Is Captain America is the Strongest one in All Superheros?</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/will-iron-man-return-after-death-in-endgame/\">Ironman made Infinity War a big hit. Will he return or there will be an IronMan 4? </a></li>\r\n</ul>','Chadwick Boseman (Black Panther Star) Dies At 43|Biography and Movies','','publish','open','open','','chadwick-boseman-black-panther-star-dies-at-43biography-and-movies','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/how-powerful-is-captain-america-marvel/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/will-iron-man-return-after-death-in-endgame/','2021-01-24 17:07:43','2021-01-24 11:37:43','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=2422',0,'post','',0),(2425,4,'2020-08-31 19:05:45','2020-08-31 13:35:45','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2444 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/3-min-19.jpg\" alt=\"Prateik Babbar | Life, Bollywood Journey and Success Story\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An actor whom not many know about. An actor whom we have seen in several movies but at times forget to remember his name. We often never realize that this actor is even a part of the movie until we see his face come up in between of a movie. Prateik Babbar may be an exceptional actor. But the fame he has found has been unfortunately very limited.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The actor who has been on the screen since 2008, has made strides in the industry but at the end of it all has not made a name for himself as big as he would have liked to make. Yet he is an actor whom we do know about. While he may not be the biggest name in Bollywood, it is a name with a story behind it. So read on ahead to find out about the name and story that is Prateik Babbar.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prateik Babbar Early Days</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prateik has a story to be told, nobody can argue against that and after reading ahead you will find out exactly what we mean by that. He started low by being an assistant to <strong>Prahlad Kakkar</strong> who is an advertisement filmmaker. Babbar worked with him as a <strong>Production Assistant</strong> and gained some valuable experience. But with his goal being acting, he kept trying to step into the limelight.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since he was working in the advertisement sector, eventually he did receive some advertisement roles including an ad for KitKat which is a product all of us know quite well. His work with Kakkar allowed him to step into the advertising sector easier and gave him opportunities to start applying for acting roles. The son of a popular industry couple, he is a question of whether a part of nepotism or not which is a topic we will get into later. The actor kept auditioning for roles and eventually his big break came in 2008 in a movie all us know all too well.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Debut Success</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2008, Prateik was cast in an<strong> Aamir Khan Production</strong> that also starred <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imran_Khan_(Bollywood_actor)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Imran Khan</strong></a> and <strong>Genelia Dsouza</strong>. That cast would remind us all of just one movie <strong>Jaane Tu Ya Jaane Na</strong>. This movie did so well and made a space in the audience\'s heart. This is also one of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-15-movies-on-friendship-that-you-must-watch/\">the best Movies on friendship in Bollywood</a>. Cast in a supporting role of the movie as the young annoying brother of Genelia, Babbar found the success that he craved. He won the critical acclamation for his acting and won awards as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2441 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6-min-13.jpg\" alt=\"Prateik Babbar debut\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prateik received nominations such as Best Supporting Role and Best Debut as well for his role in Jaane Tu ya Jaane Na at the 54th Filmfare awards. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He went on to do several more movies over the next few years. Including having as many as 4 films in 2011. Those four movies included ‘<strong>Dum Maaro Dum</strong>’ with Abhishek Bachchan which was an Action-Thriller. He also acted with the Senior Bachchan in the Social-Drama <strong>‘Aarakshan’</strong> directed by Prakash Jha which had an immense cast with Deepika Padukone, Amitabh Bachchan, and Saif Ali Khan. The film was a commercial success and Prateik kept earning a name for himself. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2446 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5-min-14.jpg\" alt=\"Ekk Deewana Tha \" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\nHe also did a famous romantic movie in which he played a mechanical engineer who is love action and wanted to follow his passion. He falls in love with a girl and now the story starts. It is one of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">the must-watch romantic movies.</a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His profile includes several more movies in the time such as <strong>‘My Friend Pinto</strong>’ and ‘<strong>Dhobi Ghaat’</strong>. After being in a string of movies, Babbar then fell off the radar for a while in 2013. He stopped making movies and had issues in his personal life that he had to take care of. Find out ahead what had him fall off the radar in such a manner. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Addiction and Recovery</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2013, Prateik realized about his level of substance abuse. He realized that he was an addict and went into rehab. He joined a rehabilitation program in Mumbai in 2013 and decided to fight against his addiction. Once he recovered and came out of sobriety he decided to further improve his acting skills and join an acting school while being the best version of himself.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2443 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-min-19.jpg\" alt=\"Prateik Babbar life\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He decided to take up a course in method acting at the Jeff Goldberg Studio in 2016. It is a welcome change to see an already established actor doing well and trying to improve himself by joining an acting school. Especially with method acting being such a difficult art to master. His big return after a phase of recovery was in 2018 when he returned with success as well. But more on that later.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nepotism or not?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An important question that comes to the mind of many when reading or talking about Prateik Babbar is whether he is a product of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders/\">Nepotism</a> or not. Prateik is the son of actress <strong>Smita Patil</strong> and <strong>Raj Babbar</strong>. While he is the son of such a huge name, it is not that he approached YRF or Karan Johar and walked into the next movie that they were making. It was a different story as we discussed.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2442 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-min-19.jpg\" alt=\"Prateik Babbar family\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prateik found his footing as an assistant and worked and found the work that he wanted. It is difficult to know how much of an influence having famous and rich parents made on his career. It is obvious that the famous parents’ background gives him an added advantage in terms of knowing people etc. But it is not that he did not find his own way in the industry. So, whether he is a product of nepotism or not is a topic that is up for discussion and debate. But for now, he is a part of the industry and even is now. How? Read our next section to find that out.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prateik Babbar </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Return and Resumption of Success?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ever since his return to the industry in 2018, Babbar has been in around 6 movies and has found success in several. His big return was in Baaghi 2 which had Tiger Shroff in the cast with Prateik as the main villain of the story. With this new beginning for him, it was a huge commercial success and gave him the platform he needed. He then went on to make several great movies such as Chicchore, Mulk, Darbar, etc. There is no denying that he is a wonderful actor and we’re sure we will see much more success for him!</span>\r\n<h2>Prateik Babbar A Fitness Freak:</h2>\r\nYou can check his Instagram is full of related to the gym, art, boxing. Check out some Instagram posts here.\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDoAqc8HcIk/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"12\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: