lin will leave an everlasting impact on your mind! This movie is a must-watch!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even though Robert Downey Jr has ended his Marvel stint, his performances won’t stop! With Sherlock Holmes’s second sequel already in talks, it remains a mystery when we would see the return of Robert Downey on the silver screen again. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let us know in the comments section below about your thoughts on his best work,</span>\r\n<h2>Best Articles of the year:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-11-terrorism-movies-based-on-real-life/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Top Terrorism Movies based on Real Life</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/science-and-mathematics-movies-based-on-real-life/\">Science and Mathematics Movies Based on Real Life</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-13-war-movies-based-on-real-stories/\">Top 13 War Movies Based on Real Stories</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Best Movies of Robert Downey Jr (Except MCU)','','publish','open','open','','best-movies-of-robert-downey-jr-except-mcu','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-crime-movies-based-on-true-life-stories/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/courtroom-movies-based-on-real-life-stories/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/science-and-mathematics-movies-based-on-real-life/','2021-01-15 16:48:06','2021-01-15 11:18:06','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=2565',0,'post','',0),(2581,4,'2020-09-02 21:53:48','2020-09-02 16:23:48','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is time to talk about Captain America himself. Chris Evans. Chris Evans has had a long career in Hollywood. Unfortunately, most of his Hollywood career that is spoken about is his career in the MCU or the Marvel Cinematic Universe as it is known. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But Chris Evans has had quite a few movies well before his MCU career, and has and will continue to have one well after his MCU caree