t Watch These Top 10</span></a></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-biography-career-and-struggles-in-film-industry/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Randeep Hooda | Biography, Career and Struggles in Film Industry</span></a></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sanjana-sanghi-bollywood-blockbusters-and-interesting-facts/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sanjana Sanghi Bollywood Blockbusters and Interesting Facts</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;','Bhoot Police, A Horror-Comedy Saif Ali Khan and Arjun Kapoor','','publish','open','open','','bhoot-police-a-horror-comedy-saif-ali-khan-and-arjun-kapoor','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-movies-list-must-watch-these-top-10/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/saif-ali-khan-said-about-his-autobiography-reactions-on-twitter/','2020-12-26 17:23:00','2020-12-26 11:53:00','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=2595',0,'post','',0),(2609,6,'2020-09-07 13:03:32','2020-09-07 07:33:32','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2612 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Dolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n\r\nDolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare is a movie with different but interesting stuff. Bollywood is changing its theme day by day.\r\n\r\nMovies like this are the biggest example of it. Now the Biggest news is that <strong>this movie is going to release on Netflix on 18th September 2020.</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie is silently making its name and coming front despite the secrets which are being revealed on Bollywood due to the death of Sushant Singh Rajput. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Directed by Alakrita Shrivastava “Dolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare” is a type of comedy-drama film which starts <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhumi_Pednekar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bhumi Padnekar</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Konkona_Sen_Sharma\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Konkana Sen Sharma</a> in their female lead roles. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alongside in the male lead role section Vikrant Messy and Amol Parashar are making their appearance in this movie. The film is being produced under Balaji Telefilms and it has Ekta Kapoor and Shoba Kapoor as it’s the producer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And it was also premiered in the 21st Busan International film festival.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Plot of Dolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie is all about Dolly (portrayed by Konkona Sen Sharma) and Kitty (Bhumi Padnekar). They share a relation of cousins. They also have a secret known to each other which is not disclosed to anyone.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2614 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Dolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If we talk about Dolly, she is a typical Middle-class mother who takes care of her son and she has a husband who works all his day to give his family a comfortable lifestyle. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After all the hard work Dolly and her husband plan to buy an apartment which was quite above their budget and it was kind of a luxurious apartment. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This fact of moving into an apartment was kept a huge secret from everyone. It was to show that Dolly’s family is still living in the same monetary situation as it was earlier.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kajal on the other side wants to climb the heights of material pleasure quite early in her career. So, for this reason, she moves to the city of Delhi (Northern Capita Region). </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But after entering Delhi, she noticed that a woman like her who has limited skills to perform has tiny scope to grow in this megacity.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So to meet her needs, she started a hidden career under the name of Kitty in an Online Dating app. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now the twist comes here when Kitty meets a man on a dating app, and she starts to share all the secrets with her cousin Dolly and Dolly to share all of her secrets.</span>\r\n<h2>Watch Trailer of Dolly Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare:</h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=as3YLG5DmL0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>What are these actresses doing now?</b></h2>\r\n<h2><b>Bhumi Padnekar</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can call Bhumi Padnekar the Female Hit Superstar of the Bollywood Industry. In the previous ten Bollywood movies that she has done approximately five to six films were hit on the screens. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some of the films that were superhit on the screens are <strong>Dum Laga Ke Haisha, Toilet: Ek Prem Katha, Bala, Saand Ki Aankh, Subh Mangal Savdhan</strong>.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2615 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-2-min.jpg\" alt=\"bHUMI pADNEKAR UPCOMING MOVIE\" width=\"564\" height=\"473\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, do you know that out of eighteen award nominations she has won ten of them (that is more than half of the awards)? By this, we can someway conclude how effective she is when she comes on screens and how well can she connect with her audience.</span>\r\n<h3>Social Issues Raised By Bhumi Padnekar:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bhumi has always been a top figure on social media and when it comes to equality she never stops. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bhumi Padnekar has raised some serious issues, for example, she raised the is