 <strong>Hrithik Roshan</strong> in the drama,<em><strong> ‘Super 30’</strong></em>. The movie was about the famed <em>mathematician Anand Kumar</em> who was played by Hrithik Roshan. It showed how he went from a budding mathematician with money problems to a teacher of great potential. Mrunal played opposite Hrithik in the movie. She was applauded by many for her acting by critics and viewers alike.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2653 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-min-4.jpg\" alt=\"MRUNAL THAKUR BATLA HOUSE\" width=\"564\" height=\"473\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She then even acted across <strong>John Abraham</strong> in \'<em><strong>Batla House\'</strong></em> in 2019 as well. Her career has been on a constant rise upwards. And the two quality movies that she has made is a very genuine indication of the quality that she has.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>The Break</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then came along 2020 and it brought a halt to everyone’s lives and their movie-making careers have been halted as well. While many have struggled career-wise, others have made strides to further their career even more. Mrunal Thakur is one of those who has made huge strides to further her career by signing movies for the upcoming future.</span>\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CCNe-8xnoj3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"12\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 16px;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;\">\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-rig