 normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px;\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chhotathalaiva/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Biswapati</a> (@chhotathalaiva) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2019-04-16T16:44:03+00:00\">Apr 16, 2019 at 9:44am PDT</time></p>\r\n\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\"></script>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Biswa did not give up though, he decided to convince his family and especially his mother to let him take this opportunity to work for The Viral Fever Videos as a scriptwriter and take a very different path in life to the one that they had planned for him. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They eventually gave in and let him pursue his new dream in the entertainment sector. What the future held for him he did not know and what came ahead he definitely could not have imagined nor predicted. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TVF Success Story</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To say the absolute least, TVF was a success. When TVF began, India as a country and its people were just discovering the joys of the internet. At that time, they discovered the wonderful content that was being published by TVF. The name became a name that everyone knew. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And the original audience that TVF was targeting which was the youth, was reacting in a very positive manner as well. They had said themselves that they were targeting the youth of the time, who avoided the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">entertainment</a> sector and had no interest in watching the soap operas that came on television regularly.</span>\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); mar