x; width: 20px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: auto;\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;\"><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BIHG8YHDhiv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Last day of PR shoot. :)</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\">A post shared by <a style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px;\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chhotathalaiva/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Biswapati</a> (@chhotathalaiva) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2016-07-21T05:02:45+00:00\">Jul 20, 2016 at 10:02pm PDT</time></p>\r\n\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\"></script>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A vast number of satirical skits and plays that TVF made were getting immensely popular within the country and were finding a very big following with all the content that came. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And a major influence in that was Biswapati Sarkar. He started with content such as ‘Chai Sutta Chronicles’ in which he made his writing and acting debut as well. But his rise came as a result of a very different show that he created a bit later in his career.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He created a youtube show by the name of ‘Barely Speaking with Arnab’ which was a parody of the Indian news reporter Arnab Goswami. To say the least, the show absolutely took off. Finding fans and views from everywhere. The show kept growing and kept getting more and more views reaching as many as a million views as well. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And if that was not enough, he then had guest stars on his show as well. And these guest stars were huge. By huge we mean people such as<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/bollywood-actors-ranking-as-per-their-net-worth\"> Shahrukh Khan</a>, Ranveer Singh, and even in a completely different direction with the Chief Minister of Delhi, Arvind Kejriwal being a part of his show as well.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Where is he now?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From rolling out constant hits to the pace of their popularity slowing down quite quickly. TVF does not have the popularity from times before. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They have had a topsy-turvy time which included being hit by a scandal and having a lot of money being invested in them as well. Biswapati continues to follow his dream and we hope to see him rise and go very far in his career.</span>\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); m