s brother comes under drug trafficking and making money. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Later Bharat had to join the Indian army, due to border crises with Pakistan. The film has Imdb ratings of 7.6 and the lead roles were played by Manoj Kumar, Asha Parekh, and Prem Chopra.</span>\r\n\r\nAbout Upkar:\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=STDzzzhHG9Y[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>7. Manthan (1976) | Movies on Farmers </b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manthan was one of the best films ever because this film was produced by the farmers themselves. If you are looking for Indian movies based on farmers then you should definitely for it. The film was based on the story of farmers and the white revolution in India.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4111 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-10-Indian-films-based-on-farmers-9.jpg\" alt=\"Manthan (1976)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film clarifies the growth of India as the world’s largest milk producer and around the story of Dr Rao who convince farmers to open milk dairy. This has Imdb ratings of 7.7 and Rotten tomatoes Ratings of 95% fresh. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film had a huge star cast From India’s theatre fraternity as actors like Smita Patil, Girish Karnad, Naseeruddin Shah, Amrish Puri, and Kulbhushan Kharbanda. Directed by Shyam Benegal.</span>\r\n\r\nWatch Full Movie:\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L9AUGWvjHJM[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>6. Kadvi Hawa (2017)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly you will be amazed to know that, Kadvi Hawa is one of the best performances, of Sanjay Mishra. The list of Bollywood films on farmers can not be completed without it. This film clarifies the struggles of farmers in the draughted land, where is no rain is there for a very long period. The film ha