ai?</b></h2>\r\n<h3><b>A Tribute to a great movie franchise</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So starting off from the reason to watch this amazing season is its homage to one of the most popular movies of the 80s, The Karate Kid series. The trilogy itself is great, simply because of the love of Karate.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4153 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/cobra-kai-season-3-release-date-1.jpg\" alt=\"cobra kai season 3 release date (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s first part simply shows how to stand up against people and how violence should only be resorted to as self-defence. At this point, everyone who is bullied at school will reflect on this and it simply gives them a sense of retribution at home.</span>\r\n<h3><b>A whole new Perspective</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So Cobra Kai not only talks about self-defence but also talks about rising through adversity. The climax of the movie (the first part...) leads to a karate tournament, wherein the finals, the aggressor, Johnny Lawerence faces off against his victim, Daniel LaRusso. LaRusso upsets his aggressor’s expectations and finds himself the victor of the tournament. He manages to move and become a car dealer as witnessed from the First Season of Cobra Kai. However, the season centres around the aggressor who becomes oppressed and mourns off his life miserably, one beer at a time.</span>\r\n<h3>Johnny &amp; Daniel vs John Kreese Final Fight</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=01F1T-qNXfQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><b>A Promising Sequel itself</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another fact which you might have guessed by now is the concept of moving along with the story. The fact that the seasons of Cobra Kai act entirely as a sequel to the movies is a unique concept. You are to witness the characters of the movie all grown up and now have kids of their own.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4152 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/cobra-kai-season-3-release-date-3.jpg\" alt=\"cobra kai season 3 release date (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ironically, the kids are at each other’s throats and the audience of the digital generation has something of their own to live with. One validating aspect of this point is the footage of the movie fitting in between the storyline of Cobra Kai. That ensures the young audience with a comprehensive story. This without a shadow of doubt brings past references very clearly and to the point. At the same time provides a great show for the fans of the movie as well.   </span>\r\n<h2><b>So what’s next for Cobra Kai?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So the </span>Cobra Kai season 3 release date Netflix<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> was formerly announced for January 7th. But provided the eagerness of the fans, the directors decided not to make them wait for long. They then decided to release the third season on January the 1st. So here’s what we will expect from Cobra Kai Season 3 cast</span>.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So starting off with the trailer of the season itself, we see that Johnny, after establishing a great karate dojo for the Valley, finds one of his best students (Miguel) in the hospital after suffering from an expected broken back from his famously “infamous school fight”.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=92wZP_6qz8A[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> All Johnny wanted for the students to become better people who can stand up for themselves and be the exact opposite of himself (and what he suffered in life). As for the fight himself, this leads us to the characters in their distressing states. Fed up and disheartened, he hands over his dojo to his former master, Sensei Creese (which was his intention to take over in the first place). </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Daniel tries to talk sense into Johnny that both there are because of them and it is now a matter of time to make things right. He believes that the bad blood between them shouldn’t pass on to their kids. He also believes that despite starting this bad blood, they can still manage to work together and past their differences (provided the movie brings them their history). This season will most likely show the undoing of their rivalry. Asides from his rivalry with Johnny, we are to expect more familiar faces from the movie. But I think people should see for themselves why they were there, in the first place.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=01F1T-qNXfQ[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hawk tries to punish himself for being not enough in the school fight. He blames himself for not subduing people from the fight. He thinks of himself and his dojo fellows in a great sense of loss. In the trailer, we find him beating up a punching bag from the gym and struggling to move on from his losses (including his girlfriend, Moon. He has a tattoo on his chest reflecting on her name, which is now all covered up.)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Robby (Johnny\'s son, who is also one of LaRusso’s students) finds himself in a children\'s correctional facility. He finds himself doing time for being in the wrong place at the wrong time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tory after heartbroken by Miguel’s affiliation with a drunk and confused Sam (of which Tory does not know of at all), makes her escape from school life. From the trailer, she seems to work at an underground level of the Valley, probably fighting for money. She also meets up with Sam at one point where it seems she will fulfil her revenge against her.    </span>\r\n<h3><strong>Have a look at the Cobra Kai season 3 trailer below:</strong></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LcDQqGJG8pA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>My Verdict:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So finally concluding this article with my verdict, I think the third season will unfold more about the movie franchise. Furthermore, we will definitely come about familiar faces from both the season as well as the franchise itself. Also, you will get the quick information for cobra kai season 4 as soon as possible. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Time will tell how these new faces will support the never-ending problems between Miyagi-Do and Cobra Kai. If you still don’t believe me, check the IMDB ratings of this season yourself. This Cobra Kai Cast will not fail me!. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Happy Binging! And a Happy New Year! <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">The Tv Freak</a></span>','Cobra Kai- A Series to Start off 2021','','publish','open','open','','cobra-kai-a-series-to-start-off-2021','','','2021-01-24 09:18:55','2021-01-24 03:48:55','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=4136',0,'post','',0),(4139,12,'2021-02-03 12:08:34','2021-02-03 06:38:34','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4202 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/amazing-best-funny-Hollywood-facts-2.jpg\" alt=\"amazing, best, funny Hollywood facts (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The glamorous, exciting ‘Lights-Camera-Action’ world of Hollywood has been a dream destination for many of us. All these years, Hollywood has gifted us with some of the iconic actors, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/\">fascinating movies</a>, best music, and whatnot. Hence, to honour the special place it holds in our hearts, here tvfreak.com presents to you some of the amazing and interesting facts about its past, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/celebrities/\">celebrities</a>, movies, Hollywood facts etc. which are surely going to bewilder you.</span>\r\n<h2><b>1. The Father of Hollywood | Hollywood facts</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4203 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/amazing-best-funny-Hollywood-facts-3.jpg\" alt=\"The Father of Hollywood amazing, best, funny Hollywood facts (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H.J. Whitley (1847-1931), considered the ‘Father of Hollywood’. But he had no connections with the world of cinema or any other forms of entertainment and was in fact a real estate developer. It was he who coined the term ‘Hollywood’. According to Whitley’s diary, in the year 1886 when he visited the town of ‘now called’ Hollywood along with his wife. It was a Chinese man who on being asked what he was doing in the hills, replied ‘I Hollywood’, which means ‘hauling wood’. It is this surprising reply that Whitley decide to name the town ‘Hollywood’.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BLdDLeFbVow[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>2. The Story Behind the ‘HOLLYWOOD’ Sign | Hollywood facts</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The most remarkable landmark of Hollywood, the hillside ‘Hollywood’ sign, which attracts tourists from all over the world was embedded in the year 1923 and was original ‘HOLLYWOODLAND’. Also, as a matter of fact, the sign wasn’t to denote the entertaining world of Hollywood at that time. It was only for advertising the new housing development in the hills above the Hollywood district. It was then in the year 1949 the ‘LAND’ was removed and the sign became, as we see now, ‘HOLLYWOOD’.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JVng9mObaG4[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>3. The Hollywood Walk of Fame</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the famous tourist attractions in the district of Hollywood is the Hollywood Walk of Fame consisting of around 2690 brass stars implanted in the pavement, featuring names of celebrities. It is including all ranging from producers, actors, musicians, characters, directors, and so on).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, something that may sound amazing to you is here for you. It is the fact that an amount of $50,000 (as of 202) has to be submitted as a sponsorship fee during submission of the nomination application, for making of the star as well as, as a donation to the Hollywood Historic Trust for its maintenance. Of course, the celebrity himself doesn’t pay the amount. It is usually sponsored by the nominating organization, i.e., a fan club, a film studio, or any other associated sponsor.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4. Celebrity with the largest number of stars in the Walk of Fame</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Of course, having your name featured in only one star of the Hollywood Walk of Fame is not the limit. In fact, many of the celebrities like Tony Martin, Bob Hope, Frank Sinatra have their names written in 3 or 4 stars but the renowned artist of all time, Gene Austry is the one to have his name in the highest number of five stars.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EELDW-b_K4A[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>5. In Old California | Hollywood facts</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first-ever Hollywood film, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In Old California</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, released in 1910 was shot in just two days and has a running time of only 17 minutes.</span>\r\n<h2><b>6. Yoda’s physical appearance is the whose animated version?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From the epic space opera of </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Wars, </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">one of our favourite characters, Yoda has a very uncanny resemblance with a world-famous personality. Can you guess who? Yes, right...with none other than the greatest theoretical physicist of all time, Albert Einstein. The reason behind this is more surprising.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gv7J8rvIHok[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Star Wars’ </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">special effect artist, Stuart Freeborn wanted to give Yoda a wise look as per the character and was inspired by a photo of Albert Einstein, one of the most recognizable wise faces in the world. If you are feeling confused even now, take a closer look at Yoda\'s picture. Here, you will find, even if not the entire face, how much its wrinkles and eyes are similar to that of Einstein!</span>\r\n<h2><b>7. The fearsome dinosaur sounds from Jurassic Park | Hollywood facts</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Of course, dinosaurs didn’t exist during the making of the movie </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jurassic Park</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which released in 1994. So, what about the frightening dinosaur sounds in the film? Some of the sounds are from tortoises mating!</span>\r\n<h3>Must Watch:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g-WSsQstq-0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>8. Aladin’s character is inspired by which Hollywood actor?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The famous animated Disney film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aladin</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> narrates the story of a princess who falls in love with a very handsome and charming Aladin. So, for the on-screen portrayal of Aladin’s character, the makers of the film turned towards Hollywood for the perfect face that could inspire the looks of the character. And reportedly, the makers built up this animated character keeping in mind the picture of legendary actor Tom Cruise.</span>\r\n<h3>Check out your Favorite Cartoon character came from:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHWJxhKQNsA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>9. A different Jack and Rose!</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We, the 90s, as well as 2000s kids, literally grew up watching the heart-warming yet tragic romance of Jack and Rose from </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Titanic.</span></i> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Can we imagine anyone other than Leonardo DiCaprio and Kate Winset playing the roles and stealing our hearts, only to leave us teary-eyed? Well, let me tell you then; before them, Gwyneth Paltrow and Mathew McConaughey were reportedly the first choices for the iconic roles of Jack and Rose.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4204 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/amazing-best-funny-Hollywood-facts-4.jpg\" alt=\"Jack and Rose!\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4201 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/amazing-best-funny-Hollywood-facts-1.jpg\" alt=\"titanic\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>10. Lady Gaga’s fear of ghosts | Hollywood facts</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anything paranormal or supernatural story or real happenings, of course, make all of us more or less shiver in fear. But are you going to sacrifice your entire earnings to overcome your fear? Well…Lady Gaga did!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from buying an expensive ghost-hunting machine, she has even spent about 40,000 pounds to hire a NASA trained chemist. She even reported the presence of Ryan around her. Where, Ryan is not any cold-blood human being, but allegedly a male ghost!. What sounds more astonishing is the fact that a team of paranormal investigators is always sent by her to venues where she is to make a visit.</span>\r\n<h2><b>11. A round of applause for the makers of </b><b><i>Theory of Everything</i></b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With all the perfect elements of inspiration, romance, science, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Theory of everything</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, showcasing the relationship of the world-famous celebrated scientist Stephen Hawking with his wife Jane Hawking and their fight against the unknown, has always been one of the favourite movies of all time. But was it making it easy? Of course not.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The screenwriter from the movie, Anthony McCarten had to spend about a span of 3 years to convince Jane Hawking to agree to this movie adaptation of her book. It took him 10 long years to finally portray the entire film on the screen. His efforts definitely deserve a round of applause!</span>\r\n<h2><b>12. Hollywood-inspired nicknames all over the world</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The famed film industry of Hollywood has been an inspiration to nicknames of various film industries in different locations around the world. Reportedly, the first Hollywood inspired nickname came in 1932 to a regional film industry of our own country, i.e., Tollywood. It is the Bengali film industry in West Bengal. Other remarkable example is Bollywood (Hindi film industry of India). In China, it is China wood (the largest film studio in China), Hogawood (the cinema world of Japan), and so on.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are some of the amazing and interesting facts about the alluring universe of Hollywood. Hope you like the content. For more of such amazing updates about the entertainment industry, subscribe to Tv Freak.</span>','11+ Amazing, Best, Crazy and Funny Hollywood facts','','publish','open','open','','11-amazing-best-crazy-and-funny-hollywood-facts','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-rated-movies-you-should-watch/','2021-02-03 19:35:12','2021-02-03 14:05:12','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=4139',0,'post','',0),(4195,12,'2021-01-28 21:42:24','2021-01-28 16:12:24','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from the COVID-19 pandemic, what 2020 observe is a series of celebrity weddings. From Indian television and Bollywood to cricket, many of our favourite stars tied wedding knots last year. Of co