ess. But soon things went between them smoothly and love blossomed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finally, on 11th November 2017, these love birds tied the knot in Italy and embarked upon the beautiful journey of married life. After almost 3 years, news of Anushka’s pregnancy made all her fans and admirers really happy.</span>\r\n<h2><b>The ‘slaying’ Anushka!</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prior to making this big declaration, Anushka and Virat had spent quite a good time with each other in the self-isolation period. And it was evident from their social media posts. From playing cricket on the terrace to enjoy with their pet dog, the pair utilized the lockdown period the most to grow closer to each other. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Through all these months, Anushka Sharma pregnancy pics ruled over the internet. We can say that this actress-producer just slew the maternity game and set goals for all the ‘going-to-be’ moms.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">My personal favourite is the one she shot with VOGUE India, the one in which she appeared as a ravishing flawless Indian beauty in a green one-piece dress. In another beautiful picture taken in a pool, we saw Anushka wearing a black jumpsuit. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The happy and content pregnancy glow in her face is worth noticing in this picture and trust me, it couldn’t be expressed in words. Anushka Sharma Instagram feed has been one of our favourites these days.</span>\r\n<h2><b>How is the soon-going-to be parents spending their time?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Speaking of Anushka’s latest Bollywood movies, as a female lead, she was last seen in 2018 Shah Rukh Khan starrer film, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Zero</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Seems like the ambitious actress for the time being has involved herself fully in building a perfect family. </span>\r\n\r\n<span