INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (4347,12,'2021-01-26 12:54:09','2021-01-26 07:24:09','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bollywood has been the safest place for star kids. Just a debut and they become a national crush. On the other hand, for most of the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/nepotism-and-favouritism-in-bollywood-star-kids-vs-outsiders/\">outsiders</a>, it’s a different scenario. Years of hard work in the industry and still not able to achieve the targeted destiny and the expected appreciation has been the fate of many talented actors and actresses.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s time when we should promote the real treasures Bollywood has. Whether star kids or outsiders, instead of just looking out for pretty faces, we should go ahead. Hence, Tv Freak presents to you a list of underrated Bollywood actors and actresses, who deserve a lot more:</span>\r\n<h2><b>Divya Dutta</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4809 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/underrated-actors-and-actresses-in-Bollywood-1.jpg\" alt=\"Divya Dutta\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Divya started her career in 1994 with the Hindi film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ishq Mein Jeena Ishq Mein Marna</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Since then, she has been cast in several significant roles in movies like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Baghban, Veer Zaara, Aaja Nachle, Special 26, Delhi 6, Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose – The Unforgettable Hero, Gippi, Badlapur, Blackmail, Traffic, Manto, Fanney Khan, Music Teacher</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Divya has always been a versatile actor in the industry and be it an art film or commercial movie, she has aced each role with so much ease.</span>\r\n<h3>A Short n Sweet movie of her:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jKyXUJceZ6k[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">