 who can’t juggle his work and family responsibilities. It also tells us how these unsung heroes work hard for the welfare of society.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4763 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/The-Family-man-2-2023.jpg\" alt=\"The Family man 2 (2021)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, the season centres around the terrorists who are linked to ISIS. They arrested these terrorists and investigated their plan, but they couldn’t stop them one of the terrorists ran away and executed the plan. After an exhausting chase of that terrorist one of the intelligence agents is relieved to find the terrorist dead, thinking that his plan of toxic gas leak foiled.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When we look a little further into this the plan was already active with the pressure of gas causing it to leak. Officers who were in the factory tried to inform this but their calls missed. They hold on till here in the last episode.</span>\r\n<h2><b>What’s next?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview, The Family Man co-creator Raj Nidimoru revealed that they had one more ending idea. In which, few of the officers would be having chai and they would also include the Indian flag at the back in the frame but the concluding scenes turned out so good that they concluded with a cliffhanger.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4762 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/The-Family-man-2-2022.jpg\" alt=\"The Family man 2 (2021)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His statement gave us a hint that they have planned a save. One of the biggest question marks after the first season is only one. It is whether they will be able to save the city people from the dangerous gas leak or not. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The director has already given hi