 couple. It was he who broke the ice and posted a mind-blowing candid snap of his wedding with her with a very romantic lovable caption, ‘Lifelong love just became official’. The happiness in the faces of the couple couldn’t be express in words.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4777 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4778 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-2.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4779 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-3.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4780 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-4.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4781 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-5.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4782 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-6.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4783 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Varun-Dhawan-Natasha-Dalal-Marriage-pics-7.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Natasha Dalal Marriage pics\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4784 size-