30-year-old actress has a good height and a weight of about 51 kgs. With her dark brown coloured hairs, dark black eyes, a perfect figure accompanied by sharp features, Pooja is the definition of a true Indian beauty</span>\r\n<h2><b>Early life</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This Mumbai-based actress and model are originally from a Punjabi family. In her teenage years, she always aspired to become ‘Miss India’. But like in any other conservative family, her desire was something that couldn’t be approved. So, Pooja completed her school education at St. Xavier’s High school.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Post that, she obtained her engineering degree in biotechnology from Dr DY Patil University. To bear her family expenses, she started to try her hands in different jobs in the corporate world. But of course, for someone who always dreamt of belonging from the glamorous world of modelling and acting, jobs such as in BPO or as a high school Biology teacher couldn’t yield satisfaction.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Dreams do come true</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While Pooja was going through this confusing phase of her career, the beauty pageant of ’<strong>Miss Queen of India</strong>’ was held. She decided to take a chance and participated in it. As destiny planned, in the year 2011, Bamrah won the pageant.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5387 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Pooja-Bamrah-wiki-___Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-3.jpg\" alt=\"Pooja Bamrah wiki ___Biography and other interesting facts (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, she was still involved with her academic career and was preparing to appear for MBA entrance examinations. It was a tough decision to leave the academic field entirely. But then, Pooja’s dream came true when she got her first fashion show with Storm Fashion and walked on the ramp.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thus, her journey began as a model. Shows after shows – she had already chosen modelling as a full-time career. Pooja admitted that she is aware of the competition and rivalry in the industry. But definitely, those things can never hold her back.</span>\r\n<h3><strong>Pooja Bhamrrah as mids queen of India 2011</strong></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=30buxaJddk0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>And then acting happened – Pooja Bhamrrah serial - Pooja Bamrah movies and TV shows</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the actress’s words, ‘I had never thought I’d take up acting.’ But again, her talent made her get the first show as a lead on Channel V’s </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Yeh Jawani Tera Riri</strong> </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">in 2014. In 2015, she was cast in the youth television series </span><strong><i>Swim Team</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which was aired on the same channel for about 1 year. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She was also seen as Vyoma in the Star Plus soap opera, </span><strong><i>Dil Sambhal Jaa Zaara</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Pooja has always looked forward to improving her acting skills and hence attended many workshops by famous actors like Neeraj Kabi, Dalip Sondhi, Chris Edmund.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KCmThBdcFh4[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From model to actor as well as anchor, life was a roller coaster ride for Pooja. Yes! You read it right. This talented actress had emerged with flying colours in the anchoring field as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She has successfully hosted several TV shows related to fashion, lifestyle, sports. These include </span><strong><i>Kabbadi World Cup, Pro Kabbadi, Lakme fashion week, Wedding Times Fashion Fiesta, Zee trendsetters</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (a Bollywood show for international viewing), and many more.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5388 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Pooja-Bamrah-wiki-___Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-4.jpg\" alt=\"Pooja Bamrah wiki ___Biography and other interesting facts (4)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This pretty actress made her Bollywood debut with a cameo appearance in the Anil Kapoor, Rajkumar Rao, Aishwariya Rai starrer Hindi film </span><strong><i>Fanney Khan </i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">which was released in the year 2018. She was playing the role of host of a reality show ‘India ki Awaz’ in the movie.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2019, she appeared in the sports movie </span><strong><i>The Zoya Factor</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, in her character of Sonali, a mischievous reporter, who can go to any extent for accomplishing her own task of attaining exclusive news.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Other works</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only on screens, but Bamrah has also given astonishing performances on stage. Yes, she has been a part of theatre as well. Her act in the play </span><strong><i>Kaun Salim Kiski Anarkali</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> received appreciation.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have also seen her in several TV commercials such as Pepe Jeans, Samsung S9, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pooja has also played a major role in the 2020 must-watch short film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rashq </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">directed by Rajiv Walia.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Pooja Bhamrrah web series – the big break</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undoubtedly, a small screen has given the actress wider recognition as she is yet to grab a major or lead role in any Bollywood movie. She has made appearances in 2 movies as of now and perfectly did the characters.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O-wqv_pL5HA[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But she got a big break and proved herself to be a good actress fit for any major role in the Alt Balaji web series </span><strong><i>Broken but Beautiful</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. She played the character of Porno, the bold, practical best friend of Samira in both seasons of the series. In the show, it seemed like the lead character of Samira, played by Harleen Sethi is so incomplete without Porno, the one who always remains there to rescue her bestie whenever she is on the verge of an emotional breakdown.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QoBpFUX6CE[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview, Pooja mentioned her liberating experience to play the character of Porno. She received lots of praise and love for the amazing portrayal of the character.</span>\r\n<h3>Season 2:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Squg0G-vqIg[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><strong>Watch Pooja Bhamrrah Glimpses From Broken But Beautiful season 2 Trailer:</strong></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qOA-OKLc9hQ[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2020, she has also been seen in the danish Alam-directed Eros Now crime thriller series </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flesh </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">which received positive reviews from critics.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Ekta Kapoor on Pooja</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekta Kapoor, the legendary producer who produced the series </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Broken But Beautiful</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> didn’t move backwards to praise Bamrah. She said that she is really a good actor. When she saw her on-screen, she got excited. She held her own.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Pooja Bhamrrah</b><b> husband</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This ravishing beauty is not dating anyone and is already married to Gurpreet Singh since February 2016. Reportedly, they married in a private ceremony at a five-star property in Bangalore. This adorable couple is very fond of travelling and Pooja Bhamra Instagram handle is a witness to it. These pictures can consider as major couple goals!</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Pooja unbelievable relationship with Massey</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pooja shares a unique familial relationship with her </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Broken But Beautiful</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> co-star Vikrant Massey. Surprisingly, they themselves were not aware of it. Pooja thought Vikrant to be her paternal cousin but actually, Vikrant, being the cousin of her Bua (father’s sister) is her uncle.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Pooja Bhamrrah on nepotism</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During an interview about her new movie </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Zoya Factor</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, Pooja was asked about her opinion about nepotism in the Bollywood industry. The actress firmly replied, ‘Star kids have their own set of challenges. But somebody like me will have to wait in line to give an audition.’</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pooja Bhamrah is a rising actress who has the potential as well as aims to be a leading actress in Bollywood one day. Her hard work, superior acting skills, energetic attitude never fail to impress the audience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. Hope you like it. For more such interesting updates about the entertainment industry, subscribe to Tv Freak.</span>','Pooja Bhamrrah, Biography, Relationships, Web Series, Movies & Tv Shows','','publish','open','open','','pooja-bhamrrah-biography-relationships-web-series-movies-tv-shows','','','2021-02-16 14:36:56','2021-02-16 09: