atch?v=iQpb1LoeVUc[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Two cops in disguise: one as a good guy, the other as a bad guy. The Departed is what you call a dynamic movie. It is also one of the best multi-star cast Hollywood movies. The movie starred a few of the strongest method actors of the time. For those who like crime thrillers and movies with cop-stories, this movie is a must-watch for them.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Awards and Nominations:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film scored 4 Oscars in the categories of Best Picture, Best Director, Best Writing (Adapted Screenplay), Best Achievement in Film Editing.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark Wahlberg was also nominated in the category: Best Actor in a Supporting Role.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Only Oscar win in Martin Scorsese\'s eminent career to this day.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Departed is a remake of the Hong Kong movie trilogy ‘</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Infernal Affairs’</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Martin Scorsese was unaware of this fact until he agreed to direct it. It is also the only Best Picture Oscar-winning film to be remade from a foreign film.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>7. Contagion (2011)</b></h2>\r\n<b>IMDb Rating: 6.7 </b>\r\n\r\n<b>Director: Steven Soderbergh (Also Directed Erin Brockovich, Traffic)</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Platform: Amazon Video, VUDU</b>\r\n<h3><b>Star Cast:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gwyneth Paltrow</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Matt Damon</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">John Hawkes</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jude Law</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Laurence Fishburne</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marion Cotillard</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kate Winslet</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jennifer Ehle</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bryan Cranston</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Elliott Gould</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4sYSyuuLk5g[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, in this worldwide catastrophic situation, no movie can be more suitable than Contagion. Contagion manifests a world that is infected by a virus (not so different from the Corona) that forces a pandemic across the globe.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie did not get much response when it was released. But in 2020, due to the COVID19 situation, it became one of the most popular and discussed movies of that year mostly because of the reality it represents.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The star cast of this movie consists of 5 Oscar winners and 5 Oscar Nominees.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>6. The Expendables (2010, 2012, 2014)</b></h2>\r\n<b>IMDb Rating: 6.4 (Average)</b>\r\n<h3><b>Directors:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li aria-level=\"1\"><b> Sylvester Stallone (Also Directed Rocky (2, 3 &amp; 4) and Rambo)</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li aria-level=\"1\"><b> Simon West (Also Directed Con Air, Lara Croft: Tomb Raider)</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li aria-level=