: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cary Elwes (Westley from The Princess Bride)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Common (Yes, the Oscar-winning Rapper)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jessica Biel</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seth Meyers</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sarah Paulson</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Katherine Heigl</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jon Bon Jovi (The man who sang It’s my life)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sofia Vergara</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ashton Kutcher</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sarah Jessica Parker</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Abigail Breslin (Played Little Rock in Zombieland)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Josh Duhamel</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hilary Swank</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ludacris (The Rapper)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nat Wolf</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h_dt27_0vL4[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s a film with a very simple plotline about people making New Year\'s resolutions and their endeavour to spend special and happy occasions with their loved ones. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">New Year’s Eve is a feel-good movie. It is also the best-suited movie to watch on the New Year.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Halle Berry, Michelle Pfeiffer and Anna Hathaway— all of them played the role of Catwoman at some point in their career.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>3. Valentine’s Day (2010)</b></h2>\r\n<b>IMDb Rating: 5.7</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Director: Garry Marshall</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Platform: Sling TV</b>\r\n<h3><b>Star Cast:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jessica Alba</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kathy Bates</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jessica Biel</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bradley Cooper</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Eric Dane</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Patrick Dempsey</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hector Elizondo</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jamie Foxx</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jennifer Garner</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Topher Grace</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anne Hathaway</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 4