ory of eight different couples who are somehow connected one way or another.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Again, the greatness of this movie lies in the simplicity of its plot. This movie tells the story of not one but several happy endings in the most non-cynical way possible.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keira Knightley was only 18 years old when she played in this movie.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the debut film by Richard Curtis as a director.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is a short film spin-off of this movie created as a </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comic_Relief\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Red Nose Day</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> project. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>1. Ocean’s Trilogy (2001, 2004, 2007)</b></h2>\r\n<b>IMDb Rating: 7.03 (Average)</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Director: Steven Soderbergh</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Platform: HBO Max</b>\r\n<h3><b>Star Cast:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">George Clooney</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bernie Mac</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Brad Pitt</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Matt Damon</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Andy Garcia</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Elliott Gould</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don Cheadle</span></li>\r\