i starrer movies.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts: </b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This trilogy is actually a remake of the original Ocean’s 11 where Frank Sinatra played the role ‘Danny Ocean’.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don Cheadle is uncredited in Ocean\'s Eleven despite having a major role.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, what do you think about this list? Which of the titles do you think is the best, let me know in the comment box.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Happy Watching!!!</span>','7+ Non-Superhero Hollywood Movies with Huge Multi-Star Cast','','publish','open','open','','hollywood-movies-with-huge-multi-star-cast','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/hollywoods-top-10-feel-good-movies-you-must-watch/','2021-02-11 22:21:47','2021-02-11 16:51:47','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=4792',0,'post','',0),(4905,12,'2021-01-27 19:17:15','2021-01-27 13:47:15','<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4909 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vidyut-Jammwal-Rukmini-Maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak-3.jpg\" alt=\"Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller! sanak (3)\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" /></h2>\r\n<h2><b>Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller! | Sanak</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Popular Bengali actress <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/rukmini-maitra-biography-age-boyfriend-photos-and-movies/\">Rukmini Maitra</a>, known for regional movies like Cockpit, Champ, Kidnap, Password is soon going to be seen in Bollywood. She is going to share the big screen with none other than the super charming action hero, the rising star of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/bollywood/\">Hindi films</a>, Vidyut Jamal in the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/trailers/\">upcoming Bollywood movie </a></span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sanak: HOPE UNDER SIEGE.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>The shared posters</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4907 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vidyut-Jammwal-Rukmini-Maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller! sanak (3)\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The announcement of the movie was made on 25</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> January. Its poster was shared by VJ on his Instagram handle with the caption ‘SANAKNA Zaroori Hai, coming tomorrow!’. It gave an indication that more posters will be surfaced soon. The same day film critic and trade analyst, Taran Adarsh shared the same poster and tweeted about the upcoming action thriller. The poster shows a blood-stained hospital bed with a gun on it.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4908 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vidyut-Jammwal-Rukmini-Maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak-2.jpg\" alt=\"Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller!\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On Republic Day, more three posters were released which ruled over the internet. In each of these posters, we witnessed the actor in different positions. The first poster is of a trapped Vidyut, surrounded by 2 or 3 face-covered goons. In the 2</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nd</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> poster, the actor is seen in the pose of an action sequence, firing a gun, while two other goons at the back were pointing their guns toward him. The 3</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">rd</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> poster features a picture of Vidyut pointing his index finger towards the viewers.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from these, no other actors from the movie are seen in the poster. Fans are now eagerly waiting for the teaser and trailer to be released.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Genre and storyline of the emotional action thriller Sanak</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, This is a Vipul Amrutlal Shah Production. This film is expected to be a super-duper action thriller with some elements of love and emotion. But we are still not exactly sure about which specific genre it will belong to. Much has not been revealed by the makers.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secondly, Regarding the storyline, let’s make a wild guess! It can be a spy film and VJ will be seen playing the character of a spy. As the name and the poster indicates, it can also be the escape story of military personnel trapped in a siege.</span>\r\n<h2><b>The director</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kanishk Verma has directed this upcoming action thriller Sanak. As a director, he is only 2-movies old. He made his directorial debut with Gulshan Devaiah starrer psychological thriller film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Footfairy</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in 2020. It hasn’t been much appreciated by critics. Hence, we hope that the director is going to give his best and yield a unique, outstanding work this time which will not fail to impress the audience as well as critics.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Who all-stars in the movie_Sanak cast</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4910 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vidyut-Jammwal-Rukmini-Maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak-4.jpg\" alt=\"Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller! \" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The pretty model turned Bengali actress Rukmini Maitra is going to make her grand Bollywood debut with this action-packed movie opposite VJ. He will be seen as the central character of course. Apart from this Neha Dhupia and Chandan Roy Sanyal will be reportedly seen in important roles. Neha was last seen in the 2018 movie </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Helicopter Eela</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and the 2020 short film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Devi</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Roy Sanyal is known for films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rang De Basanti, Ganesh Talkies, Jaazba, Jab Harry Met Sejal, Chef</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4911 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Vidyut-Jammwal-Rukmini-Maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak-5.jpg\" alt=\"Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller! sanak (3) cast\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After performances in movies like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Force, Commando series, Khuda Hafiz,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> it’s not wrong to set high expectations from Jammwal. Rukmini has also repeatedly proven her good acting skills in Bengali movies. Multiple talents combining together, we are expecting a well-made non-cringy, realistic, intense, thrilling, worth watching blockbuster Bollywood action film. All our heartiest wishes to team </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sanak</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for their soon-to-be-released project.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finally, this was the content for today. Hope you like it. For more such interesting updates about the entertainment industry, subscribe to <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Tv Freak</a>.</span>','Vidyut Jammwal, Rukmini Maitra to star in action thriller | Sanak','','publish','open','open','','vidyut-jammwal-rukmini-maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak','','','2021-02-06 21:27:53','202