lass=\"aligncenter wp-image-4962 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/2-7.jpg\" alt=\"College Romance Season 2 scene\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The season finale witnessed the reunion of their bonds. Trippy’s relationship with his girlfriend Naira grew stronger when she chose him over her ex-boyfriend. Karan and his love interest, a dominating Deepika despite going with different individuals on a date to a pub ended up with each other, though not very sure about their relationship status.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Naira and his boyfriend Bagga also ended their fights and embraced each other with a kiss. In the last scene, the squad was being chased by a police car which had been summoned by Naira’s mischievous ex, Anshuman. And once again they were overcoming the obstacle unitedly and joyfully. The season ended there.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since then, after eagerly waiting for more than 2 years, Season 2 is here to lighten up our monotonous days.</span>\r\n<h2><b>IMDB Rating</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The series has an IMDB rating of<strong> 8.9 </strong>out of 10.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>College Romance Season 2 official Trailer Launch</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">College Romance Season 2 </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">official trailer was launched on the 15</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of January, 2021, almost 2 weeks back. In it we again witnessed the drama and fun of the gang’s college life.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obdU7vvafEI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>What we witnessed in the trailer?</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4963 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/3-7.jpg\" alt=\"College Romance Season 2 scene love birds\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Raveena and Trippy had most probably broken up due to their long-distance relationship. Karan and Deepika as well as Naira and Bagga are also facing problems in their relationships. Friendship has come in the way of love. All will again pass the test of time. We are eager to see how things survive in all such situations as the squad creates some best lifetime memories.</span>\r\n<h2><b>College Romance Season 2</b><b> release date</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The new season is already here. It’s released today itself i.e., 29</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of January, 2021 on the highly recommended OTT platform Sony Liv.</span>\r\n<h2><b>College Romance season 2</b><b> cast and crew</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Its cast of the show consists of the familiar faces we witnessed in the previous season. Manjot Singh, Keshav Sadhna, Apoorva Arora, Gagan Arora, Shreya Mehta are seen slaying again in their respective roles of Trippy, Karan, Naira, Bagga, and Deepika.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from these, we have spectated a few new faces in the trailer. But you will get to know more of this extended cast only once you go and see the season.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This season has been directed by the </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flames </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Engineering girls</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> fame Apoorv Singh Karki. Writing credits for such an amazing script of this season goes to Sidhant Mago, Aakash Ahuja, and Manan Madan. The music, the soothing background scores have been given by Tushar Mallek in this season. Lastly, the 5 episodes have been produced by Arunabh Kumar, Vijay Koshi, and Shreyansh Pandey.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13QjV3SoZ0c[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Where to watch this Hindi web series online? _ Watch </b><b>College Romance Season 2</b><b> online</b></h2>\r\nAs the series has already released you can watch it on Sony Liv. In the case of College Romance S2 download, you can do so on the platform and then watch it. It is also available on the Telegram app but due to copyright issues, it may get deleted soon.\r\n<h2><b>Queries about </b><b>College Romance</b></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Is College Romance on Netflix? </span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As mentioned earlier, Netflix has picked the 1</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">st</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> season of this series after it gained popularity. But the second season is streaming on only SonyLiv and the Timeliners only and is still not available on Netflix.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Where was College Romance shot?</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to sources, a major part of College Romance is being shot at the Echelon Institute of Technology, Faridabad. Surrounding this college, all the ups and downs occur in their lives. Some parts are shot in other locations like different pubs which are clearly not known to us. Echelon Institute of Technology is one of the best institutes in India for pursuing engineering.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgMPc7GV95Y[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>College Romance Season 2 Reviews So Far</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The new season has somewhat not failed to receive positive responses and reviews. For some, it is a one-time watch and fails to attain the season 1 level. Some have described it as the perfect portrayal of friendships and heartbreaks, leading to the development of an emotional connection with the characters.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whatever be the case, we can ensure that the new episodes are not going to dishearten you at all, and if you are a college student yourself no one can stop you from loving it. Regarding the story of this season, we are not revealing anything as those may act as spoilers for you. Still waiting for what, go and give it a watch ASAP.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. Hope you like it. For more such interesting updates about the entertainment industry, subscribe to <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Tv Freak.</a></span>','College Romance Season 2 Released | Trailer, Cast & Story | Watch Online','','publish','open','open','','college-romance-season-2-released-trailer-cast-story-watch-here','','','2021-03-15 09:18:13','2021-03-15 03:48:13','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=4958',0,'post','',0),(4996,13,'2021-01-31 16:07:34','2021-01-31 10:37:34','<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2020 has been a bad year for most of us. COVID-19 tore us apart, we faced losses in both our personal and professional lives, California and Australia caught wildfire. So let’s take a look at some of the best Netflix Original <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-hollywood-movies-of-2020-that-you-cant-afford-miss/\">Hollywood Movies of 2020</a>. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We lost many talented artists, many of the long-waited movie releases got postponed and whatnot. But amid all these negativities of 2020, Netflix has been a platform of many original contents, documentaries and it has allowed quite a few talented directors to make their directorial debut.</span>\r\n\r\nLet\'s start\r\n<h2>27. To All the Boys: P.S. I Still Love You</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.0</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Michael Fimognari</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Lana Condor, Noah Centineo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5025 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-1.jpg\" alt=\"Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is the first sequel of the trilogy. The tale goes on with Lara and Peter just getting in an official serious relationship but a former love interest comes into the scene to make things a mess. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To All the Boys: P.S. I Still Love You shows a complex side of Young adult love, that it is hard to pick the right person while going through all the emotional challenges. It also has been one of the best romantic Hollywood movies on Netflix in 2020.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To the fans of this movie <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/series/\">series</a>, good news for you. The third and final sequel of this movie: To All the Boys: Always and Forever is coming this February.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIU4xb61PHc[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>26. Rebecca</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.0</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Ben Wheatley (Also Directed High-Rise)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Armie Hammer, Lily James</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5027 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-3.jpg\" alt=\"Rabecca Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Rebecca is the story of a woman whose husband is still romantically haunted by his late wife\'s ghost. Rebecca is the name of the ghost wife by the way.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Adaptation of the 1938s classic novel by Dame Daphne du Maurier, Rebecca is one of the new Hollywood movies that is a remake of the Alfred Hitchcock directed 1940s masterpiece movie.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Though the movie could not live up to the 1940s version’s reputation, it was nonetheless a highlight among the Netflix originals of 2020.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LFVhB54UqvQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>25. Uncorked | Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.2</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Prentice Penny</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Courtney B. Vance, Lashun Pollard, Michael Mobley</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5028 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-4.jpg\" alt=\"Uncorked Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (4)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uncorked portrays a reality many of us have to face in our lives.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is a story of a young black male who had to face parental disappointment to pursue his dream to be a wine waiter. With some upbeat music and a positive attitude, this movie is very easy to enjoy and very easy to relate to real life.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TAs2cEY4fhI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>24. Murder to Mercy: The Cyntoia Brown Story</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Daniel H. Birman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5026 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-2.jpg\" alt=\"Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (2) Murder to Mercy: The Cyntoia Brown Story\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">First Documentary on this list. This documentary movie tells the story of Cyntoia Brown who was charged with murder in 2004 in the court of Tennessee. A girl who could not escape the fate of her mother and went to prison at the age of 16.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What you will see in this documentary is how the outlook of law changes with time. In 2004, this teenage girl was convicted as a murderer who was a prostitute and drug addict. But today the scenery could have been different.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eb2Ce6mj-iI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>23. All the Bright Places | Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Brett Haley</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Elle Fanning, Justice Smith, Kelli O\'Hara</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5029 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-5.jpg\" alt=\"All the Bright Places Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (5)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">All the Bright Places is one of the latest Hollywood movies covering the Young Adult genre.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Finch is a boy with an abusive father, an absent mother, and cursed with depression, and loneliness.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Violet is the girl suffering from the loss of her sister and the guilt of survival. When these two people find each other in an unexpected moment, they discover that it is possible to find comfort and help in the presence of one another. </span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is the first feature film for Elle Fanning to get a producer credit.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfQXKVCudec[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>22. All Together Now</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Brett Haley</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Auli\'i Cravalho, Rhenzy Feliz, Justina Machado</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5030 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-6.jpg\" alt=\"All Together Now Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It’s like Murphy\'s law—\"Anything that can go wrong will go wrong\". Amber is a high school teenager who is suffering from both financial and emotional problems. She possesses a love for drama and music that she wants to pursue but her current conditions are letting her down. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“All Together Now” is a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-15-movies-on-friendship-that-you-must-watch/\">movie about the strength of friendship</a>. That, in the darkest and hardest times, there can be a ray of hope if you have good enough friends that care about you.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-BryKyM9u9E[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>21. Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: David Dobkin (Also Directed Wedding Crashers, The Change-Up, The Judge)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Will Ferrell, Rachel McAdams, Pierce Brosnan, Demi Lovato, Graham Norton.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5031 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-7.jpg\" alt=\"Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lars and Sigrit are two childhood friends from a small town in Iceland who have dreams to win the Eurovision Song Contest. This movie will teach you any dream is worth pursuing no matter how much struggle you have to go through. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">For those who don’t know, Eurovision Song Contest is a real-life competition program generally featuring European countries. This very movie uses this contest as a platform to show the story of two music lovers who have dreams to prove themselves.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Among the Netflix comedies\' new releases, Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga is undoubtedly one of the top-ranked movies. </span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pierce Brosnan played Will Ferrell’s father in this movie. In real life, Pierce is only 13 years older than Will.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7q6Co-nd0lM[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>20. Da 5 Bloods | Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Spike Lee (Also Directed Malcolm X, Inside Man, BlacKkKlansman)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Delroy Lindo, Jonathan Majors, Clarke Peters, Jean Reno, Chadwick Boseman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5032 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Da 5 Bloods Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A group of four soldiers goes on an adventure to rescue the gold their squad captain has hidden in the landscape of Vietnam. But the amount of rich may stray them from their way, ethics and even make them doubt one another.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da 5 Blood is one of the greatest crime actions in Netflix movies of 2020.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">My personal recommendation:</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> If you like this movie, I suggest you watch </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Blood Diamond</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (If you have not watched it already). The movie starred Leonardo DiCaprio, Djimon Hounsou, Jennifer Connelly, and was directed by Edward Zwick.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Facts:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This movie is the debut of director Spike Lee as a Feature Film on 