https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-5-1.jpg Copy URL to clipboard Smush 3 images reduced by 620.0 B (0.9%) Image size: 34.9 KB View Stats ATTACHMENT DISPLAY SETTINGS Alignment None Link To Custom URL URL http:// Size Medium – 300 × 240 Selected media actions 1 item selected Clear Insert into post\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Extraction was the 2020s one of the most expected action movies. It was also one of the most-watched movies on Netflix 2020. The movie is directed by Sam Hargrave, who previously worked as <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-movies-of-chris-evans-except-mcu/\">Chris Evans’s</a> stunt double in the MCU movies. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The plot of the movie is not very unique and does not dip in too deep. But the movie is visually satisfying when it comes to the action sequences.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is the debut film of Sam Hargrave as a director.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L6P3nI6VnlY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>15. Becoming</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Nadia Hallgren</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Barack Obama, Michelle Obama, Oprah Winfrey</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5037 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Becoming Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Another documentary in this list, this film is based on the book tour of the book ‘Becoming’ written by the former first lady Michelle Obama. The movie simply highlights the insights of how Michelle Obama connects with people, her naturality, hope, and ambition.</span>\r\n<h3>Awards and Nominations:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This documentary feature was nominated for 4 Primetime Emmys.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wePNJGL7nDU[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>14. The Boys in the Band | Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Joe Mantello</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Jim Parsons, Zachary Quinto, Matt Bomer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5038 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-7-1.jpg\" alt=\"The Boys in the Band Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (7)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The story of this movie starts with a party that leads to a massacre and ends with a lot of confessions about past loves. A group of gay men of the late 60s forthcoming with the feelings and reliving the friendship and love.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">‘The Boy in the Band’ is a remake of a 1970s movie that goes by the same name. The movie starred Jim Parsons whom you may know as </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sheldon Cooper</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> from the sitcom</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> The Big Bang Theory.</span></i>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=862Pb9oDDAo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>13. Hillbilly Elegy</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.7</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Ron Howard (Also Directed Apollo 13, A Beautiful Mind, Cinderella Man, Rush)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Amy Adams, Glenn Close, Freida Pinto</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5039 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-8.jpg\" alt=\"Hillbilly Elegy\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hillbilly Elegy is a true story of J.D. Vance about his tragic family life, a drug-addicted mother, and sad childhood.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Though the movie mostly reflects the struggles and troubles J.D. Vance has to go through growing up because of all the family melodrama, I would like to say, it is also a story of a mother who failed herself and her children repetitively because of irresponsibility. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The skillful acting of the stars in this movie takes this movie to another level. So there is no denying that Hillbilly Elegy is one of the best Hollywood movies of 2020.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is director Ron Howard’s first time working together with a female cinematographer.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PrlmlDWu5ag[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>12. The Half of It</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 6.9</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Alice Wu (Also Directed Saving Face)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Leah Lewis, Daniel Diemer, Alexxis Lemire</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5040 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-9.jpg\" alt=\"Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (9) The Half of It\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In a small town like Squahamish, Ellie chu is a girl who is smart and different. She writes essays for other people in exchange for money. But one day a boy in her school comes to her demanding writing a love letter for cash. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Half of it is a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">romantic comedy-drama</a>. But that’s not half of it. The story of this movie is different and soothing which makes it one of the best Netflix original movies in 2020.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The whole idea behind this movie is about finding and accepting oneself, accepting new friendships in life, and realizing the impact of it.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B-yhF7IScUE[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>11. Enola Holmes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.6</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Harry Bradbeer</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Millie Bobby Brown, Henry Cavill, Sam Claflin, Helena Bonham Carter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5041 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-10.jpg\" alt=\" Enola Holmes Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (10)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Enola Holmes was one of the popular movies of 2020.</span></i>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The name ‘Enola’ comes from writing backward the word ‘Alone’. Now, why would a mother name her daughter with such a word? Does she want to curse her with loneliness? No, it is to mean that Enola will be alright when she is alone and on her own. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Many of the audience of this movie got disappointed. To those, I want to say, this is not a canonical Sherlock Holmes movie. The plot is written by Nancy Springer and this story is solely focused on Enola Holmes, not the Holmes brother. This movie manifests feminism in a way that I have never seen before.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The movie is set in 1884 but Eudora Holmes is a mother who is way ahead of her time. We need mothers like her in every family to raise wonderful children of the future. Also, the ‘breaking the fourth wall’ scenes in the movies are really enjoyable.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Though Sam Claflin played Mycroft in this movie, In real life he is younger than Henry Cavill who plays Sherlock in this movie.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1d0Zf9sXlHk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>10. The Devil All the Time</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Antonio Campos</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Bill Skarsgard, Tom Holland, Sebastian Stan, Robert Pattinson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5042 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">When you are seeing signs in everything, it is hard to detect if it is either from God or it was the devil all the time. PTSD from war, religious blindness, cringe-worthy violence are just some ingredients of this film. But Tom Holland’s acting was at a remarkable level in this film.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you want to experience how much of a good and color-changing actor Tom Holland is, you need to watch this movie. Also, you need to watch this movie because it is one of the top-rated Hollywood thriller movies of 2020.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Facts:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This movie is co-produced by Jake Gyllenhaal. </span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Though Tom Holland is one of the highest-paid actors in this film, he does not appear in the first 46 minutes of it.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6XoWOUgCpo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>9. Mank | Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: David Fincher (Se7en, Fightclub, Gone Girl, and <i> many other amazing movies</i>)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Gary Oldman, Amanda Seyfried, Lily Collins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5043 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Mank\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Mank is a biographical movie about Herman J. Mankiewicz. If you do not know who </span>Mank<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">iewicz is, he was a famous movie critic and screenplay writer. He won the Academy Award in 1942 for Best Writing (Original Screenplay) for the film Citizen Kane.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">He also wrote the screenplays of The Wizard of Oz and The Pride of the Yankees. This movie manifests Mank’s writing progression of the timeless movie Citizen Kane.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We all know David Fincher from making hardcore thriller action movies. Mank on the contrary is a well-made drama-comedy that was appreciated by the critics and loved by the audience. So it is one of the best to watch Hollywood of 2020.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Facts:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Script of this film is written by the late Jack Fincher, David Fincher’s father.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This film honorably took place in Barack Obama’s favorite movie list.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The entire film is made in Black and White.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aSfX-nrg-lI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>8. American Murder: The Family Next Door</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.2</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Jenny Popplewell</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5044 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"American Murder: The Family Next Door\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This crime documentary features the murder of the Watts family. In 2018 the husband of the family Christopher Watts killed his pregnant wife and four-year-old daughter by himself in  Frederick, Colorado.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This film is made of archive footage. You will feel how vicious and frightening it can become when the person who vowed to protect you turns against you.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ep8iKiQNSrY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>7. The Forty-Year-Old Version</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.2</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Radha Blank</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Radha Blank, Peter Kim, Oswin Benjamin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5045 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-4-2.jpg\" alt=\"The Forty-Year-Old Version Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (4)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Yeah, don’t confuse the title with Steve Carrel’s The 40-Year-Old Virgin. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Forty-Year-Old Version is the story of a black woman in her late thirties named Radha Blank.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Radha was a rising star in her youth. She was awarded some 30 under 30 awards for writing plays. But lately, there have been no remarkable highlights in her career. When everyone around her is biased with racism and sexism, Radha thrived to go through a breakthrough by choosing a new way.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The whole movie is very entertaining. With high-level sarcasm and drama, this movie is one of the best Netflix original movies in 2020.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is Radha Blank’s debut movie.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RRpGNnaDzeE[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>6. Miss Americana</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.4</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Lana Wilson</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Taylor Swift</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5046 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-5-2.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Americana\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Miss Americana is a biographical documentary film about the iconic pop star and America’s sweetheart Taylor Swift.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> From </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Taylor Swift</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lover,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Taylor Swift has gifted us with 7 of her amazing albums. And this movie unleashes the transformation and progression of her talent, appreciation for her works, with life challenging moments along with the poisonous internet culture she has and is still suffering from.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">I won’t be exaggerating if I say, Americana will take you on an emotional journey.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q07_k5VKuaQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>5. Ma Rainey\'s Black Bottom</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: George C. Wolfe</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Viola Davis, Chadwick Boseman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5047 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-6-2.jpg\" alt=\"Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (6) Ma Rainey\'s Black Bottom\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Though IMDb did not include biography as a main genre for this film, the main character of this film, </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ma_Rainey\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ma Rainey</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, was a real-life r&amp;b singer. The movie shows a recording event of Ma Rainey and her bandmates that gradually turns into chaos and disaster. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2020 was a very unfortunate year for us. And one of the most unrecoverable losses we had to go through is the death of Chadwick Boseman. So watching this movie will be an emotional ride.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This film is produced by Denzel Washington.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The last movie by Chadwick Boseman. He left the world of living on August 28, 2020, after fighting an exhausting 4-year cancer. Rest in Peace.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ord7gP151vk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>4. Athlete A</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.7</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Bonni Cohen, Jon Shenk</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Maggie Nichols, Gina Nichols, John Nichols</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5048 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-7-2.jpg\" alt=\"Athlete A: Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (7)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">When I say this is a sports-crime documentary, I say it’s not a typical sports crime like the ones we read in the newspaper. It’s not a film about drug usages, match-fixing, or any of that sort.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is a story about a sexual predator who hides in the pure daylight by disguising himself as a national gymnastic team doctor. What’s so horrifying is that there is no way to identify these people before they get involved in crimes that will scar their victims for life.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JzeP0DKSqdQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>3. Crip Camp</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: James Lebrecht, Nicole Newnham</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5049 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Crip Camp\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Another documentary on this list. The real name of Crip Camp is Camp Jened. This film simply exhibits how a simple camp for the disabled becomes a utopia for the disabled spirits.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Influenced by many aspects, culture, and views, Crip Camp tells the story of how a camp became a positive activist and how it provides encouragement to those whose life has let themselves down.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XRrIs22plz0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>2. The Trial of the Chicago 7</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Aaron Sorkin (Also Directed Molly\'s Game)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Eddie Redmayne, Sacha Baron Cohen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5050 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"The Trial of the Chicago 7\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The story is set up in the late 60s. 7 men were arrested on the accusation of initiating a rebellion where they were simply protesting a convention. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Trial of the Chicago 7 was one of the most top-rated and highlighted features of 2020. That is why it is on the list of ‘ the best movies on Netflix Top 10’.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you liked this movie, I suggest you watch the mini TV series When They See Us.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FVb6EdKDBfU[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>1. A Secret Love</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.9</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Chris Bolan</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Terry Donahue, Pat Henschel, Diana Bolan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5051 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-10-1.jpg\" alt=\"A Secret Love: Top Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020 (10)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A Secret Love is a coming-of-age story of Terry Donahue and Pat Henschel about how their love survived for more than 70 years keeping it a secret.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Love bloomed between two women in 1947 when homosexuality was regarded as deviance, a disorder, and a crime. But their love lasted forever until death made them apart. This is the main theme of A Secret Love.</span>\r\n<h3>Fun Fact:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This film is produced by Ryan Murphy.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ghv3-lpFOcc[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>Conclusion:</h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">So this was the 2020s top Netflix original Hollywood movie. Let us know which ones have you seen and liked the most in the comment box below.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Happy Watching!!!</span>','Top 27 Netflix Original Hollywood Movies of 2020','','publish','open','open','','top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/best-movies-of-chris-evans-except-mcu/','2021-10-03 13:07:15','2021-10-03 07:37:15','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=4996',0,'post','',0),(5055,12,'2021-02-06 21:26:22','2021-02-06 15:56:22','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5127 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/750x600.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra from Sanak | Biography and other Interesting Facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An active face in the Bengali film industry, Rukmini Maitra, is soon going to step into the glamorous world of Bollywood. She has been cast and is a part of the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/vidyut-jammwal-rukmini-maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak/\">upcoming Hindi film SANAK</a> – Hope Under siege. Let us take a detailed close look at Rukmini Maita biography, her life journey, significant works, and other interesting facts.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra Biography: Birth, Family, and Education</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5149 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1.jpg\" alt=\"Mother\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maitra is from a humble, non-filmy Bengali family in Kolkata. She came into the world as a girl child born to the IIM gold medallist, Late Soumyendra Mitra and his wife Madhumita Maitra on 27 June 1991. Back then nobody had ever guessed the mark she is going to set in the alluring world of modelling and cinema.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5150 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2.jpg\" alt=\"family\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra completed her school education at a convent institution in Kolkata. Being the granddaughter of renowned chief justice, BN Maitra, she aspired to be a lawyer during her school days. She pursued under graduation from Kolkata’s Loretto College. After that, she attained her MBA degree from Kozhikode’s IIM.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra Age, Height, and Physique</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This actress is currently 29 years old and will enter her 30s soon. But due to her bubbly nature and intact glow on face, it’s quite hard to guess her age. With a fair complexion, black hair, and brown eyes she is the true epitome of a Bengali beauty. Her height is somewhere between 5’6” and 5’9” which is the perfect height when it comes to modelling.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Path of Modelling</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maitra is the perfect example of beauty with brains. Besides continuing her studies, Maitra also started modelling at a very young age when she was just in standard VIII. Since then, she didn’t look back and worked hard to establish her firm foothold in the modelling industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She has worked with several popular brands including Lakme, Parachute, Vodafone, Reliance, Sunsilk, PC Chandra Jewellers, Titan, Senco Gold, etc. Apart from these, we have overwhelmingly witnessed this stunning beauty getting featured on covers of famous magazines such as Sananda and Femina Bangla.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5151 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra from Sanak | Biography family\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only photoshoots but also as a model Rukmini successfully slew the ramp game several times. Besides walking the ramp for various fashion shows, she did the same for illustrious fashion designers like Masaba Gupta, Anju Modi, Anita Dongre.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5152 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5153 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra Movies: Journey in Tollywood</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After becoming successful as a model, Rukmini embarked upon her acting journey by doing films in her mother tongue. Her first film, opposite Bengali superstar Dev, was a sports movie Chaamp which surrounds the backdrop of boxing. It had a theatre release during the festival of Eid in 2017.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5154 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/6.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch Rukmini Maitra Cockpit</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_WVnutAftY[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini and Dev in an interview about Chaamp</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1vAA3q-DWU8[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch her romancing co-star Dev in the song Jaya Tomari from Champ</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5iZU2jYIieQ[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the same year, she grabbed the female lead of another Bengali adventure movie Cockpit where she was seen as an air hostess. In the film, as a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/successful-self-made-bollywood-stars-who-had-no-root-in-industry/\">newcomer</a>, her acting skills received much appreciation despite the presence of other much more experienced lead actors like Dev and Koel Mallik.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As of now, Rukmini is 6-movies old which is not bad as a number, that too just within a span of 4 years. Five of her movies, including Chaamp, Cockpit, Kabir, Kidnap, and Password are with her co-star Dev.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Her last movie, a family drama in, Switzerland was released during Diwali 2020. It was opposite the charming Bengali actor, Abir Chatterjee. Throughout her acting career till now, she has one various challenging roles which diversified her horizons as an actress and proved her to be a versatile artist of present times.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5155 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/7.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5156 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Switzerland trailer Official Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vKOYTVWmok[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5157 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/9.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h3><strong>Rukmini in Kabir trailer:</strong></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XSa0XSKM0QU[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from movies, if you ask about Rukmini Maitra TV series, she has not made any such appearances in any TV show or such videos.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra Awards and Nominations: Appreciations are always in the basket of Rukmini</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nominated for various categories in different award shows, Rukmini often impressed her fans and admirers by winning them. From being the best debut (female) for movies like Champ and Cockpit to being the recipient of awards like Most Promising Actress 2018 and many more, she always stole the .limelight.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra Upcoming Movies: Bollywood Debut</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After her success in the regional film industry, the pride of Bengal, Rukmini Maitra is all set to make her grand Bollywood debut. It is opposite Khuda Haafiz actor Vidyut Jammwal in the upcoming action-packed Bollywood movie, SANAK: Hope Under Siege.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Its teaser posters have already surfaced and now the audience is eagerly waiting to welcome this new prettiest face, the house of talent, Rukmini Maitra in the Hindi film industry.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Relationship Status</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is rumoured that Maitra is dating none other than her co-star, Dev for a long time. Reportedly, they have met sometime back in the 1st decade of 2000 when the actress was just a student of class X. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra and Dev, both reportedly have tattoos of their rumoured lovers’ names in their respective hands. Despite this, they have always avoided speaking of their relationship status or love life publicly. Though they are often seen in each other’s Instagram posts, such posts and captions are very professional and don’t give a glimpse of their relationship.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5158 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/10.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra boyfriend\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini once mentioned that the word ‘Dev’ instilled in her hand refers to ‘God’, implying it has no connection with her rumoured boyfriend.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, we are quite sure that the pair has a special bond. Whatever be the fact, they look Charming and adorable together, and they are often spotted in public with each other. They are probably the most talked-about celebrity couple in Bengal.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if Rukmini Starred in Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi, opposite SRK?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes, you read it right! The actress in an interview made this surprising revelation that she had been asked to do the female lead in the 2008 romantic movie, Rab Ne Bana di Jodi. But she was still in school at that time in class XI and wanted to focus on her studies, thus declining the offer.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If she had done the movie, maybe we would have a completely different Rukmini Mitra’s journey to narrate.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A good dancer too!</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maitra never fails to impress us when it comes to dancing too. In this context, let’s mention the incident when during the shoot of her last movie Switzerland, she was spotted perfectly grooving along with her co-star Abir Chatterjee on a terrace for the film’s party sequence.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Niece Amira</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5159 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a girl, Rukmini seems to be very family-oriented and the person whom she adores the most in her family is none other than her cutest little niece Amira, the daughter of her brother Rahul. She often posts her pictures and videos on social media.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rukmini Maitra is undoubtedly a very talented actress who has the potential to rule Indian films. With talent she has successfully made herself a leading actress in Tollywood; now Bollywood awaits her. Her superior acting skills have the ability to give competition to famous actresses from the Bolly town too.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is now a matter of time with which we can witness her new heights of success. We are pleased to give you enough information about Rukmini Maita age, husband, boyfriend, family, works, and other such interesting facts.</span>\r\n<h2>Feeling Bored While reading, Let\'s watch it all:</h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UQ3vW8Esuks[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We always publish articles on interesting celebs. This is to let you know the hard work they did, the problems they faced also what they achieve. You will find interesting stuff as well like movies to watch that are on any other platform. Wish you have a happy reading!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also check all the Bollywood and English recent trailers on our page. Also, you can go to the biography section. There, you can check all the best sports biography, top War Biography, best films on real-life rich people, and many more. There is a section for Novels as well. Everybody loves to watch movies based on novels. So we have created all the categories like War, romantic, spy, sci-fi movies based on novels.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. We will soon come up with new updates and entertaining news about the film industry. Till then, have a safe and nice time. See you in the next article.</span>','Rukmini Maitra | Biography, Age, Boyfriend, Photos, Awards and Movies','','publish','open','open','','rukmini-maitra-biography-age-boyfriend-photos-and-movies','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/vidyut-jammwal-rukmini-maitra-to-star-in-action-thriller-sanak/','2021-02-14 20:08:55','2021-02-14 14:38:55','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5055',0,'post','',0),(5113,9,'2021-02-14 14:06:07','2021-02-14 08:36:07','<h2>Introduction</h2>\r\nSo the past couple of years realized that <a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/in/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Netflix</a> is a platform worth binging. Asides from being the support system of so many renowned shows in one place, it has now a support system for many great Indie movies and films over the years.\r\n\r\nSo I thought to myself, why not I make a list of some of the best independent <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/\">movies on Netflix</a>. Note that these movies have low IMDB ratings but they are worth the watch. Today’s list will include some of the new indie movies of the past year. So Let’s Dive In!\r\n<h3>1. Project Power (2020)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Ariel Schulman</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Jamie Foxx, Joseph Gordon Levitt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3900 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Top-10-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-2.jpg\" alt=\"Project Power Top 10 Hollywood Movies of 2020 (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nStarting with one of my personal favourites (despite the low IMDB Ratings), this movie is an interesting mix of mystery and Sci-Fi. Instead of dealers selling drugs, they happen to sell powerful pills, capable of giving the user many kinds of power, all based on their DNA.\r\n\r\nThe movie revolves around a former US ranger, formerly known to be subjected to many experiments, as an agency aims to make their breed of super-soldiers. By the passage of time, the Ranger lives on and raises a daughter. She happens to inherit many powers, due to his experiments.\r\n\r\nAs a result, she gets kidnapped by the agency and she becomes the subject of their experiments. This leads to a lot of havoc wrecking in different cities, which makes way to the city of New Orleans.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xw1vQgVaYNQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>2. Extraction (2020)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6.7</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Sam Hargrave</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Chris Hemsworth, David Harbour, Randeep Hooda</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3905 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Top-10-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-7.jpg\" alt=\"Extraction Top 10 Hollywood Movies of 2020 (7)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nExtraction is one of the best indie films on Netflix, bringing us a unique and diverse cast, with an amazing story. It features Chris as the main protagonist named Tyler, a mercenary whose family is no longer with him due to reasons unknown.\r\n\r\nHe is assigned with the extraction of the Indian crime lord\'s son, who has been abducted by his Bangladeshi counterpart, as vengeance for a drug deal gone wrong. Tyler soon finds himself alone with his team shot down, the criminals in his pursuit, and the escort all terrified and helpless. Tyler himself in an alien environment where chances are merely slim.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> The Director of the movie happens to be formerly known for being the stunt double for Captain America.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L6P3nI6VnlY[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>3. The Devil All the Time (2020)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Antonio Campos.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Sebastian Stan, Robert Patterson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3906 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Top-10-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-8.jpg\" alt=\"The Devil All the Time Top 10 Hollywood Movies of 2020 (8)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nAntonio’s ‘The Devil All the Time’ features a psychological thriller with a mind-blowing star cast.\r\n\r\nThis thriller brings us to a small town where a young man named Arvin, realizes that the town he lives in has gradually become sinful and corrupted. It happens to have all sorts of sinful people; a sinful preacher, a corrupt yet selfish policeman, and a stalking cameraman (as shown from the trailer).\r\n\r\nThe movie ironically revolves around the phrase \"Some people were born so that they could be buried”. Although the movie gives the impression of a horror film, this movie is capable of making the audience look over their soul.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6XoWOUgCpo[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>4. Six Underground (2019)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Michael Bay.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Ryan Reynolds, Adria Arjona, Corey Hawkins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5277 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Six Underground (2019)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nSo who would have thought that Michael Bay will be coming around the Netflix platform and come out with one of the best independent movies?\r\n\r\nThe fact that he produced one of the best Indie movies franchises like Transformers and then re-animated the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles with his film-making cunning, should be highly considered while expecting out of this movie as well. So the movie also features the sarcastic brilliance of Ryan Reynolds while he is the leader of six individuals.\r\n\r\nThese individuals are operatives who faked their death to become guns for hire. They put their free time to good use as they take down some of the most infamous influences from around the globe. They are only known by their numbers assigned to keep things strictly professional. This movie is very promising to bring the best auction possible for your home theatres or laptop screens.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> Just how Michael Bay keeps it very promising in his first movie outing with Netflix, the scenes of the crew in Turkistan was shot in Abu Dhabi. Furthermore, the soldiers involved in the movie belonged to the UAE Military.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U0DO24Qy7jQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>5. The Old Guard (2020)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6.6</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Gina Prince Bythewood.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Charlize Theron, Harry Melling, Kiki Layne</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5278 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"The Old Guard (2020)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nAmong the best indie movies of 2020, The Old Guard is one of the underrated yet timeless movies of its kind. It features four immortal individuals, also guns for hire, who have lived for centuries in the fighting of many different wars and battles since they can remember.\r\n\r\nFast forward to the 21st Century, they find themselves across one of their own again but this time, they are now more unsure than aware whether they are even immortal anymore.\r\n\r\nThe plot discusses this mastermind who manages to uncover the truth about the old guard and they intend to bring them down for their desires. The action scenes are very promising and it almost resonates with an MCU like theme and environment. Better add this movie to your weekend list!\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> Despite her age, Charlize still proves that age is just a number. The fact that she trained 3 to 4 hours per day to master all the fight scenes is truly extraordinary. It showed that Charlize truly put it all to her craft, ensuring all of us that the movie is worth the watch.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aK-X2d0lJ_s[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>6. Avengement (2019)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> Jesse V. Johnson</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Scott Adkins, Kierston Wareing, Craig Fairbrass.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5279 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nThe Arrangement is not your average Hollywood movie. This is another movie that features one of Hollywood’s well-known names, Scott Adkins, who decided to direct his movie. He plays the role of an inmate recently released from incarceration.\r\n\r\nThe plot revolves around him (playing the role of Cain Burgess) who gets framed in a crime. He became a loose end for his older brother, who intends to kill him during his incarceration. But now, Cain goes after the people who were responsible for the plotting of his crimes.\r\n\r\nThis recent masterpiece will ensure that the action is promising, from a movie actor who mainly plays supporting roles in most of his cameos. He will ensure you to put you on a thrilling journey.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pUQzHB8hs_s[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>7. Bright (2017)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb rating:</strong> 6.3</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director:</strong> David Ayers</li>\r\n <li><strong>Starcast:</strong> Will Smith, Joel Edgerton, Lucy Fry.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5276 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4-2.jpg\" alt=\"Bright (2017)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nSo these last Indie movies I will add to the list. It happens to be the very first Indie movie on the Netflix platform. This is the kind of movie which highlights a topic offensive in nature (Racism). But the irony of it all is that it does not offend any race at all.\r\n\r\nThe plot revolves around three races; namely Humans, Orcs, and Elves. The movie shows how these races coexist together, with Orcs being the bottom of the food chain, the humans in the middle and the Elves being the superiors. With that out of the way, the story then focuses on the city’s police department, having a new Orkish recruit in their department.\r\n\r\nHe later goes on patrol with his partner (coming out of injury), who would then embark on this journey which brings the entire department onto its feet. They encounter dark elves, who wish to resurrect the Dark Lord and enslave all of the races. It’s up to the duo, who find a wand that can upset the entire world and all the races along with it.\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> Despite the dull dialogues (and the chemistry) between the duo, the insane plot twists, and the bizarre theme of the movie, it is confirmed that the movie will get a sequel. However, the date for the sequel’s release is not confirmed yet.</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6EZCBSsBxko[/embedyt]\r\n<h2>Conclusion:</h2>\r\nThe Netflix platform is a treasure with hidden gems. It brings movies worldwide to your mobile phones, tablets, and laptops. So these are the best indie movies on Netflix right now. Although these movies haven’t made much commercially, these movies will not fail you at all. So stay tuned, for I will dig into more movies from the platform. Happy Binging Everyone!','Some of the Best Indie Movies, Courtesy of Netflix','','publish','open','open','','some-of-the-best-indie-movies-courtesy-of-netflix','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/','2021-03-15 09:17:59','2021-03-15 03:47:59','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5113',0,'post','',0),(5129,12,'2021-02-05 20:52:15','2021-02-05 15:22:15','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As COVID-19 was taking grip of the universe, our normal busy life halted and we were locked within the walls of our houses since the month of March. A situation of despair it was, and the whole world was scared, panicking and crying.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5134 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/7dd50x600-1.jpg\" alt=\"Best Bollywood movies of 2020 that you can watch on Netflix and Amazon Prime\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All the movie halls were shut down for social distancing issues and thus Indian audience thought that their sources of entertainment were also lost for indefinite months. But this was not the case when astonishing OTT platforms like Netflix and Amazon Prime were there. It can be rightly said that these OTTs gifted us with some best Bollywood works the previous year.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We were able to watch, in fact, binge watches most of them, thanks to lockdown!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now when life almost came back to normal, situations improved, and even the vaccination arrived after a long wait, let’s go back a little. So here, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">TV freak</a> presents to you some of the best Hindi movies on Netflix as well as the best amazon prime Hindi movies 2020:</span>\r\n<h2><b>1. Ludo</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Srp90Hp0G70[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The maker of iconic movies like </span><strong><i>Barfi, Life in a Metro</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, Anurag Basu once again created magic on-screen in his latest release Ludo, undoubtedly one of the best Netflix original Hindi movies 2020. A startling story it is...where four different well-written narratives merge together after a series of events and twists.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This multi-starrer Hindi film amazingly tangles four different colours of the board game with the realities of life. It also didn’t fail to utilize the superior acting skills of actors like<strong><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards/\"> Pankaj Tripathi</a>, Sanya Malhotra, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/fatima-sana-shaikh-biography-controversiesawards-and-movies/\">Fatima Sana</a> Shaikh, Rajkumar Rao, Adiya Roy Kapoor, Abhishek Bacchan, Rohit Sharaf, Pearle Maney.</strong></span>\r\n<h2><b>2. Thappad</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jBw_Eta0HDM[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, A theatre release in February, </span><b><i>Thappad</i></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, later became one of the </span><b>best</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Hindi movies on Amazon Prime 2020. The Tapsee Pannu starrer, a female-centric film, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thappad</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is also the story of a broken marriage. A story of happiness shared by two people destroyed by a single blow, a single slap, which is definitely not just a slap – the main backdrop of </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thappad</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secondly, Apart from addressing patriarchy, it bravely stands against many such Bollywood films that normalize or romanticize abuses or mistreatment against women by toxic heroes, in the name of love. The way various subplots of the movie like those of a single working mother Shivani; the tortured maid, Sunita; the ‘unhappy-in-marriage’ lawyer, Netra intertwined with the protagonist’s journey against a slap is worth-praising.</span>\r\n<h2><b>3. Axone</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jAW1U8PLwY0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the list of Netflix Bollywood movies 2020, the next one that deserves a round of applause is the June release, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Axone</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The beauty of north-eastern culture accompanied by a beautiful plot with elements of love, friendship, emotions, internal struggle, and even racism has been perfectly shown by director Nicholas Kharkongor.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A simple realistic story surrounding a few north-eastern in Delhi finding difficulties in just arranging a wedding party due to their distinct culture has been so amazingly portrayed, Apart from the director, fabulous jobs have been done by underrated actors like <strong>Sayani Gupta, Vinay Pathak, Dolly Ahulia, Lin Laishram</strong> and several other significant and talented new arrivals in Bollywood.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4. Chaalang</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BY-0SbSF2dE[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coming back to Prime, another of the best Bollywood movies on Amazon prime 2020</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is <strong>Hansal Mehta</strong>’s honest attempt, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chaalang</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This perfect family watch revolves around the backdrop of the importance of sports and physical activities in a school’s curriculum, amidst everything.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Few things like the ‘quite known storyline’ of guiding and preparing some noobs to win a conflict, an angle of love story, and formation of a love triangle, later on, seemed quite unnecessary in the film. But Hansal Mehta’s pragmatic direction with exact details, some of the dialogues, lifelike acting by <strong>Rajkumar Rao, Mohammad Zeeshan Zayuub, Saurabh Shukla, Ila Arun, Nusrat Bharucha</strong> makes the movie stand out.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 5. </span><b>Raat Akeli Hai</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Among the Bollywood Netflix Hindi movies 2020, a significant one that made a mark is the <strong>Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Radhika Apte</strong> starrer crime thriller </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Raat Akeli</span></i> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hai</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uc78PxSxXMg[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the shade of which seemed like a murder mystery, this movie is darker and went to the roots of violence against women. Though the screenplay seems quite slow at certain times, the strong acting, the environment of suspense and secrets with powerful direction and dialogues has the ability to rule out such loopholes. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nawazuddin Siddiqui slew in the character of a cop while the well-built female characters of suspects played by Radhika Apte, <strong><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/shweta-tripathi-biography-tv-shows-movies-and-commercial-ads/\">Shweta Tripathi</a>, Shivani Raghuvanshi</strong> did steal the show. A whodunit Bollywood murder mystery of a politician has a distinctiveness of its own in many ways.</span>\r\n<h2><b>6. Gulabo Sitabo</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ayushman Khurana, known for brilliant acting in movies addressing social issues, again impressed us with another mind-blowing performance in another such flavourful movie, </span><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020/\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gulabo Sitabo</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></a>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o0qeQ_yHqtA[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A story of greed, conflicts, and their outcomes along with some dark humour as well as saddening elements, have been very expressively represented by director<strong> Shoojit Sarkar</strong>.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A simple form of storytelling exploring quarrels of old, greedy, selfish man Mirza (outstandingly played by <strong>Amitabh Bacchan</strong>) and Baankey, his tenant (played by <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/ayushmann-starts-to-transform-physically-for-his-upcoming-movie/\"><strong>Aayushman</strong></a>) over an almost destroyed Haveli with Lucknow city being the backdrop, was a perfect movie to watch on a lonely lockdown afternoon.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"937\" name=\"Gulabo Sitabo Movie (2020) | Trailer and Story\"]\r\n<h2><b>7. Chaman Bahar</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While this Netflix release got few critic reviews like ‘uncomfortable to watch’, it received praises from most sections of the audience.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BvBd0vhOkZI[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This small-town one-sided love story involving a </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">paan-wala</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Billu and a minor girl from a higher middle-class family is one of my personal favourites because trust me...</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chaman Bahar</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is not a movie where one-sided obsession has been romanticized. Rather, its harmful consequences form the climax of the film.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The impeccable act of the <strong>Panchayat</strong> famed <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/jitendra-kumar-life-biography-and-bollywood-journey/\"><strong>Jitendra Kumar</strong> </a>must be in the spotlight as he represented how small-town guys from poor families actually are, instead of depicting typical Bollywood heroes. It’s not just another Bollywood love story, rather a tale close to reality.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"2353\" name=\"Jitendra Kumar | Life, Biography and Bollywood Journey\"]\r\n<h2><b>8. Bulbul</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another remarkable movie, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bulbul</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> met our high expectations and turned out to be one of such best Bollywood <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/\">movies on Netflix 2020</a>.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4MGReT9-cAg[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, In the light of the horror genre, this movie tells much more about oppression against women in a 19</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> century zamindar-dominated Bengal. ‘A woman is never weak; she can rise as a </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">devi</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and fight back against the wrong’ – this strong message to patriarchy serves as the main motive of </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bulbul</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secondly, The film’s red filter creates an ideal mood or environment.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And finally, The brilliant direction by debutant director <strong>Anvika Dutt</strong> combined with flawless performances of <strong>Tripti Damri, Rahul Bose, Parambrata, Paoli Dam</strong> makes it the best female-oriented movie of the year.</span>\r\n<h2><b>9. Shakuntala Devi</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Will it be wrong if I say that the female hero dominated Bollywood last year? </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shakuntala Devi</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, the July release, is also one of the worth-watching Bollywood movies on Amazon Prime</span><b>.</b>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8HA1HRufYso[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This <strong>Anu Menon</strong> directed inspiring biopic of ‘human computer’, Shakuntala Devi has some flaws of its own. But <strong>Vidya Balan</strong>’s iconic performance of a mathematical genius as well as, as a ‘somewhat flawed’ mother and a wife cancels out everything else. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sanya-malhotra-story-biography-and-movies/\"><strong>Sanya Malhotra</strong></a> and Jishu Sengupta also don’t lack behind to portray all the required emotions in their respective roles.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"2097\" name=\"Sanya Malhotra | Story, Biography and Movies\"]\r\n<h2><b>10. Serious men</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another show stealer of <strong>Nawazuddin Siddiqui</strong> got an OTT release on Netflix in October 2020.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=naXf8R1aOik[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Based on <strong>Manu Joseph’s novel</strong>, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Serious Men</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> addresses the social issue of caste divide and narrates the tale of a frustrated middle-aged Dalit who involves himself in a lie by making people believe that his son is a science genius.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nawazuddin’s superior performance as the anti-hero as well as performances by <strong>Aakshath Das</strong> (child actor), <strong>Sweta Basu</strong> Prasad are noteworthy. All credits to the cast and crew for gifting us with such an impactful heart-breaking dark comedy of the year</span>\r\n<h2><b>11. AK vs AK</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After a long wait and anticipation, one of the notable Bollywood Netflix Hindi movies 2020</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">got a Christmas release in the OTT. And you know that </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A brave attempt like this has rarely been made in a Bollywood movie.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXZPMb51IQU[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An imagined extension of real-life famed artists like <strong>Anil Kapoor</strong> and <strong>Anurag Kashyap,</strong> an imagined feud between them leading to kidnapping and then its portrayal on-screen, the entire promising concept has driven audiences to give this movie a watch.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"4296\" name=\" Best Directors in Bollywood and Their Successful Movies of All Time\"]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though put down by many critics, this Vikramaditya Motwane’s non-cringe black comedy kidnapping thriller by huge margin failed to dishearten the audience.</span>\r\n<h2><b>12. Unpaused</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kXGfGV2v6GE[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, In the ‘Amazon Prime movies list 2020’, it’s time to add the anthology film, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unpaused</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> consisting of 5 short films. Directed by <strong>5 different directors</strong>, it gives different perspectives on COVID-19 pandemic effects in the lives of various people.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secondly, it has lots of relevance to the current situation. Next, it gives a closer view of reality. Successfully showing the outcomes of virus attacks in the forms of problematic issues like weakening of mental health, loss of jobs, loneliness, suicidal thoughts, this movie deserves a watch.</span>\r\n<h2><b>13. Subh Mangal Zaada Saavdhan</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A must-watch movie for Indian parents as well as for all those Homophobic people out there.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r6r8UYU7Zcs[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The struggles of the queer community and their non-acceptance by society have been narrated engagingly in this 117 minutes long <strong>Ayushman-<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/jitendra-kumar-life-biography-and-bollywood-journey/\">Jitendra</a></strong> starrer movie. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With some critics calling it ‘clunky’ or ‘erratic in parts’, I feel the film has been a very strong step towards this newly explored genre of ‘queer’ in Bollywood.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some parts may feel lacking expected humour or emotions, but again, watching the entire movie isn’t going to disappoint you. A theatre release, this film is now available on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n<h2><b>14. Cargo</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an era of crime, thriller and mystery genres, this Netflix released sci-fi has been a fearless attempt by its writer-director <strong>Arati Kadav</strong>.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZvpdN4VltKY[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The story about a spaceship with a single crew member and also his new assistant gives an exciting perspective on life post-death. An innovative and creative approach, we really desire for more of such movies from Bollywood!</span>\r\n<h2><b>15. Har Kisse k Hisse Kaamyab</b></h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8KwQkxW1bVc[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acting brilliance combined with good writing and fortified direction, that is the basis of the audience’s love for this movie. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sanjay-mishra-biography-life-facts-and-interests-on-his-birthday-6-oct/\"><strong>Sanjay Mishra</strong></a>, in his role of retired character actor Sudheer who still dreams to achieve a unique goal. As we know he once again proved his potential in the film and left the audience teary-eyed.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"2884\" name=\"Sanjay Mishra | Biography, Life, Facts and Interests | On His Birthday 6 oct\"]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hats off to director <strong>Hardik Mehta</strong> for shading light on such a real concept and paying tribute to all the current and forgotten character actors of Bollywood. If you missed this Netflix film then you really missed something great in 2020!</span>\r\n<h2><b>16. Jawani Janeman</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sometimes, a perfect comedy film is required to lighten up your mood. In that case, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jawani Janeman</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a good option.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_lkFyfcrvkU[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, It is a story of a playboy man, Jazz (played by <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/saif-ali-khan-said-about-his-autobiography-reactions-on-twitter/\"><strong>Saif Ali Khan</strong></a>). His 21-year-old daughter suddenly returns one day and claims to be pregnant.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secondly, The film has been highly praised by audiences for its light-hearted, genuine comedy sequences.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even most of the critics appreciated it too for the wonderful cast. Mainly, Saif Ali Khan, as well as debutant actress Alaya F, did fantastic jobs in this one-tie entertainer.</span>\r\n<h2><b>17. Dolly, Kitty Aur Woh Chamakte Sitare</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another female-centric movie on Netflix! However, this film centring around the lives of two cousin sisters, Dolly and Kajal received some negative responses. But with in-depth analysis, you will realize that each of the aspects the story highlighted has its own significance.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=as3YLG5DmL0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes, the narrative changes can be felt too fast sometimes leaving scenes not fully developed. But the way director <strong>Alankita Shrivastava</strong> played with themes like women’s sexual desires, sexuality, male dominance, gender biases will leave you impressed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, let’s thank actors like <strong>Konkona Sen Sharma, Bhumi Pednakar, Vikrant Massey, Amol Parashar</strong> for their spellbound performances.</span>\r\n\r\n[irp posts=\"2991\" name=\"7 Bollywood Celebrities Who Underwent a Dramatic Transformation\"]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are some of the best Indian movies on Amazon Prime 2020 as well as some best movies released on Netflix this year.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. We will soon come up with new updates and interesting news about the entertainment industry. Till then, have a safe and nice time. See you in the next article.</span>','16+ Best Bollywood Movies of 2020 on Netflix and Amazon Prime','','publish','open','open','','16-best-bollywood-movies-of-2020-on-netflix-and-amazon-prime','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/sanjay-mishra-biography-life-facts-and-interests-on-his-birthday-6-oct/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/jitendra-kumar-life-biography-and-bollywood-journey/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/fatima-sana-shaikh-biography-controversiesawards-and-movies/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/saif-ali-khan-said-about-his-autobiography-reactions-on-twitter/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/shweta-tripathi-biography-tv-shows-movies-and-commercial-ads/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/sanya-malhotra-story-biography-and-movies/','2021-02-14 20:09:11','2021-02-14 14:39:11','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5129',0,'post','',0),(5165,13,'2021-02-07 11:39:43','2021-02-07 06:09:43','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes! The award festival of this year has already started. This February 3rd, the 78th Golden Globe Awards Nominees have been announced. Which only means the Oscar is coming.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Golden Globe has always been an event of predicting the Oscar Nominees and winners. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is why the Golden Globe has been one of the most prestigious film awards. So let’s take a look at the Golden Globe Awards Nomination for <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/movies/\">best movie</a>-Drama 2021.</span>\r\n<h2><b>5. Mank | Golden Globe Awards Nominees</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: David Fincher (Also Directed Fight Club, Se7en, Gone Girl)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Gary Oldman, Amanda Seyfried, Lily Collins</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5043 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Mank\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is not too common to see the genres of biography and comedy side by side. But Mank has made it all possible. Mank has been a long term project for director Davin Fincher. He wanted to start shooting this film right after he was done with The Game (1997).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gary Oldman and Jodi Foster were his original choice of cast. Later Amanda Seyfried replaced Jodi Foster in this film who is almost a decade younger than her character.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mank is a great film about the progression of a great script-writer </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Herman J. Mankiewicz</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and an era-defining movie Citizen Kane. It takes an outstanding team of cast and crews to pull off a movie like this perfectly. And Mank will be a great example of that.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mank has also been nominated in 5 other categories in the 78th Golden Globe Awards.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The script of this film has been written by David Fincher’s late father Jack Fincher, who has also been nominated for Best Screenplay — Motion Picture for this movie.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aSfX-nrg-lI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>4. Nomadland</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.6</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Chloé Zhao (Also directed Eternals)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Frances McDormand, David Strathairn</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Hulu</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5170 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Motion-Picture-Drama-3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Nomadland :2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees Best Motion Picture Drama (3).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This film gives a very heart-breaking message. It’s about letting things go, things that are dearest to you but holding you back to move on with your life. When you live in a certain stable arrangement for a long time (For this film which is a workplace and house), it’s hard to imagine what life would be like outside that world.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s hard to find yourself when your life revolves around that sort of settlement. This is what reflects on the life of the main protagonist of this movie.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nomadland is an adaptation of a non-fictional novel written by Jessica Bruder. With greatness and grace, this movie has already won the Golden Lion at the 77th Venice International Film Festival. This movie starred two time Academy Award winner Frances McDormand and many other new artists.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This film has been nominated for 3 other nominations in the 78th Golden Globe Awards.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6sxCFZ8_d84[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>3. Promising Young Woman | Golden Globe Awards Nominees</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.5</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Emerald Fennell</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Carey Mulligan, Bo Burnham, Alison Brie</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: VUDU, DIRECTV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5168 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Motion-Picture-Drama-1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"Promising Young Woman 2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees Best Motion Picture Drama (1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cassandra was a medical student until her best friend Nina was raped by a classmate. Finding no justice, Nina drops out and Cassandra follows her to look after her. Rape is not something a victim can ever forget. And so couldn’t Nina and it cost her, her life. So when the rapist is about to get married, Cassandra rises from the ashes to get revenge on everyone who did wrong to her best friend.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Promising Young Woman is a very dark thriller that manifests feminism quite strongly. It’s about how society fails a woman after she is raped and the rapist gets bailed out like nothing really ever happened. Carey Mulligan was shown as a femme fatale character in this film which was very refreshing. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie has 3 other Golden Globes 2021 nominations.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Margot Robbie and Carey Mulligan are two of the producers of this film.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Directorial Debut of Emerald Fennell for a full-length feature film. She only directed a 13-minute long short film before this film.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7i5kiFDunk8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>2. The Father</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 7.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Florian Zeller</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Anthony Hopkins, Olivia Colman, Mark Gatiss (Played Mycroft Holmes in Sherlock)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: HBO Max</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5169 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Motion-Picture-Drama-2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"The father Promising Young Woman 2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees Best Motion Picture Drama (1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">‘The Father’ just as the name, portrays a father-daughter relationship played by Academy Award-winning actor and actress— Anthony Hopkins And Olivia Colman.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anthony is a very old fellow who is losing his sense of reality day by day. He is hard to take care of because he is stubborn and refuses help from other people. His daughter Anne is very frustrated about this and is on the verge of losing her patience. The Father exhibits a feeling or a situation we want to avoid for the best.   </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Florian Zeller, whose most credits are earned from writing, made his dream film. Anthony Hopkins was his prime aim. He even named the main protagonist ‘Anthony’ in honour of Sir Anthony Hopkins. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Father has a total of 4 Golden Globes nominations this year.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is Florian Zeller’s directorial debut for a feature film.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4TZb7YfK-JI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>1. The Trial of Chicago 7 | Golden Globe Awards Nominees</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.8</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Aaron Sorkin (Also Directed Molly’s Game)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast</strong>: Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Eddie Redmayne, Sacha Baron Cohen</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Netflix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5050 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Top-Netflix-Original-Hollywood-Movies-of-2020-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"The Trial of the Chicago 7\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/\">Netflix</a> has been doing a very good job of creating quality biography films and series. The Trial of Chicago 7 is undoubtedly one of them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie is based on a real-life event of 1968. 7 people were charged for initiating a riot at the protest of the Democratic National Convention in Chicago, Illinois. This movie shows the rise of the falsely accused convicts through judicial misconduct.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though all the 7 protagonists are Americans, most of the characters are played by non-Americans. That takes a lot of effort in the accent department to do the acting perfectly. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aaron Sorkin is the director of this film. He previously won an Oscar for Best Writing, Adapted Screenplay for the movie— The Social Network.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Trial of Chicago 7 has also been nominated for 4 other categories at this year’s Golden Globes.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The second feature Film Directed by Aaron Sorkin.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IsFCZ_B2o5w[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Two Netflix Originals, both of them are biography films. If we look at the 77th Golden Globe Awards nominees for best movie in 2020, we will see that all the movies were nominated for the Oscars. We can predict the same for these 5 fabulous films too. So for now, let’s just cross our fingers and hope for the best.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, let us know which of these movies you liked the most and which one should win the award in your opinion by leaving a comment in the comment box.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Happy Watching!!!</span>','Golden Globe Awards Nominees 2021| Best Motion Picture - Drama','','publish','open','open','','golden-globe-awards-nominees-2021-best-motion-picture-drama','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/','2021-02-08 17:46:31','2021-02-08 12:16:31','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5165',0,'post','',0),(5173,12,'2021-02-13 17:10:22','2021-02-13 11:40:22','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5206 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A talented, versatile Indian actor who has been very active currently and is often impressing us by his superior works is none other than the Chhapak man Vikrant Massey.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The great artist Vikrant is whom we know, the struggle behind is something many of us are not aware of. So, here <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">Tv freak.com</a> presents to you a close and detailed look at Massey’s inspiring life journey.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Vikrant Massey Early life</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vikrant Massey was not born with a silver spoon in his mouth. Like me and you, he is from a small, simple middle-class working family. His likeness and passion for acting and dancing started growing since the time he was very young. Speaking of education, his schooling was from Mumbai itself.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5210 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-1.jpg\" alt=\"vicky kaushal\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His acting basically began in his school days when he used to take part in various plays.  Besides these, he also took professional dance training and his dedicated dance performances also started mostly since he was only 7 years old.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After 12th, Vikrant obtained his Bachelor’s degree from a college at his birthplace only.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He had his teachers’ continuous encouragement from the beginning. This inspired and motivated him to choose the path of entertainment as a full-time career.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>So what\'s about Vikrant Massey Age, body, and Height?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Entering the world on 3rd April 1987, the actor is currently 33 years. With a height of about 5’9”, a pair of dreamy black eyes on an attractive face with the perfect jawline, he has a very charming appearance.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>Let\'s know who are in Vikrant Massey family and friends?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The acting was something that was not in Vikrant’s gene as he took birth in a complete non-filmy family to a couple, Jolley Massey (father) and Meena Massey (mother). He spent those days in just a 1BHK flat where the family used to reside. He is still lovingly and affectionately called Sonu by his close ones.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sonu is the second child of his parents. He has a brother elder to him. His name is Mohsin Massey.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5207 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Childhood\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5208 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regarding friendships, we are not very sure how much he is close to people from the Bollywood or TV industry, with whom he hangs out, with whom he does not. But a well-mannered Vikrant has always been seen laughing and spending good time with co-stars like Harleen Sethi, Shweta Tripathi, Ali Fazal, etc. in promotions or interviews.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Vikrant Massey Instagram handle also has pictures consisting of snaps from his promotions or posters of his films/web shows.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a few unprofessional pictures, we have seen him with Vicky Kaushal, Rhea Chakraborty, Shaan Muttathil, Tilottama Shome, Gulshan Devaiah, etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5209 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Relationships\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Post his work with Ranveer Singh, he was questioned about his equation with the star in an interview. To it, he replied, ‘Ranveer is a co-star, not a friend’.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seems like Vikrant has more close friends outside the industry. In a 2020 interview, he even spoke about losing a very close friend named Kushal Punjabi who ended his life by suicide.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5211 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>Beginning of the journey</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He took training in Ballet dancing professionally and was phenomenal in this field. Since 10th standard, he embarked upon the journey of involvement in work with well-known choreographer Shiamak Davar.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For his ambition of being recognized as an actor, Massey started to give auditions. Finally, in 2006, he got the chance to act in his first soap opera which is a historical drama Dharti Ka Veer Yoddha Prithviraj Chauhan aired on Starplus. Prior to that in 2003, he acted in another serial called Kaha Hoon Main on the same channel. But, due to some unfortunate reasons that were never aired.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Vikrant Massey TV shows</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Soon after his TV debut, Vikrant was spotted for proficient acting skills. Since then he didn’t look back. Behind teaching Davar’s dance troupes, he also acted in his Disney TV series, Dhoom Machado Dhoom where he played the character of a choreographer.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One after another serial then came on his way. Vikrant became a common face in Indian households and dominated the small screen up to 2014. His other notable works in television include Dharam Veer, Balika Vadhu. You should also check out his masterwork in Gumrah – End of Innocence, Qubool Hai, Ajab Gajab Ghar Jamai.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5212 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/7-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch VM in Dharamveer scene</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Orpv_ZLzDRE[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch the last shot of VM from Qubool Hai</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWlITQfQxqQ[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He grabbed two prestigious awards, one back in 2008 and another in 2013 for his television performances.</span>\r\n<h2><strong>What are the best of Vikrant Massey movies and tv shows so far?</strong></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vikrant has made significant contributions in many Hindi films with his superior acting skills. His debut on the big screen was back in the year 2013 with the Bollywood movie, Lootera. Vikrant’s supporting character of Dev gained enough appreciation. In the very first movie, he did a fabulous job and worked shoulder to shoulder with actors like Ranveer Singh and Sonakshi Sinha.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5213 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2015 he was seen as a significant character in the romance drama Dil Dhadakne Do.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His breakthrough performance was in the Konkona Sen Sharma. It was directed in 2016 with the title A Death in the Gunj. Vikrant’s central role as a gentle, sensitive, struggling university student made clear how multifaceted Massey is as an actor. For his astonishing performance as Shutu, he won the ‘Best Performance by a Male Actor’ Award in the Caleidoscope Indian film festival 2017.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VM in death in Gunj trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XliKkuxa_nA[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have also witnessed him in appreciable roles in movies like Half Girlfriend. He is also part of the most liked movie Lipstick Under My Burkha and Ramprasad Ki Tehri. He recently did a masterpiece movie i.e. Chhpak. Dolly Kitty Aur Who Chamakte Sitare is also one of the best works of his.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5214 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/9-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nIn 2020, we saw him as the male lead in the sci-fi, Cargo as well as in the romcom Ginny Weds Sunny. His admirable role in Chhapak also stole the spotlight.\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VM in Cargo Trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZvpdN4VltKY[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jinny weds Sunny trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WTJW2Ol1c0g[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nHis upcoming film 14 Phere, opposite Kriti Karbanda, is soon to release in July this year. It seems like a romantic comedy film as we got glimpses from the poster he shared.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5215 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/10-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>Vikrant Massey web series and short films</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Is just a ‘thanks’ enough to Vikrant for his outstanding works in Vikrant Massey, Broken But Beautiful, Criminal Justice, Rise? Be romancing Sameera as Veer in Broken But Beautiful or fighting away goons in Mirzapur or even giving a cameo appearance as Nawab Khan in Made in Heaven- Vikrant’s presence in any web show in any form will make you fall in love with his immense talent.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch VM in rising Trailer</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3D2MaghAZl8[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch VM in Broken But Beautiful S2 scene</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lp9rp10h0bk[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch VM in Mirzapur scene</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7jr1vKDniDk[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have also seen him in various short films including Un Hazaron Ke Naam, Best Girlfriend, Local Girlfriend, 35MM, and Copy.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Best girlfriend short film</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQT5UuOVHjw[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Appearances in commercials</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have also witnessed Massey endorsing various brands in TV commercials. These include brands like Cornetto, Nescafe, Cadbury, Idea 4G, etc.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">VM Cornetto Ad</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yY_YwHdxrok[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Relationship status</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vikrant Massey is in love with actress Sheetal Thakur for a long time now. This real-life couple was also seen together on-screen as ex-lovers in Broken But Beautiful Season 1. The duo privately got engaged in 2019.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since then, both were always on each other social media accounts and of course, they looked very adorable together. Fans are now eagerly waiting for the news of their marriage. Vikrant spilt the beans in an interview and mentioned getting hitched with his fiancee at the right time. They are often spotted together now and also attend each others\' family events.</span>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5216 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/11-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" /></h2>\r\n<h2><b>Vikrant Massey net worth</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As per reports, Vikrant charges about 50 Lakhs per movie. As of 2020, his net worth is $1 million.</span>\r\n<h2><b>A dog lover?</b></h2>\r\nVikrant Massey often posts cute photos with dogs. This clearly shows his love and affection for the animal. An enchanting human being with such a lovable animal, what else can be more beautiful!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5204 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/12.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>A cricketer too?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reportedly the actor has some surprising hobbies too, one of which includes playing cricket.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5205 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/13.jpg\" alt=\"Vikrant Massey Biography and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, it can be rightly said that Vikrant Massey is the kind of actor Bollywood needs today. And it is the industry\'s good luck that it is now realizing his ability to be the main protagonist of good films. We wish him all the success for his future. And we do desire to see more of his best works in the upcoming times.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We, at TV Freak, try to bring up to you many known and unknown facts about artists who are extremely talented but still haven’t been fully classified in the category of A-listed actors. Their inspiring journeys and struggles motivate everyone to chase their dreams, be it acting or any other field.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this era of nepotism, these actors have proved that being an outsider in the entertainment world cannot kill your ambition; the struggle maybe a little more but you will reach the destination. Besides these, we also provide you with regular updates and interesting news of the Bollywood and Hollywood industry. To know more, you can check our articles.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. We will soon come up with something new about the entertainment industry. Till then, have a safe and nice time. See you in the next article.</span>','‘Mirzapur’ limelight Vikrant Massey Biography and Other Interesting Facts','','publish','open','open','','mirzapur-limelight-vikrant-massey-biography-and-other-interesting-facts','','','2021-02-13 17:12:17','2021-02-13 11:42:17','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5173',0,'post','',0),(5198,12,'2021-02-12 12:00:59','2021-02-12 06:30:59','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5220 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nusrat-Bharucha-biography-movies-family-and-other-interesting-facts-2.jpg\" alt=\"Nusrat Bharucha biography, movies, family, and other interesting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another outsider making a mark in <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/trailers/bollywood-movie-latest-trailers/\">Bollywood</a> by her lovable performances is none other than the beautiful actress Nusrat Bharucha. Today let’s get to know a little more about her journey from being a girl-next-door to being what we call ‘celebrity’.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Early life</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bharucha’s birth and then her growing up was in the commercial capital of India, Mumbai. The city is the witness of Bharucha’s transition from a child to a teen, and then to an adult.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Her alma meter includes Lilavatibai Poddar High School and then the famous Jai Hind College where she spent her three years of graduation.</span>\r\n\r\n<span 