span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Later in 2010, we saw her magnificent performance in another TV series, Seven. That was aired on Sony Entertainment Television.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regarding Nusrat Bharucha web series, she hasn’t been a part of any such project and has made appearances in serials or films.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Nusrat Bharucha movies</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Like any other artist, Bharucha also had ups and downs in her career. Her first Hindi film was Jai Santoshi Maa (2006) and then Kal Kisne Dekha which was released in 2009.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jai Santoshi Maa scene of NB</span></h3>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vto4cKiVkJY\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, her first breakthrough was the role of Shruti Dahiya in the critically acclaimed movie Love, Sex Aur Dhoka in 2010. The same year she made her debut in the Telugu film industry too with the film ‘Taj Mahal’. In 2011, she was a part of the multi starrer comedy film Pyar Ka Punchama, opposite Karthik Aaryan.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Listen to the beautiful songs from Tajmahal</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YT7fy1FS6ps[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love sex or Dhoka trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YNxrPvqj9Yc[/embedyt]\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch NB in Pyar Ka Panchama trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ26AdrU4GM[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Till 2013, Bharucha did not achieve success professionally as two of her films Akkash Vaani and Darr @ Mall turned out to be unsuccessful.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">watch NB I Akkash Vaani movie scene</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z6h0XW3IWP8[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> But, she continued the struggle and ultimately Pyar Ka Panchama 2 in 2015 turned out to be the turning point of her career. It was loved by the audience and was her first big commercial success. It established her as a competition to contemporary Bollywood actors and gave her the deserved recognition.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch NB in Pyar Ka Panchama 2 trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tC-HGUhxyyc[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There was no turning back after 2015. From time to time, she has gifted us with some iconic blockbusters including Sonu Ki Tittu Ki Sweety and Dream Girl.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Listen to the gem Subah Subah from Sonu ki Tittu ki sweety</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZgTKmRPWMq4[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2020, her two releases include Jai Mummy Di (cameo) and the sports drama Chaalang.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch NM in Chaalang trailer</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BY-0SbSF2dE[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2021 is most probably going to witness her major releases, including Hurdang, Chhori.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Appearances in music videos</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Her first music video appearance was in Atif Aslam’s romantic melody, Baarishein in 2019. In the same year, she starred in Guru Randhawa’s Ishq Tera. She then featured in a song of the Siddharth Malhotra starrer, Marjawaan. She was last seen in 2021 in Yo Yo Honey Singh’s music video ‘Saiyan Jee’.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Watch her in Baarishein</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P0NfnFYpENo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Other works</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She has also done some modelling and has been featured on the covers of some famous magazines which include Femina Brides, Travel +leisure etc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style