,0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5249',0,'post','',0),(5286,12,'2021-02-13 13:56:02','2021-02-13 08:26:02','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">‘Love loves to love love’ is what James Joyce said. But I am no author and if you ask me to describe love, my answer will always be Bollywood. Yes, romance has always been Bollywood’s favourite genre and such Bollywood Romantic Movies are what have taught us to accept love in various forms. They have taught us to love, to feel loved, and be with that love forever.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are going through the week of love and the V-day will be arriving soon. Don’t be sad if you still haven’t found ‘the one’ because trust me, there is no such parameter that can define this beautiful feeling. Love always doesn’t mean getting butterflies in the stomach.  Whatever you are, single, committed or heartbroken, let’s celebrate love altogether this Valentine.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, here TV Freak presents to you some all-time favourite Hindi Bollywood<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\"> romantic movies</a> which you can watch with your partner, crush and even with your best friends or your mom (who is more than a Valentine to you) on 14</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> February.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">25. Qarib Qarib Single</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5297 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-1.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love has got no age and this is what this Tanuja Chandra directed Bollywood movie has reminded us. It is not a story of getting butterflies in the stomach for the first time. Instead, it narrates how one needs to let go of long-lost loves and live in the present, live in the solace of someone who is a keeper.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How a 35-year-old lonely widow and a middle-aged man cross paths, develop a special bond, deals with their past loves, and rediscover themselves form the major background of the story. One of the best romance movies, you can definitely give this a watch. It’s <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-27-netflix-original-hollywood-movies-of-2020/\">available on Netflix</a>.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyCU5wgCR84[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">24. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bachna Ae Haseeno</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5299 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-3.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When Ranbir Kapoor is on-screen, who needs a valentine? Speaking of </span><b>romantic movies</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, this 2008 film always has a special place in our hearts.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It amazingly shows how a playboy who has no respect and trust in love finally finds his dream girl and mends his ways. Ranbir’s sizzling chemistry with all the 3 ravishing heroines, the songs, the locations, everything feels so romantic and so full of love in this movie. To make your 14</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> better, what can be a more preferable option other than rewatching this gem? It’s available on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8xucGudsO4[/embedyt]</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">23. Mere Brother ki Dulhan</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5300 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-4.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With all the essential elements of a rom-com, this Imran-Katrina starrer amazingly narrates the story of a guy falling for his brother’s fiancée. With impressive performances and comical situations, it’s worth a watch.  Don’t miss this film on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fqkE46sP4W8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">22. Ashiquui 2</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5301 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-5.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What can you do to express your love? Write poems? Make a promise of ‘forever’? Our protagonist from the movie, Rahul sacrificed his life to make it worth living for his girl.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This Mohit Suri made romantic musical drama falls in that category of romance movies which can make you cry, miss your ‘someone’ who is no longer a part of your life. Combined with the tragic tale of love are its songs sung by legendary singers like Arijit Singh, Ankit Tiwari, Palak Muchal.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The lead pair played by Shraddha Kapoor and Aditya Roy Kapoor will always be one of our favourite Bollywood jodis because of this movie. It’s available on YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aLD28SldPpo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">21. Aisha</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5302 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-6.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s a story about a rich girl named Aisha, played by Sonam Kapoor who thinks of herself as an efficient matchmaker without considering the thoughts or feelings of those involved.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film brings out the relatable confusions all of us in our 20s go through, a series of loves, heartbreaks, and reconciliations. It’s an easy watch that will not disappoint you. You can watch it on Amazon Prime, Disney Hotstar, and YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uACawUfxc74[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">20. Namastey London</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3014 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8-2.jpg\" alt=\"Namastey London (2007)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Another Box-office hit, the 2007 movie will be a good motivation if you are still finding ways to win over your crush. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/\">Akshay Kumar</a> as Arjun, the innocent Indian boy-next-door as well as Katrina as Jazz, the young, smart, modern NRI fitted perfectly in their respective roles.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Along with his beloved NRI, Arjun makes the Indian audience fall for him as well. The pain to be in one-sided love, the purity of unconditional love has been depicted very well in this Hindi film. It’s available on Netflix, Prime, Voot as well as YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NxoG9ixz9tQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">19. Tamasha</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5303 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-7.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An incredible thought-provoking masterpiece narrating the journey of an individual and his self-discovery under the umbrella of the girl he loves. With fantastic acting of the leads, Ranbir and Deepika, Imtiaz Ali’s pragmatic direction, and some soul-touching music, this film takes you to experience an unforgettable roller coaster journey of love and madness. It’s available on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XoJ3etxs48[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">18. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I hate Luv Storys</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5304 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-8.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another very genuine love story to watch on V-day. Each and every aspect and scene in this movie is worth praising. The saying that opposites attract goes very well with the movie. It’s a story about a boy who has no belief in love and a beautiful girl, to whom love is all about happiness, getting butterflies in the stomach, and so on. Let’s witness the amazing journey of Jai and Simran, aka Imran Khan and Sonam Kapoor this Valentine.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JVlkOr4_vUg[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">17. Dev D</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1990 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7-min.jpg\" alt=\"Dev D Bollywood Romantic Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A modern-day adaptation of Sarat Chandra Chatttoadhyay’s Bengali novel, Devdas, this dark romantic film deserves a watch. It tells the tale of two childhood lovers separated by circumstances that make the man turn alcoholic and self-destructive, seeking solace in a prostitute. A love triangle, formed between three individuals has been depicted in a unique way. The film is there on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M3HpfVUovQc[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">16. Tanu weds Manu</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5305 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-9.jpg\" alt=\"Romantic movie for valentine day (9)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Heart touching and relaxing elements is what this movie gives. It’s the story of a crazy small-town girl Tanu and an NRI who in his quest for a bride in India falls for her. How their story goes forward through a series of hilarious events form the main plot of the film. It’s there on Netflix as well as Voot.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3cvkdC7dASU[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">15. Yeh Jawani Hai Deewani</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5306 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-10.jpg\" alt=\"Yeh Jawani Hai Deewani, Romantic movie for valentine day (10)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ‘Re Kabiraaa man jaaa’ – the lyrics still buzz in my ears as Naina and Bunny think going in different paths is the only way to achieve their dreams. Not a very new storyline, but Ayan Mukherjee has even used the cliches so likably. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The adorable love story of a nerd Naina and a charming Bunny, the best friendships shared between Bunny, Aditi and Abhi set goals for the Indian audience.  It’s the best movie to watch with your old squad or your lover-turned-wife and remember all the golden days, the old times spent in the company of each other. You can watch it on Netflix, Prime, YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8gMvS4y0KI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">14. Do Lafzon ki Kahani</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5307 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-11.jpg\" alt=\"Do Lafzon ki Kahani, Romantic movie for valentine day (11)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The story of a boxer and a blind girl, played by <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-biography-career-and-struggles-in-film-industry/\">Randeep Hooda</a> and Kajal Agarwal. If you are looking for a perfect package of action and romance, this is the film for you. The film is available on Zee 5.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5UTAyxXcMxk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">13. Kabir Singh</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5308 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-12.jpg\" alt=\"Kabir Singh, Romantic movie for valentine day (12)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Smoking and love are injurious to health. In Sandeep Vaganas’ direction, this movie realistically gave glimpses of the destructive sides of love. But at the same time, it has shown how love fights back against all odds and finally wins.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Kabir and Preeti’s (<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/kiara-advani-biography-movies-photos-and-controversies/\">Kiara Advani</a>)story makes us believe that true love is never meant to be destroyed and deserve happy endings. One of the perfect couple movies it is; for all the love birds out there, watch this movie on V-day and celebrate being in love. It’s there on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fDE9EiVFzb8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">12. Barfi</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5309 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-13.jpg\" alt=\"Barfi, Romantic movie for valentine day (13)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Oscar-nominated movie Barfi is a landmark film in Indian cinema. The love story of a deaf and mute Barfi and an autistic Jhilmil is iconic in various respects.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Their desire to be with each other till the last breath, their capabilities to embrace each other with all the flaws and imperfections refined Bollywood romance in new ways. Some breath-taking performances by Ranbir, Priyanka, and Ileana, can really be a treat to eyes on the 14</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of Feb. The film is there on Netflix and YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NpIWr3Mg8qU[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">11. Sir</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5310 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-14.jpg\" alt=\"Sir, Romantic movie for valentine day (14)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> A Netflix original, the film is about a simple yet unordinary love story between a handsome young man and his live-in maid. While it may sound like a physical or casual relationship, the duo depicted a heart-to-heart connection very beautifully in the movie.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The pair’s personal conflicts, how they found themselves in one another, their feeling of belonging to each other’s arms, their fear of not conforming to societal norms – every other thing has been depicted so well in this Tilottoma Shome-Vivek Gomber starrer. A perfect heart-warming entertainer to remind yourself what a beautiful feeling love is on the day of love.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tXxoTemNSDA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10. Kites</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5320 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-24.jpg\" alt=\"Kites, Romantic movie for valentine day (24)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Well, love knows no language too. The movie beautifully depicts the same emotions when two people of different languages fell in love. It was more of a realistic movie with typical non-Bollywood acting.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hrithik and Barbara Mori carried out the script very firmly and also the direction, cinematography, writing, and background scores of the movies deserve a mention. Well…it’s a perfect one-time watch. You can watch it on Sony Liv, Tubi Tv.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v2GRYfdvsMY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">9. Jaane tu yaa Jaane na</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5319 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-23.jpg\" alt=\"Jaane tu yaa jaane na, Romantic movie for valentine day (23)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> In love with your best friend? Then this film will be the best for you. After all, what can be more beautiful than two best friends falling for each other and confessing their feelings after watching a movie representing their own story? This rom-com has always been one of our favourites that Bollywood has ever made.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A refreshing and fascinating approach towards love and friendships, Imran and Genelia’s acting represent a very pleasant and worth-watching tale. Filled with fun, drama, nostalgia, it’s a really well-made and engaging film that can make you feel connected with Jai, Aditi, and their group of friends. It’s there on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjzxbP-XYoE[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">8. Jab we met</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5318 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-22.jpg\" alt=\"Jab we met, Romantic movie for valentine day (22)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> A milestone Shahid-Kareena movie which released way back in 2007 but still as an audience we lack words to appreciate the gem it has been. It’s an evergreen work..even if you watch it 10 years later it’s going to feel like the first time and touch your heart.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A soul-stirring story with absolutely stunning songs like Aoge Jab Tum that give us chills, is the perfect old-school romantic movie for Valentine\'s afternoon. Famous dialogues like ‘Main Apni Favourite Hoon’ and some of the iconic sense truly makes this Imtiaz Ali directed film a worth watch. It’s there on Netflix, Prime, YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=054rZyNf_uY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7. Jannat</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5317 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-21.jpg\" alt=\"Jannat, Romantic movie for valentine day (21)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An Imran Hashmi love story that has the capacity of taking a grip of you till the end. It again shows how love changes a person. It revolves around the story of a gambler who tries to change himself after a girl comes in his life. What follows is really interesting to watch. You can watch the movie on YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q0gM-l8oFXo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Love Aaj Kal (2009)</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5316 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-20.jpg\" alt=\"Love Aaj Kal (2009), Romantic movie for valentine day (20)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another Imtiaz Ali creation, this movie narrates two parallel love stories one set back in 1960s and another one of a modern-day couple in 2009. Various obstacles in the path of being with each other and finally reuniting after dilemmas and confusions from the main storyline.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s been a perfect movie depicting the feel and essence of true love of all time and generations. Deepika and Saif are just going to woo you with their performances. You can watch it on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cR854dpzDOA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love Per Square Foot</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5315 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-19.jpg\" alt=\"Love Per Square Foot, Romantic movie for valentine day (19)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another Bollywood romance that came out with flying colours in 2018 is this Anand Tiwari directed the movie. It revolves around Vicky Kaushal and Angira Dhar, a young boy and girl desiring to fulfill their dreams of owning a house, and thus faking a marriage.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Set in Bombay, this movie explores a simple yet fascinating story of 2 Mumbaikars and their struggle to bear up with the city. It’s complete entertainment which will make you laugh at your heart as well as have a teary-eyed smile. It’s available on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2I_eypETmKo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. Ranjhaana</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5314 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-18.jpg\" alt=\"Ranjhaana, Romantic movie for valentine day (18)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A heart touching emotional story of letting go is Ranjhaana. Some things are never meant to be forever and one needs to get over it to avoid the grave consequences. Kundan was never destined to be with Zoya, no matter how much he loved her.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie starring Dhanush and Sonam Kapoor has beautifully portrayed how some times you need to set things free when they are not in your hand. Kundan also met his fate, only to leave the audience heartbroken. A perfect story to witness on Valentine’s day; it’s there on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p5YhTL-27aU[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. Sanam Teri Kasam</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5313 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-17.jpg\" alt=\"Sanam Teri Kasam, Romantic movie for valentine day (17)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U say flawless romantic story, I hear Sanam Teri Kasam! The well-built characters of Inder and Saraswati played by Harshvarhan and Mawra are going to feel so alive when you watch the movie. How their love takes tragic turns from the climax.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It really melts our heart to see the couple caring for each other on-screen and makes us yearn for true love. Everything just feels so true to life. Do I need to mention separately about its forever favorite melodies like Tera Chehera, Bewajah, and so on?  You can watch the film on Amazon Prime.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ncysuADE9y0[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Rockstar</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5312 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-16.jpg\" alt=\"Rockstar, Romantic movie for valentine day (16)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A love story along with the beautiful musical journey of the protagonist creates magic and will glue your eyes on-screen once you start watching the film.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The narrative of the Rockstar avatar of Ranbir and an elegant and graceful Nargis Fakri, aka Janardhan and Heer always secures a position in our favourite list of movies. For all the music lovers and hopeless romantics out there, go and give this movie a watch and enjoy Imtiaz Ali’s unique style of storytelling through an exhilarating ride of emotions. It’s available on YouTube.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n-YTqs8incM[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. Azab Prem ki Gazab Kahani</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5311 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Romantic-movie-for-valentine-day-15.jpg\" alt=\"Azab Prem ki Gazab Kahani, Romantic movie for valentine day (15)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A perfect feel-good rom-com type of movie where the comical situations just steal the spotlight.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the most anticipated Bollywood couples, Katrina and Ranbir have so well expressed their on-screen chemistry and this is what makes the film more distinctive. How the protagonist helps his lady love to unite with her love and lands up in troubles is going to burst you out in laughter. A perfect V-day movie, you can give it a watch on Netflix.</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1-eKtO0E-5s[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are the top 25 Valentine day movies 2021 which you can definitely watch on the day.</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/hollywood-romance-movies-to-watch-this-valentines-day/\">Hollywood Romance Movies on Valentines 2021</a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finally, this is the content for today. We will soon come up with new updates and interesting news about the entertainment industry. Till then, have a safe and nice time. See you in the next article.</span>','Best Bollywood Romantic Movies to Watch on Valentine’s day 2021','','publish','open','open','','best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/randeep-hooda-biography-career-and-struggles-in-film-industry/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/hollywood-romance-movies-to-watch-this-valentines-day/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/akshay-khiladi-kumar-s-love-for-his-country/','2021-02-14 20:07:53','2021-02-14 14:37:53','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5286',0,'post','',0),(5334,13,'2021-02-13 19:24:26','2021-02-13 13:54:26','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s February and romance is in the air now. And tell me who does not like a good romance movie? So here I am presenting you with the best 10 <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/hollywoods-top-10-feel-good-movies-you-must-watch/\">feel-good movies</a> romance of Hollywood to cheer up your mood. Let’s start!</span>\r\n<h2><b>10. Love the Way You Are (2019)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.3</li>\r\n <li><strong>Directors</strong>: Mengying Dai, Tong Zhou</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Vivian Sung, Weilong Song</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Kissasian</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5337 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1-3.jpg\" alt=\"Love the Way You Are (2019) Hollywood Romance movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love the Way You Are </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is a new <strong>adult Chinese love story</strong>. A boy and a girl enter a well-known university in China. Both are from the same small town and what’s more, they are neighbours. The girl is fearless and badass, and the boy is quiet and nerdy. We just have to wait and watch if the opposites do attract or not.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What I greatly liked about this movie is the character of the female lead. Unlike any other typical rom-com movie, she is not clumsy, does not think out loud, has good self-confidence, and does not fall into humiliating disastrous situations.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will expect and predict her to make a public embarrassment of herself, but she won’t. There is also a small twist at the end. Overall, it is a very cute and romantic movie to watch this Valentine’s Day. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love the Way You Are</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is not a popular movie at all. But as the author of this list, I am personally recommending you to watch it.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtLegyEPKGQ[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>9. My Little Bride (2004)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.1</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Ho-Joon Kim</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Rae-Won Kim, Moon Geun-Young</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Amazon Prime Video, AsianCrush</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5338 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2-3.jpg\" alt=\"My Little Bride (2004) Hollywood Romance Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The bride of </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Little Bride</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is really little. She is 16-years old and her husband is in his mid-twenties. Seo Bo-Eun (bride) and Park Sang-Min (groom) have known each other for a very long time as both of their families are very close. Due to some promises their grandparents made, Bo-Eun and Sang-Min had to get into an arranged marriage. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes, it is a movie featuring an older-guy-younger-girl couple. But falling in love wasn’t easy for them.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie has quite a few <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">good comedy scenes</a>. Overall, this movie is highly entertaining.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=96pRBL_BoQ8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>8. Confessions of a Shopaholic (2009)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 5.9</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: P.J. Hogan (Also Directed My Best Friend\'s Wedding)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Isla Fisher, Hugh Dancy (Played Will Graham in Hannibal)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Amazon Prime Video</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5339 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-3.jpg\" alt=\"Confessions of a Shopaholic (2009) Hollywood Romance Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rebecca Bloomwood is a college graduate, freshly fired from her last job, and has a huge debt to pay. Maybe all these problems wouldn’t have been a great factor if she wasn’t a shopaholic. Yup, you read it right. She is a shopaholic, which means she has an uncontrollable desire to shop. Dress, shoes, bags, jewellery, things she doesn’t even need, you name it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Her greatest dream is to write about her favourite fashion magazine. But she ended up working for a finance magazine rather. There she meets Luke Brandon, her boss, who may have to do something to change her destructive addiction one way or another.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Confession of a Shopaholic</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is one of the most underrated <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/\">Hollywood romantic movies</a>. This movie portrays a very serious real-life problem in a fancy way. So you should know, oniomania is not something you should mess with.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZYYCSEV-i1Y[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>7. Crazy, Stupid, Love. (2011)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.4</li>\r\n <li><strong>Directors</strong>: Glenn Ficarra, John Requa</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Steve Carell, Julianne Moore, Emma Stone, Ryan Gosling, John Carroll Lynch, Kevin Bacon</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Amazon Video, VUDU</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5340 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4-3.jpg\" alt=\"Crazy, Stupid, Love. (2011) Hollywood Romance Movies\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie features 3 possible couples. Cal’s wife cheated on him and wants a divorce. Jacob is a rich playboy but it seems like he has finally met a girl who makes him happy. Robbie is a middle school boy who fell in love with his babysitter who is 5 years older than him. These people are all connected one way or another. And this is the story of their </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crazy, Stupid, Love</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I think you guys are familiar with the ‘Ryan Gosling laughing covering his mouth’ GIF, right? Well, that GIF is taken from this movie. If not anything else, I can guarantee you that you will not feel bored for a single second while watching this movie. This movie is very entertaining. It will make you laugh, think and fall in love.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Awards and Nominations:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ryan Gosling was nominated in the category of Best Performance by an Actor in a Motion Picture- Comedy or Musical at the Golden Globes.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W83iZJbVH0A[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>6. 10 Things I Hate About You (1999)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.3</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Gil Junger</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Heath Ledger, Julia Stiles, Joseph Gordon-Levitt</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Disney Plus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5341 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-2.jpg\" alt=\"10 Things I Hate About You (1999)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s a love story between a delinquent girl and a bad boy. They were not supposed to be a couple but fate and her younger sister force them into being in one anyway. This movie is very lively, hilarious, and enjoyable.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Heath Ledger with his curly long red hair, deep voice, and dazzling smile will steal your heart for sure. And it will touch your heart when Julia Stiles reads out loud her sonnet ‘</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10 Things I Hate About You</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">’. </span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This was Heath Ledger’s first Hollywood film.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie is loosely based on the Shakespearian comedy </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Taming of the Shrew</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uE7qjQlfoRs[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>5. Valentine’s Day (2010)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 5.7</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Garry Marshall (Also Directed Runaway Bride, The Princess Diaries (I &amp; II), New Year\'s Eve)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Bradley Cooper, Jamie Foxx, Jennifer Garner, Anne Hathaway</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: DIRECTV, Sling TV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5342 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/6-2.jpg\" alt=\"Valentine’s Day (2010)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Valentine’s Day</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is probably the most appropriate movie to watch on Valentine\'s Day. This movie manifests the story of several couples who are intertwined with each other. The movie also shows that Valentine’s Day does not have to be the day to celebrate only romantic love. This day could be the day to recognize the love of a friend or a parent as well.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is one of the biggest multi-star cast Hollywood movies.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mB-VVUB4Bcc[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>4. Pretty woman (1990)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.0</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Garry Marshall</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Richard Gere, Julia Roberts, Hector Elizondo</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Amazon Video</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5343 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/7-2.jpg\" alt=\"Pretty woman (1990)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pretty Woman</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is one of the most romantic movies in Hollywood ever. Directed by the romance master Garry Marshall, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pretty Woman</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tells the story of a young prostitute who meets a very rich divorced business person. Love blooms between them in secret but the barrier of society is not easy to overcome. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This movie is funny, sad, and romantic all at the same time. Also, Richard Gere looked incredibly handsome in this movie. This is a perfect couple of movie if you want to watch a movie with your partner.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Awards and Nominations:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Julia Roberts was nominated for the best leading actress for this movie at the Oscars.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:  </b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Julia Roberts was only 22 years old when she played her role in this film.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is Ralph Bellemy’s final work. (Rest in peace.)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The OST of this movie </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2C5TjS2sh4\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It must’ve been love</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is performed by Roxette. The song currently has 546 million views. It\'s a classic romantic song. You should check it out on YouTube.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2EBAVoN8L_U[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>3. Bridget Jones’s Trilogy (2001, 2004, 2016)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating</strong>: 6.4 (Average)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Directors</strong>: Sharon Maguire, Beeban Kidron</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Renée Zellweger, Colin Firth, Hugh Grant, Patrick Dempsey</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Starz, DIRECTV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5344 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/8-2.jpg\" alt=\"Bridget Jones’s Trilogy (2001, 2004, 2016)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bridget Jones’s </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is what you call a modernized version of the Jane Austen classic </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">‘Pride and Prejudice’</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with more or less modified protagonists. An extremely clumsy Lizzy, a usual Darcy, and an intensified Wickham.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Though each of the movies ends with a happy ending with no cliffhangers at all, it took a trilogy to make a proper and sure happy ending, dealing with a marriage and a baby. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This trilogy contains three of the best romantic movies in Hollywood. So you better keep it on your watch-list for this Valentine’s Day.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Awards and Nominations: </b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Renee Zellweger was nominated for the best leading actress for the movie Bridget Jones’s Diary (2001) at both the Oscars and Golden Globe. The movie also has one other Golden Globe nomination.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Renee Zellweger was again nominated in the category of the best leading actress (comedy or musical) for </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bridget Jones: The Edge of Reason</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (2004) at the Golden Globe.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This whole trilogy is directed solely by female directors. And this is also the first rom-com trilogy of this millennium. </span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ed Sheeran has a cameo on the third film of this trilogy.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ellie Goulding sang the OST of Bridget Jones’s Baby. The song is called </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvP_OwVSFpk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Still Falling for You</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It’s a very romantic song. You must check it out.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Bridget Jones’s (2016) Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJsvmscPY9w[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>Bridget Jones’s (2004) Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2DFQNPx5sxA[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>Bridget Jones’s (2001) Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EH9CWWqb-6E[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. </span><b>Before Trilogy (1995, 2004, 2013)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 8.03 (Average)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Richard Linklater (Also Directed School of Rock, Boyhood)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Ethan Hawke, Julie Delpy</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: Cinemax Amazon Channel, Max Go</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5345 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/9-2.jpg\" alt=\"Before Trilogy (1995, 2004, 2013)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Before trilogy is considered one of the greatest trilogy of Hollywood. Each of the movies has a poetic synchronization. Each of the movies takes place in different countries of Europe (Austria, France, and Greece) and the stories are set 9 years apart from each other (1995, 2004 and 2013). And all three movies portray just a few continuous hours of Jesse and Celine spending time together.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Richard Linklater has directed these movies with ungodly artfulness. No wonder these movies are three of the best romantic movies of all time.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Awards and Nominations:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This trilogy has a total of 2 Oscar nominations but no win.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before Sunset</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before Midnight</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> was shot in only 15 days.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>The Before Trilogy (1995/04/13) | All Trailers</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8QdlHgWgR9A[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>Before Sunrise (1995) Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6MUcuqbGTxc[/embedyt]\r\n<h3>Before Sunset (2004) trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oI3UuneLcyU[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nBefore Midnight (2013) Trailer:\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=It9yk1pSzPM[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>1. Flipped (2010)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>IMDb Rating:</strong> 7.7</li>\r\n <li><strong>Director</strong>: Rob Reiner (Also Directed The Princess Bride, The Bucket List, A Few Good Men, When Harry Met Sally…)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Star Cast:</strong> Madeline Carroll, Callan McAuliffe</li>\r\n <li><strong>Platform</strong>: HBO Max</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5346 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/10-2.jpg\" alt=\"Flipped (2010)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The boy next door and the story of a sycamore tree. Julie Baker has been in love with Bryce Loski since they were 8, since the first time she laid eyes on him since the day his family moved in next door to her house. But Bryce does not like Julie all that much. He would rather not interact with her at all. But as Tagore said, “Jealousy is the main factor to change a man’s character”, the same thing happens to Bryce as well.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flipped is one of the sweetest love stories ever. It is a great feel-good movie. If you are having a bad day or feeling down, this movie will cheer you up in no time.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=92SgWpDYjlo[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, this is the list of top 10 Hollywood romance movies to watch on Valentine\'s Day. None of the movies will leave you with a bitter taste. All of the movies are lively, enjoyable, and entertaining. I hope you will like the movies. Leave your thoughts about the list in the comment box.</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/\">Bollywood Romance Movies on Valentines Day 2021</a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Happy Watching!!!</span>','Hollywood Romance Movies to Watch This Valentine’s Day | Love..','','publish','open','open','','hollywood-romance-movies-to-watch-this-valentines-day','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/hollywoods-top-10-feel-good-movies-you-must-watch/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-romantic-comedies-that-are-forever-in-our-hearts/','2021-05-29 12:03:57','2021-05-29 06:33:57','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5334',0,'post','',0),(5359,13,'2021-02-14 20:46:42','2021-02-14 15:16:42','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hollywood is a great place to find love. But it is a place known for breaking hearts as well. It is too common to find actor-actresses falling in love with their co-stars or cast members while working together. Sadly, most of them do not last very long. But enough of bad breakups. It’s <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/\">Valentine’s Day</a>, so let’s talk about Hollywood top 5 most romantic couples.</span>\r\n<h2><b>6. Isla Fisher and Sacha Baron Cohen </b></h2>\r\n<b>Movie Together: The Brothers Grimsby (IMDb Rating: 6.2)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5361 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1-4.jpg\" alt=\"Isla Fisher and Sacha Baron Cohen  Hollywood romantic couples\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Isla Fisher (45) and Sacha Baron Cohen (49) are one of the cutest British couples. They have been married for 10 years now. But they have been together longer than that. Sacha met Isla in 2002 at a party in Australia. They officially got engaged in 2004 and finally, they sealed the deal in 2010 with a Jewish wedding. Together they have 3 beautiful children: two daughters and a son. </span>\r\n<h2><b>5. Ryan Gosling and Eva Mendes</b></h2>\r\n<b>Movies Together: The Place Beyond the Pines (IMDb Rating: 7.3)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5362 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2-4.jpg\" alt=\"Ryan Gosling and Eva Mendes Hollywood romantic couples\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many people don’t even know that Ryan Gosling (40) and Eva Mendes (46) are a couple. But it’s true. They have been together for 9 years now. Many people think that they are married. But they are not actually. They have two daughters together. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ryan and Eva are very private persons. They hardly share their personal lives with the media which is a wise decision. Because look what happened to Johnny Depp and Winona Ryder. Johnny and Winona were the most adorable couple in the 90s. But their relationship was very public which was a major factor for their break up.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4. Michael Douglas and Catherine Zeta-Jones</b></h2>\r\n<b>Movies Together: Traffic (IMDb Rating: 7.6)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5363 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"Michael Douglas and Catherine Zeta-Jones Hollywood romantic couples\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, this one of the Oscar-winning most romantic couples of Hollywood. Michael Douglas was previously married to a film producer Diandra Luker, which was a 23-year-long marriage. But when he and Catherine met in 1998, they immediately felt a spark between them. Michael ended his 23-year-old marriage to be with Catherine, and they got married in 2000 and have been together since then.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Michael Douglas (76) and Catherine Zeta-Jones (51) have a 25-year gap between them. But, hey! Nothing can stand between in love, right?</span>\r\n<h2><b>3. Tom Hanks and Rita Wilson</b></h2>\r\n<b>Movies Together: Sleepless in Seattle (IMDb Rating: 6.8)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5364 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4-4.jpg\" alt=\"Tom Hanks and Rita WilsonHollywood romantic couples\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A 32-year-long happy marriage and still going on. Tom Hanks always believed in true love and a woman with whom he will grow old together. But his first marriage did not end well. But then in the same year, he got married to Rita Wilson, and the rest is just a wonderful love story. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tom Hanks (64) and Rita Wilson (64) met in 1981. Hanks was married to another woman then. But they reunited in 1988. Now, they have two sons and very happy marriage.</span>\r\n<h2><b>2. Kurt Russell and Goldie Hawn</b></h2>\r\n<b>Movies Together: The Christmas Chronicles (IMDb Rating: 7.0)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5365 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-3.jpg\" alt=\"Kurt Russell and Goldie Hawn\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kurt Russell (69) and Goldie Hawn (73) have been together for 37 years now. He was previously married to Season Hubley but that marriage only lasted for 4 years. Kurt met Goldie in 1983, and they have been together ever since. They also have a daughter. They never got married though. But that never stopped Kurt and Goldie to be one of the most successful couples ever.</span>\r\n<h2><b>1. Daniel Craig and Rachel Weisz</b></h2>\r\n<b>Movies Together: Dream House (IMDb Rating: 6.0)</b>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5366 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"Daniel Craig and Rachel Weisz\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Daniel Craig (52) and Rachel Weisz (50) are a power couple. They fit together like nobody else. But it’s very hard to get information about their so successful marriage as they are very secretive about their personal lives.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As both of them are theatre artists, they met while working on a play in 1994. But love didn’t bloom so overnight. They stayed as friends for a long time until they realized they could have a perfect future together. Finally, they got married in 2011.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Some Honorable Mentions:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Blake Lively and Ryan Reynolds, Will Smith and Jada Smith, Steven Spielberg and Kate Capshaw, Javier Bardem and Penelope Cruz, Meryl Streep and Don Gummer, John Krasinski and Emily Blunt.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So this was the list featuring the most romantic couples of Hollywood. Let us know your thoughts in the comment section below. </span>','Most Romantic Couples of Hollywood & Their Movies Together','','publish','open','open','','most-romantic-couples-of-hollywood-their-movies-together','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/','2021-02-14 23:00:24','2021-02-14 17:30:24','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5359',0,'post','',0),(5368,12,'2021-02-14 20:58:39','2021-02-14 15:28:39','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First of all, a very<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/\"> happy Valentine’s day</a> to everyone out there. Hope you are having a great day and celebrating love.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bollywood has always presented love to us in various ways. Apart from seeing our favourite stars romancing on-screen, we have also witnessed many of their adorable love stories, finding their ways to a ‘happily ever after’.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Such tales of love, marriage and being stuck with each other for a lifetime have taught us how beautiful it is to have someone by your side forever. So, on this auspicious day of love, TVFreak.com presents to you all our most favourite 5 romantic couples from Bollywood:</span>\r\n<h2><i></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amitabh Bacchan and Jaya Bacchan</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5375 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-most-favourite-real-life-couples-from-Bollywood-6.jpg\" alt=\"Amitabh Bacchan and Jaya Bacchan\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The age-old love story of this evergreen couple set the real goals in this era of heartbreaks and moving on. Almost 48 years of togetherness and still counting, this Amitabh-Jaya </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jodi </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">made the saying of ‘growing old together’ a reality.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The journey from seeing each other for the first time in a film institute to bring together all these years have not been very smooth, especially when Amitabh’s name was linked with another leading contemporary actress. But they never left each other in such times of despair and today besides being a successful couple, they have proved themselves to be the best parents of two children as well.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amitabh-Jaya romantic scene from film Aj ka Arjun</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8k4KU8mqfUY[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. Ranvir Singh and Deepika Padukone | Most Romantic Couples of Bollywood</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5371 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-most-favourite-real-life-couples-from-Bollywood-2.jpg\" alt=\"Ranvir Singh and Deepika Padukone, 5 most favourite real-life couples from Bollywood (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The story which began in the sets of Ramleela finally became a golden chronicle of love on 14</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> November 2018 when the duo tied the knot in Italy. Still can’t over that smile of Deepika when Ranvir got down on his knees and proposed to her with a red heart in an award show!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The way they express their fondness for one another in various events made everyone desire for a partner like them. From professionally acting in films together to becoming the most important part of each other’s lives, the couple proved that no matter what true love finally finds its way to you.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The romantic public appearance of the couple in an award show</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7qlv7OZ-7A[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. Ajay Devgan and Kajol</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5372 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-most-favourite-real-life-couples-from-Bollywood-3.jpg\" alt=\"Ajay Devgan and Kajol, 5 most favourite real-life couples from Bollywood (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The concept of ‘love at first sight’ doesn’t fit for their relationship while ‘Casual friends the, acche friends ho Gaye, best friends ho Gaye, phir love start ho Gaya’ sound more apt, Ok…jokes apart, the duo met in the sets of the film Hulchul.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The year was 1995. After almost 2 years they started dating and finally got hitched in 1999. Today, after 22 years of their marriage they have kept their relationship like old times, alive and energetic, and are leading a blissful family life.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ajay Kajol on-screen romance</span>\r\n\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8jsCJpVm7vA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5373 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-most-favourite-real-life-couples-from-Bollywood-4.jpg\" alt=\"Akshay Kumar and Twinkle Khanna,\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once considered as a playboy of Bollywood, the self-made star Akshay Kumar finally wowed his head in front of his ladylove, the Rajesh Khanna daughter, Twinkle Khanna in 2001. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Akshay crushed over her during the shoot of a magazine. However, it became a full-fledged relationship during the shooting of the film International Khiladi when love blossomed between the two. Sharing such a delightful success story of love for about 2 decades now, they are also the committed parents of a charming teenage son, Aarav.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From a fun interview of the couple</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e8BjVB0oOns[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saif Ali Khan and Kareena Kapoor</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5374 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-most-favourite-real-life-couples-from-Bollywood-5.jpg\" alt=\"Saif Ali Khan and Kareena Kapoor, 5 most favourite real-life couples from Bollywood (5)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Their love saga also started from movie sets itself; the film was Tashan (2008). Though quite reluctant initially, when Saif proposed to her in Paris, she gladly accepted and embarked upon this roller coaster journey of love. Be it on-screen or off-screen, this couple looks the best together. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">hey got married in 2012 and in 2016 was blessed with the cutest baby boy, Taimur. Being opposites, they attracted each other well and today are having some best days of their lives.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kareena-saif\'s 1st public appearance together</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qj1ajQBMFb0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are some of our favourite real-life Romantic Couples of Bollywood who are just the perfect epitome of love, trust and understanding.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. We will soon come up with new updates and interesting news about the entertainment industry. Till then, have a safe and nice time. See you in the next article.</span>','Most Romantic Couples of Bollywood and Their Movies Together','','publish','open','open','','most-romantic-couples-of-bollywood','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/best-bollywood-romantic-movies-to-watch-on-valentines-day-2021/','2021-02-15 22:59:02','2021-02-15 17:29:02','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5368',0,'post','',0),(5390,13,'2021-02-17 21:37:12','2021-02-17 16:07:12','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Golden Globe Awards Nominees for Best Actor 2021 is as diverse as the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/golden-globe-nominations-for-best-director-2021/\">nomination for Best Director</a>— <strong>two <a href=\"https://www.today.com/popculture/complete-list-every-best-picture-oscar-winner-ever-t107617\" rel=\"nofollow\">previous Oscar winners</a></strong>, two actors of Muslim descent, and one posthumous nomination. We can surely hope that among these 5 actors, several of them will also get nominated in this year’s Oscars. So let’s take a look at the list of the Best Actor Nomination for Golden Awards 2021.</span>\r\n<h2><b>5. Anthony Hopkins</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Father</span></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hannibal Lecter from The Silence of the Lambs, Odin from Thor Trilogy, Dr Frederick Treves from The Elephant Man.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5394 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/1-5.jpg\" alt=\"2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees: Anthony Hopkins\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s amazing how even at the age of 83, Anthony Hopkins is still working in the industry like age is just a number. We all know him for his outstanding performance in </span><strong><i>The Silence of the Lambs</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as the most perfect psychopath any fiction has ever created.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This year, he has been nominated for the movie </span><strong><i>The Father </i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">at the 78th Golden Globe Awards for playing the role of a hard-to-help stubborn father who is suffering from dementia.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anthony Hopkins’s Oscar-winning role Hannibal Lecter had only about 25 minutes of screen-time. This is the second shortest screen-time performance to even win an Oscar.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4TZb7YfK-JI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>4. Gary Oldman</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mank</span></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sirius Black from Harry Potter (III, IV, V &amp; VIII), Commissioner Gordon from Batman Trilogy (Directed by Christopher Nolan), Stansfield from Léon: The Professional.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5395 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2-5.jpg\" alt=\"2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees: Gary Oldman\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From </span><strong><i>Sirius Black</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to </span><strong><i>British Prime Minister Winston Churchill</i>, <i>Stansfield</i> to <i>Commissioner Gordon</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, Gary Oldman is one of those few actors who have not confined himself into a common stereotype. He has explored all kinds of characters, fictional to real historical figures, good guy to anti-protagonist.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His career is indeed very diverse. In 2018, he won his Oscar by playing the role of PM Churchill in the movie </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Darkest Hour</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. And this year, he is up for the Golden Globe for playing another real-life personality, </span><strong><i>Herman J. Mankiewicz</i>.</strong>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He was previously married to Uma Thurman.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">David Fincher (director of Mank) and Gary Oldman, both had been married to Donya Fiorentino. Gary married her a year after she and David got divorced.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aSfX-nrg-lI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>3. Tahar Rahim</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Mauritanian</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5396 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/3-5.jpg\" alt=\"2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees: Tahar Rahim\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tahar Rahim is a new face in Hollywood. But he has already done some notable works in the French Film Industry. He is a French actor of Algerian descent. He is one of the few actors who broke the Muslim stereotype exhibition in the films.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In The Mauritanian, Tahar plays the role of a wrongly convicted Muslim prisoner. In the movie, he has proved his full potential with his amazing and bold acting skills.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He has been labelled as the French Al Pacino.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7tmxxzZXLEM[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>2. Riz Ahmed</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sound of Metal</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5397 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/4-5.jpg\" alt=\" Riz Ahmed\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Have you ever wondered, what would you do if one of your senses suddenly starts to fade away? In</span><strong><i> Sound of Metal</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>,</strong> Ruben is a heavy-metal drummer who suddenly starts to lose his hearing power. When your profession and your passion starts to hinder your life, it’s hard to adapt to something new. And this film shows the struggle of that life.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Riz Ahmed, a British actor of Pakistani descent, has already won an Emmy. He played minor roles in some popular movies. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sound of Metal</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is the first film where he had been cast in a major role and for which he has been nominated at the 78th Golden Globe Awards in the category of Best Actor.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Riz Ahmed is an Oxford Graduate.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFOrGkAvjAE[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>1. Chadwick Boseman (1976-2020)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ma Rainey\'s Black Bottom</span></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> T\'Challa from Black Panther</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5398 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5-4.jpg\" alt=\" Chadwick Boseman (1976-2020)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ma Rainey’s Black Bottom</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a real-life incident that happened with Ma Rainey, the mother of R&amp;B music. The film portrays a recording event of Ma Rainey, which soon takes a disastrous turn. <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/chadwick-boseman-black-panther-star-dies-at-43biography-and-movies/\">Chadwick Boseman</a>, who we generally have seen in a superhero role, is the antagonist here. His acting in this role really proved what an amazing actor he was. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When I try to write something about Chadwick Boseman, I get hit by a rush of sadness. What a potential actor, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/chadwick-boseman-black-panther-star-dies-at-43biography-and-movies/\">Chadwick Boseman left us so soon only at the age of 44</a>.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ma Rainey’s Black Bottom is the final film by Chadwick Boseman. (Rest in peace)</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He is the first black person to get a posthumous Golden Globe nomination.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ord7gP151vk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So this was the Golden Globe Awards Nominees for Best Actor of 2021. Let us know who you are rooting for to win and why, in the comment section below.</span>','2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees: Best Performance by an Actor in a Motion Picture - Drama','','publish','open','open','','2021-golden-globe-awards-nominees-best-actor-in-a-motion-picture','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/golden-globe-nominations-for-best-director-2021/','2021-02-17 22:10:45','2021-02-17 16:40:45','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5390',0,'post','',0),(5400,12,'2021-02-17 22:08:57','2021-02-17 16:38:57','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> So, the day of love, aka Valentine’s day 2021 is gone and it’s a wait of 1 year yet again. Be it going on romantic date nights, proposing a crush, or doing the regular ‘Netflix and chill’ stuff at home under a cosy blanket, we all celebrated love in one way or the other. Now let’s have a look at how our <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/category/celebrities/\">favourite stars from Bollywood</a> spent Valentine’s day 2021:</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. Sara Ali Khan</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On her Instagram handle, this glamorous actress posted a reel on 14</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which revealed her exciting plan for the day. Sara highlighted the spirit of self-love in the post and it seemed like she had spent the day all by herself, by working out a little more, by building herself a little more. After all, ‘we all are our own baes’.</span>\r\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/CLQ0tyyJf6B/?utm_so