lish','open','open','','bollywood-valentines-day-2021-celebration-pics-videos','','','2021-02-18 19:04:34','2021-02-18 13:34:34','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=5400',0,'post','',0),(5426,13,'2021-02-20 15:34:53','2021-02-20 10:04:53','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Women have been ruling the golden globes 2021 nominations in every category— <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/golden-globe-nominations-for-best-director-2021/\">Best Director</a>, Best screenplay, and whatnot. So let’s have a look at the best actress nominees of the 78th Golden Globe Awards.  </span>\r\n<h2><b>5. Andra Day</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5428 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Performance-by-an-Actress-1.jpg\" alt=\"Andra Day 2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees Best Performance by an Actress (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: </b><strong>The United States vs. Billie Holiday</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People generally know Andra Day for her singing career, at least that’s what her IMDb profile says. Andra has already participated in some feature films, both animation, and live-action. But </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The United States vs. Billie Holiday</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is the first movie where she played a major role. It is a biography movie focusing on the life and career of </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billie_Holiday\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Billie Holiday</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A real singer playing roles in another singer’s biopic, we see movies of this sort quite often. </span> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jennifer Lopez</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Selena Quintanilla</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Selena</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Beyoncé</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Etta James</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cadillac Records</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jamie Foxx</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Charles in Ray, etc. Jamie Foxx ever won an Oscar for best performance in a leading role for Ray. So, Andra Day is not too behind from her Golden Globe win either.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Fact:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The United States vs. Billie Holiday can be considered a remake of Lady Sings the Blues (1972) where Diana Ross played the role of Billie Holiday.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USi-ppCfxEA[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>4. Carey Mulligan</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5429 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Performance-by-an-Actress-2.jpg\" alt=\"Carey Mulligan, 2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees Best Performance by an Actress (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: Promising Young Woman</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jenny Mellor from An Education, Daisy Buchanan from The Great Gatsby</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A one-time Golden Globe Nominee and one-time Oscar nominee Carey Mulligan has again scored a nomination in 78th Golden Globe Awards for best actress. In </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Promising Young Woman</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, Carey plays a total badass Femme Fatale which people considered to be way out of her league. Dennis Harvey, a critic of the magazine </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Variety</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> stated in his review that Margot Robbie would’ve been a better choice than Carey Mulligan, because, yes, Margot does look more badass than Carey at a glance. But Carey overcame what was laying on her way to achieving perfection for the role and she succeeded. And because of that, she has been rewarded with a Golden Globe Awards Nomination for Best Actress.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7i5kiFDunk8[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>3. Frances McDormand</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5430 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Performance-by-an-Actress-3.jpg\" alt=\"Frances McDormand 2021\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: Nomadland</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marge Gunderson from Fargo, Mildred from Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Frances McDormand is a two-time Academy Award-winning actress, both for leading roles. Her versatile acting skill has been acknowledged by both critics and general people. A desperate mother, a police chief, a jobless lonely woman— Frances McDormand played many diverse characters in her career. She is a true color-changing artist. And this year she earned a Golden Globe Nominations for Best Actress 2021 which will be her 7th time. </span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is married to one of the Coen brothers, Joel Coen.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is an adopted child. Her and Coen’s only son is also adopted.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She was once the roommate of Holly Hunter.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is a Triple Crown of Acting winner.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6sxCFZ8_d84[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>2. Vanessa Kirby</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5431 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Performance-by-an-Actress-4.jpg\" alt=\"Vanessa Kirby,\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: Pieces of a Woman</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The White Widow from Mission: Impossible - Fallout, Princess Margaret from The Crown</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This may be the first Golden Globe nomination for her, but Vanessa Kirby has already scored a BAFTA TV Award. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pieces of a Woman</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tells the story of a mother’s tragedy. An incident of a home-birth to a dead daughter throws everything off balance. Vanessa Kirby, with her beauty and grace pulled off her character so flawlessly that the movie will bring you into tears. That is what real acting is.</span>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1zLKbMAZNGI[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>1. Viola Davis</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5432 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Golden-Globe-Awards-Nominees-Best-Performance-by-an-Actress-5.jpg\" alt=\"2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Nominated For: Ma Rainey\'s Black Bottom</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Other Notable Roles: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rose Maxson from Fences, Amanda Waller from Suicide Squad, Aibileen Clark from The Help</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Viola Davis has established herself as an icon for all Black actresses in the film industry. She makes the most unknown character relatable to us by her outstanding and incomparable acting skill. In </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ma Rainey\'s Black Bottom,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> she plays the R&amp;B mother Ma Rainey when the world was strictly biased by racism and sexism, which I think she has found very relatable to this day as a woman of color rising to her apex of success. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This Oscar-winning actress has five previous Golden Globe Nominations and one win. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A/n: Now that I am talking about Viola Davis, you should go see the video where Viola Davis was the presenter of Meryl Streep’s Cecil B. Demille award. That speech is an art itself. </span>\r\n<h3><b>Fun Facts:</b></h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Viola Davis is one of five actresses to receive an Oscar nomination for a performance with less than 10 minutes of screen time.</span></li>\r\n <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is a Triple Crown of Acting winner.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Watch Trailer:</h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ord7gP151vk[/embedyt]\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion:</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So this was the list of best actress nominations for golden awards 2021. Looks like a very tough competition to me. Let us know your predictions about this year’s Golden Globe in the comment section below.</span>','2021 Golden Globe Awards Nominees: Best Performance by an Actress in a Motion Picture - 