an style=\"font-weight: 400;\">did</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">her</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">graduation</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">in</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">English</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Literature</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From a young age, a liking for theatre grew in her. As a 14-year-old girl, Chaddha started performing in theatres. While in their 20s, she continued acting in plays and after some time-shifted to Mumbai.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chaddha during her theatre days:</span></h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5436 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Sheeba-Chaddha-biography-and-other-interesting-facts-2.jpg\" alt=\"Theatere\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>Sheeba Chaddha age and physical appearance</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This glamorous actress who can fit herself in any character role is currently 48 years old. She has a height of 5’3”.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Sheeba Chaddha Husband, family and friends</b></h2>\r\nMost <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">things</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">we</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">know</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">are</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">regarding</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chaddha\'s</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">professional</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">life</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">and</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">she</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">has</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">never</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">revealed</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">much</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">about</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">her</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">personal</span> <span style=