resting-facts-3.jpg\" alt=\"friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5453 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kirti-Kulhari-Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-4.jpg\" alt=\"Kirti Kulhari friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Actor <strong>Mohit Raina</strong> is also one of her good friends and besides working together, the duo also enjoys each other’s company off-screen.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5454 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kirti-Kulhari-Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-5.jpg\" alt=\"friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nKriti’s friendly nature helps her to mix well with people and hence she develops a good friendship with most of her co-stars, spends time and hangs out with them. At least, her social media handle gives us such glimpses.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5455 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kirti-Kulhari-Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-6.jpg\" alt=\"Kirti Kulhari Biography and other interesting facts (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5457 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kirti-Kulhari-Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-8.jpg\" alt=\"Kirti Kulhari Biography and other interesting facts (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And of course, she has close friends from outside the industry too.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><b>Beginning of the career</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Along with modelling, Kirti joined a theatre group Yatri to sharpen her acting skills. Post a long one-month workshop there, she delivered remarkable performances in 3 plays, namely, <em><strong>Chinta Chod Chintamani, Shehensbhah of Azeemo, </strong>and <strong>Sakharaam Binder.</strong></em></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kirti also became a common face in TV commercials as we saw her in many of such small-time screen appearances. These include the ads of ICICI Bank, Taj Mahal Tea, Whirlpool Refrigerators, Virgin Mobiles, Close – up and so on.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Kirti Kulhari movies</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5450 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Kirti-Kulhari-Biography-and-other-interesting-facts-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kirti Kulhari Biography and other interesting facts (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kirti’s first film was an <strong>Odia language movie</strong><em><strong> \"Dharini\" </strong></em>and her entry in Bollywood was in 2010 as Parmindar, a part of the Hindi movie <em><strong>Khichdi: The Movie</strong></em>. Next, she turned heads with her 2011 black comedy Bollywood film <em><strong>Shaitaan</strong></em>. From the beginning, till now she has nearly 12 Hindi movies in her basket.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Up to 2016 despite doing some films like <em><strong>Rise of the Zombie, Jal, Cute Kameena,</strong></em> Kirti didn’t receive the praise she deserves but then Aniruddha Roy directed the Bollywood film <em><strong>Pink</strong> </em>happened which changed the path of her career. Pink was a grand success and gave her enough recognition.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After that, the actress didn’t look back and became a demanding name for Bollywood. From main to supporting roles, she has the capability of performing every character gracefully on-screen. Other of her major appreciated works include Hindi movies like <em><strong>Indu Sarkar, Mission Mangal, Blackmail, Uri: The Surgical Strike.</strong></em></span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kulhari talked about her journey from Khichdi to Pink</span></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v