eresting facts\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Born in the year 1972 in a mesmerizing city named <strong>Jalandhar</strong> located in the land of five rivers, Punjab, he grew up there. Do a little math, and you will know he is going to be 49 years old as of 2021. Shorey achieved his primary education there from <strong>Dayanand Model School.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His next alma meter includes a <strong>school in Mumbai</strong> from where he completed his school-level education. For his further studies, Shorey went to <strong>Xavier\'s Institute of Communication,</strong> <strong>Mumbai</strong> as well as to Mithibai College to complete his graduation. During his school and college days, he actively took part in dramatics.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Ranvir Shorey Family and Friends</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ranvir hails from a family filled with movie professionals and of course, cannot be considered as a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/successful-self-made-bollywood-stars-who-had-no-root-in-industry/\">Bollywood outsider</a>. He was born to KD Shorey who was a well-known writer, producer and director of his time. Not a single child of his parents, his elder brother is also an actor while the other brother, Shrinath Shorey is a movie Writer and Director.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shorey is very fond of and is close to his son and his father as well whom he considers his inspiration. Sadly, his mother is no more.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5586 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Ranvir-Shorey-biography-and-other-interesting-facts-3.jpg\" alt=\"Ranvir Shorey family and friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5587 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Ranvir-Shorey-biography-and-other-interesting-facts-4.jpg\" alt=\" family and friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regarding his friends, the actor is close to eminent Bollywood figures like <strong>Rajat Kapoor</strong> and <strong>Vinay Pathak.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5588 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Ranvir-Shorey-biography-and-other-interesting-facts-5.jpg\" alt=\"family and friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">His good and friendly nature also develops a good bond with his co-actors. At least, Ranvir Shorey Instagram gave us such glimpses.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5589 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Ranvir-Shorey-biography-and-other-interesting-facts-6.jpg\" alt=\"family and friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>An impressive physique as well</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This talented actor is 6 feet tall and weighs about 78 kgs. Even at this age he has perfect body measurements and works out regularly. As per his words, that whenever he has leisure time, he hits the gym to work on his physique.</span>\r\n<h2><b>The beginning – Ranvir Shorey television shows</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ranvir Shorey has also had an appreciable television career and in fact, started his journey in the entertainment world with a small screen.  Since 1999, he has hosted numerous shows including </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Oye, House Arrest, Saba, Chat Room</strong>,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> couple dance reality show </span><strong><i>Jhalak Dikla Ja 7</i>.</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shorey had also been a part of the famous <strong>The </strong></span><strong><i>Great Indian Comedy Show</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which aired on Sahara One.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He also hosted a very successful talk show with his close friend Vinay Pathak</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, <strong>Ranvir Vinay Aur Kaun?.</strong></span></i>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2010, he played the lead role of Dashrath Srivastava in a soap opera </span><strong><i>Kaam Ka Plot</i>.</strong>\r\n<h3><strong>Watch Shorey in Kaam ka Plot</strong></h3>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tda0MY_N_o[/embedyt]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> In 2014 he was a contestant of the Rohit Shetty hosted reality show </span><strong><i>Fear Factor: Khatron Ke Khiladi Darr Ka Blockbuster.</i></strong>\r\n<h2><b>The journey in Bollywood - Ranvir Shorey movies</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Shorey made his Hindi film debut with </span><strong><i>Ek Chhotisi Love Story</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> alongside <strong>Manisha Koirala</strong> which was released in 2002 but unfortunately failed to create magic in the box office. In 2006, </span><strong><i>Khosla Ka Ghosla</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> was released. It was a good break for him as he was praised for his iconic comic role in the film.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All through the years, he has entertained us in many such superhit films such as </span><strong><i>Jism, Freaky Chakra Waise Bhi Hota Hai 2,  Lakshya, Hum Dum, The Film, Shiva,  Mixed Doubles, Pyaar Ke Side Effects</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> alongside the very talented Rahul Bose. He has also been commercial hits like </span><strong><i>Singh is King</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><strong><i>Chandni Chowk to China</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and the list goes on.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Watch this hilarious scene of Shorey from Chandni Chowk to China</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JLD_CZ_oMQY[/embedyt]</span>\r\n<h3