pqydnw\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first looks of the lead actors have also come out meanwhile and have created a lot of hype. On<strong> 22</strong></span><strong>nd</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong> October,</strong> the intro of the <strong>lead character of Bheem</strong> surfaced and we witnessed a totally different challenging version of NT Rama Rao.</span>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/tv/CGosvDejDOl/?igshid=ic1a55cg7hn6\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On 15</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> March when Alia’s first look from the movie resurfaced on social media and excited her fans and admirers. Undoubtedly the actress looks stunningly beautiful.</span>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CMbdZ1aDHoV/?igshid=gltwmil75su3\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, on 26</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> March, the poster of Ramcharan in Alluri’s character was released. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, there is news that the motion poster of Ajay Devgan’s character will also be released soon on 2</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nd</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> April i.e., on his birthday.</span>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CM4PpLjDn5l/?igshid=yew42zy5wvkf\r\n<h2><b>Direction</b></h2>\r\n<b> </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The legendary director, <strong>the creator of Bahubali,</strong> one of the greatest cinematic creations of the decade, <strong>SS Rajamouli</strong> has directed RRR. The entire nation is now waiting to see whether Rajmouli has once again created magic on the big screen. Let\'s see if it will take us to an altogether different universe or not.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The original story</strong> has however been developed by the talented <strong>KV Vijayandra Prasad</strong>, the writer of popular films like </span><strong><i>Bajrangi Bhaijaan, Bahubali,</i> and <i>Manikarnika.</i></strong>\r\n<h2><b>RRR Producers</b></h2>\r\n<b> </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The film has got a gifted, popular producer of the Tamil film industry,<strong> DVV Danayya</strong> while <strong>MM Srivalli</strong> has served as the line producer.</span>\r\n<h2><b>RRR Storyline / Plot</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As mentioned earlier, RRR is a period drama and hence will take us in a world of the past. However, <strong>it is not a biopic</strong> or it is<strong> not ‘inspiring from true events’</strong> kind of movie. Reportedly it is going to narrate<strong> a fictional story</strong> about 2 Indian freedom fighters. And it will show their journey and struggle for their motherland to free them from the hands of the British. Till now anything more is not in the news about it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, this is all the news we have till now about </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">RRR</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Baahubali</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has really made the entire nation fall for SS Rajamouli’s filmography and hence now we are really expecting a lot of <strong>magic in this film</strong> too. Hope it keeps up to our expectations. And lastly, all the very best wishes to the entire team for their soon-to-be-released project.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the content for today. We will soon bring to you some other updates about the world of entertainment. Till then have a safe and nice time.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/trailers/bollywood-movie-latest-trailers/\">Checkout Latest Bollywood Movie Trailers</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/trailers/hollywood-movie-trailers/\">Checkout Latest Holywood Movie Trailers</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Upcoming Movie RRR | Storyline, Release, Ca