>nd internet buzz. The dark realities of Bollywood, the dark secrets of Bollywood</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">or some of the hidden tales of our favourite celebs are really entertaining to read. Today, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/\">TVfreak.com</a> presents to you some of those Bollywood masalas. So, keep on reading till the end.</span>\r\n<h2><b>1. Amir Khan’s probable love affair and its consequence</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6253 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Bollywood-secrets.jpg\" alt=\"Bollywood secrets\" width=\"700\" height=\"941\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let’s begin narrating the dark secrets of Bollywood celebs with the Mr. perfectionist of the industry.</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amir Khan, known to give his best when it comes to movies, may have a very happening professional life but his personal life seems to be controversial. While Kiran Rao is his second wife and the duo has a son, Khan has two more children from his first wife Reena Dutta.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wait, there is more when it comes to his love life. He reportedly had a passionate love affair with Jessica Hines, a journalist and the author of Amitabh Bachchan’s biography. In 2004, Jessica gave birth to a baby boy, and allegedly it was Amir Khan’s son whom the actor abandoned. However, they got separated, and Hines went to London with his son who is now a model.</span>\r\n<h2><b>2. Sonakshi’s striking resemblance with Reena Roy – just a sheer coincidence or something else?</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6244 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sonakshi’s striking resemblance with Reena Roy – just a sheer coincidence or something else?\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sonakshi Sinha, the actress known for famous Hindi movies like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Akira, Mission Mangal, Ittefaq, Lootera</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has a striking resemblance with the veteran actress Reena Roy. In this reference, if we go back to a little past, there was a time when a love affair or a physical relationship in Bollywood between Sonakshi’s father, Satrughna Sinha, and Reena Roy had been making headlines.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As Sonakshi grew up, her physical appearances began quite similar to that of Reena Roy’s. Here the question arises, is she really the daughter of the couple whom she considers her parents, or is she the illegitimate child of her father and his ex-lover? However, she has always brushed such a possibility calling it to be a rumour; but who knows the truth? </span>\r\n<h2><b>3. The virgin sultan of Bollywood</b></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6245 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-2.jpg\" alt=\"The virgin sultan of Bollywood\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes, I am talking about Salman Khan, the most eligible bachelor of Bollywood. This 55-year-old actor got his name linked with many of the young faces like Katrina Kaif and Jacqueline Fernandez. However, it seems like love has never been his cup of tea and he never tied the knot.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In one of the episodes of the famous talk show </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Koffee with Karan,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> he was asked whether he can please someone in bed or not and a lot of buzzes was created when Khan blushed and gently replied that he is still a Virgin. We still don’t know about the real side of Salman Khan and this gives rise to many possible questions like is his dislike ness about sex one of the reasons of him getting never married? Nobody knows.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4. Rishi Kapoor bribed for an award</b></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6246 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the biggest stars of the Indian film industry whom we lost last year is Rishi Kapoor. Undoubtedly, he is one of the finest and talented actors Bollywood has ever got. But his past is also not free from the dirty secrets of the Bollywood industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It was in 1974 when he bagged the prestigious Best Actor FilmFare Award for his performance in the super hit movie, Bobby. However, in his autobiography, he himself had confessed to having bought the award by bribing an amount of INR 30,000.</span>\r\n<h2><b>5. Ranbir’s active sex life since a young age</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6247 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ranbir Kapoor seems to have a playboy image from a very young age. Some of the A-listed actresses of the industry including Deepika, Katrina, and now Alia have fallen for him. Actors usually don’t like revealing much about their past but Kapoor has been an exception.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview, he revealed that just at the age of 15 he lost his virginity and had sexual intercourse with his school girlfriend. However, he always refrained from saying who that girl was and also stated that the relationship didn\'t last for a very long time.</span>\r\n<h2><b>6. Kangana Ranaut, a victim of abuse</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6248 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the many</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">dirty secrets of film industry</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">got revealed when the fearless tigress of Bollywood, Kangana Ranaut who now never fails to give an opinion on any matter, admitted being a victim in an abusive relationship with the actor Aditya Pancholi with whom she shares an age difference of about 20 years.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ranaut spilt the beans in an interview by saying that it was during the early phase of her career when she was struggling, she had an affair with Aditya Pancholi. However, she admitted that the actor used to physically abuse her but she never spoke about it openly for the sake of her career.</span>\r\n<h2><b>7. Kalki Koechlin\'s favours</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6249 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regarding dark side of heroines, let’s speak of Kalki Koechlin. The beautiful actress Kalki Koechlin known for her roles in films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Margarita with a straw</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yeh Jawani hai Deewani</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has made a very shocking but brave revelation that many actors or actresses cannot. She confessed in an interview that during her initial days to get chances in movies, she used to sleep with directors and producers. And by sleeping I mean having sex.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is no such information about this Bollywood actress for night rates. She admitted to stopping such acts she gained success in the industry.</span>\r\n<h2><b>8. Ranveer’s a bad experience</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6250 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-7.jpg\" alt=\"Top 10 dark secrets of Bollywood industry (7)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ranveer Singh, now one of the highest-paid as well as most demandable actors in the country, shared one of his disastrous experiences from the initial days of his career and revealed another of the dark dirty secrets of the Bollywood industry.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In an interview, he confessed that a casting director asked him to do a physical favour in order to give him a role. When he said no, the director seemed heartbroken. The director started requesting to give the least favours like letting him touch or see Singh’s private parts.</span>\r\n<h2><b>9. Sunny leone\'s exploration in the world of sex</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6251 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-8.jpg\" alt=\"Sunny leone\'s exploration in world of sex\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s a quite known fact that Sunny Leone started her career as a blue film actress. However, what may sound a little more shocking to you is that her first kiss was at the age of 11. And very soon at the age of 16 or 18 she discovered her bisexuality. In fact, during her career in the porn industry, she decided of doing lesbian scenes.</span>\r\n<h2><b>10. Big B’s act in a B-grade film</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6252 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-dark-secrets-of-Bollywood-industry-9.jpg\" alt=\"Big B’s act in a B-grade film\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amitabh Bachchan, the evergreen superstar of all time has also been a part of the dark secrets of film industry. appeared in the blue film. Yes, you read it right. It was a film named </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boom</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Reportedly the actor was facing some backlashes in his career at that time due to which a financial crisis arose. And for that he took such a decision.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are some of the really dark secrets behind the faces we see on screen. There are more. We will write about them some other time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This is the content for today. Hope you had a happy reading. See you in the next article.</span>','Top 10 Dark Secrets of Bollywood Industry','','publish','open','open','','top-10-dark-secrets-of-bollywood-industry','','','2021-05-17 12:10:42','2021-05-17 06:40:42','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=6243',0,'post','',0),(6257,13,'2021-05-17 10:48:45','2021-05-17 05:18:45','Let\'s check out the list of  Romantic Comedy Anime and have fun with this collection. And one more thing every movie is must watch here. So save your time and invest for yourself here.\r\n<h2><b>10. Ookami Shoujo to Kuro Ouji (2014)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Wolf Girl and Black Prince</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 7.1</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 7.14</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Takahiro_Sakurai\">Takahiro Sakurai</a>, Kanae Itou</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: TYO Animations</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Crunchyroll</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6259\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-1-300x240.jpg\" alt=\"Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (1)\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shinohara Erika is in trouble. She was ashamed that being a high school student she did not have a boyfriend. So she took a photo of a random hot guy from the street and showed it to her girlfriends saying that the guy in the picture is her boyfriend. But lying has its consequences, doesn’t it?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Erika soon finds out that the guy he took the picture of is actually a student in her school. So to prevent the cat from coming out of the bag, the guy (Sata Kyouya) and Erika make a deal. Sata will pretend to be her boyfriend and in return, Erika will comply with his every command like a dog. Now Sata may seem like a charming guy from the outside but inside he has a sadistic self which will punish Erika to its heart’s content. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This anime also has a live-action adaptation.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Personal recommendation: If you liked this anime, </span></i><b><i>Itazura na Kiss</i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (Mischievous Kiss) is a very similar anime to this.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>9. Ore Monogatari!! (2015)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: My Love Story!!</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 7.8</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 7.94</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Eguchi Takuya, Namikawa Daisuke, Fukuyama Jun</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: Madhouse</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Crunchyroll</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6260 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-2.jpg\" alt=\"My Love Story!!: Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ore Monogatari is an <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/6-anime-movies-that-were-nominated-for-the-oscar/\">anime</a> that broke the stereotype of a typical shoujo anime having handsome male leads. The male lead of this anime is not actually what you call a handsome young man. Gouda Takeo is a giant guy, he is large in both length and width, he has bushy eyebrows, a boring hairstyle, and thick lips. But most importantly he has a heart of gold.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ironically girls can not see that and they don’t want to date him seeing his not so beautiful physical features. But when one day Takeo saves Yamato Rinko from a pervert on the train, Yamato instantly falls in love with him seeing his kindness. And that’s how the story begins. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Personal recommendation: </span></i><b><i>The Lovely complex</i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is another anime that broke the common stereotype. Hope you will enjoy it as well.</span></i>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A/n: Shoujo is a genre of anime and manga (Japanese comics) which’s main target audience is young girls. Most of the time romance is the main theme of these anime.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>8. Ao Haru Ride (2004)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Blue Spring Ride</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 7.4</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 7.66</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Uchida Maaya, Kaji Yuuki, Hirakawa Daisuke, KENN</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: Production I.G</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Crunchyroll</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6261 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-3.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Spring Ride: Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What happens when you meet your unsuccessful first love again? And what if he is more handsome, cooler, and seems to have gone through some serious changes? Futaba is a high school student who had a chance as such. Will she be able to confess her feelings to Kou, unlike the previous time? You will have to watch the anime to find out.</span>\r\n<h2><b>7. Wotaku ni Koi wa Muzukashii (2018-2021)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Wotakoi: Love is Hard for Otaku</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 7.6</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 7.95</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Sawashiro Miyuki, Kaji Yuuki, Sugita Tomokazu</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: A-1 Pictures</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Amazon Prime Video</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6262 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-4.jpg\" alt=\"Love is Hard for Otaku: Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (4)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is a super funny anime. If you are a die-hard otaku, you may even find it relatable to yourself. Narumi is an adult office lady. But she had to quit her previous job because her ex-boyfriend found out that she was an Otaku and spread the news in her office. On the first day of her new job, Narumi finds out that her childhood and otaku friend Hirotaka also works in the same office. What a coincidence!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At the end of the first day at the office, they go out for a drink and Hirotaka asks Narumi to be his girlfriend. Now Hirotaka is not the type that Narumi likes but he has been in love with her since childhood. Together and with another quarrelsome otaku couple from the office, they start their new journey of love and friendship. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A/n: </span></i><b><i>Otaku</i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a term for people who are greatly interested in anime, manga and video games. It practically means nerd.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>6. Horimiya (2021-)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 8.2</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.27</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Fukuyama Jun, Nobuhiko Okamoto, Ono Daisuke</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: CloverWorks</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Hulu, Funimation</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6263 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-5.jpg\" alt=\"Horimiya (2021-): Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (5)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is the story of Hori and Miyamura. Hori is a very violent and tsundere girl. But deep inside she is a very caring person. Miyamura on the other hand oozes the aura of a bad boy. He got his face and ears pierced, skin tattooed, long hair. The truth is he actually is a very quiet and innocent guy. Now, these two also happens to be neighbours and childhood friends. What will happen if they start going out when they are completely opposite of each other? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Horimiya has been a great highlight in the </span><b>Winter 2021 season</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The manga from which the anime was adapted was recently completed. The first season of the anime was a great hit. So hopefully we will get more seasons in the future.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A/n: </span></i><b><i>Tsundere</i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a type of person who is violent on the other side but caring on the inside. If they are in love with you, they will never admit it, rather they act the opposite in front of you. But in secret, they are deeply in love with you.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>5. Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensai-tachi no Renai Zunousen (2019-)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Kaguya-sama: Love is War</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 8.4</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.42</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Aoi Koga, Makoto Furukawa, Konomi Kohara</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: A-1 Pictures</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Crunchyroll</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6264 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-6.jpg\" alt=\"Kaguya-sama: Love is War: Top 10 romcom anime you should watch (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kaguya and Miyuki both are the leaders of the student council of a prestigious school which kind of makes them rivals as well. Both of them are from extremely well-off families as well which makes them very elite persons.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The possibility of romance is hard when just one of the parties is a Tsundere. What happens when both of the male and female leads are Tsundere? Kaguya and Miyuki are madly in love with each other but neither of them will confess. So it soon turns into a game to make the opponent confess first.</span>\r\n<h2><b>4. Toradora! (2008-2009)</b></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 8.0</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.20</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Rie Kugimiya, Junji Majima, Yui Horie</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: J.C.Staff</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Crunchyroll, Netflix, Amazon Prime Video</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6265 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-7.jpg\" alt=\"Toradora! (2008-2009) romantic comedy anime \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Studio </span><b>J.C.Staff</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is kind of known for making good quality rom-com anime. Toradora is one of them. It is another anime that makes two totally different people come together by unusual circumstances. Aisaka Taiga is a very short girl. But she is also known as the palm-sized tiger for her bad temper and violent nature.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Takasu Riyuuji on the other hand is mistaken as a delinquent and ‘someone not to be messed with’ because he has intimidating eyes. Now Taiga and Ryuuji have crushes on the other\'s close friend. So they make a pact to help each other to get close to each other’s friends. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Toradora is one of those shoujo anime with a very satisfying ending. You will not be disappointed, I promise.</span>\r\n<h2><b>3. Kimi ni Todoke (2009-2011)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: From Me to You</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 7.8 </b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.01</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Sawashiro Miyuki, Nmikawa Daisuke, Nakamura Yuuichi</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: Production I.G</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Hulu, Funimation</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6266 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-8.jpg\" alt=\"From Me to You: romantic comedy anime \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Remember the Horror movie </span><b>The Ring</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? It is actually an adaptation from a Japanese horror movie called </span><b>Ringu</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The ghost girl of that movie </span><b>Sadako Yamamura</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, well, our female protagonist (Sawako Kuronuma) of this anime kind of looks like her. Her classmates are terrified of her. That’s why she has no friends and she is very quiet. But somehow she catches Kazehaya’s attention who is known to be the school’s boyfriend. With his help, Sawako starts to make new friends, find happiness and even true love maybe.</span>\r\n<h2><b>2. Kamisama Hajimemashita (2012-2016)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Kamisama Kiss</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 8.1</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.04</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Akira Ishida, Nobuhiko Okamoto, Namikawa Daisuke, Tachibana Shinnosuke</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: TMS Entertainment</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Hulu, Funimation</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6267 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-9.jpg\" alt=\"Kamisama Kiss: romantic comedy anime \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The story of Kamisama Hajimemashita starts with a kiss on Nanami’s forehead. The Kiss was from Mikage who is an earth deity. Now because of that kiss, Nanami Kind of turns into a substitute deity and when she visits her shrine, she finds a handsome fox demon waiting for her who also happens to be her familiar. (well, not for her actually, he was waiting for Mikage.). For Nanami, it was love at first sight. But that rude fox is super biased about humans. How will it turn into a love story? But don’t worry. The ending won’t disappoint you.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are a fan of Japanese mythology, this anime is perfect for you. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Personal recommendation: </span></i><b><i>InuYasha </i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is oddly similar to this anime. You should watch it if you like this one.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>1. Kaichou wa Maid-sama (2010-2011)</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alternative title: Class President is a Maid!</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>IMDb Rating: 8.0</b></li>\r\n <li><b>MyAnimeList Rating: 8.04</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Voice Artists: Hanazawa Kana, Nobuhiko Okamoto</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Studio: J.C.Staff</b></li>\r\n <li><b>Platform: Hulu, Netflix</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6268 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Top-10-romcom-anime-you-should-watch-10.jpg\" alt=\"romantic comedy anime \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now this one is a genre-defining shoujo anime. The comedy bits of this anime is outstanding. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seika High used to be an all-boys high school. Only recently it became co-ed. That’s why it has only a few female students. But the boys in this school are savages as ever.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Misaki is a female student of Seika High who became the president of the student council to make the school a better place for girls. She is strong-willed, powerful and intimidating. But she also leads a very poor life. To support her family, she works as a waitress in a maid-cafe which nobody in her school knows about. One day, by accident, Usui Takumi, a boy from Misaki’s school (whom she absolutely can’t stand, by the way) finds out about her secret. And then begins the real story.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Personal Recommendation: </span></i><b><i>Special A </i></b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is a similar type of anime to Kaichou wa Maid-sama.</span></i>\r\n<h2><b>Some Honorable Mentions:</b></h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Tonari no Kaibutsu-kun (My Little Monster)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Inu x Boku SS</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Fruits Basket</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Midara na Ao-chan wa Benkyou ga Dekinai (Ao-chan Can’t Study)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Gekkan Shoujo Nozaki-kun (Monthly Girls\' Nozaki-kun)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Kishuku Gakkou no Juliet (Boarding School Juliet)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Akkun to Kanojo (My Sweet Tyrant)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Acchi Kocchi (Place to Place)</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Tsurezure Children</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Nijiiro Days (Rainbow Days)</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So this was the list of top 10 romantic comedy anime. Let us 