ht: 400;\">After completing her high</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">er secondary level education, she took admission to the famous <strong>Jai Hind college in Mumbai.</strong> She pursued her <strong>graduation</strong> from that educational institute and attained a Bachelors’s degree in <strong>Mass Communication</strong>. In an interview, she opened up a little more about her life before entering Bollywood, she was a part of her mom’s pre-school. She used to take care of the kids, teach them, and even confessed about changing their diapers when required.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kiara is a child lover indeed. She said she would love to have her own child someday in order to embrace the heavenly feeling motherhood is.    </span>\r\n<h2><b>Kiara Advani parents and family </b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She is not completely from a <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/successful-self-made-bollywood-stars-who-had-no-root-in-industry/\">non-celebrity background as actors like well-known actors</a> like Ashok Kumar and Saeed Jeffrey are her relatives from her mom’s side. However, she is the <strong>daughter of a businessman</strong> named <strong>Jagdeep Advani</strong> and her mother <strong>Genevieve Jeffrey</strong> has been a <strong>teaching professional</strong>. Kiara is not the only child of her parents. She has a younger sibling too, a <strong>brother</strong> named<strong> Misaal Advani. </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6314 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/actress-Kiara-Advani-biography-movies-and-other-interesting-facts-4.jpg\" alt=\"brother and family\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> (Kiara with her brother)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><b>Friends of the actress</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kiara has a very bubbly nature which has led to her making some really close friends in the competitive Bollywood world. Among the actresses, she shares a very good bond with <strong>Aliya Bhatt</strong> and they are often seen together on party-like occasions.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6315 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/actress-Kiara-Advani-biography-movies-and-other-interesting-facts-5.jpg\" alt=\" friendship with alia bhatt\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> <strong>Atheya Shetty</strong> is also her close friend and they share a sister-like bonding. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6316 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/actress-Kiara-Advani-biography-movies-and-other-interesting-facts-6.jpg\" alt=\"actress Kiara Advani biography, movies and other interesting facts (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Her on-screen, as well as off-screen chemistry with <strong><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/vicky-kaushal-biography-filmy-career-and-upcoming-movies/\">Vicky Kaushal</a>,</strong> is definitely worth noting whenever they are spotted together.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> She had developed an adorable friendship with <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\"><strong>Sushant Singh Rajput</strong></a> as well after working together in MS Dhoni’s biopic; but sadly, it didn’t last long due to the actor’s unfortunate demise last year. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6317 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/actress-Kiara-Advani-biography-movies-and-other-interesting-facts-7.jpg\" alt=\"actress Kiara Advani friends\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from this, not only Kiara herself but also, her entire family shares a very good relation with Salman Khan. <strong>Reportedly, Khan is her mom’s friend since childhood and behind Kiara’s entry into Bollywood too, Salman had great support.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6318 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/actress-Kiara-Advani-biography-movies-and-other-interesting-facts-8.jpg\" alt=\"actress Kiara Advani salman khan\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, we should not miss out on the person whom Kiara considers <strong>her oldest and best friend, i.e, Isha Ambani.</strong> Yeah…you read it right. Kiara’s bestie is the <strong>billionaire Mukesh Ambani’s daughter</strong>, <strong>Isha Ambani</strong>. Not from today, they have been sailing in this boat of friendship since the time both of them were kids (childhood Chaddy buddies is what we can literally call them). In fact, when Isha was engaged, Kiara expressed her emotions on social media by calling Isha her oldest friend. </span>\r\n<h2><b>Kiara Advani Real name</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The actress was originally born <strong>Alia Advani,</strong> a name which she later changed before making her debut in Bollywood. The reason behind this is quite apparent. Her contemporary talented actress, the Mahesh Bhatt daughter, Alia Bhatt also possesses the same. If reports are to be believed, this has been the advice of Bollywood’s sultan, Salman Khan; hence, to avoid any clash, Alia changed her name to Kiara. </span>\r\n<h2><b>Kiara Advani Age and physique </b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kiara is one of the actresses who has reached the peak of success at such a young age. <strong>Born in the year 1992</strong>, she is only <strong>28 years old</strong> as of now. Though she has a cute face, her body is hot and bold enough to turn on the Indian audience. With a <strong>height of about 5’5”</strong>, she has the approximate figure measurements of <strong>34-26-34</strong>. With a perfect figure and the prettiest face bearing a pair of mag