weight: 400;\"> - Satyajit Ray</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><b><i>Ray</i></b><b> first look</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Back in March 2021, the first look of this series surfaced at an event hosted by Netflix - What’s Next India and the entire Hindi web series list (series that would be streaming on the platform this year) was released. On the same day, Gajraj Rao, one of the lead actors of this project, also excitedly shared a still from the sets on his social media account.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6404 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-6.jpg\" alt=\"Netflix series Ray (1) first look trailer\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CL85wE5JfwX/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><b><i>Ray</i></b><b> teaser release</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After so much excitement and anticipation, Netflix finally released its upcoming series, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">’s teaser on the 28th of May. Soon after the launch, it was showered with love by the fans and admirers</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Along with glimpses of the cast, the teaser also unveiled the names of each of the four stories. Any data regarding the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> trailer release hasn’t been announced yet. However, it is also expected to be launched soon.</span>\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/4W5ocAI2O3k\r\n<h2><b>Netflix series </b><b><i>Ray</i></b><b> release date</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We still have to hold back our thrill and enthusiasm regarding seeing this expected masterpiece for some more time. The release date of the series has been announced in the teaser itself. It will be streaming from the 25th of June on Netflix.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Ray </i></b><b>series cast and crew</b></h2>\r\n<h3><b>Lead actors and actresses:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some of the most talented and familiar but underrated faces of Bollywood have been cast in this series. Being an anthology, it is divided into four short stories and each of the segments stars different actors. </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first story is reportedly </span><strong><i>Hungama Hai Kyon Barpa </i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">stars </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gangs of Wasseypur</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> actor <strong>Manoj Bajpai</strong> as well as the known face from films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Badhai Ho</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shubh Mangal Zaada Savdhan</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, Gajraj Rao. </span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The second segment, </span><strong><i>Forget Me Not</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> also stars underrated gems like <strong>Ali Fazal </strong>and<strong> Shweta Basu Prasad</strong>.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The third story, </span><strong><i>Bahupriya</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has actors<strong> Bidita Bag</strong> and <strong>Kay Kay Menon</strong> in the lead roles.</span></li>\r\n <li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> In the last story,</span><strong><i> Spotlight</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sanam Teri Kasam</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> fame <strong>Harshvardhan Kapoor</strong> and the cute </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Angrezi medium</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> actress Radhika Madan will be witnessed as the lead pair.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-6409 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-4-300x240.jpg\" alt=\"Netflix series Ray (1)\" width=\"445\" height=\"356\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-6408 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-3-300x240.jpg\" alt=\"Netflix series Ray (1)\" width=\"474\" height=\"379\" />\r\n<h3><b>Supporting actors: </b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from the main actors, in various supporting pivotal roles,<strong> Chandan Roy Sanyal, Rajesh Sharma, Anindita Bose, Loveleen Mishra, Shruti Menon, Manoj Pahwa, Kharaj Mukherjee, Raghubir Yadav</strong> are also going to steal our glances.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Direction, production and more:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Being divided into four separate stories, each of the parts have been directed by different directors. Two of the segments </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Forget Me Not</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bahupriya </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">has been directed by the well-known Bengali director, Srijit Mukherjee, known for his regional works like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">22she Srabon</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dwitiyo Purush</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hungama Hai Kyon Barpa</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has been made by another reputed filmmaker Abhishek Chaubey known for films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Udta Punjab</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sonchiriya.</span></i>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Spotlight </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">has been directed by the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mard ko Dard Nahi Hota</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> director Vasan Bala.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6405 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-7.jpg\" alt=\"Srijit Mukherjee: Netflix series Ray (1) director\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (Srijit Mukherjee - director of </span><strong><i>Forget me Not</i> and <i>Bahupriya</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">)</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6410 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-5.jpg\" alt=\"Abhishek Chauby\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Abhishek Chauby - director of </span><strong><i>Hungama Hai Kyon Barpa</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">)</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6407 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Netflix-series-Ray-2.jpg\" alt=\"Vasan Bala\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Vasan Bala- director of <strong><i>Sotlight</i></strong></span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">)</span></i></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The writing part has been done by Siraj Ahmed and Niren Bhatt. Sayantan Mukherjee has carried out the show running and the entire management responsibility of </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. And the production of this show has been accomplished by Viacom 18 Studio’s Tipping point.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Ray </i></b><b>series genre and plot</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray is one of the recreations of Satyajit Ray’s iconic writings and its transition into Indian cinema. Each of the stories reportedly has different themes like love, lust, desire, betrayal, truth which has been narrated in interesting and unique ways. Much is not revealed about the genre of the plot, though Gajraj Rao, in his post claimed that the genres of each segment vastly vary from one another.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The stories have strong elements like satire, suspense, emotions and one of them is most probably a psychological thriller. The common string between each of these tales is the narration by the pen of Satyajit Ray. Not much is revealed about storylines. Also, regarding, Ray series budget, there is no such information as of now.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Conclusion</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nd</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> May 2021 was the 100</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> birth anniversary of the pride of India, Satyajit Ray. On this occasion of this auspicious year, nationwide filmmakers have joined hands once again to bring his written pieces on the big screen in order to pay honour to his contributions. Satyajit Ray has indeed been an inspiration and unforgettable hero of Indian cinema’s history. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be it writing or filmmaking, his works always created magic. And hence there are high expectations of the audience from this series which will be premiering on Netflix. They are expecting to feel and be a part of his writings themselves via </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ray.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> We really wish that this Manoj Bajpayee starrer keeps up to the expectations, yet again makes the name of Satyajit Ray a sensation all over the country and becomes one of the best Hindi web series of all time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With this, we end our content for today. Hope you had a happy reading. See you in the next article. </span>','Ray | Upcoming Netflix series Based on Satyajit Ray’s Short Stories','','publish','open','open','','ray-upcoming-netflix-series-based-on-satyajit-rays-short-stories','','','2021-07-15 08:29:02','2021-07-15 02:59:02','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=6403',0,'post','',0),(6414,12,'2021-06-05 08:48:06','2021-06-05 03:18:06','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/16-best-bollywood-movies-of-2020-on-netflix-and-amazon-prime/\">favourite OTT platforms</a> of today’s youths, Netflix is all set to gift us with another of its original<strong> feel-good films, </strong></span><strong><i>Skater Girl</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>.</strong> Expected to be a unique cinematic creation, lots of excitement has already grown surrounding this much-awaited film’s release.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6415 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Skater-Girl-Netflix-Upcoming-movie-–-Cast-Release-Date-Plot-and-Other-Updates-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> trailer</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On <strong>15th May 2021</strong>, Netflix India<strong> launched the trailer</strong> of this upcoming project which delivered a sense of satisfaction and enjoyment within 2 minutes and 38 seconds. I am pretty sure that if you are an admirer of inspirational stories with uplifting plots, then this film will be a perfect watch for you.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the trailer, the eye-captivating cinematography, direction, and realistic acting that we witnessed now make us anticipate that </span><b><i>Skater Girl</i></b><b> IMDB</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> deserves to be at least above 8. Of course, not to miss out on the trailer’s last part, where the English lyrics of the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skater Girl</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> song, ‘I am not afraid, I am free’ just touch our hearts.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=k5Fn99wmFCQ&amp;feature=emb_logo\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl </i></b><b>release date in India</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Besides giving us glimpses from the film, the trailer also unveiled its release date. Start counting days and add Skater Girl to your watch list as well as this film will be streaming on Netflix from the 11th of June, 2021.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> film language</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is an Indian American film and includes a cast and crew of both countries. So, speaking of Skater Girl’s language, you will get to hear both Hindi and English in the movie. The use of these two languages doesn\'t seem to be a force fit at all; in fact, the story calls for it.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl </i></b><b>cast and crew</b></h2>\r\n<h3><b>Cast</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Rachel Sanchita Gupta</strong>, a graduate from the University of Delhi, will be delivering her debut performance in the lead role of a village girl named Prerna in this film.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Regarding her acting career, she has already stepped into the world of cinema in 2020 and has acted in a short film named </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aghatit.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> She is also an experienced theatre artist.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apart from this, the<strong> British actress Amrit Maghera</strong>, a known face from the critically acclaimed film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Angry Indian Goddesses</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, will be seen in a pivotal role.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Other talented actors and actresses like <strong>Waheeda Rehman, Anurag Arora, Shafin Patel, Shraddha Gaikwad, Swati Das, Ankit Rao, Jonathan Readwin</strong> will be sent in major supporting roles.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6416 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Skater-Girl-Netflix-Upcoming-movie-–-Cast-Release-Date-Plot-and-Other-Updates-2.jpg\" alt=\"Amrit Maghra (British model), Skater Girl’s supporting cast\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Amrit Maghera (British model), Skater Girl’s supporting cast)</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6417 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Skater-Girl-Netflix-Upcoming-movie-–-Cast-Release-Date-Plot-and-Other-Updates-3.jpg\" alt=\"Waheeda Rehman, Skater Girl’s supporting cast\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Waheeda Rehman, Skater Girl’s supporting cast)</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6418 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Skater-Girl-Netflix-Upcoming-movie-–-Cast-Release-Date-Plot-and-Other-Updates-4.jpg\" alt=\"Anurag Arora, Skater Girl’s supporting cast\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Anurag Arora, Skater Girl’s supporting cast)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><b>Crew</b></h2>\r\n<h3>Director:</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Well-known woman filmmaker, <strong>Manjari Makijany</strong> has directed Skater Girl.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6419 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Skater-Girl-Netflix-Upcoming-movie-–-Cast-Release-Date-Plot-and-Other-Updates-5.jpg\" alt=\"Manjira Makijany, Skater Girl’s director\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(Manjira Makijany, Skater Girl’s director)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Screenplay</strong> </span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The responsibility of the <strong>screenplay</strong> has been carried out by the director along with <strong>Vinati Makijany</strong>. This writer duo has also produced the movie, via the production houses, Mac Productions and Skatepark films.</span>\r\n<h3><strong>The background score </strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The background score has been given by the iconic musician sibling duo Salim Merchant-Sulaiman Merchant known for giving melodious BGMs in films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cocktail, I Hate Luv Storys, Bang Bang!,</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Kites and so on.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> genre</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After all, be a fan or a professional sportsman, sports have always motivated us and acted as a driving force for many. And hence we Indians have always appreciated well-made movies of the sports genre. From </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chak de India</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bhaag Milkha Bhaag</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MS Dhoni the Untold Story, </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bollywood has gifted us with some of the most admirable sports dramas of all time.</span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skater girl</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is another such <strong>Indian American sports film</strong> that is expected to touch our hearts and inspire us to chase our dreams for sure. Elements of emotions and drama are going to act as a catalyst in this movie.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> meaning, plot/storyline</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It was set in the backdrop of rural Rajasthan. This film is going to narrate the journey of a teenage girl named Prerna. Revolves around how from being just a simple ordinary girl she struggles and achieves her dreams.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skater girl revolves around the sport of skateboarding. Prerna belongs to a poor family and of course, her parents are supposedly not in a position to think anything extraordinary about her.  However, fate has other plans as she discovers and learns skateboarding. It was introduced in her village by a British Indian woman. There is no looking back in Prerna’s life after that.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Soon skateboarding becomes her love, passion and she realizes the heights of freedom and happiness this sport can take her. The film will trace her inspirational journey as a skateboarder or a skater girl. Who comes from a small village and faces various obstacles in the path of achieving success.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indeed, a film that is going to break the stereotype regarding the inability of girls to take part in various sports activities.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater Girl</i></b><b> shoots and budget</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The shooting of the movie <strong>started in 2019.</strong> Most scenes are from<strong> Rajasthan’s Khempur village</strong> near <strong>Udaipur.</strong> Also, a skate part was made there. It was the most important film set for the film. In the early part of 2020, Skater Girl’s shoot was wrapped up. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skater Girl\'s</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong> budget</strong> is around<strong> $10 million.</strong></span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Skater girl </i></b><b>clothes – </b><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> outfits – </b><b><i>Skater girl</i></b><b> style and makeup</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giving a rural, poverty-stricken touch to an actor portraying such a character is not easy. Hats off to the costume designers and make-up artists of the lead actress <strong>Rachel Sanchita Gupta. </strong>And many other supporting casts and make them look so realistic. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even without any such glamorous costumes or makeup, the simple and elegant rural touch has developed a beauty in itself – at least this much is very evident from the trailer.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are all the updates we have about Skater Girl as of now. Be ready on 11</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> June to set out on a roller coaster ride with the little girl with big dreams, Prerna.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finally, this is the content for today. Hope you liked it. See you in the next article.</span>','Skater Girl Netflix Upcoming movie | Cast, Release Date, Plot and Other Updates','','publish','open','open','','skater-girl-netflix-upcoming-movie','','\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/16-best-bollywood-movies-of-2020-on-netflix-and-amazon-prime/','2021-06-10 21:50:21','2021-06-10 16:20:21','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=6414',0,'post','',0),(6421,12,'2021-06-05 09:31:49','2021-06-05 04:01:49','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All nationwide anticipations regarding the versatile roles portrayed by the veteran actor Amitabh Bachchan as well as hot, charming actor Imran Khan and others in this new <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-ullu-web-series-online-that-you-must-watch/\">Bollywood thriller</a> film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chehre</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> went in vain. Just a few days before its release, due to the second wave of COVID-19, the release of this much-awaited movie got postponed.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>Chehre </i></b><b>first look</b></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5860 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/April-movire-released-this-week-2021-6.jpg\" alt=\"Chehere, April movire released this week 2021 (6)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the very beginning of this year, on 23rd January, the first look of this poster surfaced. </span>\r\n<h2><b><i>T</i>railer and teaser release</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, Chehre’s teaser was released on 11th of March 2021. Then, after a wait of a few days, the trailer of this upcoming Bollywood movie was released on the 18th March. It got an amazing response from the fans and admirers.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The makers of the film were quite overwhelmed by this fact. And it was it is quite evident that </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chehre </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">would not only be a decent watch but also be one of the best-made movies of the year, thus becoming a hit at the box office. At the end of the trailer, we also got to hear a part of its beautiful melodious title track.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4WTPps4zM8&amp;t=1s\r\n<h2><b><i>R</i>elease Date</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firstly, it was on last year 17th July 2020, when </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chehere </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">was set to be released in cinema halls. However, during that time when the COVID-19 pandemic was creating havoc all over the country, the release of the film got postponed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Later, this hindi film was all announced to have a grand theatrical release on the 9th April, 2021. However, due to a surprising surge in the number of COVID-19 cases, the release got delayed once again. New release dates haven’t been announced soon.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6423 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-that-you-need-to-know-about-Big-Bs-upcoming-film-Chehre-1.jpg\" alt=\"All that you need to know about Big B’s upcoming film Chehre (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><b><i>Chehre </i></b><b>OTT release – will the film be released on our mobile screens?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Keeping in view the ongoing pandemic, many high budget films of 2020-21 got released on various OTT platforms like Amazon Prime. So, if </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chehere</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> gets released on any OTT, it will naturally get a good response once again and will create buzz among the audience.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, its producer Anand Pandit is highly sceptical regarding releasing this film on our cell phone screens. As per him, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chehere</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a cinematic gem which has all the elements of drama suspense combined along with the beauty of international locations. Hence, it deserves to be released on big screens. He is very optimistic about the fact that situations will get normal soon and then the movie will be hitting in our nearest theatres.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span><b><i>Chehre Star</i></b><b> cast</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> After the success of Hindi movies like Pink and Badla, actor Amitabh Bacchan has once again played a lawyer named Veer Sahay in the movie. And this is one of the very reasons for excitement among fans and admirers.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Imraan Hashmi will be seen in the character of an accused who gets trapped in an unusual game played on him by lawyers. Famous soap opera face, Krystle D’souza known for her small screen works like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Naagin</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uddan</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will be seen as Veer Sahay’s daughter. Eminent actors like Dhritiman Chatterjee Annu Kapoor have also portrayed pivotal roles. Jalebi actress Rhea Chakraborty is also seen in the trailer.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6424 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-that-you-need-to-know-about-Big-Bs-upcoming-film-Chehre-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chehre cast\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>Plot</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Much is not revealed about the story of the film. However, whatever is evident from the trailer is something like this: A young man gets summoned into an unknown Bangalore where he meets a group of lawyers. The man introduces himself as Karan Oberoi, chief of an advertising agency. He was spending some good time with the lawyer squad. However, truths started unfolding and he found himself trapped in a bizarre game of mock trial where he was accused of being a criminal and now it is his task to prove his innocence.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, the question is who is at fault? Are the lawyers really insane and traps innocent people just to pass time? or does Karan have a dark hidden past phone. The possibility of the second option is more as in the flashbacks he was seen with Veer Sahay’s daughter, most probably as her love interest. So, to find answers to these unanswered questions we will have to wait for the film to get released.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Crew of </b><b><i>Chehre</i></b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The direction of this Hindi film has been done by a very reputed Bollywood director named Rumi Jafry. The production part has been carried out by well-known production houses like Anand Pundit Motion Pictures as well as the Saraswati Entertainment Private Limited.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A story by Ranjit Kapoor, the screenplay and dialogues have been carried out under the responsibility of the Ranjit-Rumi duo. Binod Pradhan did magical cinematography while the music has been given by musical sensations like Visal-Shekhar and Gaurav Dasgupta. Bodhaditya Banerjee was involved in the editing tasks.</span>\r\n<p style=\"text