n who will be seen as a period drama hero after a long time. Om Raut and Prabash took their Instagram account to announce this movie. It was 17 August 2020 when they said an announcement will be revealed on 18 August 2020 at 7:11 am.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CD_jbZhJMv7/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n\r\nThe next day the team of <strong>\'Adipuruah\'</strong> revealed their first poster of this movie at 7:11 am.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CEAzhvYpVQB/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><strong>Adipurush Release date declared:</strong></h2>\r\nAfter the announcement of this high-budget movie, everyone is too excited to know about this movie. The entire star cast, the story, and everything. As the makers did not reveal at one time. They announced it step by step.\r\n\r\nFirst, they revealed only the two important characters in this movie are Ram and Ravana. Ram will be played by the south superstar Prabash and Ravana will be played by<strong> Saif Ali khan</strong>.\r\n\r\nThe release date was announced by the makers for this movie much later than their first announcement. They post a picture with the release date theatrical all over India or outside will be 11 August 2022. This movie will be released in 5 languages.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CHwRbospF-U/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong><u>The story of Adipurush:</u></strong></h2>\r\nThe makers did not reveal any details about the story but as the movie is titled \'Adipurush\' so it is basically based on Lord Rama. There is so much speculation about this story but some sources said it will be about the battle of Ram and Ravana. For this movie, the VFX team came from outside of India. The team who did VFX in the \'Avatar\' movie will do the VFX for this movie. So it will be exciting to see this movie in the theatre.\r\n<h2><strong><u>The star cast of \'Adipurush:</u></strong></h2>\r\nAs the maker did not reveal much about the movie when they first announced it. At first, the director only said about Prabhas will be playing the role of Rama and for Ravana\'s character, they selected Saif Ali khan. But the others important characters did not reveal at that time.\r\n\r\nFor the role of Sita, many big names come like Deepika Padukone, Anushka Sharma but they finally selected <strong>Kriti Sanon</strong> for the role of goddess Sita. And Sunny Singh for the role of Laxman in this movie. These two characters were revealed this year on March 11. When the full team of Adipurush, director Om Raut and actor Prabhas welcome their new cast Kriti Sanon and Sunny Singh as maa Sita and Laxman in their Adipurush family. Kriti Sanon and Sunny Singh also took their Instagram and Twitter handle for this.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CMTPQrsJz_P/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><strong><u>The shooting Start:</u></strong></h2>\r\nThough the announcement was made in 2020 the shooting started early this year. From the social media account of the director Om Raut, he shared a picture of \'Muhurat puja\' on the set of \'Adipurush\'.\r\n\r\nThe shooting begins in the month of February. As the entire set was created in Mumbai for this movie. And there is news that the set was burnt and the shooting was stopped for a few days but after some time the team started their shooting. But now the increasing case of Covid in Maharashtra the maker decided to shoot the movie in Hyderabad but the lockdown was also imposed on the state and the shooting of this high-budget movie is on pause.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CKyGc-bJ2Ok/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><strong><u>The Director and producer of Adipurush:</u></strong></h2>\r\nFirstly, The director of this period drama movie is Om Raut who directed the blockbuster movie TANHAJI. Om Raut already proved himself as a great director and everyone liked and appreciated his work. Now let\'s see what he will do with this mythological period drama movie \"Adipurush\". For this, we have to wait till the release of this movie next year.\r\n\r\nThe producer of this big-budget movie is T- Series. As the budget of this movie is 400 cr. But the producer Bushan Kumar is really confident about this movie.','Adipurush | Upcoming Bollywood Movie of Prabhas | 2022','','publish','open','open','','adipurush-upcoming-bollywood-movie-of-prabhas','','','2021-07-15 08:29:16','2021-07-15 02:59:16','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=6428',0,'post','',0),(6431,12,'2021-06-09 22:14:26','2021-06-09 16:44:26','The year <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2020 had indeed been a season of <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/celebrities-who-got-married-in-pandemic-year-2020/\">marriage in Bollywood</a> as many of our favourite celebrity couples including Neha Kakkar-Rohanpreet Singh, Natasha-Hardik Pandya, Shaheir Sheikh-Ruchika Kapoor tied the knot. Now in 2021, the </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Badlapur</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> actress Yami Gautam has carried forward the trend by sharing the surprising news of her marriage on social media. Read more to know about Yami Gautam husband.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Who did Yami Gautam marry?</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This gorgeous actress Yami Gautam has stepped into a blissful married life with someone from the film industry only. Her man of dreams, now husband, is the award-winning filmmaker, Aditya Dhar. Dhar made into headlines two years back in 2019 after his outstanding and flawless direction in the Vicky Kaushal starrer film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uri the surgical strike </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">was praised by the critics as well as the audience. After the grand success of the movie, he won some of the prestigious ‘best director’ awards.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uri, </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">he worked as a dialogue writer f