 of October this year</span>\r\n<h2><b>Jou</b><b>rney in OTTs - Gajraj Rao web series</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - </span><b>Gajraj Rao TV shows</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the year 2015, Gajraj Rao made his web series debut with the admirable and high rated Amazon prime original series </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bang Baaja Baaraat</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2016, he appeared in an episodic role in TVF\'s creation </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Day with. </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">He played the lead role of professor RD Sharma in the episode named </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A day with RD Sharma</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. He then worked in three mode TVF original series including </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">F.A.T.H.E.R.S</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tech conversations with dad</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TVF Tripling 2</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/rsII-IIPFSQ\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>(Rao in Tech Conversations with dad)</strong></em></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/9rOlvj6f6Yk\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>(Rao in A day with RD Sharma)</strong></em></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Last year, he appeared in the Netflix series </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaba Masaba</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as himself. In 2021, he also was a part of another comedy series </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PariW ar</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which is available on Disney+Hotstar.</span>\r\n<h2><b>Other works</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The actor has also impressed us with his short-time screen appearances in advertisements like those of Fevicol and Google India.</span>\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/m2yGopP6r4Y\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/qbdA72ubLbs\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>(Gajraj Rao ads)</strong></em></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> He has also appeared in some short Youtube videos Girliyappa, TVF, etc. </span>\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/b8UoC23jhPc\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>(FAJRAJ rao Girlyappa video)</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><b>Recognition for performances – Gajraj Rao awards and achievements</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rao proved his acting brilliance whenever he appeared on screen. It is indeed a matter of pride that an actor like him has been recognized quite a few times for his works in Hindi films. For his negative role in the 2016’s critically acclaimed film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Talvar, </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">he has received two prestigious nominations. For </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Badhai ho</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> where the actor stole the limelight along with Ayushman Khurana, he received two awards. In 2021, he grabbed the best supporting actor film fare award for delivering an amazing performance in the romcom </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shubh Mangal Zyada Saavdhan</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6575 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bollywood-actor-Gajraj-Rao-biography-6.jpg\" alt=\"Gajraj Rao\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b>Gajraj Rao net worth</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ads and films are his main sources of income. Definitely, Rao’s earnings have increased in the past few years. If sources are to be believed, he has a net worth of $125 million as of 2021.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, these are