movie will release in the expected time or not. With the current vaccination drive going on, we really hope that nationwide conditions improve and </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">777 Charlie</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is released on big screens.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6460 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Upcoming-Pan-India-film-777-Charlie-5.jpg\" alt=\"Upcoming Pan India film 777 Charlie \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b><i>777 Charlie </i></b><b>plot– the film’s out-of-the-box storyline</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The movie basically revolves around two lead characters, one of a human being played by Rakshit Shetty and another of a dog named Charlie. Shetty’s character Dharma is a lonely young man with no energetic attitude towards life, until one day he meets this white-coloured pup Charlie who changes his outlook towards life.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6458 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Upcoming-Pan-India-film-777-Charlie-3.jpg\" alt=\"with puppy\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><b><i>777 Charlie</i></b><b> movie genre</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With all the elements of adventure, drama, comedy, and a bit of romance 777 Charlie is expected to be a feel-good movie packed with entertainment.   </span>\r\n<h2><b>In which languages is this film made? – </b><b><i>777 Charlie</i></b><b> languages</b></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Originally this film was made in the Kannada language. But later it has been dubbed and is decided to be released in four other languages including Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam as well as Hindi. This pan India release will surely help this masterpiece in reaching out to more Indian audiences.</span>\r\n<h2><b><i>777 Charlie</i></b><b> cast and crew</b></h2>\r\n<h3><b>Cast:</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First