 400;\"> </span>\r\n<h2><b>9. Salim Diwan adopts kids</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6513 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/8.jpg\" alt=\"Salim Diwan \" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Meanwhile, Another Bollywood actor who has walked in the path of Sonu Sood by driving inspiration from him is none other than Salim Diwan known for films like </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bollywood Diaries.</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> He has adopted 20 children and has guaranteed to bear the responsibility of their education. As per him, he is trying to contribute his best towards the society during this time of need.</span>\r\n<h2><b>10. Alia Bhatt’s preparations for a new project</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6514 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/9.jpg\" alt=\"Alia Bhatt\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here comes our next Bollywood hot topic, trending on top 25 bollywood news. One of the successful actresses the Bollywood industry has right now is the Mahesh Bhatt daughter Alia Bhatt. After a number of noteworthy blockbuster films </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dear zindagi, Gully boy</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Razi</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> she started preparing for her upcoming movie </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Darlings</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Reportedly it is a black comedy exploring a mother-daughter relationship, Apart from Bhatt, Shefali Shah has also been casted in a major role.</span>\r\n<h2><b>11. PC’s new mission</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1510 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/7-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Priyanka Chopra Jonas\" width=\"717\" height=\"466\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our Kashi Bai from </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bajirao Mastani</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, aka Priyanka Chopra is now a global icon. As she is attaining the greatest heights of her dreams,<strong> she has now been selected as the new spokeswoman for Victoria’s Secret, an international lingerie brand.</strong></span>\r\n<h2><b><i>12. Toofan</i></b><b>’s new release date</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4503 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/upcoming-movie-2021-the-tv-freak-5.jpg\" alt=\"toofan\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The new, highly anticipated sports film </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Toofan, </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">by now, has witnessed multiple delays in having a release because of this ongoing pandemic. Last week, it got a new release date. It is all set to release on 16th July,2021.</span>\r\n<h2><b>13. An Indian film’s achievement</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6515 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/10.jpg\" alt=\"Uljhan the knot\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An Indian film, </span><strong><i>Uljhan / The Knot</i></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> which has also marked Ashish Pant’s beginning of a journey as a director has made an entry to Shanghai International Film Festival and has an Asia premiere there. The film stars Saloni Batra and Vikas Kumar in lead roles.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span>\r\n<h2><b><i>14. Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam</i></b><b>’s 22</b><b>nd</b><b> anniversary</b></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6498 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11.jpg\" alt=\"salman khan\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This evergreen film starring Salman Khan, Ajay