ing field.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6647 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/750x600-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Pankaj tripathi, kriti sanon - Mimi\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h2><strong>The release date of the New upcoming movie \'Mimi\':</strong></h2>\r\nThis movie was announced much earlier though but the makers could not release it because of the pandemic situation. As we know that for Covid 19 the theatre was closed from the last year 2020.\r\n\r\nFinally, the makers of this movie decided to release this movie on the web platform. For the last few months, there has been some news of this movie on various online platforms but on 10th July the lead actress of this movie declared the date on which they release their movie through her social media account like Twitter and Instagram.\r\n\r\nThe movie will be streaming from 30th July 2021 this month on Netflix and jio cinema. From that day onwards, audiences will be able to see this movie on these two OTT platforms(Netflix, Amazon prime, <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/top-10-ullu-web-series-online-that-you-must-watch/\">ullu web series online</a>).  On 6th July the team and the actress shared the first poster of this movie with a caption like Nothing like what you expected.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CRDfSTBrXEf/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CRIo2ZwrW_o/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><strong>The movie first announcement:</strong></h2>\r\nThis movie \'Mimi\' was announced much earlier on 30\'th Aug in the year 2019 where the actress Kriti Sanon first shared the movie poster for the first time. This movie\' a story is based on the famous Marathi movie \'Mala Aai Vhhaychy\'.\r\n\r\nThe director of the movie is Lakman Utekar. In this movie both the actress and the director collaborated for the second time after their first one \'lukka chuppi\' was a massive blockbuster at the box office. After announcing this movie Kriti said about her role and her excitement for this movie in her many interactions with the media and audience. She put on an extra 15 kg weight for this role. So, she was working too hard for shaping this role.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/B1xmV4kgd9N/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n<h2><strong>The star cast in the movie:</strong></h2>\r\nAs the movie is a usual story from other commercial Bollywood movies. This is a women-centric movie where you can see a journey of a young girl to become a surrogate mother. Though the concept is different from the story of the other.\r\n\r\nFor this role, the director and maker chose Kriti Sanon as a lead role who becomes a surrogate mother. As for this role the actress has to put extra weight so many stars did not agree to do this kind of role. But Kriti Sanon being a commercial heroine ready to face this challenge in her work field. With her, you can also see versatile actor<a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards/\"> Pankaj Tripathi</a>, Supriya Pathak, and Marathi actress Sai Tamhankar.\r\n<h2><strong>The shooting of this movie:</strong></h2>\r\nAs the movie \'Mimi\' was announced earlier in the year 2019. During the middle of November 2019, the stars cast of this movie along with the director and production members started their shoot for the first part of the movie.\r\n\r\nAccording to the sources the movie set was in the Churu, Rajasthan. Though there is some news that came from that time that the director and production did not take any permission for the shooting at the local location. Most of the part of this movie was shooting in Rajasthan.\r\n\r\nThough the maximum part of this movie was completed before the first lockdown imposed in our country all over. But few parts remain left so, they completed those parts in Mumbai 2021.\r\n<h2><strong>The Director and producer of the movie \'Mimi\':</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Lakman Utekar</strong> is the director of this movie. After lukka chuppi, he decided to make this movie under the banner of Maddox production house. His earlier movie was also the same production house and the producer, Dinesh Vijan. So, we can say that after lukka chuppi rocks at the box office. They decided to surprise the audience with something different from a rom-com romantic commercial movie.\r\n\r\nDinesh Vijan is a great producer, in 2018 and 2019 he gave the audience some great movies that will be remembered for a long time. Now, it\'s a time for their collaboration in this movie and how the audience will react for that we have to wait for 30th July.\r\n<h2><strong>The trailer released:</strong></h2>\r\nFor the last year due to the pandemic, our life has changed in many ways. Everyone is now connected through social media. Like that most of the big announcements from the Bollywood industry are now done by their social media account or some virtual interview rather than a big trailer launch or poster launch event.\r\n\r\nTo go with this concept on 7th July the actress shared the released date of her new upcoming movie on 13th July 2021 through her Twitter and Instagram account. Now, we have to wait to see how the production house will release the trailer. Either they choose virtual release or they conducted any public event to release their movie trailer will be seen by 13th of this month.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CRGCmWgnFv1/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/CRJLL7KrBNn/?utm_medium=copy_link\r\n\r\nThough there is lot of buzz in media about this movie, and the star casts. For that audience will wait for 30th July and after they will decide is it a blockbuster movie or a not so good movie.','Mimi: Bollywood Upcoming Movie | Trailer | Insta | Tweets','','publish','open','open','','mimi-bollywood-upcoming-movie-trailer-insta-tweets','','','2021-07-16 17:58:04','2021-07-16 12:28:04','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=6646',0,'post','',0),(6654,13,'