ward</strong> for Best Dailouge (2019) for the movie Stree.\r\n<h2>Pankaj Tripathi Web Series and Tv Career- :</h2>\r\nPankaj Tripathi is not only a renowned face for the Bollywood film industry but also a renowned face in Television and web series.\r\n<ol>\r\n <li><strong>Sacred Games (2018)</strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Pankaj Tripathi Mirzapur (2018)</strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Criminal Justice </strong><strong>(2019)</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nHe also did some television shows like Sarojini -Ek Nayi Pehal from 2015-2016 and powder in 2010. In an interview with Telegraph, he said,” I haven’t made a six-pack or eight-pack, Neither am I spotted at parties at the airport or outside gyms. I don’t know where people spot me and shower their love on me.”\r\n<h2>Facts about Pankaj Tripathi:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Pankaj Tripathi helped his father in farming until he was in standard 11. He used to go with his father in the fields and do farming. He said in an interview,\r\n<em>“I remember my father took a loan of Rs 5000 from a cooperative bank to buy a small five-horsepower tubewell pump. A certain part of it, which cost around Rs 500, was easily detachable. Thieves could steal it easily. To save that Rs 500, my father and I would have dinner early and reach the farm by 8 pm. Every day we would sleep near the tubewell to save Rs. 500.”</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-994\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/PANKAJ-TRIPATHI-farming.jpg\" alt=\"TRIPATHI - a farmer\" width=\"803\" height=\"452\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>His life was changed because of Manoj Bajpayee. Another side of the river near his village in Gopalganj, there is the village of Manoj Bajpayee i.e. Champaran. When \"Satya\" movie was released people in the village used to talk a lot about Manoj Bajpayee. Then Pankaj felt that if a normal person near my village can be an actor then I can do it too.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-995 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/satya.jpg\" alt=\"Satya movie - Pankaj Tripathi \" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h2>Some more interesting facts:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>His father wanted him to be a <strong>doctor</strong>. So he set off to Patna after High School.</li>\r\n <li>He was sent to <strong>Jail once for seven days</strong>. During college times, he was part of Akhil Bharatiya Vidyarthi Parishad. In 1993, He was jailed because he raised his voice against the state government. The ruling party was Lalu Prasad Yadav.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-996\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/pankaj-tripathi-o.jpg\" alt=\"tripathi - intresting facts \" width=\"834\" height=\"469\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Laxam Narayan Rai</strong>’s play, <strong>Andha Kuan</strong> came as a turning point in his life. In Interviews, he said, “My life completely changed. The actress, Pranita Jaiswal, had a powerful monologue. Listening to that, I started to cry. That was when I realized what a powerful medium drama is. I had never experienced such a thing before in my life.”</li>\r\n <li>Do you believe he was Rejected by the National School of Drama twice? In the third attempt, he made it to the National School of Drama. And then he graduated in 2004.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-997 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/PANKAJ-TRIPATHI-NSD.jpg\" alt=\"PANKAJ TRIPATHI NSD\" width=\"479\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>He was Married to Mridula who was then a professor in the school.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-999 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/PANKAJ-TRIPATHI-marriage-1.jpg\" alt=\"Family and marriage wife\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>He came to Mumbai and after eight years he gave an audition for the Gangs of Wasseypur in 2012 in which he has to play the character of Sultan. And This audition went on for eight long hours and he got selected for Sultan\'s Roll.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1000 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/PANKAJ-TRIPATHI-.jpg\" alt=\"Auditions\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h3>Some More Interesting Topics, you don\'t want to miss!!</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Interesting Facts about Shushant Singh Rajput.</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/aparshakti-khurana/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Know about Aparshakti Khurana</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/aparshakti-khurana/\">Why Black Widow Movie is Super Awaiting?</a></li>\r\n <li><a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020/\">Why did Gulabo Sitabo was made?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Pankaj Tripathi -  Biography, Movies, Web Series, TV and Awards','','publish','open','open','','pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards','','https://www.thetvfreak.com/sushant-singh-rajput-facts-journey-to-bollywood/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/aparshakti-khurana/\nhttps://www.thetvfreak.com/gulabo-sitabo-movie-2020/','2021-01-24 17:08:48','2021-01-24 11:38:48','',0,'https://www.thetvfreak.com/?p=982',0,'post','',0),(1017,11,'2020-06-23 12:33:15','2020-06-23 07:03:15','<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1021 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/VICKY-KAUSHAL.jpg\" alt=\"VICKY KAUSHAL\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h2>Biography of Vicky Kaushal:</h2>\r\n<strong>Vicky Kaushal</strong> is a Hindi movie artist. He is known for his acting talent that made him a versatile artist. Vicky Kaushal has made his career from zero to one. He is now an inspiration for new actors and actresses who are still working in Tv and Stages.\r\n\r\n<strong>Full Name</strong>:  Vicky Kaushal\r\n<strong>Date of birth</strong>:  16-05-1988\r\n<strong>Hometown</strong>:  Mumbai\r\n<strong>Height</strong>:  6’3\r\n<strong>Skin Colour</strong>:  Dark Brown\r\n<strong>Weight</strong>:  80kg\r\n<h2>Early Life of  Vicky Kaushal:</h2>\r\nAs usual, like other struggling actors Vicky Kaushal is also from a middle-class family. He is from the Brahmin family. His father\'s name is Shyam Kaushal and he used to do stunts for living in movies and other platforms.\r\n\r\nHis mother\'s name is Veena Kaushal and she was a nonworking woman or the manager of the family. Vicky was born in an area of North Mumbai on 16 May 1988 in Malad. When he in school he liked to study. Apart from this he also liked to watch movies and enjoying Cricket.\r\n\r\nVicky also has a younger brother, Sunny who is a Hindi Film actor and started his career with the movie Sunshine Music Tours and Travels. Sunny played the character of Sunburn.\r\n\r\nHe is also the assistant director and worked as an assistant director in Gunday (2014) in which he worked with Ranveer Singh, Arjun Kapoor, Priyanka Chopra. Sunny also acted in Goal (2018) movie with Akshay Kumar and played the role of Himmat Singh (Sardar).\r\n\r\nHe was not totally in acting from starting. But he used to do some stage competition for fun. In College days he showed up as a performer. Once he went for a visit to a company and he felt exhausted after seeing the employees of the company.\r\n\r\nHe asked himself if he can do that 10 AM to 6 PM sitting on the same chair doing the same job and the answer was \"No\". After this incident, Vicky Kaushal started to go with his father.\r\n<h2>Qualification of Mr Kaushal:</h2>\r\nVicky Kaushal did the schooling for S.C.D.B. High School in Mumbai. While schooling he loved to do dramas and other stage competitions like dance etc. After this, Vicky Kaushal moved for his higher education. Because he loved studying so he decided to study engineering.\r\n\r\nHe pursued Engineering and took B.Tech (EC). Then after that company visit, he changed his path towards actings. For acting, he selected Kishore Namit Kapoor Acting Institute. This College is in Mumbai.\r\n<h2>Filmy Career and Movies of  Vicky Kaushal:</h2>\r\n<h3>Vicky Kaushal (2012-2015):</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1031 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/VICKY-KAUSHAL-gangs-of-wasseypur.jpg\" alt=\"VICKY KAUSHAL gangs of wasseypur\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\nHis starting in this field was quite interesting. The 1st Film he did was of the famous director Mr Anurag Kashyap. He didn\'t get any role for acting but his work was more than that. He works under Mr Kashyap in \'The Gangs of Wasseypur\' as an assistant in 2012\'.\r\n\r\nFrom this movie, he learned a lot about acting as well as the plotting of the script. At this time he was also that part of a theatre in which famous actor Nasruddin was working.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1030 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/vicky-kaushal-chicken-khurana.jpg\" alt=\"vicky kaushal chicken khurana\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\nNow it\'s the time when he got his break. It was 2012 and he was offered a side role in the film \'LuvShuv Tey Chicken Khurana. The part was small but effective and he played that very well. After this movie in 2013, he was also offered a short film named \"Greek Out\". Greek Out was directed by Vasan Bala.\r\n<h3>2015:</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1029 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/vicky-kaushal-massan.jpg\" alt=\"vicky kaushal massan\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\nNow in 2015, Vicky Kaushal\'s golden time came, and he did a film that had broken the Bollywood barriers. He played the lead actor role Neeraj Ghayawan\'s Masan (2015). In Masan Movie, he played the role of Deepak Kumar. He gave an outstanding performance and also worked with famous faces like <a href=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/pankaj-tripathi-biography-movies-tv-and-awards/\">Pankaj Tripathi</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richa_Chadda\" rel=\"nofollow\">Richa Chadda</a>. Then He received lots of good reviews from Indian Critics. He also won many awards.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1028 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/vicky-kaushal-massan2.jpg\" alt=\"vicky kaushal massan\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h2>Watch Trailer:</h2>\r\n[embedyt] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SKJfBo3xMW0[/embedyt]\r\n\r\nHe appeared in many Hindi movies like \'Bombay Velvet\' where he pursued the role of Basil. He also acted in one more movie in 2015 was \'Zubaan\' where his character name was Dilsher.\r\n<h3>Vicky Kaushal (2016-2020):</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1027 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/raman-raghav.jpg\" alt=\"raman raghav\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\nThen he did the movie Raman Raghav 2.0 (2016). In Raman Raghav the psychological thriller based film, he worked with Nawazuddin Siddiqui.\r\n<h3>2017:</h3>\r\nHe appeared in a TV Series Tata Sky Acting Adda.\r\n<h3>2018:</h3>\r\n<h4>Raazi(2018)</h4>\r\nAfter this Vicky Kaushal, he did \"Love Per Square Foot\". It\'s a romantic comedy film and released on Netflix. Then he was offered the Movie Raazi 2018. Raazi is a movie made on different content in which he is a Pakistani officer and his wife is an Indian Spy. The movie is beyond thinking, how he died. There is so much love, emotion, respect, and patriotism in Raazi. He was opposite to Alia Bhatt who was in the lead role.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1024 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lust-stories2.jpg\" alt=\"lust stories\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\nAfter Raazi, Vicky Kaushal did Lust Stories, an Indian Hindi-language anthology film. This movie basically consists of four short stories. Indeed you will find yourself like you are watching Love Actually.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1025 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lust-stories.jpg\" alt=\"lust stories2\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<h4>Sanju(2018)</h4>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1023 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/SANJU.jpg\" alt=\"sanju\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\nIn 2018 He did one bigger movie that is Sanju (2018), based on the biography of Sanjay Dutt. Rajkumar Hirani’s film boosts his career and he was able to show his acting in another character.\r\n\r\nIt is a biography film of Mr. Sanjay Dutta. Vicky played the role of Kamlesh Kanhaiyalal Kapasi who is the best friend of Sanjay Dutta.\r\n\r\nHe is in a supporting role but almost equal to Ranbir Kapoor. He gave his best here and achieved the best-supporting actor award.\r\n<h4><span class=\"wo fr-21\" data-num=\"21\">Uri</span>: The Surgical Strike:</h4>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1022 size-full\" src=\"https://www.thetvfreak.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Uri-The-Surgical-Strike.jpg\" alt=\"Uri The Surgical Strike\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Then After Manmarziyaan, he did his life\'s best movie i.e. Uri: The Surgical Strike. This year he played Major Vihan Singh Shergill in the movie \'URI The Surgical Strike ’was his best performance to date. This was his first action movie. With this movie, he was in the heart of the Indian audience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Although this movie was a blockbuster and break every record. Basically, this movie is based on a mission that was done by the Indian army after the URI attack. You will lose yourself in this movie and compare it with the best Hollywood action movie.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There is so much energy and action and the major part was shot in Serbia.</